(9320, 'ielts-toefl-duolingo-what-are-the-differences', 3, 0, 'IELTS, TOEFL, Duolingo: What are the differences?', '<p>If you\'re planning to study at an English-speaking university as a non-native speaker, chances are you\'ll have to sit for an English language proficiency test. Lately, there have been various options available including IELTS, TOEFL, and Duolingo. While all serve the same goal in mind, namely to evaluate English language skill level in an academic setting, there are key differences to know.&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Curious about the differences and the special features of each English proficiency test? Continue reading to find out!<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>IELTS</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7f/IELTS_logo.svg/1280px-IELTS_logo.svg.png\" alt=\"Berkas:IELTS logo.svg - Wikipedia bahasa Indonesia, ensiklopedia bebas\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>For non-native English speakers, the International English Language Test (IELTS) is one of the most widely accepted and well-recognized English language proficiency tests. IELTS tests are divided into two categories: <strong>IELTS Academic </strong>and<strong> IELTS General Training</strong>. The IELTS Academic test is for those applying for higher education or professional registration in an English-speaking environment, while the IELTS General Training test is for those who are going for secondary education, work experience, or training programs in English-speaking countries.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>The IELTS test includes four different sections:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Listening (30-40 minutes)</li><li>Reading (60 minutes)</li><li>Writing (60 minutes)&nbsp;</li><li>Speaking (11-14 minutes)</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Questions found in the IELTS test consist of a mix of multiple choice, diagram labelling, matching, short answer, and sentence completion. The IELTS test takes <strong>about 2 hours and 45 minutes</strong> to complete, with the first three sections always completed immediately after each other and with no break. The Speaking test, on the other hand, is commonly done on a separate date.&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h4>IELTS Grading System</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>The IELTS is graded on a <strong>9-point scale including half scores</strong>, with four subsection scores averaging out to give an overall band score. IELTS scores are accepted as proof of English language proficiency by almost all universities in the United Kingdom and Australia, more than 3,400 institutions in the United States, and the majority of academic institutions in Europe, Ireland, and Canada.&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>In response to COVID-19, <strong>IELTS Indicator</strong> was created, which is an <strong>online test</strong> that allows test takers to take the test in the comfort and safety of their own homes. This <strong>2 hours 45 minutes</strong> test is similar to the IELTS test taken in a test center in terms of questions and difficulty. It spans all four sections:&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Listening (30 minutes) - 40 questions</li><li>Reading (60 minutes) - 40 questions</li><li>Writing (60 minutes) - 2 tasks</li><li>Speaking (11 to 14 minutes) - 3 tasks over Video Call</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>The IELTS Indicator test must be completed in one session for the Listening, Reading, and Writing sections, with the Speaking test conducted via video call with a fully qualified and trained examiner a few days before or after the other sections. Within <strong>seven days</strong> of taking the test, test takers will receive an indicative score for each section as well as an overall band score. The IELTS Indicator is not a substitute for the in-person IELTS test as it only provides an <strong>indicative score</strong>. Therefore, not all organisations accept it, and once testing resumes, university or education providers may require the in-person IELTS test to be taken.&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Find out which organisations accept IELTS Indicator at <a href=\"https://www.ieltsindicator.com/who-accepts-ielts-indicator-scores/\">https://www.ieltsindicator.com/who-accepts-ielts-indicator-scores/</a>&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>TOEFL</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9c/TOEFL_Logo.svg/1200px-TOEFL_Logo.svg.png\" alt=\"File:TOEFL Logo.svg - Wikimedia Commons\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The TOEFL is available in two formats: an <strong>internet-based test (iBT)</strong> and a <strong>paper-based test (PBT)</strong>, both of which are widely used for university admissions, employment, and immigration. Over 11,000 universities in over 150 countries recognize the test, which is graded on a scale of 120 points. The format of the test may vary based on the location of the test takers.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>The TOEFL iBT has four components:&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Listening Comprehension (54-72 minutes)</li><li>Structure and Written Expression (41-57 minutes)</li><li>Reading Comprehension (17 minutes)</li><li>Written expression (50 minutes)</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Between the listening and speaking sections, there is a 10-minute break, making the test <strong>about 3 hours and 30 minutes</strong> long. Each section is graded on a scale of <strong>0 to 30</strong>, with <strong>120 </strong>as the maximum score. It usually takes <strong>six to ten days</strong> for the TOEFL iBT scores to be released. Both the iBT and PBT versions of the TOEFL test have the same four sections, but the scoring scales and timing are different.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Duolingo English Test</h3>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<p>The Duolingo English Test is an <strong>online test</strong> that can be taken from anywhere and at any given time. As it does not require an appointment, this test has become more widely accepted, particularly during the COVID-19 pandemic. More than 2,000 universities already use this test for admissions, with 70% of them based in the United States. Even the most prestigious educational institutions have accepted it!<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Just like the TOEFL and IELTS, it tests all four language skills:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Reading</li><li>Writing</li><li>Listening</li><li>Speaking</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h4>Duolingo Test Format</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Duolingo offers a variety of questions in formats that may be unfamiliar to you. The tests includes:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Listening to spoken words and selecting the real ones</li><li>Reviewing written words and selecting the real ones</li><li>Completing missing letters from a text</li><li>Describing an image in writing or aloud</li><li>Recording yourself saying a written sentence</li><li>Verbally answering a spoken question</li><li>Responding in writing to a written question (writing samples have a maximum of 500 words but are usually much shorter)</li><li>Typing out a statement that you hear</li><li>Video interview - speak for 1-3 minutes on a chosen topic<ul><li>Ungraded but goes along with the test results&nbsp;</li></ul></li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Within 60 minutes, the Duolingo English Test is divided into three parts:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Quick setup (5 minutes)</li><li>Adaptive test (45 minutes) - Evaluates Listening, Reading, Speaking, and Writing</li><li>Video interview (10 minutes)&nbsp;</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>The test is adaptive in nature, which means that if a test taker answers correctly, the next question will be more difficult than the previous one. Conversely, if a wrong response is provided, the next question will be easier. As the Duolingo English Test blends all questions into a single exam, you can get a writing question following a reading question, for instance. The test lasts <strong>between 45 and 60 minutes</strong>, and is graded on a <strong>scale of 160 points, with 5-points increment</strong>. The test score will usually be released in<strong> 48 hours</strong>.&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>To check which institutions accept the Duolingo English Test, head over to <a href=\"https://englishtest.duolingo.com/institutions\">https://englishtest.duolingo.com/institutions</a>.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>The Comparison </h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Score comparison charts for all three - IELTS, TOEFL iBT, and Duolingo</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td><strong>Proficiency Level</strong></td><td><strong>IELTS</strong><strong>	</strong></td><td><strong>TOEFL iBT</strong></td><td><strong>Duolingo</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Expert</td><td>9</td><td>118 - 120</td><td>155 - 160</td></tr><tr><td>Very good</td><td>8 - 8.5</td><td>110 - 117</td><td>135 - 150</td></tr><tr><td>Good</td><td>7 - 7.5</td><td>94 - 109</td><td>115 - 130</td></tr><tr><td>Competent</td><td>6 - 6.5</td><td>60 - 93</td><td>95 - 110</td></tr><tr><td>Modest</td><td>5 - 5.5</td><td>35 - 59</td><td>75 - 90</td></tr><tr><td>Limited&nbsp;</td><td>4.5</td><td>32 - 34</td><td>65 - 70</td></tr><tr><td>Extremely limited&nbsp;</td><td>4</td><td>0 - 31</td><td>55 - 60</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Key differences</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td><br></td><td><strong>Where do I take the test?</strong></td><td><strong>Test duration&nbsp;</strong></td><td><strong>Test Structure</strong></td><td><strong>How long would it take to get the results?</strong></td><td><strong>Validity of scores</strong></td></tr><tr><td><strong>IELTS Academic&nbsp;</strong></td><td>Test center</td><td>2 hours and 45 minutes</td><td>Four sections: Listening, Reading, Speaking, Writing&nbsp;</td><td>Computer-delivered IELTS: 3-5 days<br>Paper-based: 13 days</td><td>2 years</td></tr><tr><td><strong>IELTS Indicator&nbsp;</strong></td><td>Online&nbsp;</td><td>2 hours 45 minutes&nbsp;</td><td>Four sections: Listening, Reading, Speaking, Writing&nbsp;</td><td>7 days</td><td>Only provides indicative score for each section along with an overall indicative score</td></tr><tr><td><strong>TOEFL iBT</strong></td><td>Online</td><td>about 3 hours and 30 minutes</td><td>Four sections: Listening, Reading, Speaking, Writing&nbsp;<br></td><td>6 to 10 days&nbsp;</td><td>2 years</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Duolingo&nbsp;</strong></td><td>Online</td><td>Between 45 minutes and 1 hour</td><td>Three parts: Quick Set up, Adaptive Test, Video Interview&nbsp;</td><td>48 hours&nbsp;</td><td>2 years&nbsp;</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Now you\'ve known the differences between these three English language proficiency tests! Regardless of your choice, make sure to practice consistently and double-check with your university requirements. Best of luck!<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>So which one are you planning to take? IELTS, TOEFL, or Duolingo? Aiming the best result in your English language proficiency test? Let ALL-in help you!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\"><strong>Admission Mentoring</strong></a><strong>.</strong></li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries on <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\"><strong>Career Exploration.</strong></a></li><li>Improve grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\"><strong>Academic Tutoring.</strong></a></li><li>Upscale your personal brand on <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/writing-skills/\"><strong>Writing Skills</strong></a><strong> </strong>improvement program.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!</p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>', 'closeup-person-filling-out-questionary-form-scaled.jpg', 'IELTS, TOEFL, Duolingo: What are the differences?', 'publish', '', 'IELTS TOEFL Duolingo', 'IELTS, TOEFL, Duolingo? If you\'e facing a dilemma to choose which english test is the best for you, check out this article to find out the differences!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2021-11-23 17:00:00', '2021-11-04 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(9369, 'student-project-solar-powered-automatic-dog-feeder', 5, 0, 'Student Project - Solar-powered Automatic Dog Feeder', '<p>The old-school approach of learning facts and memorizing them is no longer sufficient for preparing students who wants to seek more. In developing both essential and 21st-century skills (such as problem-solving, project management, research), starting a student project can be a good place to start. In the spirit of student projects, check out Abian\'s Solar-powered Automatic Dog Feeder project!</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Abian Susatyo - Grade 11</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Project Type:</strong> Seed Project (0-3 months)</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Backstory of the Student Project</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Abian Susatyo, who has traveled around the world, has noticed the same problem in every place: numerous stray dogs roaming the streets. Stray dogs, like any other living animals, needed just as much food and drink to survive.&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>The Initiatives</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Being an animal lover himself, Abian thought of a solution to make it more convenient for people who feed stray dogs. As a gesture of his gratitude, he came up with <strong>Solar-powered Automatic Dog Feeder</strong> for ALL-in\'s student project. Abian, who aspires to be a mechanical engineer, collaborated with his mentor Nicholas to create an automatic dog feeder that dispenses food at an adjustable period of time.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>The Project</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>In the span of three months, Abian has been working on his automatic dog feeder in his school\'s workshop. What started with watching YouTube videos on DIY dog feeders has progressed into the prototyping stage. Abian has gone through his third prototype.&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>For the past few weeks, Abian has been researching the circuit aspect of his automatic dog feeder. Currently, he is creating some adjustments on the dispenser component of his automatic dog feeder prototype to make it compatible with the Arduino circuit.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is what Abian\'s project looks like right now:&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image is-resized\"><img src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/DiNO_zUzmVryfWc64vckEPbX8V3QJCdpJ8IWFPA_T45pFd9jUN49TGFqZZxTL49uPV-TIoTdQg-0bKTKi5jHsenJNzm9q_8iHE41m1B2dU_8YSPYRglYWioJ72BKDvG8szCSUJiq\" alt=\"Student Project \" width=\"569\" height=\"758\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image is-resized\"><img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/hYy_3XTvsXCl498S0DTNlQRuUiIrJ-YQ_qWwIazhfCDsAsk4of4sRrq6nL_CcZNFLs5wt42L82yQCnR6AFpJ7zXrL5X-xssNwwVvlVqmNEQPadybWPei67ls_dHNpexJYSlpdQ92\" alt=\"Student Project\" width=\"545\" height=\"969\"/><figcaption>The circuit component of Abian\'s Solar-powered Automatic Dog Feeder </figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Future plan for Abian\'s Student Project</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Even after Abian has only finished his first prototype, he has expressed optimism with his plan on starting a crowdfunding initiative for his project. In addition, he plans to tackle any stray animal problems by working together with animal welfare organizations.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Abian\'s Solar-powered Automatic Dog Feeder project is the winner of ALL-IN BEST PROJECT OF THE MONTH for December 2021 in the category of Seed Project!<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Now let\'s hear what our judge, Eviana Misty (ALL-in mentor), says about Abian\'s creative project:</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>“The vision and mission are already clear and specific. There is a clear problem that he really wants to try to solve: how to feed stray dogs effectively. Al</em>t<em>hough the project has just been started, it is not just a mere idea.</em> It<em> has started to be developed & there has been progress on the prototype even in just a short time!”</em></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Got a creative idea in mind? Make it into a reality with ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\"><strong>Admission Mentoring</strong></a><strong>.</strong></li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries on <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\"><strong>Career Exploration.</strong></a></li><li>Improve grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\"><strong>Academic Tutoring.</strong></a></li><li>Upscale your personal brand on <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/writing-skills/\"><strong>Writing Skills</strong></a><strong> </strong>improvement program.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'header_dog-feeder.jpg', 'Student Project - Solar-powered Automatic Dog Feeder', 'publish', '', 'Student Project', 'Being an animal lover with aspirations of being a mechanical engineer? Discover ALL-in\'s student project of Solar-powered Automatic Dog Feeder!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2021-12-09 17:00:00', '2021-12-09 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(9372, 'student-project-filtro', 5, 0, 'Student Project - Filtro', '<p>Creating a student project may require maximum concentration and thoughtful decisions. However, it could be a powerful teaching method for students. Student projects allow students to receive hands-on learning while building life skills such as critical thinking, self-confidence, and in-depth understanding. Speaking of student projects, let\'s discover Rayden\'s project of building Filtro!</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Ignacio Rayden Yap&nbsp; - Grade 9</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Project Type:</strong> Unicorn ( 9-month ++)<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Backstory of Rayden\'s Student Project</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The start of the pandemic was faced with several problems. Sanitary kits were limited, masks were in short supply and irresponsible actors went on a hoarding streak. As a result, many couldn\'t afford sanitary supplies, particularly those who lost their jobs.&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>The Initiatives</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Rayden saw this problem, and decided to tackle any COVID-19-related problems by building his own company, Filtro. He has a vision on reducing the environmental damage of single-use masks while promoting a safer and healthier Indonesia.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>The Product</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Filtro is a business that produces and sells artisanal masks to Indonesian youth who are conscious of sourcing, production, and environmental sustainability. Their sustainably-produced masks are not only WHO-verified safe, but also use eco-friendly materials sourced from local stores.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>With a mission to give back to the community, 70% of Filtro\'s monthly goes to funding sanitary kits to donate. Filtro\'s sanitary kits include items like hand-painted masks,&nbsp; toothpaste, soap, and a bottle of hand sanitizer. Across Jakarta, Filtro has donated 50 to 100 sanitary kits monthly. Not just that, Filtro has also collaborated with other organizations for said donations, increasing them to 200 sanitary kits. In addition, Filtro has been working on the creation of sanitary stations to orphanages like Komunitas Anak Ceria.</p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Progress of the Student Project</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>For the past year, Filtro has faced impressive feats. Within the first 6 months, Filtro has partnered up with several charity organizations. Not just that, they have also collaborated with international schools, academic competitions, and donation initiatives. For instance, Filtro acted as a supplier for National High Jakarta School\'s \'English Week\' annual event. In addition, Filtro was invited as a collaborator in EduSummit 2021. It is a Model UN conference that involved the collaboration with other organizations as media partners.&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Although Filtro is now on a hiatus on their social media page, their sales have not been affected.&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Future plan</strong> </h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Rayden is currently focusing on UN Sustainable Development Goals 3 and 6. These goals are directly correlated to Filtro\'s prime mission, COVID-19-impact relief. After coming in second in the Ascend Now Bullpen, Rayden is fueling Filtro\'s growth phase through the seed fund. He is now developing new merchandise and implementing new donation initiatives.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Rayden is planning on hosting webinars and seminars on educating the pressing conditions the community in Jakarta is facing. He thought of giving solutions to these issues while establishing Filtro\'s presence.</p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Rayden\'s student project of Filtro is the winner of ALL-IN BEST PROJECT OF THE MONTH for December 2021 in the category of Unicorn Project!</p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Now let\'s hear what our judge, Eviana Misty (ALL-in mentor), says about Rayden\'s influential project:</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>“The project relates to the problem we are currently facing, Covid-19 and global warming. It already runs and proven to give a great impact with the ability to donate 200 sanitary kits from the sales. This project also has received many achievements including winning a competition and getting $1,000 investment. Way to go!”</em></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Inspired on doing something similar to Rayden? Let ALL-in hear your ideas!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\"><strong>Admission Mentoring</strong></a><strong>.</strong></li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries on <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\"><strong>Career Exploration.</strong></a></li><li>Improve grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\"><strong>Academic Tutoring.</strong></a></li><li>Upscale your personal brand on <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/writing-skills/\"><strong>Writing Skills</strong></a><strong> </strong>improvement program.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'header_FILTRO.jpg', 'Student Project - Filtro', 'publish', '', 'Student Project', 'The pandemic comes with many problems: unemployment, mask shortage, limited supplies. Discover how Rayden tackle these problems through his student project!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2021-12-07 17:00:00', '2021-12-05 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(9376, 'student-project-pedal-power-bicycle-generator', 5, 0, 'Student Project - Pedal Power Bicycle Generator', '<p>Nowadays, students\' learning processes have transitioned more into the \"Do It Yourself (DIY)\" mode. In doing so, students typically create their own student project. This allows them to bring theoretical concepts into life, which generates their creativity while also boosting their understanding of a topic. Let\'s take a look at Mellvin\'s project, Pedal Power Bicycle Generator, while we\'re on the subject of student projects!</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Mellvin Chia - Grade 12&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Project Type:</strong> Series A (3- 6 month)<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Backstory</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Mellvin realized that many activities are restricted due to the on-going pandemic. Keeping that in mind, more and more time will be spent in the comforts of his home. With limited body movement, Mellvin figured that regular exercise is needed in order to maintain his body in a good shape.&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>What\'s more, the COVID-19 pandemic has accelerated digitalization. As a result of this, energy will be needed more than ever. Instead of using non-renewable energy, Mellvin thought of generating and storing clean energy, especially in light of global warming concerns.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>The Initiatives of the Student Project</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>In response to these problems, he created a project called <strong>Pedal Power Bicycle Generator</strong>. This bicycle project, with a vision of solving global warming as well as keeping a healthy body, converts the energy used from pedalling the bike into electrical energy. He can later use the energy to power anything from tablets, handphones, to a WiFi router. For instance, if a blackout occurs, Mellvin can still continue his online classes using the energy generated from his project.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Mellvin\'s project, with the support of his ALL-in mentor Nicholas, solved three problems all at once: keeping people fit during the pandemic, providing clean and renewable energy, and powering gadgets in case there\'s no electricity, all while addressing global warming concerns.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>The Product</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>On building his electricity-generating bicycle that has been on-going for about 6 months, Mellvin uses a 2V alternator, 500W pure sine wave inverter, and a 12V battery.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is what Mellvin\'s project looks like:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image is-resized\"><img src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/lTBObRbWp2cAbZ6LGpAyxBBbevgBj2qPxcMUKFqHIDC7kUc44vo0ybBW4YQL4TrFM9oo9VMfeVOLF8DiMZRVi13JbScYsyKD1OoBJtCa2qbXBlE-tdH4gH1VrVfETiedk2lvGpI6\" alt=\"Student project\" width=\"461\" height=\"615\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Future plans for Mellvin\'s Student Project</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Mellvin realized that his project, while functional, has a size that is a little too long. He plans to redesign it to create a more compact and eco-friendly electricity-generating bicycle. Not just that, he also plans to do further research on determining the number of calories burnt on the monitor.&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Mellvin\'s project of Pedal Power Bicycle Generator is the winner of ALL-IN BEST PROJECT OF THE MONTH for December 2021 in the category of Series A Project!<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Now let\'s hear what our judge, Eviana Misty (ALL-in mentor), says about Mellvin\'s innovative project:</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>“The project of making bicycles that can be converted to electrical energy actually works, and the evidence is clear. It also has the potential for further development and Mellvin already knows what is lacking & needs to be improved for this project.”</em></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Thinking of creating your own innovative student project? Let\'s do it with ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\"><strong>Admission Mentoring</strong></a><strong>.</strong></li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries on <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\"><strong>Career Exploration.</strong></a></li><li>Improve grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\"><strong>Academic Tutoring.</strong></a></li><li>Upscale your personal brand on <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/writing-skills/\"><strong>Writing Skills</strong></a><strong> </strong>improvement program.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'header_BICYCLE.jpg', 'Student Project - Pedal Power Bicycle Generator', 'publish', '', 'Student Project', 'Providing clean energy, staying fit on the pandemic, and powering gadgets: How can all this be related? Check out Mellvin\'s student project!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2021-12-08 17:00:00', '2021-12-04 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(9382, 'student-project-portable-solar-power-bank', 5, 0, 'Student Project - Portable Solar Power Bank', '<p>Wondering how to boost your innovation skills? Starting a student project can be a great way to start. From developing a growth mindset, integrating literacy and creativity, to managing obstacles, the benefits of starting a student project is limitless. While on the subject of student projects, let\'s learn more about PS2\'s project of Portable Solar Power Bank!</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>PS2:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Rayandra Bharata Harun - Grade 11</li><li>Dylan Lim - Grade 12</li><li>Brandon Widodo - Grade 10</li><li>Darren Adrian - Grade 12</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Project Type:</strong> Series B (6-9 months)<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Backstory of the Student Project</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Indonesia, being a tropical country, receives sunlight abundantly. In spite of this, this nation has not use solar energy as its primary energy source. Brandon, Darren, Dylan, and Rayandra saw this problem, and turned this into an opportunity. They planned on creating a project of transforming solar energy into a good help in our daily lives.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>The Initiatives</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Right at the start of the project, they already have two goals in mind: developing a useful solar-powered product and spreading awareness about renewable energy.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>The Product</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>In developing a useful product, they focused on their daily lives. Brandon, Darren, Dylan, and Rayandra landed on a <strong>portable solar power bank</strong> after several brainstorming sessions.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>After months of development, their first prototype was successfully developed. Although it\'s a simple product, it\'s useful as it uses the sun to power the portable charger.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Towards fulfilling their second goal of spreading awareness, PS2 members make use of Instagram. Their Instagram page (@powerourfuture) serves two purposes: a precursor to their main product and spreading awareness regarding renewable energy, its implications, and its potential in Indonesia.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is what PS2\'s product looks like:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image is-resized\"><img src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/JbWjs1WA3aLUS4g8a2uj3O9m3Per05LgHgiN-YIGRUASPc98pRGGYZESw1R19SlUAp75ijpXTlKxNqQAkh_VWsMlCPAgn8L-bYpDMtc8ebeqhHVXes32qrz5SICZAKk-L1qDtC6r\" alt=\"Student Project\" width=\"434\" height=\"334\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/I-7h-XRIAqJ8No3nd0wgdG4b-LeFeNplLLTutEWFsEu9OvvQvKagZEtVA1-9Z6QMg9yOlXU2msYcvA9N4_d-u9fGXR7iT9UktmbGUIRiRXPpe6-rXICGI5BvINm7RJm-gQVkWeNu\" alt=\"Student Project \"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Progress of PS2\'s student project</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>In the span of nine months, PS2 members have already developed a working prototype along with their ALL-in mentor, Nicholas. Additionally, they have launched an Instagram page and displayed their product at ALL-in\'s student club fair.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Future plans</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>In the future, the four teenagers are looking to raise funding through Bantoo.id. This will complement their future plan, which includes launching the device, and scaling up production of their portable solar power bank.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>PS2\'s project of Portable Solar Power Bank is the winner of ALL-IN BEST PROJECT OF THE MONTH for December 2021 in the category of Series B Project!<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Now let\'s hear what our judge, Eviana Misty (ALL-in mentor), says about PS2\'s outstanding project:</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>“We love that the vision & mission is clear, and the prototype already exists and there is a plan to scale up for PS2\'s future.”</em></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dreaming of turning your student project into a reality? ALL-in is here for you!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\"><strong>Admission Mentoring</strong></a><strong>.</strong></li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries on <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\"><strong>Career Exploration.</strong></a></li><li>Improve grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\"><strong>Academic Tutoring.</strong></a></li><li>Upscale your personal brand on <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/writing-skills/\"><strong>Writing Skills</strong></a><strong> </strong>improvement program.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'image.png', 'Student Project - Portable Solar Power Bank', 'publish', 'Student Project - Portable Solar Power Bank', 'Student Project', 'Indonesia\'s abundance of sunlight has not been fully put to work. PS2 members realized this, and turned into a student project. Find out more about it here!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2021-12-09 17:00:00', '2021-12-17 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(9454, 'study-abroad-why-you-should-do-it', 1, 0, 'Study Abroad - Why you should do it!', '<p>If you\'re planning to study far away from home, one question that might pop in your mind is ‘Why study abroad?\' Simply put, it\'s a life-changing experience. Studying abroad gives you the power to make meaningful connections, expand your perspective, and give you a competitive edge on the job market! When the world is your classroom, you\'ll gain an education like no other.&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Still not convinced enough? Here are four reasons to choose when your mind is thinking of ‘Why study abroad?\'&nbsp;<br> </p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Gain an edge from employers</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>In an increasingly globalised world, employers seek graduates with international experience and education. According to a survey conducted by The Erasmus Student Network, 92% of employers look for transferable skills that are typically gained from study abroad experience. These include:<br></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Communication skills - On your time abroad, you\'ll learn to overcome language barriers in a range of different scenarios. Furthermore, you can develop several key skills like negotiating and public speaking.</li><li>Independence - Studying abroad demonstrates the strength to take a leap of faith, adapting to unexpected situations, and solving problems on your own.&nbsp;</li><li>Project management - From navigating around a different environment to adapting to foreign transportation and different currencies, studying abroad builds your ability to plan ahead, manage your time, and think logically.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Enhance and build connections&nbsp;</h3>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<p>Why study abroad? For most students, this is their only opportunity to build invaluable relationships with people from all over the world. From exchanging stories to collaborating on a project with people from different cultures, you could broaden your connections while also building lifelong friendships. Some connections can even turn into career opportunities, including internships, job offers, and business partners!</p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Develop a global mindset and perspective</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>In today\'s connected world, an open-minded approach and cultural awareness is essential. From your classmates to your professors, learning in an international environment challenges your assumptions and introduces you to different ways of thinking about the world. Gaining a variety of perspectives helps you view things in an entirely new way.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Additionally, you can get introduced to various educational settings. Adapting to various teaching styles can help you adjust to different management styles, making you more versatile in the workplace. Several teaching styles you may find abroad include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Authority Style</li><li>Facilitator Style</li><li>Delegator Style</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Bonus reason of \'Why Study Abroad?\': Challenge yourself</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>There is nothing quite like being on your own in a foreign country. You may feel overwhelmed, but the challenges you overcome will help you grow into a more mature person. Remember that challenge = growth, which is probably the best one-word answer to the question ‘why study abroad?\'.&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Quickly adapting to your new environment will hone your self-reliance and resilience. From small and mundane tasks, like going to the doctor or setting up an international bank, to major issues, like learning how to negotiate with a professor or adapt to a different culture\'s management styles, your daily life can shape you into a more capable person.</p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Whichever country you visit, you\'ll never return as the same person. All those experiences will impact you for years to come. So, what are you waiting for?&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Thinking of studying abroad? Let ALL-in help you!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximise your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\"><strong>Admission Mentoring</strong></a><strong>.</strong></li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries on <strong><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/programs/passion-project-mentoring/\">Career Exploration</a></strong><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\"><strong>.</strong></a></li><li>Improve grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\"><strong>Academic Tutoring.</strong></a></li><li>Upscale your personal brand on <strong><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/ib-extended-essay-coaching/\">Writing Skills</a> </strong>improvement program.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'pexels-artem-beliaikin-1079033-scaled.jpg', 'Study Abroad - Why you should do it!', 'publish', '', 'Why Study Abroad', 'One question that might pop in your mind is \'Why study abroad?\' From expanding your connections to gaining valuable experiences, find out the reasons here!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-01-18 17:00:00', '2021-12-26 17:00:00', '2023-01-17 17:00:00'),
(9463, 'benefits-of-studying-abroad', 1, 0, 'Benefits of studying abroad', '<p>Some have said it before: studying abroad is a life-changing experience. What sets studying abroad apart is that it\'s more than just receiving the degree you yearn for; it\'s a whole package that catalyzes your growth, as well as ticking off your travel bucket lists and gaining hands-on learning!&nbsp; Find out four benefits of studying abroad that you might consider.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Gain real-life experience to your classroom learning</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Several international universities incorporate in-the-field learning experiences to support and complement your classroom-only learning. Imagine studying art and then visiting the Louvre, or taking an Environment & Sustainability class and then going snowshoeing to monitor forests.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Getting hands-on opportunities not only allows you to get up close and personal with your major, but it also bridges the gap between theory and practice. This could help you to get your foot in the door before starting your dream job!</p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Explore the world</h3>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<p>Studying abroad is not a holiday. Exams, long-term assignments, and club events will fill your schedule. Nevertheless, any spare time you have can be spent exploring your new city; you\'ll learn everything about the local food, tradition, and history.&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Furthermore, when studying abroad, you are not limited to only one place; you can travel to nearby regions and countries. If you\'re studying in France, for instance, you can travel throughout Europe, including to Milan, London, and Barcelona. Who knows, your newfound friends might take you to places you\'ve never heard of!</p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>A step into adult life</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Studying abroad could be your first time living away from home. Without your parents and families to back you up, your time-management and decision-making skills will be tested. From cleaning the house to staying on top of academics while seeking part-time work and financial budgeting – you have to master all these things fast!<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Nevertheless, you\'ll grow in maturity in ways that you might not have at home. Ultimately, the benefits of studying abroad are not restricted to academic qualification or professional advancement; it\'s a life school as well.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Acquire new interests</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>If you\'re still wondering about the benefits of studying abroad, you should know that studying in a different country exposes you to different activities that you have never experienced or heard before. Don\'t be surprised if you suddenly took up water sports, hiking, skiing, or many other new sports. You could attend a sports game and discover it\'s your new favorite.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>The key is to get out of your comfort zone, expand your horizons and jump into new things. Remember that studying abroad shouldn\'t all be about academics!</p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<p>You may never have considered the thought of studying abroad. However, given the numerous benefits of studying abroad, it may be time to give the idea serious consideration!<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ready to study abroad? Let\'s pave your way into your dream university with ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\"><strong>Admission Mentoring</strong></a><strong>.</strong></li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries on <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\"><strong>Career Exploration.</strong></a></li><li>Improve grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\"><strong>Academic Tutoring.</strong></a></li><li>Upscale your personal brand on <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/writing-skills/\"><strong>Writing Skills</strong></a><strong> </strong>improvement program.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'free-time-students-bachelor-s-campus-life-rhythm-five-friendly-students-are-walking-scaled.jpg', 'Benefits of studying abroad', 'publish', '', 'Benefits of Studying Abroad', 'Studying abroad is not just living in a different environment or getting a degree. Find out the benefits of studying abroad in this article!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-01-16 17:00:00', '2021-12-16 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(9466, 'extended-essay-tips-from-an-ib-examiner', 3, 0, 'Extended Essay Tips (from an IB Examiner)', '<p>The Extended Essay (EE), a 4,000-word independent research paper, is a mandatory component of the IB Diploma Programme that gives IB students the chance to explore topics related to one of their DP subjects. Though it\'s known to keep many IB students awake at night, the EE can be broken down into a manageable, doable process.&nbsp;Read on to know Extended Essay tips and tricks that can help you excel from Paul Edison, an IB examiner and ALL-in mentor!<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Extended Essay Tips #1:&nbsp;</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Find the right supervisor&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>A great supervisor can not only help with finding the right topic but also cheer you on when your experiment fails for the sixth time. They will be able to point you in the right direction when you\'re stuck, and they can help evaluate whether or not your argument is critical.&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Your supervisor does not have to work at your school or even be your subject teacher. Sometimes, when given a choice between an overloaded supervisor with subject expertise and a smart, sympathetic supervisor with a manageable workload without the subject knowledge, the latter is the one who will be able to help you progress the most.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Extended Essay Tips #2:&nbsp;</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Do a feasibility study</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Doing a thorough feasibility study before committing to your RQ will save you so much time. Make sure there are enough secondary sources out there that would help deepen your analysis before you choose to analyze that exotic foreign film. Before you commit to building your own energy reactor, make sure your school lab has the proper tools and materials to support your endeavor. Prior on conducting a massive city-wide survey on the impact of social media on teenage girls\' slang, make sure there\'s actually a noticeable linguistic shift.&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Spending an hour or two on feasibility studies might save you dozens of hours of research dead-ends and heartbreaks.&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Extended Essay Tips #3:</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Synthesize, not summarize!&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Well, obviously you\'d have to do both. But so often I see students do nothing more than paraphrasing various experts from their secondary sources.&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>In other words, don\'t do this:&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Professor A said that Jane Austen only appears in public at night, and Professor B said that Jane Austen is afraid of garlic and silver crucifix. Therefore, Jane Austen only appears at night and is afraid of garlic and silver objects.&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Instead, do this:&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Professor A said that Jane Austen only appears in public at night, and Professor B said that Jane Austen is afraid of garlic and silver crucifix.&nbsp; This strongly suggests that Jane Austen is actually a vampire.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Extended Essay Tips #4:</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Keep track of your secondary sources</strong></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<p>Even as you read through journals and articles, it will be very tempting to just jot down quotes and leave the citation for a later date. Do NOT do this. Otherwise, you might find yourself having to find the source of a particularly useful quote in the pile of 40-50 different sources.&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Extended Essay Tips #5:</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Don\'t sleep on your Reflection!&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Seriously, so many students think that the reflection is just a formality. It isn\'t! If you look at the rubric, you\'ll see that Criterion E is entirely graded based on your three Reflection entries. These 500 words will determine almost 1/5th of your total score!&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Bonus Tip:&nbsp;</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Dive deep into the rubrics</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>For every subject, there\'s a specific way to interpret the rubric. Make sure you know what the examiners are looking for. Otherwise, you might think your essay is really strong while it\'s not actually meeting the criteria.</p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Questioning how to write your IB Extended Essay is a common thing. With its complexity, many IB students find themselves puzzled and sometimes overwhelmed as well. Nevertheless, the Extended Essay can be one of the most rewarding experiences with enough preparation, planning and supervision. You got this!</p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Facing some struggles with your Extended Essay? Fear not, ALL-in is here for you!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\"><strong>Admission Mentoring</strong></a><strong>.</strong></li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries on <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\"><strong>Career Exploration.</strong></a></li><li>Improve grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\"><strong>Academic Tutoring.</strong></a></li><li>Upscale your personal brand on <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/writing-skills/\"><strong>Writing Skills</strong></a><strong> </strong>improvement program.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'laptop-gaedffff95_1920.jpg', 'Extended Essay Tips (from an IB Examiner)', 'publish', '', 'Extended Essay Tips', 'Feeling overwhelmed and confused with your Extended Essay assignment? Needed some guidance? Check out some Extended Essay tips in this article!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-01-17 17:00:00', '2021-12-10 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00');
INSERT INTO `tb_blog` (`id`, `slug`, `cat_id`, `mt_id`, `blog_title`, `blog_description`, `blog_thumbnail`, `blog_thumbnail_alt`, `blog_status`, `seo_title`, `seo_keyword`, `seo_desc`, `lang`, `click_count`, `duration_read`, `is_highlight`, `publish_date`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(9484, 'mentees-spotlight-glocolis-competition', 5, 0, 'Mentees’ Spotlight - GloCoLis Competition', '<h4>Our Mentees who joined Global Competition for Life Sciences (GloCoLis):</h4>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Ariel - Ipeka Integrated Christian School</li><li>Qimiwa Njoto - Sekolah Ciputra</li><li>Amos Tanoyo - British School Jakarta</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Backstory</strong><br></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Three of our mentees, Ariel, Amos, and Qimiwa have a common interest in mind: life sciences. Back in November 2021, the trio decided to enter the Global Competition for Life Sciences (GloCoLiS) to fulfill their curiosity as well as their passion in the Life Sciences field.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>What is GlocoLis?</strong><br></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>GloCoLis is an international-level Invention competition in the field of Life Sciences, which was the product of collaboration between Indonesian Young Scientist Association (IYSA), Indonesia International Institute for Life Sciences (I3L), Institut Pertanian Bogor, and the Faculty of Dentistry at Brawijaya University. With more than 100 participants, the competition covers six categories in the Life Sciences field: Bioinformatics, Biomedicine, Biotechnology, Food Technology, Pharmacy, and Food Science and Nutrition. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>In short, GloCoLis is a research paper competition which focuses on the topic of Life Sciences. In this competition, participants will team up into a group of five or less.&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Competition Journey</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>At first, Ariel, Qimiwa, and Amos didn\'t know each other. All of them have different interests revolving around the field of Life Sciences. Nevertheless, they tried to work things out, and ended up on joining the Food Science division. Upon finding the specific topic to work on, the trio share out and brainstorm several ideas with their ALL-in mentor and supervisor, Sharon.&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>In the end, they settled on a topic: Association of Covid-19-induced Stress to Snacking Behavior in High School Students. According to Qimiwa, the topic they landed on appears&nbsp;to be a feasible one. This is because further research could possibly be done, especially during this time period.&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>With a little over a week to work on their research paper, the trio\'s time management was put to test, especially with a lot of different activities they never did before. This includes learning to search and curate research papers, extracting information from past studies, constructing a survey, and processing the collected data. In addition to this, they still had to keep up with schoolwork, with school assessments coming up, as well as dealing with burnouts.&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Although they were working in a limited amount of time, Ariel, Qimiwa, and Amos tried to encourage and rely on each other by splitting all the different works in the competition. Eventually, they all managed to finish the research paper by the due date.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Stages of the Competition</strong> </h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td>November 8, 2021</td><td>Submission of Report and Poster</td></tr><tr><td>November 24, 2021</td><td>Opening Ceremony</td></tr><tr><td>November 25-26, 2021</td><td>Online Judging Session through Zoom Meeting</td></tr><tr><td>November 28, 2021</td><td>Awarding Ceremony</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s give a round of applause to our mentees as they managed to win the <strong>Silver Medal</strong> and <strong>I3L Special Award</strong>! Congratulations Ariel, Qimiwa, and Amos!</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Mentees\' Comment</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p><em>‘Personally, I joined this competition because I was passionate about research and wanted to expand my skill set in this area.\'&nbsp;</em></p>\n\n\n\n<p>- Qimiwa, Sekolah Ciputra</p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>‘I think overall it taught me that I should manage my time better, think ahead of things, and communicate well with my team members. After all, we\'re all relying on each other to complete the work.\'</em></p>\n\n\n\n<p>&nbsp;- Ariel, Ipeka Integrated Christian School</p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Inspired by our mentees\' stellar achievement? Let ALL-in hear your passion and ideas!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximise your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\"><strong>Admission Mentoring</strong></a><strong>.</strong></li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries on <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\"><strong>Career Exploration.</strong></a></li><li>Improve grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\"><strong>Academic Tutoring.</strong></a></li><li>Upscale your personal brand on <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/writing-skills/\"><strong>Writing Skills</strong></a><strong> </strong>improvement program.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'WhatsApp-Image-2021-12-22-at-12.28.36-PM-1.jpeg', 'Mentees’ Spotlight - GloCoLis Competition', 'publish', '', 'Competition', 'Life Sciences was a common interest between our mentees. Check out their journey on joining the Global Competition for Life Sciences (GloCoLiS)!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2021-12-21 17:00:00', '2021-12-04 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(9547, '5-essay-writing-steps-for-beginner', 3, 0, '5 Essay Writing Steps for Beginner', '<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"https://thewritelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/photodune-11477592-essay-concept-notepad-s.jpg\" alt=\"Essay Writing Steps\"/><figcaption>Source: Toppr.com</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Writing Essay can be overwhelming as you need to cover your whole argument in one go. These essay writing steps can guide you through creating the best essay that suits your needs, whether it is an essay homework, dissertation, or even a thesis.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Some people can just sit in the corner of the room and start writing their essays quickly. On the contrary,&nbsp; a beginner might get confused about where to start and what to do. You can follow these steps to keep you organized and arranged as you write your essay.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Decide the types of essays.</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The first thing you can do is decide what kind of essay you are going to write. There are a lot of types which you can choose from:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>1. Narrative Essay</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>A narrative essay tells a story and imparts knowledge about a subject to the reader in a clear, ordered manner, similar to how a story is told.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>2. Persuasive Essay</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>A persuasive essay or argumentative essay is an essay in which you use logic and reason to demonstrate that your point of view is more valid than others. You must present clear arguments and back them up with convincing facts and logic.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>3. Expository Essay</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>This essay style demands you to research an idea, analyze evidence, elaborate on the concept, and present a clear and concise argument about the topic.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>4. Descriptive Essay</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>This type of essay describes the subject to the reader in-depth. The purpose of this type of essay is to provide sufficiently specific descriptions for readers to visualize or imagine the chosen topic.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Research the topic.</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The second thing that you need to do is research your topic. The topic is the root of your essay. You can not write anything if you do not have any topic in the first place. Sit and write down any topic which comes up in your mind. Once you write it all down, you can narrow it down and choose the best one.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Develop the main point</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The next phase is developing your main point or thesis statement. In this phase, you decide the basic premise of your essay. For example, the thesis statement might be “Electric is better than Gas.” Then, your whole essay is going to revolve around this idea. Make sure your thesis statement is general or broad enough to have more things to write.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Start writing</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Begin by writing a thesis statement at the start of your writing, then a topic phrase for each paragraph preceding it. Creating these outlines implies that you should exactly know what each of your paragraphs will be about before writing. Make sure there are transitions between paragraphs so the reader can follow the writing flow from one idea to the next.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Proofread the essay</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Lastly, you need to proofread the essay. Look thoroughly for any mistakes and typos! Check for any grammatical or spelling errors in your paper and revise it accordingly.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Follow these essay writing steps correctly to get a clear and perfect essay.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Do you want to learn more about <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/essay-writing-one-guide-to-master-them-all/\">essay writing</a>? Let\'s prepare yourself with ALL-in Eduspace!&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries on <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/\">Career Exploration</a>.</li><li>Improve grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring</a>.</li><li>Upscale your personal brand on the <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/writing-skills/\">Writing Skills improvement program</a>.</li><li>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!</li></ol>', 'photodune-11477592-essay-concept-notepad-s.jpg', '5 Essay Writing Steps for Beginner', 'publish', '5 Essay Writing Steps for Beginner. Follow these 5 simple steps', 'essay writing steps', 'These essay writing steps can guide you through creating the best essay that suits your needs. Follow these 5 simple steps to smoothly finish your essay.', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-01-09 17:00:00', '2022-01-06 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(9550, 'the-complete-essay-writing-examples', 3, 0, 'The Complete Essay Writing Examples ﻿', '<p>Are you struggling with writing essays? This article will show you some great essay writing examples that you can reference when writing.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The possibility of essay application is endless. Every field use essay as their tools to convey research. The fields varied from marketing, business, law, medical to physics.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Basically, they still share the same four types of essays. Those four types are descriptive, narrative, argumentative, and expository. We will go through and provide you with examples of each.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>1. Descriptive Essay</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>As the name implies, a descriptive essay provides a thorough description to the reader. When you choose this essay type, you will describe persons, objects, situations, experiences, or situations. In the essay, you are expected to inform the readers using their imagination to understand more about the subject. Here are a few descriptive examples:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>A place, broken down into geography, climate, politics, religion, and culture.</li><li>A famous person, president, actor/actress, singer.</li><li>Personal experience.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>2. Narrative Essay</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A narrative essay provides the reader with a piece of information with narrative style. Therefore, the purpose of the essay is to tell the story to the reader and emphasize the importance of the subject. In most cases, narrative writing is related to personal experience. It challenged you to be more expressive about your experience. The topic examples for this type is:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Your vacation abroad.</li><li>Unforgettable experience.</li><li>A tragedy you encounter.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>3. Argumentative Essay</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>When writing an argumentative essay, you are taking a stance on some issue. In an argumentative essay, you attempt to persuade the reader to support your stance on the subject. Furthermore, This type of essay usually has two points of view. It should weigh a lot more in your perspective on the subject. In addition, You should back the essay with the essential evidence as this type of essay usually covers various fields like politics, science, medicine, and technology. Some examples of this essay:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Should teachers befriend their students?</li><li>Could we colonize Mars?</li><li>Should families avoid watching the TV?</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>4. Expository Essay.</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This type of essay clarifies a subject for the reader. When writing an expository essay, you are expected to explain the topic thoroughly. While they may have a storytelling element, their objective is far more prominent. It\'s always to explain to the reader some key topic. As a result, they provide information, descriptions, and explanations. The examples for this are:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Racism in the US.</li><li>The unseen poverty of Jakarta.</li><li>Gun Control is out of control.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>These are some of the essay examples out there. Though there are a lot of <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/essay-writing-one-guide-to-master-them-all/\">essay writing</a> services out there that can help you write essays effectively, it does not hurt to exercise it yourself.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Need help with writing an essay effectively? ALL-in Eduspace can help you out!</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries on <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/student-clubs/\">Career Exploration</a>.</li><li>Improve grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring</a>.</li><li>Upscale your personal brand on the <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/writing-skills/\">Writing Skills improvement program</a>.</li><li>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!</li></ol>', 'photo-1486312338219-ce68d2c6f44d.jpg', 'The Complete Essay Writing Examples ﻿', 'publish', '', 'Essay writing examples', 'When writing an essay, you might encounter a blocker and do not know what to write. You can find some great essay writing examples here. Check it out!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-01-10 17:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(9552, 'the-ultimately-effective-essay-writing-tips', 3, 0, 'The Ultimately Effective Essay Writing Tips', '<p>An essay is the essence of every academic study. As a student with a lot of essay workload, you need excellent writing tips to make sure you got everything fully covered. With these essay writing tips, you are guaranteed to make the best essay.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For some people, essay writing is like a natural talent. On the other hand, many people struggle when doing their essays. It is possibly because they do not know the secret behind writing an essay. Once you learn these tips to write a great essay, you can apply them to almost any piece of academic writing. It does not matter whether it is a regular essay, a reflective essay, a dissertation or thesis, a course assignment, coursework, or anything else.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>1. Analyze the Prompt.</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This essay writing tips is one of the most critical. You have to analyze what is asked of you thoroughly. Find out whether it is to analyze something critically, compare or contrast, analyze a particular situation, or evaluate the usefulness of a specific concept.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>2. Define your point of view.</h2>\n\n\n\n<p> As you write your essay, you need to think about your point of view of the essay. For instance, This means forming an informed opinion on the question\'s subject and developing and delivering a specific topic. For example, “Solar Panel Usage on Electric Car.” Statements like these help to define the argument of an essay. They provide coherence by establishing a central theme and perspective to which the entire essay is dedicated.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>3. Use evidence and scholarly sources.</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Pay attention to this essay writing tips. To convince your readers about your argument, you need support from multiple elements such as evidence and sources.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Evidence is tangible information that backs up your argument. Specific examples, facts, statements, statistics, infographics, and illustrations are usually included.</li><li>Scholarly sources to show the readers that your claim is based on expert research. You can put it as your evidence or a supporting statement for your argument. Avoid using Wikipedia as your source because anyone can add or remove anything from the page. Stick to scholarly sources!</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>4. Write in a clear manner.</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Writing an essay clearly is one of the ultimate essay writing rules. Do not try to mess with it. It is essential to present your argument with great clarity. One of the few things that you can do is remember these things:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Make sure you use complete sentences.</li><li>Avoid abbreviations</li><li>Use \"children\" instead of slang language like \"kids\"</li><li>Do not use a contraction.</li><li>Remove any figures of speech from the essay</li><li>Remember to not overuse the same words or phrases</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>These essay writing tips can help you write an excellent essay for your academic purposes. Furthermore, You can apply these tips to many types of academic papers to make sure you create the best piece.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” Guidebook to find out all the things you need to know before applying for scholarships. It\'s FREE, <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/\">download here</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Are you eager to master your essay writing skills? Let\'s prepare yourself with ALL-in Eduspace!&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:<br></p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries on <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration</a>.</li><li>Improve grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring</a>.</li><li>Upscale your personal brand on the <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/writing-skills/\">Writing Skills improvement program</a>.</li><li>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!</li></ol>', 'photo-1602016736566-7ed6a58894bd.jpg', 'The Ultimately Effective Essay Writing Tips', 'publish', 'The Ultimately Effective Essay Writing Tips for your academic purposes', 'Essay writing tips', 'it is a fact that many people struggle when doing their essays. Learn some of these essay writing tips to get better at writing effectively.', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-01-11 17:00:00', '2022-01-16 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(9622, '10-jurusan-kuliah-anak-ipa-yang-paling-populer', 2, 0, '10 Jurusan Kuliah Anak IPA yang Paling Populer ﻿', '<p>Untuk kamu anak IPA yang akan lulus tahun ini, kamu sudah cari tau jurusan kuliah anak IPA yang cocok buat kamu belum?&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sebagai seorang siswa yang akan lulus dari sekolah menengah atas, kamu pasti sudah tidak sabar untuk melangkah ke jenjang selanjutnya kan? Beberapa jurusan kuliah anak IPA di bawah ini akan mempermudah kamu memilih mau melanjutkan ke jurusan apa nih.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>1. <strong>Kedokteran</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Semua orang pasti tau tentang jurusan yang satu ini. Selama masa pandemi, dokter menjadi pahlawan yang paling dibutuhkan di dunia. Oleh karena itu, Hal tersebut membuktikan bahwa semakin hari, ilmu kedokteran menjadi semakin penting. Selain itu, ilmu kedokteran ini mempelajari ilmu-ilmu untuk menangani penyakit. Jurusan ini sangat cocok untuk kamu yang suka pelajaran biologi.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>2. <strong>Astronomi</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Pernahkah kamu melihat ke arah langit lalu membayangkan ada berapa banyak objek yang ada di luar sana? Kalau kamu tipe orang yang suka dengan konsep alam semesta dan segala isinya, ilmu astronomi cocok buat kamu. Kamu yang suka pelajaran fisika bakal cocok banget nih.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>3. <strong>Ilmu Gizi</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan kuliah anak IPA yang satu ini mempelajari bagaimana cara menyiapkan atau memperbaiki gizi di berbagai sektor. Ilmu gizi ini juga mempelajari hal-hal yang berkaitan dengan pertanian, ekonomi, hingga sosial budaya. Maka, kalau kamu tipe orang yang suka mempelajari biologi dan kimia, kamu cocok masuk jurusan ini.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>4. <strong>Farmasi</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan farmasi adalah jurusan yang mempelajari penuh tentang ilmu obat-obatan. Kombinasi dari ilmu kimia dan ilmu medis ini tentu saja sangat dibutuhkan di dunia medis yang selalu berkembang. Kamu akan memperdalam ilmu menyeleksi, mengidentifikasi, meracik, memelihara, hingga menganalisis obat. Kamu tipe anak IPA yang suka penelitian di lab. Kimia akan cocok di jurusan ini.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>5. <strong>Psikologi</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Psikologi adalah salah satu juruan kuliah anak IPA yang paling banyak digemari nih. Di jurusan, kamu akan mempelajari banyak hal mengenai psikologi manusia. Ilmu ini seringkali membahas menganai serangkaian keputusan yang diambil oleh seorang manusia dan mempelajari latar belakang mengapa ia mengambil tindakan tersebut.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>6. <strong>Bioteknologi</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan kuliah anak IPA yang satu ini lagi sedang naik daun nih. Jurusan bioteknologi adalah jurusan yang mempelajari tentang pengaplikasian teknologi untuk pemanfaatan mahluk hidup. Penerapan bioteknologi modern dalam bidang medis adalah pembuatan vaksin, berbagai hormon, antibodi, berbagai enzim, terapi gen, transplantasi sel, transplantasi organ, tes kesehatan, dan juga mendiagnosis berbagai penyakit.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>7. Teknik Industri</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan teknik industri menjadi salah satu jurusan yang paling dicari di Indonesia pada saat ini. Seluruh dunia sedang mencoba meningkatkan perekonomian di bidang industri, dan ilmu teknik industri menjadi sangat penting untuk membantu peningkatan perekonomian tersebut. Di jurusan ini, kamu akan belajar banyak hal mengenai proses industri, baik dari sisi produksi hingga manajemen.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>8. <strong>Teknik Informatika</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Untuk kamu yang suka komputer, teknik informatika adalah jurusan yang cocok nih buat kamu. Di jurusan ini kamu akan mempelajari bagaimana cara membuat aplikasi, pengoperasaian komputer dan berbagai macam hal lainnya. Di dunia yang semakin berkembang menjadi digital, teknik informatika akan semakin banyak dicari. Untuk kamu yang suka mata pelajaran matematika, kamu akan cocok di jurusan ini.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2><strong>9. Teknik Sipil</strong></h2>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan kuliah anak IPA yang satu ini sangat banyak pesaingnya di tahun ini. Hal ini karena lulusan jurusan ini banyak yang dicari di dunia kerja. Di jurusan ini, kamu akan mempelajari tentang perencanaan bangunan, konstruksi, hingga pemeliharaan bangunan. Lalu, Bangunan yang dimaksud disini melingkupi banyak hal mulai dari jembatan, gedung, jalan raya, bandara, hingga stasiun.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>10. <strong>Teknik Pertambangan</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Teknik pertambangan merupakan salah satu jurusan yang paling ideal untuk siswa lulusan IPA. Hal ini karena di teknik pertambangan, kamu akan mempelajari banyak hal yang berkaitan eksplorasi tambang, pengeboran bumi, hingga pemeliharaan tambang.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Banyak juga kan <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/bingung-pilih-jurusan-kuliah-ini-solusinya/\">jurusan kuliah</a> anak IPA? Jurusan ini tidak hanya ada di Indonesia, tapi tersedia di luar negeri juga lho.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kalau kamu tertarik untuk memulai perjalanan akademikmu di luar negeri, kamu bisa mempersiapkannya bersama EDUVERSE by ALL-in Eduspace lho!<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi seputar:</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Study Abroad</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://landing.mailerlite.com/webforms/landing/p7d6e2\">Beasiswa</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/programs/\">Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Bedah Universitas&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!</p>', 'istockphoto-1150397417-612x612-1.jpg', '10 Jurusan Kuliah Anak IPA yang Paling Populer ﻿', 'publish', '10 Jurusan Kuliah Anak IPA yang Paling Populer ﻿yang bisa Kamu pilih', 'jurusan kuliah anak IPA', 'Sebagai lulusan IPA, kamu sebenarnya punya banyak sekali piihan untuk melanjutkan pendidikan. Berikut adalah jurusan kuliah anak IPA yang bisa kamu pilih!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-01-16 17:00:00', '2021-12-31 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(9627, 'essay-writing-one-guide-to-master-them-all', 3, 0, 'Essay Writing: One Guide to Master Them All', '<p>You might be wondering, “how come you get an overloaded amount of essay writing homework?”. Essay writing is an essential part of your learning. By doing an essay, you challenge your understanding of a particular subject and your ability to explain it.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>To master an essay, you need to see the essay holistically. This essay writing article will guide you through and make sure that you will be able to make a better essay with ease by the end of reading it.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To understand the essay a little bit better, we need to start from the beginning. Let\'s start with the way to do it.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/5-essay-writing-steps-for-beginner/\">Essay Writing Steps</a></strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>To know the steps is to be able to outline your essay. Outlining your essay will prove helpful because it trains your mind-mapping ability. To put it simply, there are five steps to creating a beautiful essay.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>1. Decide the types of essays.</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; After understanding your task, choose the type of essay which suits your need. There are four main types of essays that you can use. Those types are narrative essays, descriptive essays, expository essays, and persuasive essays.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>2. Research the topic</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Your topic will be the center of your essay. Researching the topic is the most integral part of your essay. It might take some time to find the right topic, but it is worth doing.&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>3. Develop the main point</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Developing your main point or argument is like the first throw on the basketball. It means the game starts to heat up. The more specific your idea, the less you can write. So, if you plan to write an extended essay, make sure to choose a broader argument.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you want to know more about these essay writing steps, you can read more [<a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/5-essay-writing-steps-for-beginner/\">here</a>].<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>After learning the steps, the next thing that you have to understand is the structure. By knowing the structure, it helps you outline your essay. It makes things easier as you go.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/simple-essay-writing-structure-for-everything/\">Essay Writing Structure</a></strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; There is three main essay writing structure. It is pretty simple, and it helps you a lot when you want to start writing. The outline of an essay is the introduction, body, and conclusion. Let\'s get to know them more!</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>1. The Introduction</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The introduction consists of three sections. Those sections are packed in the very first paragraph of your essay. The first section is a hook that lures the reader to read more about your essay. The second one is the background for your topic. Finally, the last section is your thesis statement.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>2. Body</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The body is the soul of the essay. It usually consists of four to five paragraphs, and each paragraph has its topic sentence. You should give a topic sentence in each paragraph that supports your main argument and thesis statement in each paragraph.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>3. Conclusion</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The conclusion is the last part of your essay. It wraps up your essay and presents the reader with the answer to the case. In the first section, you should remind the reader about your thesis statement. Do not add any new information in the conclusion! If you need to add a new point, just create a new paragraph in the body.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Deep dive about essay writing structure [<a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/simple-essay-writing-structure-for-everything/\">here</a>].<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>So you know the steps and structure, but you still do not know what to write and what topic is suited to which type of essay. Here is a few essay writing example that you can use as references for your writing.<br></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<h2><strong><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/the-complete-essay-writing-examples/\">Essay Writing Example</a></strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Previously, you have learned that there are four types of essays. Here are topic examples that you can choose to start your writing.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>1. Descriptive Essay</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>A descriptive essay is all about description. This type of essay is meant to give the reader information using their senses. You use this type of essay to describe something in particular. A topic example for this type is a descriptive essay about US President. In the essay, you can describe his physics, hair color, and eye color.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>2. Narrative Essay</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>This type of essay will tell the reader about a story. You will use this type of essay to retell a particular experience or situation. The topic example suitable for this type of essay is “My vacation in Europe”. With this topic, you will tell a story about your personal experience.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>3. Argumentative Essay</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>This type of essay challenges you to take a stance on some issues. Imagine a debate. There are two sides, and one is pro and the other contra. You need to choose which side you are on. The example for this topic is “Should baby drink formula?” You just need to choose which side you are on and expand the idea.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>4. Expository Essay</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>When you use this type of essay, you are expected to explain some issues to the reader. The reader will expect complex data in the essay. The topic example for this is “Muslim Struggle in India”. If you use this topic, you can provide the data on what kind of struggle they are having.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can get more essay writing examples [here].<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Now you are pretty much can create your essay with ease. Check out three essay writing tips that you can try to optimize your essay.&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/the-ultimately-effective-essay-writing-tips/\">Essay Writing Tips</a></strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A few things that you can do to optimize your writing is to proofread thoroughly. Some people think that the job is done when the essay concludes. It is not! You have to proofread your essay and purge any grammatical errors in the essay.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>To take your essay to another level, check out essay writing tips [<a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/the-ultimately-effective-essay-writing-tips/\">here</a>].<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Do you want to learn to write an essay effectively? ALL-in Eduspace can help you out!<br></p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries on <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/\">Career Exploration</a>.</li><li>Improve grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring</a>.</li><li>Upscale your personal brand on the <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/writing-skills/\">Writing Skills improvement program</a>.</li><li>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!</li></ol>', 'writing-essays.jpg', 'Essay Writing: One Guide to Master Them All', 'publish', '', 'essay writing', 'Essay writing is an essential part of your learning. This article will guide you and make sure that you are able to make a better essay with ease.', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-01-13 17:00:00', '2022-01-24 17:00:00', '2022-10-26 17:00:00'),
(9636, 'simple-essay-writing-structure-for-everything', 3, 0, 'Simple Essay Writing Structure for Everything', '<p>If you are here, then you are still confused about how to outline your essay correctly. Well, <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/essay-writing-one-guide-to-master-them-all/\">essay writing</a> structure is pretty simple, and it applies to every type of essay.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As we all know, essay types vary from narrative essays, persuasive essays, argumentative essays, expository essays, and descriptive essays. The fact is, at the very core, they all share the same structure.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The structure of essays is divided into three parts. Those are introductions, body, and conclusion. Pretty simple right? Let\'s dive deep into these three parts based on the types.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Narrative Essay Writing Structure</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The structure of the narrative essay is very particular. You can try to divide it into three parts:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>1. Introduction</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>In a Narrative essay, this part will give the readers insight into your story. This part is filled with hooks that entice readers\' curiosity to read more about the story you tell.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>2. Body</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The body structure of the narrative essay is the soul of the story. This is where the readers enjoy reading the most. The body of the narrative essay is divided into three parts.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Rising Action</li><li>Climax</li><li>Falling Action</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h3>3. Conclusion</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>This is the last part of the narrative essay. This is the part where readers learn the moral of the story.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Argumentative, Descriptive, Expository, and Persuasive Essay</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The structure of the argumentative, descriptive, expository, and persuasive essay is similar to each other. Therefore, You can try to divide it into three parts: </p>\n\n\n\n<h3>1. Introduction</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; The introduction part of the essay is the most critical. When writing an introduction, you can divide it into three sections.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Section one is the part where you present the reader with a hook. A hook is a neutral sentence that engages your reader and arouses their curiosity about your essay.</li><li>Section two is where you present the reader with your topic, background, and thesis statement. By giving background to your topic, you will give the reader more knowledge about your subject. Your thesis statement will represent your answer to the problem.</li><li>Section three is the outline of your whole argument in general. Give a concise explanation of how you plan to address each issue and the order in which you will do it.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h3>2. Body</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The body paragraph is the essence of your essay. It is usually four to five paragraphs long, each explaining its key point. To keep it simple. Let\'s divide it into three sections.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>The topic sentence comes first. It carries the point of the paragraph. Topic sentence informs the reader about the paragraph\'s topic and the key point it will make.&nbsp;</li><li>The supporting sentences follow, expanding on the main idea by discussing it in greater depth, analyzing what it means, and, of course, providing the evidence and argument that support it. This is where you support your claim with evidence from your study.</li><li>The final part of the paragraph is to remind the reader of your main idea, which restates the notion from the topic sentence.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h3>3. Conclusion</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The conclusion is the last part of an essay. In this part, you summarize your thesis statement and its supporting idea. It does not contain any new information. Remind the readers of the thesis statement first. Do not use the exact words you used in your introduction. Instead, you use different words to emphasize the same point: your overall response to the question is based on your logic. Then give a brief explanation of why your overall conclusions are significant.&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Remember! In this part, the readers should feel as they are learning something new.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Want to know more about essay structure? Let\'s learn together with ALL-in Eduspace!&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries on <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/\">Career Exploration</a>.</li><li>Improve grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring</a>.</li><li>Upscale your personal brand on the <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/writing-skills/\">Writing Skills improvement program</a>.</li><li>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!</li></ol>', 'shutterstock_114474988.webp', 'Simple Essay Writing Structure for Everything', 'publish', 'Simple Essay Writing Structure for Everything', 'essay writing structure', 'Essay writing structure is pretty simple, and it applies to every type of essay. Find out what they are and master essay writing now!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-01-12 17:00:00', '2022-01-08 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(9643, '10-jurusan-kuliah-anak-ips-yang-paling-dicari', 2, 0, '10 Jurusan Kuliah Anak IPS yang Paling Dicari', '<p>Kamu sudah tau mau melanjutkan studi ke jurusan apa belum? Jurusan kuliah anak IPS banyak yang mempunyai prospek tinggi di dunia kerja lho. Kalau kamu bisa memilih dengan tepat, pasti kamu bisa mendapatkan karir yang baik ke depannya.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Untuk kamu yang masih bingung mau memilih untuk melanjutkan studimu ke mana, kamu bisa lihat di bawah ini ada 10 jurusan kuliah anak IPS yang paling dicari di dunia kerja.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>1. <strong>Hubungan Internasional</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan kuliah yang satu ini merupakan jurusan kuliah paling bergengsi di dunia kuliah ini. Pasalnya, hubungan internasional mempelajari ilmu-ilmu mengenai komunikasi antar negara mulai dari isu keamanan, ketidakseimbangan perdagangan dunia, masalah lingkungan secara global, dan kemiskinan melalui kerja sama antarnegara. Sebagai lulusan hubungan internasional, kamu bisa berkarir sebagai diplomat, duta besar, staf ahli, dan staf kedutaan.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>2. <strong>Hukum</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan kuliah anak IPS ini pasti sudah tidak asing lagi di telinga kita. Banyak lulusan jurusan hukum yang menjadi pengacara terkenal dan hebat. Salah satu contohnya adalah Hotman Paris yang mempunyai klien sampai ke negara lain. Jurusan ini cocok untuk kalian yang suka riset dan membela kebenaran. Setelah lulus dari jurusan ini, kamu bisa bekerja sebagai hakim, jaksa, pengacara, atau notaris. Banyak juga lho perusahaan yang mencari lulusan jurusan hukum untuk menjadi HRD di tempat mereka.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>3. <strong>Ilmu Komunikasi</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Kalau kalian ingin belajar dengan mata kuliah yang seru, kalian harus coba ke jurusan ini. Jurusan komunikasi menawarkan pelajaran tentang <em>public speaking</em>, keterampilan menulis, videografi, fotografi dan keahlian menulis. Jurusan ini sangat cocok untuk kalian yang suka orasi. Kamu bisa masuk ke dunia marketing, advertising, maupun broadcasting, seperti bekerja sebagai copywriter, youtuber, content creator, videografer, penulis skenario, hingga produser TV. Kamu juga dapat bekerja di berbagai jenis agensi, perusahaan, media, dan instansi pemerintah.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>4. Ilmu Politik</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Untuk kamu yang mempunyai cita-cita memajukan bangsa kita menjadi lebih baik lagi, jurusan ini merupakan jurusan yang paling tepat untuk kamu. Di jurusan ini kamu akan mempelajari jurusan politik dari teori hingga praktik. Dengan mengambil jurusan ini kamu mungkin bisa punya relasi yang kuat dengan politikus-politikus di partai politik lho. Kamu mempunyai peluang kerja yang sangat fleksibel. Bisa tetap di bidang politik sebagai politikus atau anggota partai politik. Namun kamu juga bisa berkecimpung di bidang akademis, sebagai peneliti, dosen, atau analis politik.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>5. <strong>Manajemen</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan kuliah anak IPS yang satu ini sudah tidak perlu diperkenalkan lagi. Manajemen merupakan jurusan yang paling banyak peminatnya. Di jurusan ini, kamu akan belajar cara mengatur, merencanakan, dan mengelola perusahaan atau organisasi untuk mencapai tujuan yang diinginkan. Selain itu, kamu juga akan belajar manajemen SDM yang akan memungkinkan kamu untuk mengambil karir sebagai HRD.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>6. <strong>Ekonomi</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Di jurusan Ekonomi, kamu akan mempelajari keuangan di berbagai sektor yang ada. Di jurusan ini kamu akan dilatih untuk lebih peka mengenai situasi dan fenomena politik yang terjadi di dunia. Bagi kamu yang cinta dengan pelajaran ekonomi, jurusan ini sangat cocok untuk kamu. Peluang kerja yang menanti kamu adalah perencana keuangan, akuntan, peneliti ekonomi, analis risiko keuangan, analis data, konsultan keuangan, analis investasi.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>7. <strong>Aktuaria</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan kuliah anak IPS satu ini bisa dibilang sedang naik daun saat ini. <em>Actuarial science</em>, yaitu ilmu yang merancang dan meneliti solusi dari permasalahan dan pengelolaan risiko pada industri perbankan, investasi, asurasi, dana pensiun, jaminan sosial, serta industri lainnya. Saat ini, lapangan kerja di bidang ini mempunyai peluang yang sangat besar seperti aktuaris di bidang Klaim dan Asuransi Properti, Manajemen Risiko, Penaksir Asuransi Kerusakan Kendaraan, Asuransi Jiwa, Kesehatan, Agen Penjualan Asuransi.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>8. <strong>Kriminologi</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Kriminologi adalah ilmu yang mempelajari perilaku menyimpang dan kriminalitas. Di jurusan ini kamu akan mempelajari penyebab-penyebab dan latar belakang seseorang melakukan tindakan kriminal untuk mengetahui pola seseorang berbuat kriminal. Dengan begitu, kamu bisa mencegah tindakan-tindakan kriminal yang mungkin akan dilakukan orang lain. Jika lulus dari jurusan ini, kamu akan berkesempatan menjadi salah satu kriminolog di kepolisian, kejaksaan, Badan negara seperti KPK, BIN, Kemenhum, BNN, BNPT, Komnas Perempuan, dan Komnas HAM.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>9. <strong>Sosiologi</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Sosiologi atau ilmu sosial adalah jurusan yang mempelajari tentang fenomena sosial yang terjadi di masyarakat. Jurusan ini juga meneliti dan membahas tentang perilaku manusia di lingkungan sosial mereka. Prospek kerja untuk lulusan ini sangatlah luas, kamu bisa bekerja sebagai analis riset pasar, personalia, hubungan masyarakat, atau di instansi pemerintah.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>10. Akutansi</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan kuliah yang satu ini juga merupakan salah satu jurusan yang banyak penggemarnya. Pasalnya, hampir semua perusahaan membutuhkan sosok akuntan di tim mereka. Sebagai seorang akuntan, nantinya kamu akan membuat laporan keuangan sebuah perusahaan untuk keperluan perpajakan. Kamu juga berkesempatan bekerja sebagai perencana keuangan, penganalisa keuangan, dan internal auditor.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Banyak kan <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/bingung-pilih-jurusan-kuliah-ini-solusinya/\">jurusan kuliah</a> anak IPS? Kamu tidak hanya bisa belajar di dalam negeri lho! Jurusan kuliah yang satu ini juga populer di luar sana.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Apa kamu siap melanjutkan belajar di luar negeri? EDUVERSE by ALL-in siap untuk membantu mempersiapkan kamu untuk masuk ke universitas-universitas terkenal di luar negeri.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Study Abroad</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://landing.mailerlite.com/webforms/landing/p7d6e2\">Beasiswa</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/programs/\">Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Bedah Universitas&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!</p>', 'istockphoto-1158889603-612x612-1.jpg', '10 Jurusan Kuliah Anak IPS yang Paling Dicari', 'publish', '10 Jurusan Kuliah Anak IPS yang Paling Dicari', 'jurusan kuliah anak IPS', 'Kamu sudah tau mau melanjutkan studi ke jurusan apa belum? Jurusan kuliah anak IPS banyak yang mempunyai prospek tinggi di dunia kerja lho.', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-01-15 17:00:00', '2022-01-07 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00');
INSERT INTO `tb_blog` (`id`, `slug`, `cat_id`, `mt_id`, `blog_title`, `blog_description`, `blog_thumbnail`, `blog_thumbnail_alt`, `blog_status`, `seo_title`, `seo_keyword`, `seo_desc`, `lang`, `click_count`, `duration_read`, `is_highlight`, `publish_date`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(9649, 'macam-macam-jurusan-kuliah-yang-jarang-orang-tau', 2, 0, 'Macam-Macam Jurusan Kuliah yang Jarang Orang Tau', '<p>Untuk kamu yang sedang bingung mencari jurusan kuliah untuk melanjutkan studimu, mungkin jurusan kuliah yang satu ini akan memberikan referensi untuk keputusanmu. Di luar sana sebenarnya ada banyak macam-macam jurusan kuliah yang tidak semua orang tau.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kamu mungkin sudah bosan mendengar jurusan-jurusan kuliah yang itu-itu saja. Untuk kamu yang ingin jurusan kuliah dengan sedikit pesaing, mungkin jurusan-jurusan kuliah dibawah ini bisa kamu pertimbangkan.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>1. <strong>Teknik Nuklir</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Nuklir merupakan pembangkit energi yang luar biasa. Pasalnya, daya sebuah PLTN berkisar antara 40 Mwe sampai mencapai 2000 MWe. Maka dari itu jurusan ini merupakan jurusan yang sangat penting di dunia sumber daya.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Di jurusan teknik nuklir, kamu akan mempelajari pengaplikasian teknologi nuklir sebagai pembangkit daya listrik. Selain itu kamu juga dapat mempelajari pengaplikasian radiasi dan radioisotop di industri. Lalu kamu juga akan diajari pengaplikasian yang mendukung radiologi klinik seperti radiodiagnostik dan radioterapi.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>2. <strong>Antropologi Sosial.</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Di jurusan kuliah yang satu ini, kamu akan mempelajari hubungan antara masyarakat dalam suatu kelompok dan budaya etnis, mulai dari perilakunya, budaya, dan keanekaragamannya. Jurusan ini cocok sekali untuk kamu yang suka dengan budaya dan hubungan antar manusia. Sebagai lulusan dari jurusan ini, kamu akan banyak dicari lembaga dan instansi negara di bidang ilmu budaya. kamu bisa bekerja sebagai peneliti, antropolog, pengajar, wartawan PNS, konsultan, budayawan, HRD, dan masih banyak lagi.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>3. <strong>Oseanografi</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Oseanografi adalah ilmu yang mempelajari tentang kelautan. Kamu akan belajar berbagai hal mulai dari ekosistem laut, gelombang, arus samudera, dan geologi laut. Jangan meremehkan jurusan ini ya! Prospek karir kamu adalah sebagai <em>coastal modeler</em>, <em>oceanographic surveyor</em>, <em>metocean engineer</em>, <em>hydrographic surveyor</em>, <em>oceanographer</em>, <em>marine seismic navigator (offshore navigator)</em>, <em>marine environmental scientist</em>. Selain itu kamu juga mempunyai kesempatan bekerja di perusahaan yang melakukan penyulingan <em>offshore</em> seperti Pertamina.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>4. Teknik Desain dan Manufaktur</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan Teknik Desain dan Manufaktur menawarkan ilmu yang sangat penting untuk diterapkan dalam kehidupan sehari-hari. Kamu akan belajar banyak hal tentang berbagai macam inovasi produk sesuai dengan kemajuan serta perkembangan pengetahuan. Sebagai lulusan jurusan ini, kamu dapat bekerja di bidang bidang perancangan dan pengembangan produk (desain produk), perancangan proses Manufaktur (teknologi Manufaktur), serta pengelolaan sistem/manajemen produksi/pabrik, sehingga produk yang dirancang dan dibuat memiliki kualitas tinggi, diterima oleh pasar (konsumen) dan memiliki nilai jual yang kompetitif.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>5. <strong>Geofisika</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan Geofisika mempelajari bumi menggunakan kaidah-kaidah fisika. Di jurusan ini kamu akan belajar mengenai fenomena-fenomena menarik yang terjadi pada bumi kita. Pada dasarnya, lempengan bumi kita tidak statis melainkan selalu bergerak perlahan-lahan. Jurusan ini sangat cocok untuk kamu yang punya keinginan bekerja di perusahaan tambang, instansi pemerintah, atau sebagai peneliti.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>6. <strong>Jurusan Kearsipan</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan ini mungkin terdengar janggal dan aneh di telinga kita, tapi jurusan ini ada lho. Walaupun jarang peminatnya, tapi jurusan ini merupakan salah satu jurusan yang paling jarang peminatnya nih. Di sisi lain, jurusan ini adalah jurusan yang paling banyak dicari saat pembukaan CPNS. Selain itu, lulusan dari jurusan ini akan berkarir sebagai sekretaris perusahaan, pustakawan, staf administrasi, dan staf dinas pendidikan.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>7. Fisioterapi</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Kalau mendengar fakultas ilmu kesehatan, yang pertama kali terlintas di pikiran kita adalah kedokteran, keperawatan, dan kebidanan. Tapi di cabang ilmu kesehatan juga ada ilmu fisioterapi lho. Untuk kalian yang belum tau, peluang kerja fisioterapi ini merupakan salah satu yang paling dicari. Semua tim olahraga profesional membutuhkan fisioterapi di jajaran stafnya.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>8. <strong>Manajemen Transportasi</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Kalian pasti pernah bingung kenapa jalan-jalan yang dua arah tiba-tiba menjadi satu arah. Kenapa tiba-tiba jalan yang biasa dilewati mobil-mobil besar jadi hanya bisa diakses kendaraan roda dua. Mengatur arus lalu lintas adalah salah satu tugas dari manajemen transportasi. Di sini kamu akan belajar banyak mengenai manajemen lalu lintas baik di darat, laut, dan udara. Setelah lulus dari lulusan ini, kamu bisa berkarir di maskapai penerbangan, biro travel, cargo agent, dan perusahaan ekspor/impor.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>9. <strong>Ilmu Hama dan Penyakit Tumbuhan</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Pertama kali mendengar nama jurusan ini, kamu pasti akan sedikit bingung. Jurusan ini mempelajari tentang berbagai macam penyakit tumbuhan dan cara mengatasinya. Ilmu ini sangat penting untuk meningkatkan perekonomian di sektor pertanian dan perkebunan.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Lulusan jurusan ini dapat bekerja di lembaga-lembaga pemerintah (seperti Departemen Pertanian, Kementerian Ristek, LIPI, Bappeda, Badan Karantina Nasional), perusahaan-perusahaan BUMN, dan maupun perusahaan-perusahaan di bidang pangan dan pertanian.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>10. <strong>Teknik Biodemis</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan Teknik Biodemis ini merupakan jurusan yang sedikit pesaingnya namun mempunyai prospek yang sangat besar. Kalau bicara soal prospek kerja, lulusan Teknik Biomedis mempunyai beberapa pilihan karier yang sampai saat ini masih banyak dibutuhkan. Misalnya, menjadi laboran di laboratorium kesehatan ataupun laboratorium riset di lembaga-lembaga penelitian.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Menarik kan macam-macam <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/bingung-pilih-jurusan-kuliah-ini-solusinya/\">jurusan kuliah</a> yang jarang orang tau ini? Jurusan-jurusan ini mempunyai peluang yang besar di luar negeri lho!<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kalau kamu tertarik untuk memulai perjalan akademikmu di luar negeri, kamu bisa mempersiapkannya bersama EDUVERSE by ALL-in Eduspace.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi seputar:<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Study Abroad</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://landing.mailerlite.com/webforms/landing/p7d6e2\">Beasiswa</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/programs/\">Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Bedah Universitas&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!</p>', 'young-attractive-smiling-student-showing-thumb-up-outdoors-campus-university_8353-6394.webp', 'Macam-Macam Jurusan Kuliah yang Jarang Orang Tau', 'publish', '', 'macam-macam jurusan kuliah', 'Di luar sana sebenarnya ada banyak macam-macam jurusan kuliah yang tidak semua orang tau. Ayo cari tau apa saja jurusannya!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-01-14 17:00:00', '2022-01-07 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(9653, '10-jurusan-kuliah-yang-menjanjikan-untuk-karir-masa-depanmu', 2, 0, '10 Jurusan Kuliah yang Menjanjikan untuk Karir Masa Depanmu!', '<p>Kamu yang sedang mencari jurusan kuliah untuk melanjutkan studi pasti ingin masuk ke jurusan kuliah yang menjanjikan kan?&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Pada dasarnya, kita semua melanjutkan kuliah untuk meraih cita-cita yang kita inginkan. Tapi tidak bisa dipungkiri kalau kita sendiri pun ingin mendapat pekerjaan yang mempunyai bayaran yang tinggi.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Berikut adalah beberapa jurusan kuliah yang menjanjikan untuk karir di masa depanmu yang bagus:</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>1. <strong>Hukum</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan kuliah yang satu ini sudah tidak perlu diragukan lagi prospek ke depannya. Kamu bisa berkarir sebagai pengacara, notaris, atau hakim. Lulusan jurusan hukum akan selalu dibutuhkan entah itu oleh perusahaan maupun individu.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>2. <strong>Bisnis/Ekonomi/Keuangan</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Selain mempunyai peluang kerja yang luas, jurusan yang satu ini juga mempunyai insentif yang cukup besar. Lulusan jurusan ini akan mempunyai karir di bidang akuntan, auditor dan analis keuangan. Pendataan keuangan merupakan salah komponen utama dalam menjalankan perusahaan. Kalau kamu memilih jurusan ini, peluang kerja akan selalu terbuka untukmu.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>3. <strong>Teknik</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan yang lumayan banyak pesaingnya ini juga mempunyai peluang kerja yang tinggi. Hampir semua sektor membutuhkan seorang lulusan teknik sebagai penyokongnya. Di dunia yang terus berkembang, lulusan teknik menjadi semakin penting. Kamu mempunyai kesempatan untuk masuk ke industri jasa seperti keuangan, konsultasi, teknologi informasi, juga pelayanan masyarakat.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>4. <strong>Ilmu Komputer</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Di dunia <em>digital</em> seperti sekarang, ilmu komputer menjadi bagian paling penting dalam perekonomian. Kalau kalian tau Silicon Valley, itu adalah tempat perusahan-perusahan <em>digital</em> terbesar di dunia menetap. Ada Facebook, Twitter, Snapchat, dan banyak lainnya. Semua perusahaan ini membuka peluang untuk lulusan ilmu komputer sebagai bagian dari staffnya. Peluang lulusan jurusan ilmu komputer akan terus terbuka seberjalannya waktu.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>5. <strong><em>Data Science</em></strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ilmu yang mempelajari tentang pengolahan dan pengaplikasian data ini merupakan salah satu jurusan kuliah yang menjanjikan. Banyak perusahaan dan instansi yang membutuhkan lulusan jurusan ini untuk mengubah data menjadi informasi. Proses riset tersebut tidak akan pernah bisa dipisahkan dari perusahaan.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>6. <strong>Psikologi</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Lulusan jurusan kuliah yang satu ini merupakan yang paling banyak dicari di lapangan kerja. Pasalnya, semua perusahaan di dunia membutuhkan HRD untuk mengurus keberlangsungan staff yang mereka punya. Selain itu, lulusan jurusan ini juga bisa membuka praktek spesialis atau konsultan.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>7. <strong>Kedokteran</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan di ilmu kesehatan ini adalah salah satu yang paling dicari juga. Sudah dibuktikan di tahun 2020, Indonesia masih kekurangan tenaga kesehatan dalam mengatasi masalah pandemi. Selain prospek karir yang jelas dan luas, gaji yang bisa kamu terima itu termasuk tinggi.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>8. Ilmu Komunikasi</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Kalau kamu suka menonton acara televisi, orang-orang jurusan inilah yang bertanggung jawab dibalik semua kelancaran program-program yang kamu tonton. Lulusan jurusan ini mempunyai berbagai macam keterampilan seperti <em>public speaking</em>, videografi, dan fotografi yang akan selalu dicari di industri dunia hiburan. Prospek kerja untuk lulusan ini sangat bervariasi dan luas.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>9. Bahasa</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ini merupakan jurusan kuliah yang menjanjikan. Lulusan jurusan bahasa akan mempunyai prospek kerja yang lumayan luas. Setelah lulus dari jurusan ini, kamu mempunyai karir yang cukup beragam. Kamu bisa menjadi <em>copywriter</em>, penerjemah, penulis, bekerja di kedutaan besar, atau bahkan bekerja di sektor pariwisata.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>10. <strong>Jurusan Tata Boga</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Di jurusan ini kamu akan mempelajari teknik-teknik memilih dan mengolah bahan makanan dengan sempurna. Lulusan jurusan ini biasanya akan menjadi juru masak di hotel atau rumah makan terkenal. Kamu juga bisa membuka rumah makan sendiri dan mencoba berbagai macam peluang di bidang kuliner.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/bingung-pilih-jurusan-kuliah-ini-solusinya/\">Jurusan kuliah</a> ini tidak hanya menjanjikan di Indonesia lho. Di belahan dunia lainnya jurusan-jurusan ini juga mempunyai prospek kerja yang bagus.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Apa kamu siap melanjutkan belajar di luar negeri? EDUVERSE by ALL-in siap untuk membantu mempersiapkanmu untuk masuk ke universitas-universitas terkenal di luar negeri.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Study Abroad</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://landing.mailerlite.com/webforms/landing/p7d6e2\">Beasiswa</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/programs/\">Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Bedah Universitas&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!</p>', '69-20210129105604729.jpg', '10 Jurusan Kuliah yang Menjanjikan untuk Karir Masa Depanmu!', 'publish', '10 Jurusan Kuliah yang Menjanjikan untuk Karir Masa Depanmu!', 'jurusan kuliah yang menjanjikan', 'Kamu yang sedang mencari jurusan kuliah untuk melanjutkan studi pasti ingin masuk ke jurusan kuliah yang menjanjikan kan? Simak di sini!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-01-13 17:00:00', '2022-01-15 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(9658, 'bingung-pilih-jurusan-kuliah-ini-solusinya', 2, 0, 'Bingung Pilih Jurusan Kuliah? Ini Solusinya!', '<p>Sebagai seorang siswa yang baru akan lulus dari sekolah menengah atas, kamu sudah harus mempersiapkan tujuan jurusan kuliah yang sesuai dengan minatmu. Ada banyak sekali jurusan kuliah yang tersedia di luar sana, saking banyaknya mungkin akan membuatmu bingung.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sebelum menentukan ingin kuliah di jurusan apa, kamu harus melakukan banyak pertimbangan. Kamu harus memikirkan minat dan cita-citamu juga. Jangan sampai kamu memilih jurusan yang tidak sesuai dengan minat dan cita-citamu. Ketika kamu mencintai apa yang kamu lakukan, kamu akan lebih bersemangat untuk belajar di jurusan yang kamu pilih.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Berikut adalah beberapa hal yang bisa mengatasi kebingunganmu saat ingin mengambil jurusan kuliah:</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Jurusan Kuliah Anak IPA</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Kita akan bahas mulai dari jurusan kuliah yang bisa diambil oleh anak IPA. Sebagai seorang anak IPA, kamu mempunyai banyak pilihan jurusan yang tersedia untuk kamu. Rata-rata jurusan tersebut akan berhubungan langsung dengan mata pelajaran yang telah kamu pelajari seperti fisika, kimia dan biologi.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Di bawah ini adalah beberapa jurusan yang bisa kamu pilih sebagai lulusan jurusan IPA:<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>1. <strong>Kedokteran</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan kuliah ini pasti sudah tidak jarang didengar oleh anak IPA. Kedokteran merupakan salah satu jurusan kuliah yang paling dinanti-nanti untuk dimasuki. Kamu harus mempersiapkan dirimu dengan sebaik-baiknya karena pesaing di jurusan ini sangatlah banyak.&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>2. <strong>Ilmu Gizi</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Di jurusan ini, kamu akan memahami pentingnya nilai gizi dan nutrisi bagi manusia. pemahaman tentang pola makan sehat, gaya hidup, hingga cara memproses makanan. Kamu juga akan belajar tentang zat gizi penting apa saja yang dibutuhkan dan bagaimana takaran idealnya sesuai dengan ilmu pengetahuan.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>3. <strong>Farmasi</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Di sini, kamu bukan hanya sekadar mempelajari cara dan teknologi pembuatan obat-obatan saja. Ilmu farmasi juga mempelajari cara penyimpanan, penyediaan, dan penyalurannya. Sebagai mahasiswa farmasi, kamu akan mempelajari senyawa dan sintesis obat. Selain itu, kamu juga akan belajar cara meraciknya menjadi obat yang layak dan aman dikonsumsi. Materi kuliah yang akan&nbsp; kamu pelajari jika masuk ke jurusan farmasi di antaranya adalah farmasi fisika, biokimia, farmasetika dasar, farmakologi dasar dan toksikologi.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/10-jurusan-kuliah-anak-ipa-yang-paling-populer-!/\">Untuk mengetahui lebih lanjut tentang jurusan apa saja yang bisa diambil oleh anak IPA, kamu bisa cek di [sini].</a><br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/10-jurusan-kuliah-anak-ips-yang-paling-dicari/\">Jurusan Kuliah Anak IPS</a></strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Selanjutnya untuk jurusan anak IPS. Jurusan kuliah yang bisa dipilih oleh anak IPS ini juga sangat beragam lho. Ada beberapa jurusan yang bisa kamu pilih untuk melanjutkan jenjang pendidikan di universitas.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Di bawah ini adalah beberapa jurusan yang bisa kamu pilih sebagai lulusan jurusan IPS:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>1. <strong>Aktuaria</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan Ilmu Aktuaria sering kali disebut sebagai “Matematika Asuransi”. Karena aktuaria sendiri adalah ilmu tentang asuransi, atau ilmu tentang pengelolaan risiko keuangan di masa yang akan datang. Di jurusan ini, kamu akan mempelajari ilmu yang merupakan kombinasi antara ilmu tentang peluang, statistika, keuangan, matematika, pemrograman komputer, hingga <em>data science</em>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>2. Kriminologi</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Jika kamu memilih jurusan ini, kamu akan belajar menganalisis fenomena kejahatan, mulai dari penyebab, dampak, dan penanggulangannya. Pada dasarnya, ada 4 fokus bahasa yang akan kamu pelajari yaitu pelaku, korban, tindak kejahatan, dan respons masyarakat terhadap kejahatan yang terjadi. Jika lulus dari jurusan ini, kamu akan berkesempatan menjadi salah satu kriminolog di kepolisian, kejaksaan, Badan negara seperti KPK, BIN, Kemenhum, BNN, BNPT, Komnas Perempuan, dan Komnas HAM.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>3. <strong>Sosiologi</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan kuliah satu ini berfokus pada perilaku dan sifat masyarakat. Kamu akan belajar aspek-aspek sosial yang berada di masyarakat seperti sistem kehidupannya, interaksinya, karakteristiknya, dan perkembangannya dari masa ke masa. Prospek kerja untuk lulusan ini sangatlah luas, kamu bisa bekerja sebagai analis riset pasar, personalia, hubungan masyarakat, atau di instansi pemerintah.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sebenernya masih ada banyak lagi lho jurusan anak IPS yang bisa kamu pilih. Untuk lebih lengkapnya, kamu bisa baca [di sini].</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<p>Selanjutnya, untuk kamu yang benar-benar mengejar karirmu, berikut di bawah ini ada beberapa jurusan yang paling menjanjikan untuk karirmu di masa depan.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/10-jurusan-kuliah-yang-menjanjikan-untuk-karir-masa-depanmu/\">Jurusan kuliah yang Paling Menjanjikan</a></strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Kalau kamu masih bingung mau memilih jurusan apa, kamu bisa memilih jurusan di bawah ini nih. Jurusan-jurusan di bawah ini adalah jurusan yang menjanjikan untuk masa depanmu.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Berikut jurusan-jurusan tersebut adalah:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>1. <strong>Hukum.</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan kuliah yang satu ini sudah tidak perlu diragukan lagi prospek ke depannya. Kamu bisa berkarir sebagai pengacara, notaris, atau hakim. Lulusan jurusan hukum akan selalu dibutuhkan entah itu oleh perusahaan maupun individu.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>2. <strong>Bisnis/Ekonomi/Keuangan</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Selain mempunyai peluang kerja yang luas, jurusan yang satu ini juga mempunyai insentif yang cukup besar. Pendataan keuangan merupakan salah komponen utama dalam menjalankan perusahaan. Kalau kamu memilih jurusan ini, peluang kerja akan selalu terbuka untukmu.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>3. <strong>Teknik</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan yang lumayan banyak pesaingnya ini juga mempunyai peluang kerja yang tinggi. Hampir semua sektor membutuhkan seorang lulusan teknik sebagai penyokongnya. Di dunia yang terus berkembang, lulusan teknik menjadi semakin penting. Kamu mempunyai kesempatan untuk masuk ke industri jasa seperti keuangan, konsultasi, teknologi informasi, juga pelayanan masyarakat.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kalau kamu masih penasaran jurusan lain apa saja yang menjanjikan untuk masa depanmu, kamu bisa baca lebih lengkap [di sini].</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Selain itu, jurusan sebenarnya tidak hanya itu-itu saja. Masih banyak lho macam-macam jurusan yang jarang orang tau.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/macam-macam-jurusan-kuliah-yang-jarang-orang-tau/\">Macam-macam jurusan kuliah</a> yang jarang orang tau.</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Untuk kamu yang tidak ada minat di jurusan-jurusan yang orang pada umumnya tertarik, mungkin jurusan-jurusan di bawah ini bisa menarik minat kamu. Beberapa jurusan kuliah di bawah ini memiliki sedikit pesaing karena memang tidak semua orang mengetahui kalau jurusan kuliah di bawah ini ada.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan kuliah tersebut adalah:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>1. <strong>Teknik Nuklir</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Nuklir merupakan pembangkit energi yang luar biasa. Pasalnya, daya sebuah PLTN berkisar antara 40 Mwe sampai mencapai 2000 MWe. Maka dari itu jurusan ini merupakan jurusan yang sangat penting di dunia sumber daya.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Di jurusan teknik nuklir, kamu akan mempelajari pengaplikasian teknologi nuklir sebagai pembangkit daya listrik. Selain itu kamu juga dapat mempelajari pengaplikasian radiasi dan radioisotop di industri. Lalu kamu juga akan diajari pengaplikasian yang mendukung radiologi klinik seperti radiodiagnostik dan radioterapi.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>2. <strong>Antropologi Sosial</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Di jurusan kuliah yang satu ini, kamu akan mempelajari hubungan antara masyarakat dalam suatu kelompok dan budaya etnis, mulai dari perilakunya, budaya, dan keanekaragamannya. Jurusan ini cocok sekali untuk kamu yang suka dengan budaya dan hubungan antar manusia. Sebagai lulusan dari jurusan ini, kamu akan banyak dicari lembaga dan instansi negara di bidang ilmu budaya. kamu bisa bekerja sebagai konsultan, budayawan, HRD, peneliti, antropolog, pengajar, wartawan PNS, dan masih banyak lagi.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>3. <strong>Oseanografi</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Oseanografi adalah ilmu yang mempelajari tentang kelautan. Kamu akan belajar berbagai hal mulai dari ekosistem laut, gelombang, arus samudera, dan geologi laut. Jangan meremehkan jurusan ini ya! Prospek karir kamu adalah sebagai <em>coastal modeler</em>, <em>oceanographic surveyor</em>, <em>metocean engineer</em>, <em>hydrographic surveyor</em>, <em>oceanographer</em>, <em>marine seismic navigator (offshore navigator)</em>, <em>marine environmental scientist</em>. Selain itu kamu juga mempunyai kesempatan bekerja di perusahaan yang melakukan penyulingan <em>offshore</em> seperti Pertamina.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Untuk mengetahui jurusan apa saja yang jarang orang tau, kamu bisa cek di sini.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Daftar <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/daftar-jurusan-yang-banyak-peluang-kerja-di-masa-depan/\">Jurusan yang Banyak Peluang Kerja</a></strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Kamu pasti ingin masuk ke jurusan yang paling banyak peluang kerjanya kan? Berikut adalah daftarnya untuk kamu!</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Ilmu Komunikasi</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan ilmu komunikasi ini merupakan salah satu jurusan paling populer di Indonesia. Hal ini karena peluang kerja yang bisa kamu ambil sangatlah banyak. Di jurusan ini, kamu akan mempelajari berbagai macam ilmu dan metode yang digunakan seorang individu atau kelompok dalam berkomunikasi dalam konteks sosial, politik, dan media.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Manajemen</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan yang satu ini mempunyai tanggung jawab yang cukup besar. Di sini, kamu akan belajar caranya bertanggung jawab dan menjalankan bisnis dengan baik. Semua orang bisa memulai bisnis, tapi tidak semuanya bisa mengelolanya dengan baik. Maka dari itu, manajemen adalah salah satu yang mempunyai jurusan yang banyak peluang kerjanya..</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Teknik Mesin</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Teknik mesin adalah salah satu jurusan yang paling banyak peminatnya. Jurusan ini menggabungkan matematika dan fisika untuk mendesain, menganalisa, dan manufaktur sistem mekanik. Walaupun secara umum kamu akan mempelajari mesin, namun pengaplikasian ilmu ini sangat luas. Salah satu bidang yang sedang naik daun adalah industri otomotif.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/daftar-jurusan-yang-banyak-peluang-kerja-di-masa-depan/\">Ingin tahu lebih banyak? Ayo baca di sini!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/daftar-5-jurusan-kuliah-yang-tidak-ada-matematika/\">Jurusan Kuliah yang Tidak Ada Matematika</a></strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Bukan cuman kamu kok yang tidak suka matematika. Mata pelajaran yang satu ini memang kadang bisa sangat menantang untuk semua siswa di seluruh dunia. Untuk kamu yang ingin masuk jurusan kuliah yang tidak ada matematika, kamu bisa melihatnya di bawah ini. Ayo kita simak bersama-sama!</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Ilmu Filsafat</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Filsafat adalah jurusan atau ilmu yang mempelajari cara berpikir. Kedengarannya berat banget kan? Tapi yang jelas di jurusan ini tidak ada matematikanya sama sekali. Kenapa? Karena di sini kamu akan dilatih untuk mempertanyakan suatu keadaan. Selain itu, kamu akan belajar bagaimana cara memformulasikan dan mengokohkan pandanganmu secara bebas tentang suatu permasalahan di dunia ini.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Hubungan Internasional</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Hubungan internasional adalah jurusan yang mempelajari hubungan negara satu sama lain dan dengan organisasi internasional dan entitas subnasional tertentu (misalnya, birokrasi, partai politik, dan kelompok kepentingan). Ini terkait dengan sejumlah disiplin ilmu lain, termasuk ilmu politik, geografi, sejarah, ekonomi, hukum, sosiologi, psikologi, dan filsafat.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Kriminologi</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Kriminologi adalah ilmu yang mempelajari tentang kejahatan. Jika kamu mengambil jurusan kriminologi, kamu akan belajar tentang penyebab kejahatan yang berkaitan dengan biologi, psikologi, atau faktor sosial seperti status sosial ekonomi. Jurusan-jurusan ini mengkaji kejahatan di berbagai tempat, mulai dari lingkungan sekitar hingga negara lain.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color has-vivid-cyan-blue-color\"><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/daftar-5-jurusan-kuliah-yang-tidak-ada-matematika/\">Cari tahu lebih lanjutnya di sini!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/jurusan-kuliah-yang-paling-dibutuhkan-di-dunia-kerja/\">Jurusan Kuliah yang Paling Dibutuhkan di Dunia Kerja</a></strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ada banyak jurusan kuliah di luar sana. Tapi gimana cara kamu bisa milih apa yang cocok untuk kamu? Jika kamu menginginkan karir yang cemerlang, tentu saja kamu harus mencari jurusan kuliah yang paling dibutuhkan di dunia kerja. Berikut adalah beberapa jurusan yang wajib kamu pertimbangkan untuk masa depan akademismu.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Kedokteran</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Kedokteran merupakan salah satu jurusan kuliah yang paling dibutuhkan di dunia kerja. Di jurusan ini, kamu tentu saja akan belajar banyak hal mengenai dunia medis mulai dari mendiagnosa, merawat, dan mengobati berbagai macam penyakit. Jurusan ini mempunyai karir yang cukup spesifik dan hanya bisa diaplikasikan di bidang medis.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Ekonomi</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Ilmu ekonomi adalah ilmu yang mempelajari tentang pengelolaan sumber daya dengan memperhitungkan efisiensi dan efektifitas yang dimiliki oleh sebuah perusahaan atau organisasi. Sumber daya yang dimaksud bukan hanya tentang uang saja, tetapi juga waktu dan tenaga.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Teknik Industri</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Insinyur industri bekerja untuk mengurangi pemborosan waktu, uang, material, energi, atau komoditas lain dengan menyederhanakan prosedur dan proses. Insinyur industri bekerja untuk mengurangi pemborosan waktu, uang, material, energi, atau komoditas lain dengan menyederhanakan prosedur dan proses. Hal ini dicapai melalui penerapan pengetahuan dan keterampilan khusus untuk menentukan, memprediksi dan mengevaluasi hasil dari proses dan sistem.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color has-vivid-cyan-blue-color\"><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/jurusan-kuliah-yang-paling-dibutuhkan-di-dunia-kerja/\">Baca di sini untuk info lebih lengkap!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Jurusan Kuliah yang Paling Mudah Dapat Kerja</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ada banyak sekali jurusan kuliah yang disediakan oleh universitas top di seluruh dunia. Dari semua jurusan kuliah itu, ada juga beberapa jurusan kuliah yang bisa dikatakan cukup mudah karena porsi praktek dan teori yang seimbang. Tapi tentunya kamu tidak hanya mengincar kemudahan saja bukan? Jurusan kuliah yang kamu masuki juga harus mempunyai peluang kerja yang bagus pula. Penasaran? Berikut adalah beberapa <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/jurusan-kuliah-yang-paling-mudah-dapat-kerja-di-indonesia/\">jurusan kuliah paling mudah</a> untuk kamu!</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Jurusan Teknik Perminyakan</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Teknik perminyakan adalah kombinasi dari inovasi, eksplorasi dan ekspansi. Jurusan ini memberikan landasan bagi setiap profesi lain untuk secara efektif menjalankan pekerjaannya. Insinyur perminyakan menggunakan superkomputer, tidak hanya untuk analisis data eksplorasi dan simulasi perilaku reservoir tetapi juga untuk otomatisasi produksi ladang minyak dan operasi pengeboran.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Jurusan Psikologi</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Psikologi adalah studi ilmiah tentang pikiran dan perilaku, menurut American Psychological Association. Psikologi adalah disiplin multifaset dan mencakup banyak sub-bidang studi seperti pengembangan manusia, olahraga, kesehatan, klinis, perilaku sosial dan proses kognitif. Entah itu sikap atau reaksi sosial, psikologi akan selalu memiliki andil di dalamnya. Mengenai disiplin ilmu, psikologi mencakup banyak aspek sosial yang berbeda dari olahraga hingga ilmu saraf.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Teknik Informatika</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Salah satu jurusan yang banyak peluang kerjanya adalah teknik informatika. Teknik informatika adalah ilmu yang mempelajari tentang seluk beluk dunia komputer entah itu perangkat lunak ataupun perangkat keras. Ilmu teknik informatika telah menghasilkan beberapa hal yang telah membantu kehidupan kita seperti website, aplikasi, social media, dan kecerdasan buatan. Selain itu, di ilmu ini kamu akan belajar banyak seputar matematika, statistik, dan teknik.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color has-vivid-cyan-blue-color\"><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/jurusan-kuliah-yang-paling-mudah-dapat-kerja-di-indonesia/\">Penasaran jurusan lainnya? Simak di sini!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan kuliah di atas sangat menarik bukan? Tapi kamu harus tau kalau jurusan kuliah di atas itu tidak hanya ada di Indonesia lho. Kamu bisa melebarkan sayap akademikmu sampai ke luar negeri dan mulai memahat namamu di dunia.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Apa kamu tertarik untuk belajar di luar negeri? EDUVERSE by ALL-in siap untuk membantu mempersiapkanmu untuk masuk ke universitas-universitas terkenal di luar negeri.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi seputar:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li><a href=\"https://landing.mailerlite.com/webforms/landing/p7d6e2\">Beasiswa</a></li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas&nbsp;<br></li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!</p>', 'graduation-cap-diploma-table-books-150016685.jpg', 'Bingung Pilih Jurusan Kuliah? Ini Solusinya!', 'publish', 'Bingung Pilih Jurusan Kuliah? Simak jurusan apa saja yang bisa kamu pilih', 'jurusan kuliah', 'Sebagai siswa yang akan lulus, kamu sudah harus menentukan jurusan kuliah yang sesuai dengan minatmu. Simak jurusan kuliah apa saja yang bisa kamu pilih!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-01-12 17:00:00', '2022-01-01 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(9721, '5-best-scholarships-in-australia', 1, 0, '5 Best Scholarships in Australia', '<p>Australia has become the top destination for Indonesian students to pursue their education. Moreover, there is more than one scholarship in Australia that can help you pursue your dream of studying there.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You must be wondering, why are there so many Indonesian students who study in Australia? Aside from being close to Indonesia, Australia offers many opportunities and challenges for young people.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Furthermore, Australia has a beautiful mix of urban and natural landscapes and a world-class education system. More importantly, multiple surveys say that main cities like Sydney and Melbourne have the best quality of life for students in the world.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have interest in studying there, here are 5 best scholarships in Australia to which you can apply:</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Sydney Achievers International Scholarship</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The University of Sydney offers scholarships to international students who wish to study there. This prestigious scholarship aims to invite international students to study in Sydney and enjoy a learning experience in one of the world\'s best educational institutions.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The amount of this scholarship can be up to AUD$10,000 each for undergraduate or postgraduate programs. Besides, the requirement for this scholarship is that participants who wish to take the undergraduate program must have completed 12 years of education. Participants must also have attended the Foundation Studies Program in Australia.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>The Pathway to Victoria Scholarship Program</strong>, one of the best scholarships in Australia</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The scholarship helps international students who are pursuing English language or foundation courses in Victoria before starting their main degree, allowing them to enrol with Victorian education institutions.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With this focused funding, you will get a competitive edge in the global job market. Also, the scholarship will be administered by Victorian universities and will be made available to selected students as part of the admissions process. Moreover, this scholarship will cover the cost of your program course fees up to the amount of AUD$2,500.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Australian Awards Scholarship</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>From all of the scholarships in Australia, this one is the most famous for Indonesian students. Additionally, the Australia Awards in Indonesia program has the vision to help Indonesia\'s development by recognizing the good contributions of Indonesian? skilled professionals and enhancing the bilateral connection.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Over 9,000 Indonesians have obtained short- and long-term Australian Awards scholarships to study at Australian universities since 1953. In addition, many of these scholars have gone on to become leaders and have made significant contributions to Indonesian society.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Deakin Vice-Chancellor\'s International Scholarship</strong>, one of the best scholarships in Australia </h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Deakin University is one of the most famous universities in Australia. This university offers scholarships for bright international students who want to study at Deakin University. Also, the value of the scholarship is great. This scholarship provides two kinds of scholarships. One of them covers your full tuition fee, and the other only covers 50%.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>The Indonesian Global Leaders Scholarship (University of Queensland)</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>According to the Times Higher Education World University Rankings, the University of Queensland is ranked as the 4th best university in Australia. Meanwhile, according to the QS World University Ranking 2021, the University of Queensland is ranked 46th in the world.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Indonesian Global Leaders Scholarship is one of the best scholarships in Australia. Moreover, it is only given specifically for Indonesian students with academic achievements and who wish to continue their undergraduate or postgraduate studies in Economics, Law, and Business. Also, The scholarship grants up to $10,000 in one semester of study.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Australia offers many scholarships and opportunities for Indonesians to study there. Furthermore, These scholarships will accommodate your study and help you achieve your dreams.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Are you interested in applying for a scholarship in Australia? Let\'s prepare with ALL-in Eduspace!&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximise your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\"><strong>Admission Mentoring</strong></a><strong>.</strong></li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\"><strong>Career Exploration.</strong></a></li><li>Improve grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\"><strong>Academic Tutoring.</strong></a></li><li>Upscale your personal brand in <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/writing-skills/\"><strong>Writing Skills</strong></a><strong> </strong>improvement program.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'istockphoto-1252844327-612x612-1.jpg', '5 Best Scholarships in Australia', 'publish', '5 Best Scholarships in Australia; created to help international students', 'scholarships in australia', 'Scholarships in Australia is created to help many international students. Beside from supporting their financial needs, it can also help build their CV.', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-01-25 17:00:00', '2022-01-04 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(9728, 'top-7-scholarships-in-canada', 1, 0, 'Top 7 Scholarships in Canada', '<p>Canada is one of the most popular destinations for international students to continue their academic journey. Furthermore, Canada\'s industrialized and fast-growing economy offers limitless opportunities and potential. As one of the most resourceful countries globally, Canada provides the highest standard of life while lowering taxes and improving the economy with a 2.3% inflation rate.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Moreover, Canada is known for its excellent educational standards. Any certificate, degree, or diploma issued in this country is equivalent to those offered by the United States and other major nations. This shows the value of education in Canada.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are looking for a scholarship in Canada, there are a lot. But here are the best scholarships that you can apply to for your next academic journey:</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Lester B. Pearson International Scholarship</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This scholarship in Canada is one of the most useful for international students. In addition, the Lester B. Pearson International Scholarship Program at the University of Toronto was invented to recognize international students with excellence in an academic and creative subject and who are leaders in their schools.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This scholarship will cover your tuition, books, incidental fees, and full living expenses for four years.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>York University International Student Scholarship Program</strong>, one of the best scholarships in Canada</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Only international students accepted to York University with a solid academic record are eligible for scholarships. Also, this scholarship is ranging from $60,000 to $100,000 CAD for a four-year degree program.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>University of British Columbia Scholarship for International Students</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>UBC honours excellent students worldwide by providing more than $10,000,000 CAD in awards, scholarships, and other types of financial help to international undergraduate students each year. Moreover, to be eligible for this scholarship, international students need to demonstrate outstanding academic achievement and strong extracurricular involvement.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Carleton Prestige Scholarship</strong>, one of the best scholarships in Canada</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>For Carleton Prestige Scholarship, you must achieve an admission average of 90% or better.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Richard Lewar Entrance Scholarship, The Chancellor\'s Scholarship, the Carleton University Scholarship of Excellence, and the Carleton University SHAD Scholarship are each worth $20,000 - $30,000 CAD, while the Riordon Scholarship and the Collins Prestige Scholarship are worth $40,000 CAD.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>The International Entrance Scholarships of Calgary</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The University of Calgary International Entrance Scholarship is a distinguished fellowship that honours an international student\'s remarkable achievements before beginning their undergraduate studies. The scholarship\'s value is $15,000. Besides, it is renewable annually in the second, third and fourth year at the University of Calgary.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Winnipeg President\'s The Scholarships for World Leaders</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The President\'s Scholarship for World Leaders at the University of Winnipeg is for international students enrolling for the first time in any of the university\'s faculties. Also, the scholarships are worth between $3,500 CAD and $5,000 CAD.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>The Humber College International Entrance Scholarships</strong>, one of the best scholarships in Canada</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This award is only available to students pursuing undergraduate or master\'s degrees.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In January, there will be one full-tuition scholarship and one $5,000 CAD scholarship available, while in September, there will be seven $5,000 CAD scholarships and two&nbsp; $3,000 CAD scholarships available.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>These scholarships in Canada will help you achieve your dream academically.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Aside from the excellent education standard, studying in Canada will also open many opportunities for yourself. Moreover, it is the best place to explore more about your passion and interest. It is the best place to live and enjoy yourself as a student.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Are you excited to apply for a scholarship in Canada? Let\'s prepare yourself with ALL-in Eduspace!&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximise your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\"><strong>Admission Mentoring</strong></a><strong>.</strong></li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries on <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\"><strong>Career Exploration.</strong></a></li><li>Improve grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\"><strong>Academic Tutoring.</strong></a></li><li>Upscale your personal brand on <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/writing-skills/\"><strong>Writing Skills</strong></a><strong> </strong>improvement program.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!</p>', 'fotolia_93477743_m_resized.jpg', 'Top 7 Scholarships in Canada', 'publish', '%%title%% %%page%% %%sep%% %%sitename%% %%primary_category%%', 'scholarships in Canada', 'As an international student in Canada, you might want to apply for a scholarship to support your financial needs. Here are the best scholarships in Canada.', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-01-26 17:00:00', '2022-01-06 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(9731, 'the-5-best-scholarships-in-the-uk', 1, 0, 'The 5 Best Scholarships in the UK', '<p>As an international student, the UK is a great destination for you. Just like any other country, studying in the UK is pricey. Also, you may need a sponsor to support either your tuition or accommodation fee. However, multiple scholarships in the UK can help you pursue your study there.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You may already know that international students are eager to study in the UK. Besides, there are a lot of factors that attract international students to come here. In addition, the UK has an amazing academic reputation, welcoming culture, and a broad selection of courses.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Unfortunately, an amazing academic reputation comes with a price. If you want to pursue your study here, you might need to apply for a scholarship to support you financially. Here are a few scholarships you can apply for:</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Bristol University Think Big Scholarship</strong>, one of the best scholarships in the UK</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Bristol University offers a valuable scholarship for international students. This scholarship is only applicable to international students who want to study at Bristol University. Also, any full-time Undergraduate program except for Medicine, Dentistry, and Veterinary Science is eligible to apply for this scholarship. Furthermore, the amount of this scholarship is valued at £5,000 and £10,000 for international students who start in September 2022.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Reach Oxford Scholarship for Developing Country Students</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you want to study at Oxford, this scholarship is eligible for you. This scholarship targets international students who originate from a developing country, like Indonesia. Moreover, there is one catch: to apply for this scholarship, you have to return to your country of ordinary residence following your studies. Also, the scholarship covers your tuition fees and college fees. It also gives a grant for living expenses and one-way return airfare to the UK per year. Depending on course length, the scholarship duration is 3 or 4 years.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>International Ambassador Scholarship at the University of West London</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This scholarship intends to provide financial support for outstanding international students who wish to act as ambassadors for the University of West London. Furthermore, the student must be a non-EU International student, so you will have a higher chance of getting this scholarship. Moreover, The value of the scholarship is up to a £5,000 tuition fee discount for the first year of your study.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Westminster Undergraduate Full Scholarship</strong>, one of the best scholarships in the UK </h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Undergraduate Full Scholarships at the University of Westminster are the university\'s most competitive scholarships, eligible for international students from developing countries who aspire to pursue a full-time Undergraduate degree at Westminster. Moreover, to apply for this scholarship, you must be an international student who originates from a developing country and has been accepted into the University of Westminster.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>University of West London International Scholarships</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The International Scholarship Awards are made up of one scholarship that covers 100% of tuition costs and two scholarships that cover 50% of tuition fees for any full-time 3-year undergraduate degree study at the University of West London. In addition, you need to submit a 60-second video telling why you think the University of West London is a great match for you and what you hope to do with their degree.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>These are great scholarships that can support your education in the UK. Despite having a lot of international students, many scholarships target international students from developing countries, which is good news for you!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With preparation, you can be one of the thousands of Indonesian students studying in the UK every year! Prepare yourself with ALL-in Eduspace!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we do:&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximise your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\"><strong>Admission Mentoring</strong></a><strong>.</strong></li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\"><strong>Career Exploration.</strong></a></li><li>Improve grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\"><strong>Academic Tutoring.</strong></a></li><li>Upscale your personal brand in <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/writing-skills/\"><strong>Writing Skills</strong></a><strong> </strong>improvement program.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!</p>', '0fa6eadd76de89ed6a51fde4437bd34b.jpg', 'The 5 Best Scholarships in the UK', 'publish', '', 'Scholarships in the UK', 'Do you have a dream to go study in UK? Are you studying there right now? Get to know some of the best scholarships in the UK for international student.', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-01-27 17:00:00', '2022-01-21 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00');
INSERT INTO `tb_blog` (`id`, `slug`, `cat_id`, `mt_id`, `blog_title`, `blog_description`, `blog_thumbnail`, `blog_thumbnail_alt`, `blog_status`, `seo_title`, `seo_keyword`, `seo_desc`, `lang`, `click_count`, `duration_read`, `is_highlight`, `publish_date`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(9735, 'scholarships-in-new-zealand-you-need-to-apply', 1, 0, 'Scholarships in New Zealand You Need To Apply', '<p>Has it been one of your dreams to study in New Zealand? This island country offers a lot more than you think, from high-ranked universities, excellent education systems, as well as attractive scholarships. Let\'s find out about scholarships in New Zealand!&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Why should you apply for scholarships in New Zealand?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>On top of its jaw-dropping landscape and its laid-back locals, New Zealand also provides a world-class education equally accredited to the British system. That means you\'ll learn not only to think critically but also to solve any problems in a systematic and organised way.&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>International Excellence Scholarship - University of Waikato</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ranked among the world\'s top 1.1% of universities, the University of Waikato has offered a merit-based scholarship to international applicants with academic excellence. Also, scholarship recipients may have the chance to be appointed as a global ambassador for the University of Waikato.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Award amount: Up to NZD$20,000 for tuition fees&nbsp;</li><li>Field of study: Any undergraduate courses&nbsp;</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>In addition, eligibility requirements for the International Excellence scholarship are:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Applying for a full-time undergraduate degree program&nbsp;</li><li>Receives a conditional or unconditional offer&nbsp;</li><li>Not currently enrolled in the University of Waikato</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>International Student Excellence Scholarship - University of Auckland</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Founded in 1883 as the country\'s largest university, the University of Auckland offers the International Student Excellence Scholarship, which was established back in 2016. Academic excellence, the quality of the letter of application, and the referee\'s endorsement of the applicant will all be evaluated in the scholarship selection process.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The opening date of the scholarship application for the Semester One intake will be October 10th, 2022, and the closing date will be November 21st, 2022. In addition, for the Semester Two intake, the opening date of the scholarship application will be March 9th, 2022, and the closing date will be April 20th, 2022.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Award amount: Up to NZD$10,000 for tuition fees&nbsp;</li><li>Tenure: One year</li><li>Allocations: Up to 50 scholars annually&nbsp;</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Therefore, eligibility requirements for the International Student Excellence Scholarship are:&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Receive an unconditional offer&nbsp;</li><li>Possess overseas secondary or post-secondary qualifications</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Tongarewa Scholarship - Victoria University of Wellington</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Another scholarship in New Zealand you can get is offered by the Victoria University of Wellington. Moreover, this partial fee-based scholarship is for international students on the basis of academic excellence.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Award amount: NZ$10,000 for tuition fees&nbsp;</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Eligibility requirements for the Tongarewa Scholarship:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Received a conditional or unconditional offer&nbsp;</li><li>Paying tuition fees at the overseas rate</li><li>Applying for the first year of an undergraduate program&nbsp;</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Vice-Chancellor\'s Scholarship - University of Otago</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>With its history dating back to 1869, the University of Otago, New Zealand\'s first University, offers scholarships for international students to support their academic goals.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Award amount: Up to NZD$10,000</li><li>Field of study: Any undergraduate courses&nbsp;</li><li>Award number: varies</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Moreover, eligibility requirements for the Vice-Chancellor\'s Scholarship are:&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Applying for a full-time undergraduate degree program in the first year</li><li>Not a citizen or a permanent resident of New Zealand, or a New Zealand or Australian resident visa holder</li><li>Completed an internationally-recognized qualification in New Zealand or at an overseas high school</li><li>Paying tuition fees at the overseas rate</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>After checking out the scholarship in New Zealand, have you figured out which one you\'ll apply to?&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Planning to get your hands on one of these scholarships? ALL-in can provide you with hands-on guidance!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximise your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\"><strong>Admission Mentoring</strong></a><strong>.</strong></li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\"><strong>Career Exploration.</strong></a></li><li>Improve grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\"><strong>Academic Tutoring.</strong></a></li><li>Upscale your personal brand in <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/writing-skills/\"><strong>Writing Skills</strong></a><strong> </strong>improvement program.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!</p>', 'clocktower-and-registry-lawn-1548339487.jpg', 'Scholarships in New Zealand You Need To Apply', 'publish', '', 'scholarships in New Zealand', 'Scholarships in New Zealand is open for any international student who is studying in New Zealand. Take a look and find out here!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-01-28 17:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2022-12-07 17:00:00'),
(9739, 'scholarship-complete-list-for-international-student', 1, 0, 'Scholarship: Complete List for International Student ﻿', '<p>It has been a dream for so many students to study abroad. Why do people want to study abroad? The first thing that comes to mind is the quality of the education. Also, there are top countries which you can choose as a destination like the UK, Canada, Australia, and New Zealand.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>However, as you may know, studying abroad requires a lot of money. Moreover, you may need to apply for a scholarship to support your tuition and accomodation.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>But fret not! These countries provide scholarships for their international students. Besides, Some of these scholarships cover your full tuition and accommodation. Furthermore, Some countries even provide you with one-way airfare to arrive there.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s take a look at Australia. As one of the closest nations to Indonesia, Australia provides many scholarships for Indonesian students.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Scholarship in Australia</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Australia has become the top destination for Indonesian students to pursue their education. Moreover, more than one scholarship in Australia can help you pursue your dream of studying there.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4><strong>Australian Awards Scholarship</strong></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Over 9,000 Indonesians have obtained short- and long-term scholarships to study at Australian universities since 1953. Moreover, the scholarships are offered for the minimum period necessary for the individual to complete their academic program specified by the Australian higher education institution, including any preparatory training.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4><strong>Sydney Achievers International Scholarships</strong></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>The University of Sydney offers scholarships to international students who wish to study there. Also, University of Sydney scholarships can be up to AUD$10,000 each for undergraduate or postgraduate programs.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4><strong>The Pathway to Victoria Scholarship Program</strong></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>The scholarship will help international students who are pursuing English language or foundation courses in Victoria before starting their main degree, allowing them to enrol with Victorian education institutions. Besides, this scholarship will cover the cost of your program course fees up to the amount of AUD$2,500.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To learn about other scholarships in Australia, you can check out this link!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Next, let\'s talk about scholarships in Canada. Aside from countless career opportunities, they also have scholarships for international students.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Scholarship in Canada</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Canada is one of the most popular destinations for international students to continue their academic journey. Therefore, people worldwide are looking for the best scholarship in Canada.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are some of the scholarships which Canada provides:</p>\n\n\n\n<h4><strong>Lester B. Pearson International Scholarships</strong></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>The Lester B. Pearson International Scholarship Program at the University of Toronto was created to recognize international students with excellence in an academic and creative subject and who are leaders in their schools. Therefore, the scholarship will cover your tuition, books, incidental fees, and entire living expenses for four years.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4><strong>Carleton Prestige Scholarships</strong></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>For Carleton Prestige Scholarship, you must achieve an admission average of 90% or better. Furthermore, the Carleton University Scholarship of Excellence is worth $20,000 - $30,000 CAD.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h4><strong>The Humber College International Entrance Scholarships</strong></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>This award is only available to students pursuing undergraduate or master\'s degrees.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In addition, there will be one full-tuition scholarship and one $5,000 CAD scholarship available, while in September, there will be seven $5,000 CAD scholarships and two&nbsp; $3,000 CAD scholarships available.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Find out more about scholarships in Canada here!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Furthermore, the UK also has a lot of great universities with excellent education quality. There are a lot of scholarships in the UK. Here are some of them:</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Scholarship in the UK</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>As an international student, the UK is an excellent destination for you. Just like in any other country, studying in the UK is pricey. Despite that, the UK has an outstanding academic reputation, welcoming culture, and a broad selection of courses. However, an impressive academic reputation comes with a price. If you want to pursue your study here, you might need to apply for a scholarship to support you financially.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4><strong>Bristol University Think Big Scholarship</strong></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Bristol University offers a valuable scholarship for international students. Any full-time Undergraduate program except Medicine, Dentistry, and Veterinary Science is eligible to apply. Also, this scholarship is valued at £5,000 and £10,000 for international students who enter in September 2022.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4><strong>Reach Oxford Scholarship for Developing Country Students</strong></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>If you want to study at Oxford, you are eligible for this scholarship. Furthermore, to apply for it, you have to return to your country of ordinary residence following your studies. The scholarship covers your tuition fees and college fees. Moreover, it also grants living expenses and one-way return airfare to the UK per year.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4><strong>International Ambassador Scholarship at the University of West London</strong></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>This scholarship intends to provide financial support for outstanding international students who wish to act as ambassadors for the University of London. Besides, the value is up to a £5,000 tuition fee discount for the first year of your study.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Scholarship in New Zealand</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Lastly, scholarships in New Zealand are also available for international students.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Moreover, New Zealand also provides a world-class education equally accredited to the British system. Therefore, what better way to study in New Zealand rather than with some scholarships? Find out some of the scholarships offered in New Zealand!&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h4><strong>University of Waikato - International Excellence Scholarship</strong></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Ranked among the world\'s top 1.1% of universities, the University of Waikato has offered a merit-based scholarship to international applicants with academic excellence.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Award amount: Up to NZD$20,000 for tuition fees&nbsp;</li><li>Field of study: Any undergraduate courses&nbsp;</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>In addition, here are some of the requirements to be eligible:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Applying for a full-time undergraduate degree program&nbsp;</li><li>Receives a conditional or unconditional offer&nbsp;</li><li>Not currently enrolled in the University of Waikato</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h4><strong>University of Auckland - International Student Excellence Scholarship</strong></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Founded in 1883 as the country\'s largest university, the University of Auckland offers the International Student Excellence Scholarship, established back in 2016. Academic excellence, the quality of the letter of application, and the referee\'s endorsement of the applicant will all be evaluated in the selection process.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Award amount: Up to NZD$10,000 for tuition fees&nbsp;</li><li>Tenure: One year</li><li>Allocation: Up to 50 scholars annually&nbsp;</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>In addition, to be eligible, applicants should meet the following requirements:&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Receive an unconditional offer&nbsp;</li><li>Possess overseas secondary or post-secondary qualifications</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h4><strong>Victoria University of Wellington - Tongarewa Scholarship&nbsp;</strong></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>In New Zealand\'s capital city, the Victoria University of Wellington offers partial fee-based scholarships for international students based on academic excellence.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Award amount: NZ$10,000 for tuition fees&nbsp;</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Therefore, applicants must meet the following requirements to be eligible for the scholarship:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Received a conditional or unconditional offer&nbsp;</li><li>Paying tuition fees at the overseas rate</li><li>Applying for the first year of an undergraduate program&nbsp;</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Furthermore, with these great opportunity, studying abroad is no longer just a dream. You can overcome any financial obstacle during your study with these scholarships.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Are you ready to take on your academic future abroad?&nbsp; ALL-in can provide you with hands-on guidance!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximise your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\"><strong>Admission Mentoring</strong></a><strong>.</strong></li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\"><strong>Career Exploration.</strong></a></li><li>Improve grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\"><strong>Academic Tutoring.</strong></a></li><li>Upscale your personal brand in <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/writing-skills/\"><strong>Writing Skills</strong></a><strong> </strong>improvement program.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!</p>', 'scholarship.jpg', 'Scholarship: Complete List for International Student ﻿', 'publish', 'Scholarship: Complete List for International Student', 'Scholarship', 'If you are want to study abroad, you may need a scholarship to support your financial needs. Here are the complete list for international students.', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-01-29 17:00:00', '2022-01-09 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(9744, 'jurusan-kuliah-di-amerika-ini-5-yang-terbaik', 2, 0, 'Jurusan Kuliah di Amerika: Ini 5 yang Terbaik!', '<p>Kamu ingin melanjutkan studi tapi bingung mau kemana? Sebenarnya ada tujuan yang sangat tepat untuk kamu lho. Yep, Amerika! Jurusan kuliah di Amerika merupakan yang paling beragam dan terbaik. Banyak anak-anak Indonesia yang berusaha keras untuk bisa kuliah di Amerika.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kenapa Amerika? Sebagai negara yang sangat besar, Amerika menyajikan banyak kesempatan untuk kamu yang ingin mengenal dirimu dengan lebih baik, kamu bisa memulainya di sini.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Di sisi lain, Amerika juga menyediakan deretan universitas yang bagus beserta dengan jurusan kuliah yang luar biasa.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Berikut adalah jurusan <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/kuliah-di-amerika-bukan-cuman-sekedar-mimpi/\">kuliah di Amerika</a> yang cocok untuk kamu:</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>1. Arsitektur (<em>Architecture</em>)</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan kuliah di Amerika yang satu ini memberikan prospek kerja yang tinggi untuk lulusannya. Pasalnya, kamu akan dipersiapkan dengan ilmu dan lisensi untuk bekerja di banyak negara. Sebagai lulusan arsitek, kamu akan banyak terlibat dengan konstruksi, terutama merancang bangunan baru.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kamu akan bekerjasama dengan tim dan klien untuk memastikan bahwa desain yang kamu buat sesuai dengan kebutuhan, aman, fungsional, aman, dan ekonomis. Universitas yang memiliki jurusan arsitektur terbaik adalah <em>Harvard University</em>, <em>Columbia University</em>, <em>Massachusetts Institute of Technology, Yale University</em> dan <em>Cornell University</em>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>2. Teknik Informatika</strong>, salah satu jurusan kuliah di Amerika terpopuler</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Kalian pernah dengar <em>Silicon Valley</em>? Silicon Valley adalah daerah khusus yang berisi perusahaan-perusahaan digital besar seperti Meta, Twitter, Snapchat, dan masih banyak lagi. Sebagai mahasiswa lulusan dari Amerika, tentunya kamu akan menjadi lebih mudah untuk masuk ke perusahan-perusahaan tersebut.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Daftar universitas yang memiliki jurusan teknik informatika terbaik di Amerika antara lain adalah <em>Boston University</em>, <em>New York Institute of Technology</em>, <em>Indiana Institute of Technology</em>, dan <em>Polytechnic Institute of New York University</em>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>3. <strong>Bisnis</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Di jurusan ini, kamu akan belajar banyak tentang cara pengelolaan usaha yang baik. Selain itu, kamu juga akan belajar bagaimana melakukan pembukuan, pemasaran produk, dan pengelolaan keuangan demi keberlangsungan bisnis. Di jurusan ini, kamu juga akan tau bagaimana cara mengenal pelanggan, kebutuhannya, dan cara mengkomersialisasikannya.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Universitas yang cocok untuk kamu yang ingin masuk ke jurusan bisnis adalah <em>NYU Stern School of Business New York University, Boston University (BU) School of Management</em>, <em>Columbia Business School (CBS) Columbia University,</em> <em>University of Southern California (USC) - Marshall School of Business </em>dan <em>City University of New York (CUNY) - Baruch College - Zicklin School of Business</em>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>4.<em> <strong>Biomedical Engineering</strong></em>, salah satu jurusan kuliah di Amerika terpopuler</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Biomedical Engineering adalah jurusan yang menerapkan paham-paham ilmu terapan teknik dalam dunia biologi dan kedokteran. Lulusan ini merupakan salah satu yang paling dicari di dunia. Setelah lulus dari jurusan ini, kamu akan bekerja merancang, meneliti dan mengembangkan produk medis. Selain itu, kamu juga akan bertanggung jawab dalam penggantian sendi atau instrumen bedah dengan robot.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Universitas yang memiliki jurusan biomedical engineering terbaik di Amerika adalah <em>Massachusetts Institute of Technology</em>, <em>Johns Hopkins University (Whiting</em>), University of California—San Diego (Jacobs), <em>Georgia Institute of Technology</em> dan <em>Duke University (Pratt)</em>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>5. <strong>Psikologi</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Bagi kamu yang suka mempelajari manusia, jurusan ini akan cocok sama kamu. Psikologi merupakan jurusan kuliah di Amerika yang terkenal. Di jurusan ini kamu akan aktif melakukan penelitian, merancang hipotesis, mengumpulkan data, dan melakukan observasi. Lulusan dari jurusan ini mempunyai prospek kerja yang sangat fleksibel dan penting. Sebagai contoh, kamu bisa berkarir di bidang SDM di perusahaan-perusahaan besar.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kalau kamu tertarik dengan jurusan ini, universitas yang cocok untuk kamu antara lain adalah <em>Harvard University</em>, <em>Stanford University</em>, <em>Yale University</em>, <em>University of California</em>, <em>Los Angeles (UCLA) </em>dan <em>University of Michigan</em>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Banyak kan jurusan kuliah di Amerika? Jurusan kuliah di atas merupakan yang terbaik dan paling banyak pesaingnya. Jadi, kamu hari mempersiapkan dengan benar-benar matang ya kalau mau melanjutkan <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/kuliah-di-amerika-bukan-cuman-sekedar-mimpi/\">kuliah di Amerika</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Apa kamu siap melanjutkan belajar di Amerika? EDUVERSE by ALL-in siap untuk membantu mempersiapkanmu untuk masuk ke universitas-universitas terkenal di Amerika.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi seputar:</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Study Abroad</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://landing.mailerlite.com/webforms/landing/p7d6e2\">Beasiswa</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/programs/\">Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Bedah Universitas</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!</p>', 'gedung-kampus-Universitas-Harvard-Amerika-Serikat.jpg', 'Jurusan Kuliah di Amerika: Ini 5 yang Terbaik!', 'publish', 'Jurusan Kuliah di Amerika: Ini 5 yang Terbaik!', 'jurusan kuliah di Amerika', 'Apa kamu ingin melanjutkan sekolah di Amerika? Ketahui dahulu beberapa jurusan kuliah di Amerika yang sedang menjadi sorotan dunia.', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-01-17 17:00:00', '2022-01-21 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(9751, 'biaya-kuliah-di-amerika-serikat-ini-lengkapnya', 2, 0, 'Biaya Kuliah di Amerika Serikat: Ini Lengkapnya!', '<p>Kalau kamu punya keinginan untuk kuliah di Amerika, mungkin biaya adalah salah satu informasi penting untuk kamu. Seperti yang kita tau, biaya kuliah di Amerika Serikat itu tidaklah murah. Namun seberapa besar biaya akomodasi di sana itu tergantung dengan gaya hidup pribadi kamu sendiri.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sebelum kamu memulai <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/kuliah-di-amerika-bukan-cuman-sekedar-mimpi/\">kuliah di Amerika</a>, menentukan anggaran adalah sebuah langkah bijaksana yang bisa kamu terapkan. Pasalnya, ada banyak sekali kebutuhanmu di sana sebagai pelajar internasional.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Berikut adalah lampiran biaya untuk biaya akomodasi dan biaya kuliah di Amerika Serikat:</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Biaya Akomodasi</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Biaya akomodasi merupakan biaya yang paling penting untuk siswa internasional. Rata-rata apartemen di Amerika Serikat mempunyai harga sewa mulai dari $500 (apartemen satu kamar tidur) hingga $ 1.500 (apartemen 3 kamar tidur di daerah perkotaan).</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Harga ini juga dapat bervariasi tergantung pada utilitas yang termasuk dalam sewa Anda. Banyak penyewa di kota-kota perguruan tinggi akan memasukkan beberapa utilitas dalam sewa bulanan. Berikut adalah daftar biaya untuk keperluan akomodasi mu di sana.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Listrik: $50 hingga $100 per bulan, tergantung pada ukuran apartemen Anda dan jika ada peralatan dan lampu hemat energi yang digunakan. Jika pemanas Anda menggunakan listrik, itu dapat membuat biaya Anda hingga $150 per bulan.</li><li>Gas: Jika kamu memutuskan untuk memasak sendiri biaya gas hanya $10 hingga $15 per bulan, tergantung seberapa banyak Anda memasak. Jika digunakan untuk pemanas air, biaya yang harus kamu keluarkan bisa mencapai $50-$100/bulan.</li><li>Internet: Rata-rata $45-$50 per bulan.</li><li>Layanan seluler: Sebagian besar layanan rata-rata $50 per bulan.</li><li>Air, selokan, dan sampah. Biaya ini merupakan biaya sampingan yang sangat penting. Karena ini termasuk dalam kebutuhan sehari-hari.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Total biaya yang kamu keluarkan bisa mencapai $1000 – $1500 per bulan untuk perumahan dan utilitas.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tapi kamu tidak perlu khawatir, di Amerika banyak menyediakan pekerjaan paruh waktu untuk membantumu memenuhi biaya akomodasi dan kuliah di sana. Untuk pelajar asing, lowongan pekerja paruh waktu maksimal 20 jam per minggu. Biasanya kamu akan dibayar per jam dibandingkan per bulan. Kamu bisa bekerja di cafe, restoran cepat saji, sebagai pengantar makanan, pengantar koran, pengasuh anak, atau bekerja di perusahaan agensi kecil.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sumber: <a href=\"https://studying-in-us.org/cost-of-living-in-the-united-states/\">https://studying-in-us.org/cost-of-living-in-the-united-states/</a>&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Biaya Kuliah</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Untuk biaya kuliah di Amerika Serikat bervariasi untuk setiap perguruan tinggi. Universitas AS termasuk dalam dua kategori utama: institusi publik, dan swasta (independen). Biaya sekolah siswa internasional di universitas negeri didasarkan pada biaya bukan penduduk, yang biasanya masih lebih murah daripada di universitas swasta. Penting untuk diperhatikan bahwa biaya program di sekolah AS tidak selalu mempengaruhi kualitasnya. Berikut adalah kisaran biayanya:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td>Jenis Universitas</td><td>Biaya Kuliah di Amerika per Tahun</td></tr><tr><td>Lembaga Negara</td><td>$6,000 - $13,000</td></tr><tr><td>Institusi Swasta</td><td>$12,000 - $19,000</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Biaya Transportasi</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Jika kamu memutuskan untuk tinggal di tempat yang agak jauh dari universitas, biaya ini patut untuk kamu rencanakan. Walaupun tidak begitu banyak, kamu akan mengeluarkan biaya transportasi hampir setiap hari.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Di seluruh wilayah Amerika, biaya transportasi publik untuk satu orang sangat bervariasi, dari $435 per bulan hingga lebih dari $1.000 per bulan. Meskipun begitu, kamu bisa juga mendapatkan tiket bulanan seharga $50 - $60. Beberapa wilayah bahkan mempunyai potongan harga untuk siswa lhi.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Setelah mengetahui biaya <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/kuliah-di-amerika-bukan-cuman-sekedar-mimpi/\">kuliah di Amerika</a>, apa kamu tertarik untuk belajar di sana?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>EDUVERSE by ALL-in siap untuk membantu mempersiapkanmu untuk masuk ke universitas-universitas terkenal di luar negeri.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Study Abroad</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://landing.mailerlite.com/webforms/landing/p7d6e2\">Beasiswa</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/programs/\">Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Bedah Universitas&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!<br></p>', 'Best-Schools-For-International-Students-In-America-2018.webp', 'Biaya Kuliah di Amerika Serikat: Ini Lengkapnya!', 'publish', 'Biaya Kuliah di Amerika Serikat: Ini Detail Lengkapnya!', 'biaya kuliah di amerika serikat', 'Apa kamu sedang membuat anggaran biaya kuliah di amerika serikat? Berikut adalah detail yang perlu kamu ketahui sebelum berangkat ke sana.', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-01-20 17:00:00', '2022-01-17 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(9756, 'beasiswa-kuliah-di-amerika-ini-wajib-kamu-coba', 2, 0, 'Beasiswa Kuliah di Amerika Ini Wajib Kamu Coba!', '<p>Sudah banyak yang bilang bahwa biaya kuliah di Amerika itu tidak murah. Dengan biaya kuliah yang mencapai puluhan ribu dolar, belum lagi ditambah biaya hidup, impian untuk belajar di Amerika tampaknya tidak masuk akal. Untungnya, terdapat banyak beasiswa <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/kuliah-di-amerika-bukan-cuman-sekedar-mimpi/\">kuliah di Amerika</a> yang ditawarkan untuk mendukung siswa internasional agar mereka dapat melanjutkan pendidikan di universitas impian mereka. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Untuk kamu yang ingin membuat mimpi kamu belajar di Amerika menjadi kenyataan, baca terus untuk mengetahui beberapa beasiswa kuliah di Amerika yang bisa kamu dapatkan!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Kenapa Harus Coba Beasiswa Kuliah di Amerika?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Bukan rahasia lagi bahwa universitas di Amerika merupakan tujuan studi impian setiap siswa. Amerika menyediakan banyak hal, mulai dari sistem pendidikan yang fleksibel hingga lingkungan yang beragam,. Kamu akan menyelesaikan studi yang tidak hanya dipenuhi dengan pengetahuan namun juga dengan pengalaman yang tak terlupakan!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Michigan State University - International Tuition Grant</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Dengan komunitas yang berjumlah lebih dari 49 ribu siswa, <em>Michigan State University </em>menawarkan beasiswa ini sebesar $25,000 USD, $21,000 USD, atau $18,000 USD per tahun selama delapan semester. Beberapa faktor yang dipertimbangkan untuk mendapatkan beasiswa ini termasuk kinerja akademik, esai aplikasi, kemahiran bahasa Inggris, keterlibatan dalam aktivitas, dan keragaman geografis. Persaingan untuk mendapat beasiswa ini cukup ketat dan kompetitif, dengan hanya siswa di 5% teratas di kumpulan pelamar yang diberikan beasiswa tertinggi.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>American University - Merit Awards</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Didirikan oleh John Fletcher Hurst pada tahun 1893, <em>American University</em> menawarkan beasiswa ini bagi mahasiswa internasional yang berprestasi. Beasiswa parsial ini diberikan agar dapat meringankan biaya kuliah mahasiswa internasional. Untungnya, beasiswa ini dapat diperbarui selama empat tahun studi jika kinerja akademik dipertahankan, loh!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Oregon State University - Provost\'s Scholarships for Excellence</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Selanjutnya, beasiswa kuliah di Amerika ini ditawarkan oleh <em>Oregon State University</em>, salah satu universitas riset publik terbesar di Amerika Serikat. Beasiswa ini menyediakan potongan uang kuliah sebesar $6,000 USD per tahun, dimana dapat berlangsung selama studi jika GPA diatas 3,0.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Washington State University - International Academic Award</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Beasiswa ini ditujukan bagi mahasiswa baru <em>Washington State University</em> yang tidak memiliki status imigran atau bukan warga negara Amerika Serikat.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Terdapat dua tingkat untuk beasiswa ini:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Tingkat satu: $2,000 USD per semester jika kumulatif GPA diatas 3,6</li><li>Tingkat dua:&nbsp; $1,000 USD per semester jika kumulatif GPA diantara 3,30 sampai 3,59</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Selain itu, beasiswa ini dapat diperbarui untuk lima semester, asalkan kumulatif GPA 3,20 atau lebih tinggi dan juga mendapatkan setidaknya 24 kredit per tahun.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Arizona State University - New American University Scholarship</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Arizona State University</em>, universitas yang memiliki empat kampus di Phoenix, menawarkan beasiswa ini untuk siswa yang berprestasi. Untuk mendapatkan beasiswa ini, mahasiswa harus memiliki nilai yang cukup tinggi, mempunyai visa F-1, dan juga tidak disponsor oleh organisasi atau institusi lain. Jumlah beasiswa ini berkisar dari $3,000 USD hingga $15,500 USD.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Oklahoma State University - International Achievement Freshman Scholarship</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Sebagai mahasiswa baru di <em>Oklahoma State University</em>, kamu dapat memiliki kesempatan untuk mendapatkan beasiswa ini sebanyak $40,000 USD selama kurun waktu 4 tahun. Salah satu dari eligibilitas beasiswa ini adalah memiliki nilai diatas 8.5 dalam ujian IELTS, atau dengan nilai 115 hingga 120 dalam tes TOEFL IBT.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Diatas merupakan sebagian beasiswa yang tersedia bagi mahasiswa internasional yang ingin melanjutkan studinya di Amerika Serikat. Apakah kamu sudah memutuskan beasiswa <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/kuliah-di-amerika-bukan-cuman-sekedar-mimpi/\">kuliah di Amerika</a> yang akan kamu <em>apply</em>?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kalau kamu tertarik untuk memulai perjalanan akademikmu di luar negeri, kamu bisa mempersiapkannya bersama EDUVERSE by ALL-in Eduspace.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi seputar:</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Study Abroad</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://landing.mailerlite.com/webforms/landing/p7d6e2\">Beasiswa</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/programs/\">Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Bedah Universitas&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!</p>', 'graduation-registrar-hero.jpg', 'Beasiswa Kuliah di Amerika Ini Wajib Kamu Coba!', 'publish', '', 'Beasiswa Kuliah di Amerika', 'Apa kamu pelajar yang berencana melanjutkan studi di Amerika? Berikut adalah beberapa beasiswa kuliah di Amerika yang dapat membantumu selama berkuliah.', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-01-19 17:00:00', '2022-01-07 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(9760, 'belum-tahu-cara-kuliah-di-amerika-cek-di-sini', 2, 0, 'Belum Tahu Cara Kuliah di Amerika? Cek Di Sini!', '<p>Kuliah di Amerika merupakan cita-cita banyak pelajar di Indonesia. Mungkin banyak pelajar yang tidak tau, tapi cara kuliah di Amerika itu tidak sesulit yang kita bayangkan lho.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Salah satu alasan kenapa banyak orang yang mau berkuliah di Amerika adalah karena kualitas pendidikan Amerika yang sangat tinggi.Selain itu, kurikulum yang unik, lingkungan multikultural, dan banyak peluang adalah beberapa alasan mengapa banyak siswa internasional memilih untuk belajar di negara tersebut. Lebih hebatnya lagi, Universitas di Amerika dikenal luas di kancah dunia karena kualitas pengajaran dan penelitiannya.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Cara kuliah di Amerika ternyata cukup mudah lho. Berikut adalah langkah-langkah yang bisa kamu lakukan agar bisa berkuliah di Amerika.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Cari Tahu Tentang Universitas</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Hal pertama yang harus kamu lakukan adalah melakukan riset tentang universitas yang ingin kamu tuju. Seperti yang kita tahu, Amerika punya banyak universitas dengan kualitas pendidikan yang luar biasa. Kamu harus pintar memilih universitas mana yang mempunyai jurusan yang sesuai dengan minat dan kemampuanmu. Lalu, kamu juga harus mencari tau biaya yang diperlukan untuk akomodasi dan kuliah di tempat tersebut.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Mungkin kamu pernah mendengar tentan Ivy League. Ivy League adalah julukan untuk kumpulan universitas unggul di Amerika seperti adalah <em>Massachusetts Institute of Technology (MIT)</em>, <em>Stanford University</em>, <em>Harvard University</em>, dan <em>California Institute of Technology (Caltech)</em>.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Daftar dan Ikuti Tes Penerimaan</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Dari sekian banyak cara <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/kuliah-di-amerika-bukan-cuman-sekedar-mimpi/\">kuliah di Amerika</a>, kamu harus memperhatikan hal-hal di bawah ini dengan seksama. Setelah melakukan riset, hal yang bisa kamu lakukan selanjutnya adalah mendaftar dan mengikuti tes penerimaan. Secara umum, berikut adalah persyaratan umum untuk masuk universitas di Amerika:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>1. <strong>Resume</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Salah satu poin terpenting sebagai syarat pendaftaran universitas di Amerika adalah Resume. Kamu harus sudah menyusun resume sejak dini. Resume ini bisa berisi berbagai macam penghargaan yang telah kamu dapatkan dan pengalaman kegiatan sukarela mu selama bersekolah.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>2. <strong>SAT atau ACT</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>SAT/ACT adalah ujian masuk yang digunakan oleh sebagian besar perguruan tinggi dan universitas untuk membuat keputusan penerimaan. Tujuan SAT/ACT adalah untuk mengukur kesiapan siswa sekolah menengah untuk kuliah, dan menyediakan satu titik data umum yang dapat digunakan untuk membandingkan semua pelamar.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>3. IELTS or TOEFL</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Untuk kuliah di Amerika, kamu wajib untuk mengikuti tes IELTS atau TOEFL. Tujuan dari adanya tes ini adalah untuk menguji seberapa baik tingkat pengetahuan Bahasa Inggrismu. Tentu saja hal ini karena kegiatan akademik dan sosialmu nanti akan menggunakan bahasa inggris. Kamu bisa mendapatkan nilai IELTS atau TOEFL ini dari beberapa lembaga yang menyediakan jasa tersebut. Sudah banyak lembaga di Indonesia yang menyediakan tes IELTS atau TOEFL. Namun beberapa universitas tidak memberlakukan hal ini.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>4. <strong><em>Admission Essay</em></strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Admission Essay</em> adalah bagian dari proses penerimaan yang bertujuan untuk menyampaikan rasa karakter unik kamu kepada panitia penerimaan. Esai ini menunjukkan keterampilan menulis dan kemampuan mengungkapkan ide dan pikiran secara runtut. Penulisan esai penerimaan sangat penting untuk menunjukan kecocokan kamu dengan universitas.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>5. <strong>Surat Rekomendasi</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Surat Rekomendasi Perguruan Tinggi adalah surat dukungan agar kamu diterima di universitas yang kamu tuju. Isi dari surat ini adalah pernyataan formal singkat yang harus menonjolkan kualitas positif dan menjelaskan mengapa kamu akan berhasil dalam studi perguruan tinggi. Surat rekomendasi yang baik biasanya ditulis oleh guru atau atasan.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Susun Anggaran Kuliah</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Sayangnya,<a href=\"https://blog.cakap.com/lanjut-kuliah-di-as-atau-inggris-ya-ketahui-dulu-perbedaannya/\"> </a><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/kuliah-di-amerika-bukan-cuman-sekedar-mimpi/\">kuliah di Amerika</a> bisa memakan banyak biaya. Jika kamu merasa perlu bantuan keuangan, hindari ke universitas yang tidak menawarkan bantuan keuangan atau beasiswa kepada siswa internasional. Setiap sekolah akan memiliki instruksi untuk mengajukan beasiswa atau bantuan.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Setelah kamu diterima di universitas pilihan kamu, kamu harus membayar deposit untuk jangka waktu mendatang.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Ajukan Visa Pelajar</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Setelah kamu diterima oleh sekolah atau program SEVP (Student and Exchange Visitor Program), mereka akan mengirimkan formulir I-20 untuk diisi. Dengan formulir itu, kamu dapat mengajukan<a href=\"https://blog.cakap.com/visa-ke-amerika/\"> </a>permohonan visa pelajar kamu secara online. Kemudian, kamu perlu membayar biaya SEVIS dan menjadwalkan wawancara visa kamu.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Setelah semua persiapan ini beres, kamu hanya tinggal berangkat ke Amerika. Mudah bukan?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Apa kamu siap melanjutkan belajar di Amerika? EDUVERSE by ALL-in siap untuk membantu mempersiapkanmu untuk masuk ke universitas-universitas terkenal di Amerika.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Study Abroad</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://landing.mailerlite.com/webforms/landing/p7d6e2\">Beasiswa</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/programs/\">Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Bedah Universitas</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!</p>', '107157486_students8.jpg', 'Belum Tahu Cara Kuliah di Amerika? Cek Di Sini!', 'publish', 'Belum Tahu Cara Kuliah di Amerika? Cek Di Sini!', 'Cara Kuliah di Amerika', 'Apa kamu penasaran cara kuliah di Amerika? Banyak hal yang mesti kamu siapkan sebelum berkuliah di sana. Tapi, kamu bisa mulai dengan hal-hal ini.', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-01-18 17:00:00', '2022-01-27 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(9765, 'kuliah-di-amerika-bukan-cuman-sekedar-mimpi', 2, 0, 'Kuliah di Amerika: Bukan Cuman Sekedar Mimpi!', '<p>Kuliah di Amerika terdengar sebagai sesuatu yang sangat besar dan sulit untuk digapai. Nyatanya, hak tersebut tidak sesulit yang kamu bayangkan. Sudah ada banyak anak Indonesia yang mengenyam pendidikan di Amerika.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kenapa memilih Amerika? Amerika mempunyai kualitas pendidikan yang luar biasa.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/jurusan-kuliah-di-amerika-ini-5-yang-terbaik/\">Jurusan Kuliah di Amerika</a></strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan kuliah di amerika merupakan yang paling beragam dan terbaik. Banyak anak-anak Indonesia yang berusaha keras untuk bisa kuliah di sana. Lalu, Amerika juga menyediakan deretan universitas yang bagus beserta dengan jurusan kuliah yang luar biasa.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Berikut adalah jurusan kuliah di Amerika yang cocok untuk kamu:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>1. <strong>Arsitektur</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan kuliah di Amerika yang satu ini memberikan prospek kerja yang tinggi untuk lulusannya. Pasalnya, kamu akan dipersiapkan dengan ilmu dan lisensi untuk bekerja di banyak negara. Universitas yang memiliki jurusan arsitektur terbaik adalah <em>Harvard University</em>, <em>Columbia University</em>, <em>Massachusetts Institute of Technology, Yale University</em> dan <em>Cornell University</em>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>2. Teknik Informatika.</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Kalian pernah dengar <em>Silicon Valley</em>? Silicon Valley adalah daerah khusus yang berisi perusahaan-perusahaan digital besar seperti Meta, Twitter, Snapchat, dan masih banyak lagi. Beberapa staf di perusahaan besar tersebut berasal dari universitas terkemuka seperti <em>Boston University</em> dan <em>New York Institute of Technology</em>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>3. <strong>Bisnis</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Di jurusan ini, kamu akan belajar banyak tentang cara pengelolaan usaha yang baik. Selain itu, kamu juga akan belajar bagaimana melakukan pembukuan, pemasaran produk, dan pengelolaan keuangan demi keberlangsungan bisnis. Universitas yang cocok untuk kamu yang ingin masuk ke jurusan bisnis adalah <em>NYU Stern School of Business New York University, Boston University (BU) School of Management</em>, dan <em>Columbia Business School (CBS) Columbia University</em>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Penasaran ada jurusan apa lagi di Amerika? Cari tau lebih lengkapnya <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/jurusan-kuliah-di-amerika-ini-5-yang-terbaik/\">di sini</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kuliah di Amerika memerlukan biaya. Biaya ini melingkupi banyak hal mulai dari biaya kuliah dan akomodasi. Ayo kita bedah biaya apa saja yang kamu perlukan untuk kuliah di sana.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/biaya-kuliah-di-amerika-serikat-ini-lengkapnya/\">Biaya Kuliah di Amerika</a></strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Untuk mengetahui lebih lanjut soal biaya kuliah di sana, kita akan membagi menjadi dua bagian yaitu biaya pembayaran kuliah dan akomodasi.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Biaya Akomodasi</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Selain itu, tempat tinggalmu selama berkuliah juga akan mempengaruhi pengeluaranmu. Contohnya, tinggal di dalam kampus tentu saja akan membutuhkan biaya yang lebih besar dibanding tinggal di luar kampus. Lalu, keputusan untuk tinggal sendiri atau bersama teman akan mempengaruhi besarnya biaya untuk tempat tinggal. Pada dasarnya, biaya akomodasi yang perlu kamu keluarkan untuk kuliah di Amerika antara USD $3.000 - USD $8.000 atau sekitar Rp. 43.000.000 - $115.000.000 per tahun.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tapi kamu tidak perlu khawatir, di Amerika banyak menyediakan pekerjaan paruh waktu untuk membantu memenuhi biaya akomodasi dan kuliah di sana. Biasanya kamu akan dibayar per jam dibandingkan per bulan. Kamu bisa bekerja di cafe, restoran cepat saji, sebagai pengantar makanan, pengantar koran, pengasuh anak, atau bekerja di perusahaan agensi kecil.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Biaya Kuliah</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Untuk biaya kuliah di Amerika bervariasi untuk setiap perguruan tinggi. Universitas AS termasuk dalam dua kategori utama: institusi publik, dan swasta (independen). Biaya sekolah siswa internasional di universitas negeri didasarkan pada biaya bukan penduduk, yang biasanya masih lebih murah daripada di universitas swasta. Penting untuk diperhatikan bahwa biaya program di sekolah AS tidak selalu mempengaruhi kualitasnya. Biaya pembayaran kuliah di sana bervariasi mulai dari $6,000 - $19,000.</p>\n\n\n\n<p> Cari tau lebih lengkap <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/biaya-kuliah-di-amerika-serikat-ini-lengkapnya/\">di sini</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Walaupun biayanya cukup mahal, kamu tidak perlu berkecil hati untuk bisa kuliah di sana. Nyatanya, banyak universitas di Amerika yang menyediakan beasiswa untuk mahasiswa internasional.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/beasiswa-kuliah-di-amerika-ini-wajib-kamu-coba/\">Beasiswa Kuliah di Amerika</a></strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Sudah banyak yang bilang bahwa biaya kuliah di Amerika itu tidak murah. Dengan biaya kuliah yang mencapai puluhan ribu dolar, belum lagi ditambah biaya hidup, impian untuk belajar di Amerika tampaknya tidak masuk akal.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Untungnya, terdapat banyak beasiswa yang ditawarkan oleh beberapa universitas untuk mendukung siswa internasional agar mereka dapat melanjutkan pendidikan di universitas impian mereka.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Michigan State University - International Tuition Grant</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Dengan komunitas yang berjumlah lebih dari 49 ribu siswa, <em>Michigan State University </em>menawarkan beasiswa ini sebesar $25,000 USD, $21,000 USD, atau $18,000 USD per tahun selama delapan semester. Beberapa faktor yang dipertimbangkan untuk mendapatkan beasiswa ini termasuk kinerja akademik, esai aplikasi, kemahiran bahasa Inggris, keterlibatan dalam aktivitas, dan keragaman geografis. Persaingan untuk mendapat beasiswa ini cukup ketat dan kompetitif, dengan hanya siswa di 5% teratas di kumpulan pelamar yang diberikan beasiswa tertinggi.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>American University - Merit Awards</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Didirikan oleh John Fletcher Hurst pada tahun 1893, <em>American University</em> menawarkan beasiswa parsial ini bagi mahasiswa internasional yang berprestasi. Beasiswa ini diberikan agar dapat meringankan biaya kuliah mahasiswa internasional. Untungnya, beasiswa ini dapat diperbarui selama empat tahun studi jika kinerja akademik dipertahankan!</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Oregon State University - Provost\'s Scholarships for Excellence</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Selanjutnya, beasiswa kuliah ini ditawarkan oleh Oregon State University, salah satu universitas riset publik terbesar di Amerika Serikat. Beasiswa ini menyediakan potongan uang kuliah sebesar $6,000 USD per tahun, dimana dapat berlangsung selama studi jika GPA diatas 3,0.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi mengenai beasiswa kuliah <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/beasiswa-kuliah-di-amerika-ini-wajib-kamu-coba/\">di sini</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sekarang kita kan pergi ke bagian yang terpenting yaitu cara kuliah di sana. Seperti yang banyak orang tau, kuliah di negera adidaya ini memerlukan kita untuk melalui beberapa tahap.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/belum-tahu-cara-kuliah-di-amerika-cek-di-sini/\">Cara Kuliah di Amerika</a></strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Kuliah di Amerika merupakan cita-cita banyak pelajar di Indonesia. Mungkin banyak pelajar yang tidak tau, tapi cara kuliah di sana itu tidak sesulit yang kita bayangkan lho. Berikut adalah langkah-langkah yang bisa kamu lakukan agar bisa berkuliah di sana.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Riset Universitas</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Hal pertama yang harus kamu lakukan adalah melakukan riset universitas. Seperti yang kita tau, Amerika mempunyai banyak universitas dengan kualitas pendidikan yang luar biasa. Kamu harus pintar memilih universitas mana yang mempunyai jurusan yang sesuai dengan minat dan kemampuanmu.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Daftar dan Ikuti Tes Penerimaan</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Setelah melakukan riset, hal yang bisa kamu lakukan selanjutnya adalah untuk mendaftar dan mengikuti tes penerimaan. Secara umum, berikut adalah persyaratan umum untuk masuk universitas di Amerika:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li><strong>Resume</strong></li><li><strong>SAT or ACT</strong></li><li><strong>IELTS or TOEFL</strong></li><li><strong><em>Admission Essay</em></strong></li><li><strong>Surat Rekomendasi</strong></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Susun Anggaran Kuliah</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Sayangnya, kuliah di negeri Paman Sam bisa memakan banyak biaya. Jika kamu merasa perlu bantuan keuangan, hindari ke universitas yang tidak menawarkan bantuan keuangan atau beasiswa kepada siswa internasional.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Ajukan Visa Pelajar</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Setelah kamu diterima oleh sekolah atau program SEVP (Student and Exchange Visitor Program), mereka akan mengirimimu formulir I-20 untuk diisi.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Untuk mengetahui lebih lengkap tentang cara kuliah di Amerika, kamu bisa membacanya <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/belum-tahu-cara-kuliah-di-amerika-cek-di-sini/\">di sini</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Setelah mengetahui beberapa hal penting di atas, tentunya kamu menjadi semakin percaya diri untuk kuliah di Amerika dong!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kalau kamu tertarik untuk memulai perjalan akademikmu di luar negeri, kamu bisa mempersiapkannya bersama EDUVERSE by ALL-in Eduspace.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi seputar:</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Study Abroad</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Beasiswa</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Bedah Universitas&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!</p>', 'American_University_Gallery_campus_student.jpg', 'Kuliah di Amerika: Bukan Cuman Sekedar Mimpi!', 'publish', '', 'Kuliah di Amerika', 'Kuliah di Amerika merupakan mimpi banyak pelajar di seluruh dunia. Inilah beberapa hal yang harus kamu ketahui jika kamu mau kuliah di Amerika.', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-01-21 17:00:00', '2022-01-04 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00');
