(10890, 'front-end-developer-what-is-it', 7, 0, 'Front End Developer: What is it?', '<p>You\'ve probably looked at a website and wondered why it looked like that, how every button works, and perhaps asked yourself, ‘How can all this be done?\' Well, everything that shows up on your screen is built by a Front End developer! Do you know what it is? Let\'s find out!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>What is a Front End Developer?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Everything you see on a website, like buttons, links, animations, and graphics, was the product of Front End development, which is the programming and management of the visible parts (such as web pages and user interfaces) of a website or mobile application. Furthermore, it ensures the visual elements of a web page are functional and presented with a user-friendly interface.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The people behind it are called Front End developers. A Front End Developer is a software engineer who creates websites and applications using coding languages such as HTML, CSS, and JavaScript so that a user can access and interact with the web page or application.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>HTML (HyperText Markup Language)</strong> is a mark-up language that makes a web page readable by a web browser. Moreover, it takes care of all of the structure and displays the content on a web page including buttons, links, headings, paragraphs, and lists.</li><li><strong>CSS (Cascading Style Sheets)</strong> is a style-sheet language that is responsible for how the HTML looks on a web page. CSS controls the colors, fonts, background images, alignments, and the way the page is laid out.&nbsp;</li><li><strong>JavaScript (JS) </strong>is a programming language that allows web developers to build interactive and dynamic web pages. Furthermore, it is applicable to online games, web pages, and mobile applications, where it can update and change HTML and CSS.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>The job outlook for a Front End developer</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>From a 2020 survey conducted by Stack Overflow, Front End Developers in the United States made an average of $110,000 per year. However, factors such as education level, experience, or certifications may affect the earning rate.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Front End Developer job will continue growing in the coming years. According to the US Bureau of Labor Statistics, employment of web developers in the United States will grow at a rate of 13% from 2020 to 2030, which is well above the overall average of 8% for all occupations. There will be an average of 17,900 job openings each year over the decade.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Careers as Front End Developer</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are some common front end developer job titles:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Web designer.</li><li>User Experience (UX) designer.</li><li>User Interface (UI) designer.</li><li>CSS/HTML developer.</li><li>Front end testing engineer.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>As a Front End Developer, you\'ll use a lot of combinations. Moreover, those combinations are design, technology, and coding to ensure that the web page is easy to navigate and accessible for the user. Therefore, your responsibilities could include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Using coding to bring a concept to life.</li><li>Producing and implementing a website or application\'s visual elements.</li><li>Incorporating responsive design into the user interface of a website or application.</li><li>Usability testing and fixing any bugs for the website or application.</li><li>Maintaining software workflow management.</li><li>Modifying the user interfaces of websites and applications.</li><li>Collaborating with back-end developers.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>In a fast-moving industry like Front End Development, staying on top of the game means that you should never stop learning. With the demand for this profession constantly increasing, as well as with new technologies and software, it\'s important to always polish your skills in order to stand out among the others.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ready to be a Front End <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/developer-career-overview/\">Developer</a>? Prepare yourself with ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top uni preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/allineduspace/\">ALL-in Eduspace</a>! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'm-tavpRm_8QRcHCy6EbT6sIMD4qXzDTflE68EEWQJCClGu1SRXnW4BkrIbWIZ7b7GpW23b8EuICQYXzWj5Ua-HigbUth8KWh0gGs.jpeg', 'Front End Developer: What is it?', 'publish', '', 'Front End Developer', 'Do you want to be a Front End Developer? Read this article and find out all aspect from definition to the job outlook in the future.', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-04-04 17:00:00', '2022-04-16 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(10911, 'get-to-know-software-developer-career', 7, 0, 'Get to Know Software Developer Career', '<p>Have you ever wondered what it would be like to become a tech-oriented software developer? There\'s no doubt that it requires a unique set of skills and abilities that are hard to find. What are some of the skills needed to work as a software developer? How competitive is the job market for software developers? And what does a developer do on the job? It\'s time to find out all you need to know!<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>What is a software developer?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Software developers are the creative minds behind software products, and they also have the technical skills to construct or supervise a team\'s development. They provide software that allows users to complete specific tasks on computers.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Believe it or not, you will do a lot of research that requires you to do a lot of fun things. Therefore, you will do things like benchmarking and using how other apps operate or watching series to keep in touch with trends and behaviour. Moreover, this is to give you a lot of references and ideas for your games. Furthermore, almost every profession, industry, and government department needs good specialized software.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Software development is a constant work in progress. Therefore, you need to be proficient in multiple programming languages in order to stand out from the other software developers. Some popular programming languages include C/C++, C#, PHP, Kotlin, Swift, Go, Ruby, Objective C, Rust and Lua.&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Job outlook for a software developer</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>According to the US Department of Labor, the software developer job is on the rise. From 2020 to 2030, the employment of software engineers, quality assurance analysts, and testers is expected to expand by 22%, which is substantially faster than the national average.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Over the next ten years, an average of 189,200 jobs for software engineers, quality assurance analysts, and testers are expected. Many of those positions are likely to arise as a result of the need to replace people who change occupations or leave the workforce for other reasons, such as retirement.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Careers besides software developer</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are some careers you can pursue as software developer:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Applications developer</li><li>Cyber security analyst</li><li>Game developer</li><li>Information systems manager</li><li>IT consultant</li><li>Multimedia programmer</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>As a software developer, you\'ll work on coding and use a programming language. Moreover, this is to ensure that the software is easy to navigate and accessible for the user. Depending on the job, your responsibilities could include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Work with developers to design algorithms and flowcharts.</li><li>Produce clean, efficient code based on specifications.</li><li>Integrate software components and third-party programs.</li><li>Verify and deploy programs and systems.</li><li>Troubleshoot, debug and upgrade existing software.</li><li>Gather and evaluate user feedback.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Software development as a career path is one of the hottest fields right now, and it\'s not hard to see why. Software developers have the power to solve some of the world\'s most complex problems, and can do so in a number of different roles. Furthermore, if you love to code and you want to build amazing things for the world, getting into software development may just be one of your best bets for making that happen.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Interested in becoming a software <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/developer-career-overview/\">developer</a>? ALL-in will help you prepare your way to reach your dream!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top uni preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/allineduspace/\">ALL-in Eduspace</a>! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'p7lluf4etLDCAdTutq_Hs8snUGu0zk27F9OutV-ZHL3VZKBrBtPVEBr1j4BEPkfl0w1SrRd_sN2qOyAr9wKDJC2GRYfNlPED8e9b.jpeg', 'Get to Know Software Developer Career', 'publish', 'Get to Know Software Developer Career. Read this Article to Find Out', 'Software Developer', 'Do you have a dream to become a software developer? Read this article to find out aspects, perks, and the job outlook of the career!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-04-03 17:00:00', '2022-04-05 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(10914, 'back-end-developer-heres-what-you-should-know', 7, 0, 'Back End Developer: Here’s What You Should Know!', '<p>Websites are everywhere in our lives—from online shopping, entertainment, to social media—but did you ever wonder what goes on behind the scenes? If a site loads in less than half the time it used to, do you ever wonder how it works? It\'s all down to the magic of back end developers.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Not sure what a back end developer is? Without further ado, let\'s find out!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>What is a Back End Developer?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Unlike front end developers, who focus primarily on the visual elements of a website or application, a back end developer is responsible for creating and managing all of the components that make up the ‘back end,\' or hidden portions of an application.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The back end contains all of the behind-the-scenes activities that occur when performing any action on a website, including all of the functionality that happens on the ‘server side\'. It makes use of the three main components of web development: the server, application, and database.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Server </strong>represents a computer or program that provides services to other computers or programs in the same network</li><li><strong>Application </strong>is software that runs on a device and uses the information provided by the server to display information on a screen</li><li><strong>Database </strong>is a collection of organized data stored in one location. It can be either structured (organized into rows and columns) or unstructured (freely associated).</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>A back end developer is responsible for creating and maintaining the code, which helps browsers communicate with information stored in databases.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here\'s a little scenario. Let\'s say you\'re shopping online for a shirt and decide to purchase it. You enter in all of your information including your credit card number, the size of the shirt, and then you hit the ‘submit\' button. Furthermore, the front end of that website, the part you can see and interact with, sends your information to the back end where it gets stored in the server\'s database.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The back end is responsible for storing all of the information in a database. It\'s also responsible for making sure that when you go back to visit that same website in a week\'s time, all of that information is still there for you.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Job outlook for a back end developer</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>According to Payscale, the average salary for back end developers in the United States is about $87,000. The salary ranges from $54,000 to $131,000, depending on experience, skillset, and location.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Careers in back end development&nbsp;</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are some common back end developer job titles:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Back end engineer</li><li>SQL developer&nbsp;</li><li>Software development engineer</li><li>Software architect</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Depending on the job, your duties as a back end developer may include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Building and maintaining web applications</li><li>Managing and creating functional APIs resources&nbsp;</li><li>Implementing and writing code to solve system-related problems&nbsp;</li><li>Creating testable, well-designed, and efficient code</li><li>Building frameworks and managing hosting environments&nbsp;</li><li>Analyzing data, processes, and codes</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>It\'s no secret that in this digital age, back end development is an emerging field. With so many opportunities and technological advancement, it can be challenging to keep up. Hence it\'s important to learn new programming languages and coding techniques, apart from using well-known frameworks.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Thinking of becoming a back end <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/developer-career-overview/\">developer</a>? Let\'s make it become true with ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top uni preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/allineduspace/\">ALL-in Eduspace</a>! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!</p>', 'FaeIsXaP2vNIHhk7_BDWBd7skau_EYA_YA-l8_yiVh7pvjumo7j0S8yn4Q_b07fXLZYad697OlO61gz2I2LH1naDEVcHmndcuHMt.jpeg', 'Back End Developer: Here’s What You Should Know!', 'publish', '', 'Back End Developer', 'Back end developer is an up and coming career in the future. If you have a huge interest on becoming one, this article is perfect for you.', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-04-02 17:00:00', '2022-04-13 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(10919, 'understanding-full-stack-developer-career', 7, 0, 'Understanding Full Stack Developer Career', '<p>A Full Stack Developer is a person who has developed a complete set of skills that allows them to develop beautiful, modern, and highly scalable websites from the ground up. As demand for full stack developers grows with increasing applications in use, there are thousands of people who are looking for jobs in this field. If you are also considering a career as a full stack developer, here is what you need to know about the profession.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>What is a Full Stack Developer?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>When we are talking about Full Stack Developer, we are talking about someone who works on both Front End (client side) and Back End (server side). To be a successful Full Stack Developer, you need to have a wide range of coding specialities, and skills from managing databases to graphic design and UI/UX management.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In the developer team, this job is the jack of all trades. A full stack developer is someone who is comfortable working or concurrently serving as a back end and front end developer. More specifically, developers can work with Javascript, PHP, databases (backend) and can also convert designs into programming code such as HTML, CSS, XML (front end).</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you\'re interested in being a full stack developer, it\'s important to learn the tricks of the trade. Sharpen your technical strengths and improve your resume by developing your proficiency with these tools and skills:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Front End programming languages like HTML, Javascript, and CSS (if you\'re a beginner, you can start with these free tutorials to learn JavaScript core notions and design your first website)</li><li>Back end programming languages like Javascript. Python, Ruby, and PHP</li><li>Version control systems like Git and GitHub</li><li>APIs like REST and SOAP as well as protocol like HTTP</li><li>Database storage solutions like JSON, SQL, and NoSQL</li><li>Graphic design and visual communication skills</li><li>Apache or nginx servers</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Job outlook</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Between 2019 and 2029, the US Bureau of Labor Statistics anticipates an increase of 8% in job opportunities for web developers and a staggering 22% for software developers in the United States. The ability to build and maintain a system from start to finish, from Front End to Back End, is highly regarded. Right now, it\'s safe to assume that full stack developers are in high demand.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Careers besides full stack developer</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>When you become a full stack developer you can jump into more specialised careers such as front end or back end. The other option is you can pursue your career to a senior level and become a CTO of a company.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Depending on the job, your duties as a full stack developerr may include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Build scalable and robust APIs and systems.</li><li>Build reusable code and libraries for future use.</li><li>Optimize code and application for maximum speed and scalability.</li><li>Ensure stability and performance of the system.</li><li>Implement security and data protection.</li><li>Identify and fix bottlenecks and bugs on the system.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Full stack developers may comprise a small percentage of the overall development community. But, their importance in the field grows every day. It\'s not hard to imagine why. The reason is more of us conduct more of our business online. Therefore, we need full stack developers to help build the tools that will keep us functioning smoothly and efficiently.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dare to dream and become a full stack <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/developer-career-overview/\">developer</a>? Prepare to explore your career with ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top uni preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/allineduspace/\">ALL-in Eduspace</a>! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'JCOOHENyHw048r8Sgqd798ulBgQ2hhbPMuXo1l2dVHUMdWdZKVD4PHUN6jsosLOFLiAugk-F3Z9aNiSxH00kLv13HGaB34L-BrNa.jpeg', 'Understanding Full Stack Developer Career', 'publish', 'Understanding Full Stack Developer Career', 'Full Stack Developer', 'Full stack developer is the one of the best career out there, are you interested on becoming one? Read this article to find out everything about the job!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-04-01 17:00:00', '2022-04-26 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(10922, 'developer-career-overview', 7, 0, 'Developer: Career Overview', '<p>When you think about a “developer,” what is the first thing that comes to mind? The word developer is pretty broad, but it basically refers to someone who builds website or software using code. But there\'s much more to it than that.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For instance, there are different kinds of programming developers. A front end developer is someone who creates websites using HTML/CSS, JavaScript, PHP or Ruby on Rails. A software developer is someone who writes code in Java, C++ or Objective-C, while a back end developer is someone who works with systems and databases to create online applications.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This article will give you a glimpse of every part that makes up a developer.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Front End Developer</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Everything you see on a website, like buttons, links, animations, and graphics, was the product of front end development, which is the programming and management of the visible parts (such as web pages and user interfaces) of a website or mobile application. It ensures the visual elements of a web page are functional and being presented with a user-friendly interface.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The people behind it are called <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/front-end-developer-what-is-it/\">front end developers</a>. A front end developer is a software engineer who creates websites and applications using coding languages such as HTML, CSS, and JavaScript so that a user can access and interact with the web page or application. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Job outlook for a front end developer</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>From a 2020 survey conducted by Stack Overflow, front end developers in the United States made an average of $110,000 per year. However, factors such as education level, experience, or certifications may affect the earning rate.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Front end development is expected to continue growing in the coming years. According to the US Bureau of Labor Statistics, employment of web developers in the United States is projected to grow at a rate of 13% from 2020 to 2030, which is well above the overall average of 8% for all occupations. It is also estimated that there will be an average of 17,900 job openings each year over the decade.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color has-vivid-cyan-blue-color\"><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/front-end-developer-what-is-it/\">Interested to know more about this career? Read it in this article!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Back End Developer</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Unlike front end developers, who focus primarily on the visual elements of a website or application, a back end developer is responsible for creating and managing all of the components that make up the ‘back end,\' or hidden portions of an application.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The back end contains all of the behind-the-scenes activities that occur when performing any action on a website, including all of the functionality that happens on the ‘server side\'. It makes use of the three main components of web development: the server, application, and database.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Job outlook for a back end developer</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>According to Payscale, the average salary for <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/back-end-developer-heres-what-you-should-know/\">back end developers</a> in the United States is about $87,000. The salary ranges from $54,000 to $131,000, depending on experience, skillset, and location.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color has-vivid-cyan-blue-color\"><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/back-end-developer-heres-what-you-should-know/\">Read this article to find out more!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Full Stack Developer</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/understanding-full-stack-developer-career/\">Full Stack Developer</a> is someone who works on both the Back End (server side) and the Front End (client side) of an application. To execute their job properly, Full Stack Developers must have some knowledge of a wide range of coding specialties, from databases to graphic design and UI/UX management.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In the developer team, a full stack developer is the jack of all trades. A full stack developer is someone who is comfortable working or concurrently serving as a back end and front end developer. More specifically, developers can work with javascript, PHP, java, databases (backend) and can also convert designs into programming code such as HTML, CSS, XML (front end).</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Job outlook for a full stack developer</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Between 2019 and 2029, the US Bureau of Labor Statistics anticipates an increase by 8% in job opportunities for web developers and a staggering 22% for software developers in the United States. Ability to build and maintain a system from start to finish, from frontend to backend, is highly regarded. Right now, it\'s safe to assume that full stack developers are in high demand.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>When you become a full stack developer you can also jump into adjacent careers such as front end developer or back end developer. The other option is you can pursue your career to a senior level and become a CTO of a company.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color has-vivid-cyan-blue-color\"><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/understanding-full-stack-developer-career/\">Want to be a full stack developer? Read here for more info!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Software Developer</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/get-to-know-software-developer-career/\">Software developers</a> are the creative minds behind software products, and they also have the technical skills to construct or supervise a team\'s development. They provide software that allows users to complete specific tasks on computers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Believe it or not, you will do a lot of research that requires you to do a lot of fun things. Like benchmarking and using how other apps operates or watching series to keep in touch with trends and behaviour. This is to give you a lot of reference and ideas for your games. Furthermore, almost every profession, industry, and government department needs a good specialized software.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Job outlook for a software developer</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>According to the US Department of Labor, the software developer job is on the rise. From 2020 to 2030, employment of software engineers, quality assurance analysts, and testers is going to expand by 22%, substantially faster than the national average.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Over the next ten years, an average of 189,200 jobs for software engineers, quality assurance analysts, and testers are expected. Many of those positions are likely to arise as a result of the need to replace people who change occupations or leave the workforce for other reasons, such as retirement.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color has-vivid-cyan-blue-color\"><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/get-to-know-software-developer-career/\">Dreaming to become a software developer? Find out more in this article!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>While there are certainly job prospects for developers in the near future, one thing is clear: a developer career is on the rise. We just learned that there are a lot of types of developers and which one you want to be is entirely up to you. Therefore, if you really want to be a developer, you need to prepare from today.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Want to study in the best uni and be a developer in the future? ALL-in will help prepare you for uni admissions!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top uni preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/allineduspace/\">ALL-in Eduspace</a>! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'py7NIzt6IwtYsGZZn97lXmdApo_qTpxjsRfdljXJbB3nfXbcNahJSv3jXHIPEa21CNvkkk0OkV2N1IDgtCbmePdnRml05fRRSP9F.jpeg', 'Developer: Career Overview', 'publish', 'Developer: Career Overview, Details, & Career Prospects', 'Developer', 'Developer is one of the most up and coming field out there. There are a lot of career choices in this field. Read this article to find out!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-03-31 17:00:00', '2022-04-02 17:00:00', '2022-10-26 17:00:00'),
(10927, 'dokter-gigi-profesi-di-balik-sebuah-senyuman', 8, 0, 'Dokter Gigi: Profesi di Balik Sebuah Senyuman', '<p>Apa kamu pernah membayangkan menjadi orang yang dapat membantu orang lain untuk tersenyum dengan indah? Itulah tugas dari seorang dokter gigi. Profesi yang satu ini dapat membantu orang lain untuk menjadi lebih percaya diri dan membantu mengobati banyak penyakit dan masalah gigi.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Untuk kamu yang belum tahu, susunan gigi bukanlah sebuah hal yang sederhana. Di dalam gigi terdapat ratusan syaraf yang terhubung ke otak dan hampir ke seluruh tubuh. Maka dari itu, kamu tidak boleh sembarangan dalam mengatasi masalah gigi. Kamu memerlukan bantuan professional untuk menyelesaikannya.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Seorang profesional yang akan membantumu mengenai masalah gigi disebut Dokter Gigi.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Apa itu Dokter Gigi?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Dokter gigi adalah seorang dokter yang secara khusus mempelajari ilmu kesehatan dan penyakit pada gigi dan mulut. Profesi ini memiliki keahlian dan kompetensi dalam mendiagnosis, mengobati, dan memberikan edukasi tentang pengobatan dan pencegahan berbagai masalah kesehatan gigi, gusi, dan mulut.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Pendidikan Dokter Gigi</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Tingkat pendidikan dan pelatihan klinis yang diperlukan untuk memperoleh gelar kedokteran gigi tidaklah mudah. Seperti yang kita tahu, standar sekolah kedokteran gigi sangatlah tinggi. Lulusannya harus sudah mahir dalam praktik perawatan kesehatan mulut modern yang aman dan efektif. Sebagian besar mahasiswa kedokteran gigi telah memperoleh gelar <em>Bachelor of Science</em> atau yang setara, dan semuanya telah lulus ujian penerimaan yang ketat.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kurikulum selama dua tahun pertama sekolah kedokteran gigi dan kedokteran pada dasarnya sama – siswa harus menyelesaikan mata kuliah ilmu biomedis seperti anatomi, biokimia, fisiologi, mikrobiologi, imunologi, dan patologi.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Selama dua tahun kedua, mahasiswa jurusan kedokteran gigi berfokus pada praktik klinis – mendiagnosis dan mengobati penyakit mulut. Setelah mendapatkan gelar sarjana dan kedokteran gigi (<strong>paling lama delapan tahun</strong>), banyak dokter gigi melanjutkan pendidikan dan pelatihan mereka untuk mencapai sertifikasi di salah satu dari sembilan spesialisasi gigi yang diakui.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Setelah menyelesaikan pelatihan mereka, mereka harus lulus ujian tertulis nasional yang ketat dan ujian lisensi klinis untuk dapat berpraktik. Sebagai syarat lisensi, mereka harus memenuhi persyaratan pendidikan berkelanjutan untuk sisa karir mereka, agar mereka tetap up-to-date pada perkembangan ilmiah dan klinis terbaru.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Universitas Kedokteran Gigi Terbaik di Dunia</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ada banyak universitas yang menawarkan program kedokteran gigi. Tapi, jika kamu tertarik untuk menjadi dokter gigi terbaik, kamu harus masuk ke sekolah yang terbaik pula. Berikut adalah daftar universitas kedokteran gigi terbaik di dunia menurut QS World Ranking:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>University of Gothenburg, Swedia</li><li>University of Michigan-Ann Arbor, US</li><li>Academic Centre for Dentistry Amsterdam (ACTA), Belanda</li><li>The University of Hong Kong, Hong Kong</li><li>King\'s College London, UK</li><li>Tokyo Medical and Dental University, Jepang</li><li>University of California, San Francisco, US</li><li>Harvard University, US</li><li>University of Bern, Swiss</li><li>Karolinska Institutet, Swedia</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Spesialisasi Dokter Gigi</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Spesialis gigi adalah dokter gigi yang menerima pelatihan tambahan dalam spesialisasi gigi tertentu di luar gelar kedokteran gigi umum mereka. Orang-orang mungkin akan memerlukan bantuan spesialis, entah karena masalah tertentu atau karena faktor keturunan.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Berikut adalah 6 spesialisasi dokter gigi yang mungkin akan kamu temui di hidupmu:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Ahli Bedah Mulut dan Maksilofasial</li><li>Endodontist - Spesialis Konservasi Gigi</li><li>Orthodontist - Spesialis Perbaikan Posisi Gigi</li><li>Pediatric Dentist - Spesialis Gigi Anak</li><li>Periodontist - Spesialis Gusi</li><li>Prosthodontist - Spesialis Gigi Tiruan</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Prospek Kerja di Masa Depan</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Menurut <em>US Department of Labor</em>. Pekerjaan keseluruhan profesi ini diproyeksikan tumbuh 8 persen dari tahun 2020 hingga 2030. Pertumbuhan ini kira-kira secepat pertumbuhan rata-rata untuk semua pekerjaan.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Setiap tahunnya, akan ada sekitar 5.000 lowongan yang terbuka untuk profesi ini. Banyak dari lowongan tersebut diharapkan dihasilkan dari kebutuhan untuk mengganti pekerja yang pindah ke pekerjaan lain atau yang keluar dari pekerjaannya seperti pensiun.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dokter gigi merupakan profesi yang luar biasa. Selain banyak peminatnya, profesi ini juga sangat bermanfaat bagi orang banyak. Hal ini karena tidak semua orang paham mengenai pentingnya kesehatan gigi dan cara penanganan yang baik.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tertarik masuk ke jurusan <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/dokter-penjelasan-dan-spesialisasi/\">dokter</a> gigi terbaik di dunia? EDUVERSE by ALL-in akan memandu persiapan mu!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita:<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/edu.verse_/?hl=en\"> @edu.verse</a> dan join Telegram:<a href=\"http://t.me/Allineduverse\"> t.me/Allineduverse</a> untuk diskusi sama expert!<br></p>', 'E_WBjQWhWJAYdk7k-JZ8lSls2QRtLi6HmsLAaXIJN_URtBNO9BVf3qMHfBksIH3KimXxBiA6KZuJ8JSdj0PJtopFgHahAg1PK_qL.jpeg', 'Dokter Gigi: Profesi di Balik Sebuah Senyuman', 'publish', '', 'Dokter Gigi', 'Apa kamu punya mimpi untuk menjadi dokter gigi? Berikut adalah beberapa hal yang perlu kamu tahu sebelum melanjuktkan ke pendidikan dokter gigi.', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-03-21 17:00:00', '2022-04-12 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(10931, 'dokter-hewan-si-paling-ngerti-hewan', 8, 0, 'Dokter Hewan: Si Paling Ngerti Hewan', '<p>Bagi kamu yang pecinta hewan, pasti kamu lumayan akrab nih dengan profesi yang satu ini. Dokter hewan adalah seseorang yang kamu kunjungi sebulan sekali untuk memeriksa kesehatan anabul milikmu di rumah. Mari kita mengenal profesi ini dengan lebih dekat!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dokter hewan telah menjadi profesi yang terkenal di kalangan pelajar saat ini. Hal ini karena semakin banyak orang yang tertarik untuk mempunyai hewan peliharaan. Maka dari itu pula, permintaan untuk profesi ini pun kian bertambah dari hari ke hari.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Apa itu Dokter Hewan?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Dokter hewan adalah sebuah profesi yang&nbsp; bertugas mencegah, memeriksa, mengobati, dan melakukan perawatan pada hewan dari penyakit.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ketika mengambil sumpah, mereka bersumpah dengan sungguh-sungguh untuk menggunakan pengetahuan dan keterampilan ilmiahnya untuk kepentingan masyarakat, melalui perlindungan kesehatan hewan, pengurangan penderitaan hewan, konservasi sumber daya hewan, peningkatan kesehatan masyarakat, dan kemajuan pengetahuan medis.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dalam satu dan banyak hal, profesi mempunyai kemiripan dengan dokter anak. Hewan tidak bisa mengungkapkan apa yang salah dengan mereka atau yang mereka rasakan dengan kata-kata, seperti halnya bayi dan balita. Oleh karena itu, sebagian besar riwayat medis para hewan peliharaan didapat dari pemiliknya, seperti yang diperoleh dokter anak dari orang tua.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Spesialisasi Praktisi Dokter Hewan</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Dokter hewan adalah salah satu profesi yang mempunyai banyak spesialisasi. Hal ini karena hewan mempunyai banyak variasi. Organ-organ yang membentuk tubuh hewan ada yang sama dengan manusia, ada juga yang berbeda. Organ pembentuk tubuh ini berbeda mengikuti apakah jenis hewan tersebut adalah unggas, ikan, mamalia, atau reptil.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Spesialisasi praktisi dokter hewan tersebut adalah:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Avian (Burung/Unggas)</li><li>Feline (Kucing)</li><li>Cattle (Hewan Ternak)</li><li>Reptile (Reptil)</li><li>Canine (Anjing)</li><li>Equine (Kuda)</li><li>Exotic Animal Companion (Hewan Eksotis)</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Pendidikan Dokter Hewan</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Untuk menjadi dokter hewan, kamu harus mendapatkan gelar Doctor of Veterinary Medicine (D.V.M.) di perguruan tinggi terakreditasi. Untuk menjadi kandidat masuk&nbsp;untuk sekolah dokter hewan, sebagian besar pelajar harus menyelesaikan gelar sarjana sebelum mendaftar. Sekolah yang memeriksa aplikasi kandidat dan menilai apakah kandidat tersebut cocok. Oleh karena itu, mereka akan mencari mahasiswa yang telah mengambil mata kuliah biologi, kimia, zoologi, atau mata kuliah terkait lainnya.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Untuk menyelesaikan program kedokteran hewan, kamu akan membutuhkan waktu sekitar 4 tahun. Selama empat tahun tersebut, kamu akan memiliki ruang kelas, lab, dan komponen klinis. Seiring dengan mata kuliah matematika, humaniora, dan sains, program ini mungkin juga memiliki mata kuliah manajemen bisnis dan pengembangan karir.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Semua mata kuliah ini berguna untuk mempersiapkan lulusan kedokteran hewan baru untuk mengelola praktik mereka pribadi. Kurikulum dimaksudkan untuk memastikan kamu adalah seorang praktisi kedokteran hewan yang sukses dan siap untuk lulus ujian lisensi dokter hewan.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Universitas Terbaik</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ada banyak universitas yang menawarkan program kedokteran hewan. Untuk bisa mendapatkan ilmu terbaik seputar ilmu kesehatan untuk hewan, kamu juga harus masuk ke universitas terbaik di dunia. Berikut adalah daftar universitas kedokteran hewan terbaik di dunia menurut QS World Ranking:<br></p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Royal Veterinary College, University of London, UK</li><li>University of California, Davis, US</li><li>Utrecht University, Belanda</li><li>The University of Edinburgh, UK</li><li>Cornell University, US</li><li>University of Guelph, Canada</li><li>The Ohio State University, US</li><li>University of Cambridge, UK</li><li>University of Copenhagen, Denmark</li><li>Vetsuisse Faculty Bern and Zurich, Swiss</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Prospek Kerja di Masa Depan</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Menurut <em>US Department of Labor</em>, profesi ini diproyeksikan akan tumbuh 17 persen dari 2020 hingga 2030, jauh lebih cepat daripada pertumbuhan rata-rata untuk semua pekerjaan.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Selama satu dekade ini, kira-kira akan ada sekitar 4.400 lowongan untuk profesi ini diproyeksikan setiap tahun. Banyak dari lowongan tersebut dihasilkan dari kebutuhan untuk mengganti pekerja yang pindah ke pekerjaan lain atau keluar dari kerja, seperti pensiun.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Prospek kerja yang tinggi membuat jurusan kedokteran hewan ini banyak peminatnya. Tidak sembarang orang bisa bertahan di jurusan ini. Kamu harus menjadi seseorang yang memang mencintai hewan agar cocok di profesi ini.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tertarik menjadi <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/dokter-penjelasan-dan-spesialisasi/\">dokter</a> hewan? Ayo persiapkan untuk karir masa depanmu bersama EDUVERSE by ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita:<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/edu.verse_/?hl=en\"> @edu.verse</a> dan join Telegram:<a href=\"http://t.me/Allineduverse\"> t.me/Allineduverse</a> untuk diskusi sama expert!</p>', 'vmpJDquePivT_pTuYQaxBEk_jiquGAmrK1OnTThorqxFv_VKhqyLCkmaA7C0VPRMyZrkX3rgXfwWJ_3UfgJUUdupOAEHBmjQSFDk.jpeg', 'Dokter Hewan: Si Paling Ngerti Hewan', 'publish', '', 'Dokter Hewan', 'Apa kamu salah satu pecinta hewan? Itu artinya kamu salah satu orang yang cocok untuk menjadi dokter hewan. Tertarik? Baca lengkapnya di sini!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-03-20 17:00:00', '2022-04-15 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(10936, 'membedah-profesi-dokter-kulit', 8, 0, 'Membedah Profesi Dokter Kulit', '<p>Dokter kulit merupakan salah satu profesi yang mungkin jarang diminati di kalangan anak muda. Hal ini menyebabkan jumlah dokter kulit yang tidak sebanyak <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/dokter-penjelasan-dan-spesialisasi/\">dokter</a> lainnya. Maka dari itu, profesi ini merupakan profesi yang belum banyak pesaingnya. Tertarik? Ayo baca lebih lengkap di bawah ini!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Apa itu Dokter Kulit?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Dermatologis adalah praktisi medis yang berspesialisasi dalam kesehatan kulit. Mereka memeriksa pasien dengan kondisi kulit dan meninjau kemajuan perawatan dermatologis.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dokter kulit mendiagnosis masalah kulit, dari yang ringan (misalnya terbakar sinar matahari) hingga yang parah (misalnya kanker kulit). Mereka melakukan pemeriksaan dan evaluasi kulit, dan menganalisis riwayat medis pasien untuk menentukan perawatan yang tepat. Dermatologis juga mengawasi seberapa efektif perawatan dan merujuk pasien ke spesialis yang berbeda jika diperlukan.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Spesialisasi Dokter Kulit</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Profesi ini merupakan salah satu spesialis kedokteran yang paling penting. Kulit kita terdiri dari banyak syarat dan struktur yang sangat rumit. Belum lagi ada kulit sensitif yang memerlukan bantuan khusus dari ahli. Maka dari itu, dibentuklah sub-spesialis untuk dokter kulit. Sub-spesialis dokter kulit adalah:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Dermatologi alergi dan imunologi</li><li>Tumor dan bedah kulit</li><li>Dermatologi pediatrik</li><li></li><li>Dermatologi tropis</li><li>Geno Dermatologi</li><li>Dermatologi kosmetik</li><li> Dermatologi geriatrik </li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Pendidikan Dokter Kulit</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Minimal dua belas tahun pelatihan dan pendidikan biasanya diperlukan untuk menjadi dokter kulit di Amerika Serikat dan negara-negara barat lainnya. Ini termasuk gelar sarjana pra-medis, pelatihan medis umum, magang dan pelatihan spesialis dermatologi.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Profesi ini bertanggung jawab untuk diagnosis dan pengelolaan penyakit dan kondisi yang mempengaruhi kulit, rambut, kuku, alat kelamin dan selaput lendir. Ini mungkin termasuk berbagai kasus, dari ruam kulit ringan hingga kanker kulit terminal. Pendidikan dan pelatihan dokter kulit sangat penting untuk memastikan bahwa mereka memiliki pemahaman yang memadai tentang kondisi dermatologis dan teknik perawatan yang tepat.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Universitas Terbaik Dermatologi</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ada banyak universitas yang menawarkan program dermatologi (kedokteran kulit). Untuk bisa mendapatkan ilmu terbaik seputar ilmu medis kulit, kamu juga harus masuk ke universitas terbaik di dunia. Berikut adalah daftar universitas dermatologi terbaik di dunia menurut Edurank:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Mayo Clinic College of Medicine and Science</li><li>Harvard University</li><li>University of California - San Francisco</li><li>University of Pennsylvania</li><li>New York University</li><li>University of Miami</li><li>University of Michigan - Ann Arbor</li><li>Stanford University</li><li>Northwestern University</li><li>Post Graduate Institute of Medical Education and Research</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Prospek Kerja di Masa Depan</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Menurut US Department of Labor, Pekerjaan dokter kulit diproyeksikan akan tumbuh 1.2% persen dari 2020 hingga 2030, jauh lebih cepat daripada pertumbuhan rata-rata untuk semua pekerjaan.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Selama satu dekade ini, kira-kira akan ada sekitar 3,800 lowongan untuk dokter anak diproyeksikan setiap tahun. Banyak dari lowongan tersebut dihasilkan dari kebutuhan untuk mengganti pekerja yang pindah ke pekerjaan lain atau keluar dari kerja, seperti pensiun.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Memerlukan dedikasi dan waktu yang lama untuk bisa berhasil di profesi ini. Ahli di bidang ini mempunyai masa depan yang cerah karena banyak permintaan untuk profesi ini. Apa kamu sudah benar-benar yakin untuk menjadi dokter kulit?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ayo persiapkan dirimu dengan EDUVERSE by ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita:<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/edu.verse_/?hl=en\"> @edu.verse</a> dan join Telegram:<a href=\"http://t.me/Allineduverse\"> t.me/Allineduverse</a> untuk diskusi sama expert!<br></p>', 'rDEg_a6nmp-INLBR8yHsumYsQKK_Xn-LP-ygHh4MSgajB8YBzRymSJLHwholklGCgfJNMiE7Mj2nfYZ_xgTkUiV2yBDp7obvfDqI.jpeg', 'Membedah Profesi Dokter Kulit', 'publish', '', 'Dokter Kulit', 'Sebagai profesi yang jarang peminatnya, dokter kulit menjadi profesi yang sangat sedikit pesaingnya. Tertarik? Baca artikel ini untuk tahu lebih lengkap!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-03-19 17:00:00', '2022-04-01 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00');
