(10941, 'mengenal-lebih-dekat-profesi-dokter-anak', 8, 0, 'Mengenal Lebih Dekat Profesi Dokter Anak', '<p>Kesehatan anak merupakan sesuatu yang penting bagi setiap orang tua. Dokter anak mempunyai tanggung jawab untuk mendeteksi dan mengelola masalah yang terjadi dari anak mulai dari fisik, perilaku, dan perkembangan lainnya. Profesi yang satu ini sangat berjasa untuk memantau tumbuh kembang anak. Ayo kita mengenal lebih dekat mengenai profesi ini.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Apa itu Dokter Anak?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Dokter anak adalah sebuah profesi yang berfokus pada kesehatan bayi, anak-anak, remaja, dan dewasa muda. Perawatan pediatrik dimulai saat lahir dan berlangsung hingga umur 21 tahun. Profesi ini bertugas mencegah, mendeteksi dan mengelola masalah fisik, perilaku dan perkembangan yang mempengaruhi anak-anak. Beberapa ahli pediatri bekerja dalam praktik umum. Lainnya mengkhususkan diri dalam merawat anak-anak dengan kondisi kesehatan tertentu.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Spesialisasi Dokter Anak</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Tumbuh kembang anak tentunya bukan sesuatu yang sederhana. Kesehatan fisik dan mental merupakan sesuatu yang penting untuk membuat anak tumbuh menjadi individu yang sehat pula.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Perinatology/Neonatology</li><li>Pediatri Sosial</li><li>Gastro Hepatologi</li><li>Pulmonologi/Respirologi</li><li>Pediatri Gawat Darurat</li><li>Endokrinologi</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Pendidikan Dokter Anak</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Dokter anak menjalani pendidikan dan pelatihan ekstensif. Pertama, mereka harus mendapatkan gelar sarjana empat tahun. Selama sarjana, mereka mengambil kursus pra-medis seperti biologi dan kimia.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Selanjutnya, sarjana kedokteran harus menghadiri empat tahun sekolah kedokteran. Di sekolah kedokteran, mereka mengambil kursus seperti anatomi dan fisiologi. Selain itu, mereka mengambil bagian dalam rotasi klinis di mana mereka belajar tentang berbagai bidang kedokteran. Bidang-bidang ini termasuk pediatri, pengobatan darurat, neurologi, psikiatri dan radiologi. Selama rotasi klinis inilah banyak dokter memutuskan spesialisasi mereka.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Jika seorang <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/dokter-penjelasan-dan-spesialisasi/\">dokter</a> memutuskan untuk berspesialisasi dalam pediatri, mereka beralih ke program residensi pediatrik selama tiga tahun. Residensi mencakup pelatihan ekstra dalam berbagai spesialisasi pediatrik seperti bayi baru lahir, perawatan intensif bayi baru lahir, pediatri umum, dan pediatri perkembangan-perilaku. Selama residensi, ahli pediatri harus mendapatkan pengetahuan, keterampilan, dan pengalaman yang mereka perlukan untuk menangani berbagai kondisi pada anak-anak.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Setelah residensi, beberapa ahli pediatri pergi ke praktek pediatrik umum. Dokter anak lainnya mengikuti program di mana mereka menerima pelatihan tambahan dalam sub spesialis pediatrik. Subspesialisasi ini termasuk neonatologi, kardiologi pediatrik, kedokteran remaja, pelecehan anak dan bedah pediatrik. Program-program ini membutuhkan dua hingga enam tahun pelatihan lagi.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Universitas Terbaik untuk Pediatri</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ada banyak universitas yang menawarkan program pediatri (kedokteran anak). Untuk bisa mendapatkan ilmu terbaik seputar ilmu kesehatan untuk anak, kamu juga harus masuk ke universitas terbaik di dunia. Berikut adalah daftar universitas kedokteran anak terbaik di dunia menurut US News adalah:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Harvard University</li><li>University of Cincinnati</li><li>Johns Hopkins University</li><li>University of California - San Francisco</li><li>University of Colorado</li><li>Baylor College of Medicine</li><li>Duke University</li><li>University of Washington</li><li>University of Colorado</li><li>Baylor College of Medicine</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Prospek Kerja di Masa Depan</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Menurut US Department of Labor, Pekerjaan dokter anak diproyeksikan akan tumbuh 2 persen dari 2020 hingga 2030, jauh lebih cepat daripada pertumbuhan rata-rata untuk semua pekerjaan.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Selama satu dekade ini, kira-kira akan ada sekitar 2000 lowongan untuk dokter anak diproyeksikan setiap tahun. Banyak dari lowongan tersebut dihasilkan dari kebutuhan untuk mengganti pekerja yang pindah ke pekerjaan lain atau keluar dari kerja, seperti pensiun.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dokter anak merupakan salah satu profesi yang paling banyak dibutuhkan oleh orang-orang. Untuk bisa menjadi seorang dokter anak, tidak cukup hanya dengan belajar yang rajin. Kamu juga memerlukan dedikasi dan waktu yang sangat panjang untuk mempelajari ilmu kesehatan anak.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Punya mimpi untuk menjadi dokter anak? Ayo wujudkan dengan EDUVERSE by ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita:<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/edu.verse_/?hl=en\"> @edu.verse</a> dan join Telegram:<a href=\"http://t.me/Allineduverse\"> t.me/Allineduverse</a> untuk diskusi sama expert!<br></p>', 'mybt-bbBV2FzrNcsfCzEkFZULFdzn4P5zccNwYXl_7HMJ7lRPg0rRjhIxfWdopqir5HXIp9WcFK311m7RYcIr0gKMCort44sgmIJ.jpeg', 'Mengenal Lebih Dekat Profesi Dokter Anak', 'publish', '', 'Dokter Anak', 'Dokter anak merupakan profesi yang sedang naik daun. Lalu, banyak orang tua mulai sadar pentingnya profesi ini untuk anak. Ayo baca lengkapnya di sini!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-03-18 17:00:00', '2022-04-10 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(10944, 'dokter-penjelasan-dan-spesialisasi', 8, 0, 'Dokter: Penjelasan dan Spesialisasi', '<p>Profesi yang satu ini mendedikasikan hidupnya untuk menolong orang banyak dan mengobati berbagai macam penyakit yang mungkin diderita oleh hampir semua orang. Yap! Profesi tersebut adalah dokter. Simak artikel berikut ini jika kamu memang berminat untuk menjadi dokter!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Apa itu Dokter?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Dokter adalah seseorang yang berpengalaman dan bersertifikat untuk membuka dan melakukan praktik kedokteran yang membantu memelihara atau memulihkan kesehatan fisik dan mental. Seorang dokter bertugas berinteraksi dengan pasien, mendiagnosis masalah medis dan berhasil mengobati penyakit atau cedera.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ada banyak bidang khusus di bidang kedokteran yang dapat dipelajari siswa. Di bawah ini, kamu akan mengetahui lebih banyak mengenai spesialisasi dokter-dokter yang ada di dunia.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Dokter Gigi</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/dokter-gigi-profesi-di-balik-sebuah-senyuman/\">Dokter gigi</a> adalah seorang yang secara khusus mempelajari ilmu kesehatan dan penyakit pada gigi dan mulut. Profesi ini memiliki keahlian dan kompetensi dalam mendiagnosis, mengobati, dan memberikan edukasi tentang pengobatan dan pencegahan berbagai masalah kesehatan gigi, gusi, dan mulut.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Spesialisasi P</strong>raktisi</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Spesialis gigi adalah seseorang yang menerima pelatihan tambahan dalam spesialisasi gigi tertentu di luar gelar kedokteran gigi umum mereka. Orang-orang mungkin akan memerlukan bantuan spesialis, entah karena masalah tertentu atau karena faktor keturunan.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Berikut adalah 6 spesialisasi dokter gigi yang mungkin akan kamu temui di hidupmu:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Ahli Bedah Mulut dan Maksilofasial</li><li>Endodontist - Spesialis Konservasi Gigi</li><li>Orthodontist - Spesialis Perbaikan Posisi Gigi</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Universitas Kedokteran Gigi Terbaik di Dunia</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Ada banyak universitas yang menawarkan program kedokteran gigi. Tapi, jika kamu tertarik untuk menjadi dokter gigi terbaik, kamu harus masuk ke sekolah yang terbaik pula. Berikut adalah daftar universitas kedokteran gigi terbaik di dunia menurut QS World Ranking:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>University of Gothenburg, Swedia</li><li>University of Michigan-Ann Arbor, US</li><li>Academic Centre for Dentistry Amsterdam (ACTA), Belanda</li><li>The University of Hong Kong, Hong Kong</li><li>King\'s College London, UK</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color has-vivid-cyan-blue-color\"><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/dokter-gigi-profesi-di-balik-sebuah-senyuman/\">Ingin tahu lebih banyak mengenai dokter gigi? Baca di sini!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Dokter Hewan</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Dokter hewan adalah sebuah profesi yang&nbsp; bertugas mencegah, memeriksa, mengobati, dan melakukan perawatan pada hewan dari penyakit.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ketika mengambil sumpah <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/dokter-hewan-si-paling-ngerti-hewan/\">dokter hewan</a>, Seseorang akan bersumpah dengan sungguh-sungguh untuk menggunakan pengetahuan dan keterampilan ilmiahnya untuk kepentingan masyarakat, melalui perlindungan kesehatan hewan, pengurangan penderitaan hewan, konservasi sumber daya hewan, peningkatan kesehatan masyarakat, dan kemajuan pengetahuan medis.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Spesialisasi Praktisi</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Dokter hewan adalah salah satu profesi yang mempunyai banyak spesialisasi. Hal ini karena hewan mempunyai banyak variasi. Organ-organ yang membentuk tubuh hewan ada yang sama dengan manusia, ada juga yang berbeda. Organ pembentuk tubuh ini berbeda mengikuti apakah jenis hewan tersebut adalah unggas, ikan, mamalia, atau reptil.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Spesialisasi praktisi dokter hewan tersebut adalah:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Avian (Burung/Unggas)</li><li>Feline (Kucing)</li><li>Cattle (Hewan Ternak)</li><li>Reptile (Reptil)</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Universitas Terbaik</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Ada banyak universitas yang menawarkan program kedokteran hewan. Untuk bisa mendapatkan ilmu terbaik seputar ilmu kesehatan untuk hewan, kamu juga harus masuk ke universitas terbaik di dunia. Berikut adalah daftar universitas kedokteran hewan terbaik di dunia menurut QS World Ranking:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Royal Veterinary College, University of London, UK</li><li>University of California, Davis, US</li><li>Utrecht University, Belanda</li><li>The University of Edinburgh, UK</li><li>Cornell University, US</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color has-vivid-cyan-blue-color\"><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/dokter-hewan-si-paling-ngerti-hewan/\">Penasaran mengenai dokter hewan? Baca artikel ini!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Dokter Kulit</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Dermatologis adalah praktisi medis yang berspesialisasi dalam kesehatan kulit. Mereka memeriksa pasien dengan kondisi kulit dan meninjau kemajuan perawatan dermatologis.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/membedah-profesi-dokter-kulit/\">Dokter kulit</a> mendiagnosis masalah kulit, dari yang ringan (misalnya terbakar sinar matahari) hingga yang parah (misalnya kanker kulit). Mereka melakukan pemeriksaan dan evaluasi kulit, dan menganalisis riwayat medis pasien untuk menentukan perawatan yang tepat. Dermatologis juga mengawasi seberapa efektif perawatan dan merujuk pasien ke spesialis yang berbeda jika diperlukan.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Spesialisasi </strong>Dermatologi</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Profesi ini merupakan salah satu spesialis kedokteran yang paling penting. Kulit kita terdiri dari banyak syarat dan struktur yang sangat rumit. Belum lagi ada kulit sensitif yang memerlukan bantuan khusus dari ahli. Maka dari itu, dibentuklah sub-spesialis untuk dokter kulit. Sub-spesialisnya adalah:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Dermatologi alergi dan imunologi</li><li>Tumor dan bedah kulit</li><li>Dermatologi pediatrik</li><li>Dermatologi geriatrik</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Universitas Terbaik Dermatologi</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Ada banyak universitas yang menawarkan program dermatologi (kedokteran kulit). Untuk bisa mendapatkan ilmu terbaik seputar ilmu medis kulit, kamu juga harus masuk ke universitas terbaik di dunia. Berikut adalah daftar universitas dermatologi terbaik di dunia menurut Edurank:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Mayo Clinic College of Medicine and Science</li><li>Harvard University</li><li>University of California - San Francisco</li><li>University of Pennsylvania</li><li>New York University</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color has-vivid-cyan-blue-color\"><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/membedah-profesi-dokter-kulit/\">Kamu ingin jadi dokter kulit? Cari tahu lebih banyak di sini!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Dokter Anak</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Profesi ini adalah sebuah profesi yang berfokus pada kesehatan bayi, anak-anak, remaja, dan dewasa muda. Perawatan pediatrik dimulai saat lahir dan berlangsung hingga umur 21 tahun. Profesi ini bertugas mencegah, mendeteksi dan mengelola masalah fisik, perilaku dan perkembangan yang mempengaruhi anak-anak. Beberapa <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/mengenal-lebih-dekat-profesi-dokter-anak/\">dokter anak</a> bekerja dalam praktik umum. Lainnya mengkhususkan diri dalam merawat anak-anak dengan kondisi kesehatan tertentu.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Spesialisasi P</strong>ediatri</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Tumbuh kembang anak tentunya bukan sesuatu yang sederhana. Kesehatan fisik dan mental merupakan sesuatu yang penting untuk membuat anak tumbuh menjadi individu yang sehat pula.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Perinatology/Neonatology</li><li>Pediatri Sosial</li><li>Gastro Hepatologi</li><li>Pulmonologi/Respirologi</li><li>Pediatri Gawat Darurat</li><li>Endokrinologi</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Universitas Terbaik untuk Pediatri</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Ada banyak universitas yang menawarkan program pediatri (kedokteran anak). Untuk bisa mendapatkan ilmu terbaik seputar ilmu kesehatan untuk anak, kamu juga harus masuk ke universitas terbaik di dunia. Berikut adalah daftar universitas kedokteran anak terbaik di dunia menurut US News adalah:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Harvard University</li><li>University of Cincinnati</li><li>Johns Hopkins University</li><li>University of California - San Francisco</li><li>University of Colorado</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color has-vivid-cyan-blue-color\"><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/mengenal-lebih-dekat-profesi-dokter-anak/\">Punya mimpi untuk jadi dokter anak? Baca selengkapnya di sini!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dokter merupakan salah satu profesi yang menjanjikan. Untuk menjadi dokter saja perlu belajar bertahun-tahun, apalagi jika kamu ingin menjadi spesialis di bidang tertentu. Maka dari itu, kamu memerlukan dedikasi dan waktu yang benar-benar panjang untuk bisa menjadi dokter.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Apa kamu ingin masuk jurusan kedokteran di universitas terbaik di dunia? Ayo persiapkan dirimu bersama EDUVERSE by ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita:<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/edu.verse_/?hl=en\"> @edu.verse</a> dan join Telegram:<a href=\"http://t.me/Allineduverse\"> t.me/Allineduverse</a> untuk diskusi sama expert!<br></p>', 'Q163rKB7YaL9FnDFzyMx7sP8pEsrOYHbJYnuMbp7KmmP_5GoPve3rRrZm9R36cDndue1teJPHmKBHEdKBWHYQ6Ej7G55t1NdB2us3D_ilBl4rQ_8PiBXH_2C0hVtiTLSNi0KoubXmsR82txbv7ifmj30jGYDG_9CU2PiwzlAQqlNB5FmtDAFUfesPLT9uL8jgi8.jpg', 'Dokter: Penjelasan dan Spesialisasi', 'publish', 'Dokter: Penjelasan dan Spesialisasi. Cari tahu info lebih lengkapnya di sini', 'Dokter', 'Dokter adalah salah satu profesi yang paling terpuji. Kamu tertarik untuk menjadi seorang dokter? Cari tahu info lebih lengkapnya di sini!', 'id', 1, '', 'false', '2022-03-17 17:00:00', '2022-04-18 17:00:00', '2023-03-24 06:24:31'),
(10979, 'harvard-medical-school-history-and-facts', 1, 0, 'Harvard Medical School: History and Facts', '<p>If you have a dream to become a great doctor or personnel in medicine, then Harvard Medical School is the best choice for you. HMS is a world-renowned institution in the field of medicine. Also, Harvard Medical School has been a prominent source of innovative thinking and scientific creativity. Here, you will find the Harvard Medical School profile overview, from its history to its notable alumni.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>History of Harvard Medical School&nbsp;</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Harvard Medical School was founded in 1782 with only a few students and a three-person faculty. The first class was held in Harvard Hall in Cambridge. Furthermore, the School\'s teachers and trainees accumulated knowledge and influence over each decade, influencing medicine in the United States and beyond. Some members of the community have become legends.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Then in 1860, Charles Eliot devised a revolutionary curriculum at Harvard Medical School just a few years after becoming president. New basic and clinical sciences departments were founded, a three-year degree program was introduced, and the apprenticeship system was removed. HMS became a professional school of Harvard University, establishing the standard for medical education within a university in the United States.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>A glance at Harvard Medical School&nbsp;</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>With a single campus and an online presence, Harvard Medical School offers numerous programs. Some of the programs provided at HMS include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Medical (MD):</strong> ‍A two-year, full-time residential program that focuses on practical learning.</li><li><strong>Master\'s Degree Programs:</strong> offers three postgraduate master\'s degree programs to address the needs of clinicians, clinician-scientists, and administrators.</li><li><strong>Ph.D. Degree Programs:</strong> offers nine HMS-based Ph.D. programs.</li><li><strong>HMX Online:</strong> offers certification courses.</li><li><strong>Executive</strong>: a corporate learning program for business leaders who seek to address the most pressing challenges and opportunities facing health care.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>For physicians, researchers, and other health care workers, HMS offers a comprehensive range of postgraduate medical education. Moreover, programs and courses aim to help you develop in your career as a health care worker and stay up-to-date on the latest advancements in medical research and clinical practice, drawing on the world-class HMS faculty.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With an average acceptance rate of 3.7%, HMS is among the most competitive medical schools globally. Also, HMS offers admission in two rounds each year, and it admits nearly 500 students into its MD program each year.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Both individuals and organizations can benefit from Harvard Medical School. Also, the programs can be tailored to meet specific requirements. HMS professors develop and offer programs with input from leading academic and clinical professionals worldwide. Moreover, many students and professionals can develop skills and build a strong connection for their future careers.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Notable Alumni&nbsp;</h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>James Lovelock</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>James Ephraim Lovelock was born on July 26, 1919. He grew up in a little town called Letchworth Garden City, Hertfordshire, England. Moreover, he was an English chemist, medical doctor, scientific instrument developer, and author best known for creating the Gaia hypothesis, which holds that all life on Earth is a part of an entity that regulates the planet\'s surface and atmospheric processes. Lovelock also invented several chemical-detection gadgets, such as the electron-capture detector (ECD).<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Paul Zamecnik</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Paul Charles Zamecnik (November 22, 1912 – October 27, 2009) was an American molecular biologist who played a vital role in the early development of the field. Moreover, Zamecnik pioneered protein synthesis in vitro and contributed to understanding how cells produce proteins. Furthermore, he was a senior scientist at Massachusetts General Hospital and a professor of medicine at HMS.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Harvard Medical School is much more than just another prestigious academic institution. It is one of the oldest medical schools in the modern world, but it was also the first to campaign openly for racial and gender inclusion. Later down the line, HMS developed academic journals, which changed how we understand medicine and how doctors provide treatment. The school also engages in research that benefits humankind as a whole.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Eager to get into Harvard Medical School? Prepare to get into <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/all-about-harvard-university-post-graduate-program/\">Harvard</a> with ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top uni preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/allineduspace/\">ALL-in Eduspace</a>! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', '101032_1331178.jpg.2000x1333_q95_crop-smart_upscale.jpg', 'Harvard Medical School: History and Facts', 'publish', '', 'Harvard Medical School', 'Dreaming to be a doctor in the future? Then, Harvard Medical School is the best option for you. Find out all information about HMS in this article!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-04-08 17:00:00', '2022-05-25 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(10983, 'harvard-business-school-facts-you-should-know', 1, 0, 'Harvard Business School: Facts You Should Know!', '<p>With over 100 years of success and innovation, it\'s no surprise that Harvard Business School is known as a globally excellent institution for entrepreneurial leaders. However, behind its impressive feats and low acceptance rate, what can you expect from this Ivy League institution? Let\'s dive deeper into Harvard Business School!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>History of Harvard Business School&nbsp;</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Established in 1908, Harvard Business School (HBS) is the first graduate business school to deliver the first MBA program in the world. The HBS campus is located in Boston\'s Allston neighborhood.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>At the time of its founding, Harvard Business school only accepted male students. It wasn\'t until December 1962 that the faculty voted to allow female applicants to enter the MBA program directly, and the first group of women to do so matriculated in September 1963.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>A glance at Harvard Business School&nbsp;</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>With a single campus and an online presence, Harvard Business School offers numerous kinds of programs. Some of the programs offered at HBS include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>MBA:</strong> ‍A two-year, full-time residential program that focuses on practical learning.</li><li><strong>Executive Education: </strong>Designed for experienced executives to refine their leadership skills.</li><li><strong>Online ‍Programs:</strong> Offers the opportunity for those who want to learn essential business concepts anywhere in the world.</li><li><strong>Doctoral Programs:&nbsp; </strong>For those who are interested in receiving a Phd or or DBA degree in academic research.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>HBS has an average acceptance rate of 10%, as well as sitting fifth on the US News 2023 Best Business Schools rankings. Therefore, Harvard Business School is among the most competitive business schools in the world. HBS offers admission in two rounds each year, and it admits nearly 750 students into its MBA program each year.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Harvard Business School\'s curriculum aims to prepare students to be able to collaborate in teams to solve real-world problems. For instance, the MBA program incorporates both classroom and non-classroom learning. MBA students have the opportunity to participate in experiential learning through field study teams. This is where they work collaboratively in teams with other MBA candidates, as well as immersion trips of studying abroad.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Aside from MBA, Harvard Business School students can enroll in joint degree programs with other Harvard schools. such as Harvard Law School, Harvard Medical School, the Harvard Kennedy School of Government, and the Harvard School of Dental Medicine.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With more than 85 clubs and 200 leadership positions in the Student Association (SA), HBS students can gain real-life leadership and organizational management experience.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Notable Alumni&nbsp;</h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Sheryl Sandberg&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>After earning her MBA from Harvard in 1995, Sheryl Sandberg began her career as chief of staff to Larry Summers, who was serving as US Treasury Secretary. In 2008, Sheryl joined Facebook and served as its Chief Operating Officer, where she oversees all business operations. Alongside her work at Facebook, Sheryl Sandberg has also contributed to the field of corporate feminism, where she wrote the bestselling book <em>Lean In.</em></p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Michael Bloomberg&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>As a founder of the multi-billion dollar media group Bloomberg, Michael Bloomberg obtained his MBA at Harvard Business School in 1966. He was also the mayor of New York City, having won the election three times. He\'s famous for his work on issues such as air quality, public health, and sustainability.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>HBS is one of the most renowned business schools in the world. trying to get into it can feel like an uphill battle. But once you\'re there, from the connections you make, the education you receive, to the opportunities that present themselves—it\'s all gonna be worth it!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ready to secure your seat at Harvard Business School? Get yourself <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/all-about-harvard-university-post-graduate-program/\">Harvard</a>-prepared with ALL-in!<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top uni preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/allineduspace/\">ALL-in Eduspace</a>! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'dcf4d944-3187-11e7-9555-23ef563ecf9a-1.jpg', 'Harvard Business School: Facts You Should Know!', 'publish', '', 'Harvard Business School', 'Do you want to study business in the best place possible? Then, Harvard Business School is perfect for you. Check out all the facts about HBS here!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-04-07 17:00:00', '2022-05-17 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(10989, 'harvard-law-school-worlds-leading-law-school', 1, 0, 'Harvard Law School: World’s Leading Law School', '<p>When people hear about <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/all-about-harvard-university-post-graduate-program/\">Harvard</a>, some of the things that might come up include prestige, prominent people, and immense breakthroughs in the field. With a history that\'s nearly 400 years long, Harvard retains its reputation as one of the leading universities in the world. Now, let us look at one of Harvard\'s distinguished schools: Harvard Law School.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>History of Harvard Law School</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>With a history dating back to the early 1800s, Harvard Law School (HLS) is the oldest continuously operating law school in the United States. Situated in Cambridge, Massachusetts, it is home to the largest academic law library in the world.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Harvard Law School was one of the first law schools to admit women, beginning with the class of 1950. Among the nine women who enrolled at HLS in 1956 was Ruth Bader Ginsburg, who went on to become an Associate Justice of the US Supreme Court, where she served until her death in 2020.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>A glance at Harvard Law School&nbsp;</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Harvard Law School offers three types of graduate degrees:&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Juris Doctor (J.D.):</strong> A full-time, three-year program where students get to learn the fundamentals of legal practice, legal reasoning, and analysis. Upon graduating, students can become licensed to practice law.&nbsp;</li><li><strong>Master of Laws (L.L.M.):</strong> A one-year master\'s program meant to complement a JD or equivalent foreign law degree which can be taken on a full-time or part-time basis. By taking this degree, students can expand their legal knowledge, keep up with the latest legal developments, as well as specialize in a particular legal field. Upon graduating, students can become a solicitor, or work in law enforcement, technology companies, or transnational organizations such as the United Nations.&nbsp;</li><li><strong>Doctor of Juridical Science (S.J.D.): </strong>Harvard Law School\'s most advanced law degree designed for students interested in pursuing legal academia.&nbsp;</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>According to the US News 2023 Best Law Schools rankings, Harvard Law sits fifth on the top law school in the US, behind Stanford and Yale.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Knowing that Harvard Law is recognized as one of the best law schools in the US, it is no surprise that it has a very selective admission process. According to Harvard Law School\'s 2022 class profile, 916 applicants were offered admissions out of 7,419 applicants. This brings the admissions rate to only 12%.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Degree and Programs</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Harvard Law School\'s faculty includes more than 100 full-time professors and more than 150 visiting professors. They offer more than 400 courses and seminars covering a broad range of traditional and emerging legal fields. Currently, HLS offers seven programs of study:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><span style=\"background-color: rgb(225, 190, 231);\">Law and Business</span></li><li>Law and Government</li><li>International and Comparative Law</li><li>Law and History</li><li>Law and Social Change</li><li>Criminal Law and Policy</li><li>Law, Science, and Technology</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Harvard Law School also offers several joint degree programs that combine the study of law with other disciplines. The following are the degree programs:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>JD/MBA with Harvard Business School</li><li>JD/MPP or MPA-ID with Harvard Kennedy School</li><li>JD/MPH with Harvard T.H. Chan School of Public Health</li><li>JD/MUP with the Graduate School of Design</li><li>JD/Ph.D. with the Graduate School of Arts and Sciences</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Notable Alumni&nbsp;</h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Barack Obama</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>In 1988, Barack Obama enrolled in Harvard Law School, where he was the first Black president of the Harvard Law Review. After graduating, he worked as a civil rights attorney and taught at the University of Chicago before deciding to run for public office. In 2008, after serving three years in the US Senate, he became the 44th President of the United States.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Elena Kagan</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>After graduating from Harvard Law School in 1986, Elena Kagan clerked for Thurgood Marshall, who was then a Justice of the Supreme Court. After the end of her clerkship, she became an attorney at Williams & Connolly and later served as the dean of Harvard Law School from 2003. She was then become an associate justice of the US Supreme Court in 2010.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Being consistently ranked as one of the top law schools in the world, it\'s no surprise many wishes to get into Harvard Law School. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>While gaining admission into it is no mean feat, HLS is not only a great place to learn about the law. It\'s also about getting immersed in an environment that will challenge you and help shape who you are!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dreaming of getting into Harvard Law School? Get yourself prepared with ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top uni preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/allineduspace/\">ALL-in Eduspace</a>! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'GettyImages_525634538.jpg', 'Harvard Law School: World’s Leading Law School', 'publish', '', 'Harvard Law School', 'Mastering law requires a good education and Harvard Law School is one of the best universites that offers the program. Read this article to find out more!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-04-06 17:00:00', '2022-05-11 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(10993, 'all-about-harvard-university-post-graduate-program', 1, 0, 'All Around View about Harvard University', '<p>As one of the most prestigious schools in the world, Harvard University is famous to students from around the globe. Moreover, founded in 1636, Harvard is the oldest high institution in the United States. Its reputation and high-quality education not only apply to its undergraduate studies but also for its postgraduate schools. In this article, you will catch a glimpse of Harvard\'s full profile. Let\'s take a look!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Harvard University Majors</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Under the General Education requirements, Harvard College\'s system requires undergraduate students to take one class in each of four categories:&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Aesthetics and Culture</li><li>Histories, Societies, Individuals</li><li>Science and Technology in Society</li><li>Ethics and Civics</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>With 50 different concentrations (or majors) offered at Harvard, students must pursue in-depth study of one specific area of their interest by taking about 10-14 courses. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Molecular and Cellular Biology (MCB)</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Students concentrating in MCB at Harvard learn biological processes based on the study of molecules and their interactions in the context of cells and tissues through investigations. Furthermore, to concentrate on this major, you\'ll need to take about 12 courses, most of which are in the life-sciences field. Moreover, many of the MCB requirements overlap with pre-med requirements, making it a good choice if you\'re interested in applying to medical school in the future. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Mathematics</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have a knack for mathematics, Harvard\'s Mathematics concentration allows you to gain a deeper understanding of pure or applied mathematics. While Pure Mathematics is concerned with mathematical concepts and their interrelationships, Applied Mathematics looks at how mathematical concepts relate to issues that arise in other fields of study. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Curious about the other majors? Read here!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Harvard Scholarship</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Harvard Scholarship has helped many students finish their education. Aside from the financial aid, you can also use the scholarship to improve your credibility for your career. According to Harvard, 55% of their undergraduates receive need-based Harvard scholarships. This is due to more than 20% of Harvard parents have total incomes less than $75,000 and are not expected to contribute to the cost of their children\'s educations.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Not having the financial ability to fund your education is not something to be ashamed of. You can use this as a motivation to get one of these scholarships:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Scholarship #1: Financial Aid</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The first Harvard University Scholarship we will talk about is the financial aid offered by Harvard. Moreover, this aid is based entirely upon the student\'s needs meeting the demonstrated financial needs of students. Furthermore, international students who meet the criteria can apply for Harvard financial aid, which covers 100% of the applicant\'s demonstrated need.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The financial aid office will select eligible students based on parental contributions, employment, and student honors. Furthermore, the remaining will be paid by grant-based scholarships with no repayment requirements.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Scholarship #2: Harvard Academy Scholars </h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Another Harvard University scholarship is the Academy Scholars, which is offered to students pursuing postdoctoral research studies. Moreover, this program identifies and supports outstanding scholars at the start of their careers whose work combines disciplinary excellence in the social sciences or law. Each year, four to six Academy Scholars are named for two-year appointments. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>To be eligible for the Harvard Academy Scholars program, you must meet the following requirements:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Recipients of PhD or comparable doctoral degree and advanced doctoral candidates in the social sciences</li><li>Submit degree conferral documentation issued by their university registrar\'s office by June 30, 2023.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Looking to find out more about the scholarship? Find out more here!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Harvard University Master Program</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>In total, there are more than 95 Harvard University master programs, which are all offered on-campus only. Moreover, the most popular graduate school programs at Harvard University are business, teaching, and law. Here is a list of schools in Harvard that offers master programs: </p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Business School (HBS)</li><li>Divinity School (HDS)</li><li>Extension School (HES)</li><li>Graduate School of Arts and Sciences (GSAS)</li><li>Law School (HLS) </li><li>Graduate School of Design (GSD)</li><li>Graduate School of Education (HGSE)</li><li>Kennedy School of Government (HKS)</li><li>School of Dental Medicine (HSDM)</li><li>Medical School (HMS) </li><li>School of Engineering and Applied Sciences (SEAS)</li><li>School of Public Health (HSPH)</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>The GSAS, which houses some of Harvard\'s most popular courses, is the university\'s largest graduate school. GSAS offers a wide range of degrees, from humanities to the arts and sciences.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For a brief overview about the master degree, you can find out more here!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Harvard Medical School</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Harvard Medical School was founded in 1782 with only a few students and a three-person faculty. Also, the first class was in Harvard Hall in Cambridge. Furthermore, the School\'s teachers and trainees accumulated knowledge and influence over each decade, influencing medicine in the United States and beyond. Some members of the community have become legends.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With a single campus and an online presence, Harvard Medical School offers numerous programs. Some of the programs provided at HMS include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Medical (MD),</strong> ‍A two-year, full-time residential program that focuses on practical learning.</li><li><strong>Master\'s Degree Programs</strong> offers three postgraduate master\'s degree programs to address the needs of clinicians, clinician-scientists, and administrators.</li><li><strong>Ph.D. Degree Programs</strong> offers nine HMS-based Ph.D. programs.</li><li><strong>HMX Online</strong> offers certification courses.</li><li><strong>Executive</strong>, a corporate learning program for business leaders who seek to address the most pressing challenges and opportunities facing health care.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/harvard-medical-school-history-and-facts/\">Harvard Medical School</a> offers a comprehensive range of postgraduate medical education for physicians, researchers, and other health care workers. Therefore, programs and courses are able to help you develop in your career as a health care worker and stay up-to-date on the latest advancements in medical research and clinical practice, drawing on the world-class HMS faculty.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With an average acceptance rate of 3.7%, Harvard Medical School is among the most competitive medical schools globally. Furthermore, HMS offers admission in two rounds each year, and it admits nearly 500 students into its MD program each year.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/harvard-medical-school-history-and-facts/\">Want to know more about Harvard Medical School? Read the full article here!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Harvard Business School</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Established in 1908, Harvard Business School (HBS) is the first graduate business school to deliver the first MBA program in the world. Furthermore, the HBS campus is located in Boston\'s Allston neighborhood. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>At the time of its founding, Harvard Business school only accepted male students. Moreover, it wasn\'t until December 1962 that the faculty allowed female applicants to enter the MBA program directly. Furthermore, the first group of women to do so matriculated in September 1963.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With a single campus and an online presence, <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/harvard-business-school-facts-you-should-know/\">Harvard Business School</a> offers numerous kinds of programs. Some of the programs offered at HBS include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>MBA:</strong> ‍A two-year, full-time residential program that focuses on practical learning.</li><li><strong>Executive Education: </strong>Designed for experienced executives to refine their leadership skills.</li><li><strong>Online ‍Programs:</strong> Offers the opportunity for those who want to learn essential business concepts anywhere in the world.</li><li><strong>Doctoral Programs : </strong>For those who are interested in receiving a PhD or DBA degree in academic research.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>With an average acceptance rate of 10%, as well as sitting fifth on the US News 2023 Best Business Schools rankings, Harvard Business School is among the most competitive business schools in the world. Moreover, HBS offers admission in two rounds each year, and it admits nearly 750 students into its MBA program each year. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/harvard-business-school-facts-you-should-know/\">Eager to find out more about Harvard Business School? Read it here!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Harvard University MBA</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>When we are talking about Harvard Business school, we have to talk about the MBA. In the MBA Class of 2024, there are 1,015 students enrolled and 8,264 applications. This brings the Harvard University MBA acceptance rate to 12.3%. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>HBS offers a two-year, full-time MBA program with a general management curriculum focused on real-world practice. When you enroll in Harvard\'s MBA program, you will build deep general management and leadership skills through the case- and experience-based curriculum. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>In the first year of study, all MBA students follow the same core curriculum which will help them in laying a common foundation in the fundamental practices of business. The required fundamental curriculum for the first year includes:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Business, Government, and the International Economy (BGIE)</li><li>The Entrepreneurial Manager (TEM)&nbsp;</li><li>Strategy (STRAT)</li><li>Leadership and Corporate Accountability (LCA)</li><li>Finance 2 (FIN2)</li><li>FIELD Immersion</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>During the second year, students can choose from an unparalleled range of elective courses to build on the basic concepts developed in the Required Curriculum. They may take any combination of courses—up to five courses per semester—and also have the opportunity to cross-register for courses in certain graduate programs. Furthermore, MBA students have the opportunity to take immersive field courses (IFC), a class where the vast majority of content consists of an assignment to learn about and advise on real problems.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Need more info about the Harvard MBA? Find more here!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Harvard Law School</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>With a history dating back to the early 1800s, Harvard Law School (HLS) is the oldest continuously operating law school in the United States. Furthermore, situated in Cambridge, Massachusetts, it is home to the largest academic law library in the world. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Harvard Law School was one of the first law schools to admit women, beginning with the class of 1950. Among the nine women who enrolled at HLS in 1956 was Ruth Bader Ginsburg, who went on to become an Associate Justice of the US Supreme Court, where she served until her death in 2020.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/harvard-law-school-worlds-leading-law-school/\">Harvard Law School</a> offers three types of graduate degrees:&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Juris Doctor (J.D.):</strong> A full-time, three-year program where students get to learn the fundamentals of legal practice, legal reasoning, and analysis.&nbsp;</li><li><strong>Master of Laws (L.L.M.):</strong> A one-year master\'s program meant to complement a JD or equivalent foreign law degree which can be taken on a full-time or part-time basis. Harvard\'s LL.M. students include lawyers, judges, activists, diplomats, and government officials.&nbsp;</li><li><strong>Doctor of Juridical Science (S.J.D.): </strong>Harvard Law School\'s most advanced law degree is designed for students interested in pursuing legal academia.&nbsp;</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/harvard-law-school-worlds-leading-law-school/\">Have a dream to continue your study at Harvard Law School? Find out about the profile here!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Conclusion</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>For those who are interested in attending one of these schools, Harvard is an excellent choice. Moreover, as one of the oldest and most prestigious universities in the world, Harvard can provide an excellent environment for pursuing a master\'s or doctoral degree. Moreover, the programs are world-renowned, and the faculty is highly successful and available to students on a one-to-one basis. Furthermore, the university is located in an urban center with access to limitless cultural opportunities. Both students of medical studies will find their needs met at Harvard University.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Have a dream to study at Harvard? ALL-in will help you secure your spot!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top uni preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/allineduspace/\">ALL-in Eduspace</a>! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'vabjq.jpg', 'All Around View about Harvard University', 'publish', 'All about Harvard University Post-graduate Program', 'Harvard', 'It is without a doubt that Harvard is the best to continue an education journey. Interested? Read here to know more about Harvard postgraduate program.', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-04-05 17:00:00', '2022-05-23 17:00:00', '2023-02-15 17:00:00');
