(11248, 'top-university-of-oxford-majors-in-2022', 1, 0, 'Top University of Oxford Majors in 2022', '<p>Have you ever wondered what the top majors are at the <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/all-about-the-university-of-oxford/\">University of Oxford</a>? Whether you\'re a student who is still trying to decide on a major, or simply curious about what other degrees are offered at Oxford, this article will take you through each of the top five majors.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The University of Oxford is the second-best university in the world according to QS World University Rankings 2022. Here is the list of top majors at the University of Oxford according to US News:</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Philosophy and Theology</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Philosophy develops analytical rigor as well as the ability to critically evaluate and reason logically. It enables you to apply these skills to a wide range of contemporary and historical schools of thought and individual thinkers. Moreover, it allows you to questions ranging from how we acquire knowledge and make moral judgments to central questions in religious philosophy. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Theology studies the intellectual underpinnings of religious traditions as well as the social and cultural circumstances in which religious thought and practice take place. It brings together historical, textual, linguistic, social, literary-critical, and philosophical abilities and disciplines.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Modern Languages</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Modern Languages provides both practical training in written and spoken language. Furthermore, it gives a thorough introduction to European literature and thinking. You can study a wide range of literature or focus your studies on any time from the medieval to the current day. This is in addition to learning to write and speak the language(s) fluently. Other courses such as linguistics, philology, film, or gender studies, as well as advanced translation (in French and German) are available.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Geography</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Geography is an interdisciplinary degree that combines the natural and social sciences. These subjects enhance a wide range of transferable skills. Also, it provides an education that covers important concerns on a variety of scales, from local to global. The degree covers a lot of themes. These are Climate and environmental change, inequality, social, economic, and cultural transition.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>English Language and Literature</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The English Language and Literature at Oxford is one of the most comprehensive in the UK. ere, you will study English writing from its Anglo-Saxon origins to the present day. Also, you can study works published in English from all over the world, as well as others that were initially written in other languages. Also, this allows you to think about English literature in multilingual and global contexts over time. Studying this major will give you a lot of freedom. Both in terms of developing your personal interests across core papers and in terms of selecting a dissertation topic and a unique option for your final year.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Human Sciences</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Human Sciences is an interdisciplinary degree program that allows students to explore humans from a variety of angles, including biological and social scientific perspectives. Furthermore, the degree is based on the recognition that understanding links between biological, social, and cultural phenomena. These are critical for addressing the key difficulties and problems that humans face in an ever-changing environment. Also, the curriculum is a fun and challenging alternative to typical undergraduate programs.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As Oxford is a university of great prestige, even the most unusual courses have the potential to be a success. These types of courses not only help students to develop their skills and interests but also open their minds to new perspectives and theories.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Do you want to get into any of these top majors at the University of Oxford? ALL-in will help guide your preparation!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top uni preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'Downloader.la-62a2e5ae3352f.jpg', 'Top University of Oxford Majors in 2022', 'publish', '', 'University of Oxford Majors', 'When talking about University of Oxford majors, there are a lot that you can choose. Take a look at top majors in Oxford in this article!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-04-16 17:00:00', '2022-06-15 17:00:00', '2022-11-03 17:00:00'),
(11254, 'all-about-the-university-of-oxford', 1, 0, 'All About The University of Oxford', '<p>According to the QS World University Ranking 2022, the University of Oxford is placed number 2 in the world. Furthermore, as one of the most prestigious universities in the world, Oxford will provide you with a lot of opportunities to maximize your potential. Curious? Therefore, let\'s find out all the aspects below.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The University of Oxford is an English higher education institution located in Oxford, Oxfordshire, England, and is one of the world\'s major universities. Moreover, it is located 50 miles (80 kilometers) north-northwest of London, along the upper course of the River Thames (dubbed the Isis by Oxford students).</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Oxford had schools by the early 12th century, according to a smattering of evidence. By the end of the century, the university had grown to prominence, possibly as a result of the expulsion of English students from the University of Paris in 1167. Furthermore, with original faculties of theology, law, medicine, and the liberal arts, Oxford was modeled after the University of Paris.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/top-university-of-oxford-majors-in-2022/\">Top Majors at the University of Oxford</a></strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>University of Oxford has a lot of popular majors. Also, these majors are placed in the top 10 of the best in the world according to USnews. Here is the list of the top majors at the University of Oxford:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Philosophy and Theology</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Philosophy develops analytical rigor as well as the ability to critically evaluate and reason logically. It enables you to apply these skills to a wide range of contemporary and historical schools of thought and individual thinkers, as well as to questions ranging from how we acquire knowledge and make moral judgments to central questions in religious philosophy, such as the existence and nature of God, and the relevance of religion to human life.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Modern Languages</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Modern Languages provides both practical training in written and spoken language as well as a thorough introduction to European literature and thinking. You can study a wide range of literature or focus your studies on any time from the medieval to the current day, in addition to learning to write and speak the language(s) fluently. Other courses such as linguistics, philology, film, or gender studies, as well as advanced translation (in French and German) are available.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Geography</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Geography is an interdisciplinary degree that combines the natural and social sciences. Furthermore, this enhances a wide range of transferable skills and provides an education that covers important concerns on a variety of scales, from local to global. Moreover, there are a lot of themes that you can learn like climate and environmental change, inequality, social, economic, and cultural transition.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/top-university-of-oxford-majors-in-2022/\">Curious about the other top majors in the world? Read it here!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/breaking-down-university-of-oxford-acceptance-rate/\">University of Oxford Acceptance Rate</a></strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The undergraduate admittance rate at Oxford is around 17%. Furthermore, to put this figure in context, the UK accounts for around 80% of undergraduates and 36% of graduate students. Oxford is highly competitive, but not quite as rigorous as Harvard, Columbia, or Yale, which all have acceptance rates of roughly 5%. Oxford\'s admission percentage, on the other hand, is slightly lower than Cambridge\'s (21%). Despite this, both Oxford and Cambridge get upwards of 20,000 undergraduate applications per year from both within the United Kingdom and internationally.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>How do you apply to the University of Oxford?</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The application process in the UK is a little bit different compared to the US. This is due to all universities in the UK using one system called the UCAS to handle the applications. Moreover, UCAS is the Universities and Colleges Admissions Service which acts as an application portal for students from around the globe.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Below are the deadlines for the University of Oxford application process.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td><strong>Application Timeline</strong></td><td><strong>Dates</strong></td></tr><tr><td>UCAS Application</td><td>June - October</td></tr><tr><td>Test</td><td>November 2022</td></tr><tr><td>Written Work Submission (If needed)</td><td>October - November 2022</td></tr><tr><td>Interview</td><td>November 2022</td></tr><tr><td>Decision</td><td>January Next Year</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/breaking-down-university-of-oxford-acceptance-rate/\">Want to find out more about other aspects of the University of Oxford? Check it out here!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are an independent and ambitious student who thrives in academically challenging environments. Therefore, Oxford may just be perfect for you. Also, acceptance is very selective for this school and to get in, you need high grades, standardized test scores, and extracurricular activities. Furthermore, this highly selective school looks for students that are independent, willing to work hard and maximise their college experience. Moreover, Oxford is one of the leading schools in the world and can provide you with a great education. This makes it worth your while to apply.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Aiming to become an Oxonian? Therefore, prepare your top uni application with ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top uni preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Not many students realize that on top of showing stellar grades, a strong personal brand is also needed to set yourself apart and stand out from other applicants.<br><br><a href=\"https://personalbrand-guide.all-inedu.com/\">Download “A Guide To Polish Your Personal Brand For Top University Applications” FREE Guidebook and learn how to create a strong personal brand</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'Downloader.la-62a2ec518a11a.jpg', 'All About The University of Oxford', 'publish', 'All About The University of Oxford. the best facts and informations', 'University of Oxford', 'Aiming to get into the University of Oxford? Therefore, you will find the best facts and informations in this article. Read it now!', 'en', 1, '', 'true', '2022-04-15 17:00:00', '2022-06-05 17:00:00', '2023-11-06 08:33:47'),
(11259, 'prospek-kerja-ilmu-komunikasi-di-masa-depan', 8, 0, 'Prospek Kerja Ilmu komunikasi di Masa Depan', '<p><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/serba-serbi-jurusan-ilmu-komunikasi/\">Ilmu komunikasi</a> merupakan salah satu cabang jurusan yang sedang naik daun. Hal ini juga karena bidang Digital Marketing yang semakin terkenal di kalangan anak muda. Untuk kamu yang memang tertarik untuk masuk ke jurusan ilmu komunikasi, berikut adalah beberapa prospek kerja ilmu komunikasi yang menunggumu di masa depan.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Prospek pekerjaan media dan komunikasi diproyeksikan akan meningkat sebanyak 14 persen dari tahun 2020 hingga 2030, lebih cepat dari rata-rata untuk semua pekerjaan, dan akan menghasilkan sekitar 151.500 pekerjaan baru. Banyak prospek pekerjaan ini dilihat dari ada pertumbuhan kebutuhan untuk membuat, mengedit, menerjemahkan, dan menyebarkan informasi melalui berbagai platform yang berbeda.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Berikut adalah beberapa pekerjaan yang bisa kamu incar di masa depan:</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Public Relation</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Sebagai lulusan ilmu komunikasi, kamu akan memiliki kemampuan untuk berpikir strategis. Selain itu, kamu juga akan dibekali dengan segala ilmu mengenai proses dan strategi komunikasi yang dapat mewakili sebuah instansi atau perusahaan. PR dan humas memiliki posisi bagaimana mempengaruhi persepsi publik melalui media. Hal ini termasuk memberikan informasi, membuat klarifikasi, atau membuat permintaan maaf kepada audiens.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tugas seorang profesional PR adalah membuat siaran pers, mengatur konferensi pers, dan bekerjasama dengan media untuk pemberitaan. Humas dan PR dibutuhkan di bagian pemasaran (marketing), biro iklan, lembaga pemerintah, perusahaan, dan organisasi nirlaba. Di sisi lain, ada beberapa agency yang berfokus juga pada satu bidang ini dimana kamu mempunyai kesempatan untuk mewakili lebih dari satu perusahaan.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Prospek Kerja Ilmu Komunikasi: <strong>Event Planner</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Pekerjaan ini akan menuntutmu untuk menjadi lebih kreatif dengan cara mempromosikan dan membuat tema menarik. Tujuannya adalah untuk membuat suatu acara sukses dan menarik untuk didatangi oleh banyak orang. Jurusan ilmu komunikasi sendiri bisa memberikan kontribusi dalam kelompok untuk mengemas sebuah acara menjadi lebih menarik. Selain itu, lulusan ini memiliki keterampilan untuk memproses dan mengemas sebuah acara agar bisa menjadi sukses. Kemampuan yang dibutuhkan oleh profesi ini adalah keterampilan menulis, menyusun siaran pers dan membuat konten menarik.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Media Planner</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Pekerjaan ini dibutuhkan di televisi/radio, web, social media dan artikel majalah dan surat kabar. Media planner bertugas untuk memahami dan menganalisa kecenderungan orang-orang entah saat mereka mengklik, melihat, ataupun membaca. Selain itu pekerjaan ini bisa memilih campuran media terbaik untuk kampanye iklan. Perencana media membutuhkan keterampilan presentasi dan menulis untuk disampaikan kepada rekan dan eksekutif periklanan.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Prospek Kerja Ilmu Komunikasi: <strong>Social Media Manager</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Kemajuan teknologi membuat pekerjaan di bidang industri semakin berkembang, salah satunya social media manager. Sekarang, semakin banyak perusahaan atau UMKM yang memerlukan social media sebagai sarana pemasaran mereka.&nbsp; Pekerjaan ini sangat cocok untuk alumni ilmu komunikasi. Dibutuhkan analisis pola komunikasi dan kualifikasi untuk membantu sebuah organisasi atau perusahaan untuk memanfaatkan media sosial.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Social Media Manager punya kemampuan menulis yang baik untuk menarik pengguna di media sosial seperti Facebook, LinkedIn, dan Twitter. Di sisi lain, tugas pokoknya adalah membuat dan menjadwalkan konten yang relevan dengan audiens yang dimiliki oleh perusahaan atau organisasi tersebut. Selain itu, pekerjaan ini membutuhkan kemampuan persuasif dan keterampilan presentasi yang sangat penting untuk menyampaikan rencana pada partner atau informasi kepada audiens.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Jurnalis</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Prospek kerja ilmu komunikasi yang berikutnya adalah reporter. Media berita televisi sudah menjadi langganan anak ilmu komunikasi dari sejak lama. Sebagai alumni ilmu komunikasi, kamu akan dibekali banyak sekali pengetahuan yang bisa mendukung karirmu sebagai reporter.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ada reporter yang berfokus pada liputan jurnalistik yang berhubungan dengan bisnis dan keuangan, ada juga yang kriminal, dan ada juga yang berfokus pada politik. Liputan reporter seperti perkembangan dalam bisnis, industri, politik, dunia hiburan, dan ekonomi untuk situs web, majalah, surat kabar, dan stasiun televisi. Reporter bermanfaat untuk menyampaikan informasi dalam bahasa yang mudah dipahami oleh masyarakat.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Cukup banyak kan prospek kerja yang bisa kamu miliki sebagai lulusan ilmu komunikasi? Jika kamu punya mimpi untuk menjadi salah satu profesi di atas, tentunya kamu perlu masuk ke universitas terbaik di dunia agar kamu mampu bersaing di pasar dunia.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ayo persiapkan dirimu untuk masuk ke universitas top dunia bersama EDUVERSE by ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:<br></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/id/\">Download Gratis Panduan “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” untuk mencari tahu semua hal yang perlu kamu ketahui sebelum mendaftar beasiswa</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!<br></p>', 'Downloader.la-62a2ede936c73.jpg', 'Prospek Kerja Ilmu komunikasi di Masa Depan', 'publish', '', 'Prospek Kerja Ilmu Komunikasi', 'Apa kamu penasaran tentang prospek kerja ilmu komunikasi di masa depan nanti? Simak seluruh info lengkapnya di artikel ini ya!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-04-07 17:00:00', '2022-06-09 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(11265, 'kampus-fakultas-ilmu-komunikasi-terbaik-di-dunia', 2, 0, 'Kampus Fakultas Ilmu Komunikasi Terbaik di Dunia!', '<p>Apa kamu punya mimpi untuk masuk ke fakultas <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/serba-serbi-jurusan-ilmu-komunikasi/\">ilmu komunikasi</a> di universitas top dunia? Jika kamu memang ingin berkarir di perusahaan multinasional, tentu saja kamu harus mendapatkan pendidikan dengan kualitas terbaik yang bisa menopang masa depanmu dan memberimu akses ke banyak perusahaan terbaik lainnya.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ada banyak sekali universitas yang menyediakan fakultas ilmu komunikasi untuk pelajar internasionalnya. Tapi, untuk bisa bersaing dengan yang terbaik, kamu perlu masuk ke universitas terbaik di dunia juga.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>5. The University of Texas at Austin</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>University of Texas di Austin adalah institusi publik yang didirikan pada tahun 1883. Universitas ini memiliki total mahasiswa sebesar 40.048 orang. Universitas ini berlokasi di tengah perkotaan dengan luas sebesar hektar.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Menurut QS World University Ranking, universitas ini menempati urutan kelima untuk daftar fakultas ilmu komunikasi terbaik di dunia. Kampus ini memiliki tingkat penerimaan sebesar 32%. Tingkat penerimaan tersebut dapat dibilang cukup tinggi dibanding kampus-kampus ternama lainnya.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>4. <strong>Stanford University</strong>; Fakultas Ilmu Komunikasi Terbaik</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Stanford merupakan salah satu universitas terbaik di dunia. Kualitas pendidikan di universitas ini merupakan salah satu yang terbaik di dunia. Menurut QS World University Ranking, di fakultas ilmu komunikasi, Stanford menduduki urutan keempat terbaik di dunia. Stanford memiliki tingkat penerimaan sebesar 5.2%.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Jalur paling populer yang disediakan universitas ini berfokus pada Studi Media Digital, Psikologi Media, Jurnalisme, atau Komunikasi Politik. Departemen ilmu komunikasi Stanford menyediakan berbagai peluang penelitian terkait bidang-bidang tersebut. Kamu bisa melengkapi pengalaman kelas dan lab dengan magang di bidang yang kamu minati.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>3. <strong>The London School of Economics and Political Science</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>LSE didirikan pada tahun 1895 dan bergabung dengan Universitas London pada tahun 1900. Sekolah secara teratur menarik tokoh masyarakat terkemuka untuk memberikan kuliah, menghadiri seminar dan berkonsultasi dengan staf. Di universitas ini mencakup banyak ilmu sosial dan terkenal untuk mempelajari masalah dunia nyata, mulai dari ekonomi, politik dan hukum hingga sosiologi, antropologi, akuntansi, keuangan, dan ilmu komunikasi.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dalam daftar QS World University Ranking, universitas ini berada di urutan ketiga dari daftar universitas untuk fakultas ilmu komunikasi dengan tingkat penerimaan sebesar 8.9%. LSE menawarkan 40 program gelar Sarjana, lebih dari 140 program Master dan Diploma yang diajarkan, dan peluang PhD di seluruh ilmu sosial. Pengajaran dan penelitian dilakukan melalui 25 Departemen dan Institut dan 23 Pusat Penelitian.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>2. <strong>University of Southern California</strong>; Fakultas Ilmu Komunikasi Terbaik</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>University of Southern California adalah salah satu universitas riset swasta terkemuka di dunia. Sebuah lembaga jangkar di Los Angeles, pusat global untuk seni, teknologi, dan bisnis internasional, penawaran kurikuler USC yang beragam memberikan peluang luas berbagai macam gelar mulai dari sarjana, master, dan Ph.D.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Menurut QS World Ranking 2022, USC berada menempati urutan kedua dari daftar universitas terbaik di dunia yang menyediakan fakultas ilmu komunikasi. Semua ini karena ada banyak peluang berkualitas yang ada di USC Annenberg. USC mempunyai tingkat penerimaan sebesar 16.1 %.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Di USC, ada studio televisi yang memproduksi Annenberg TV News secara langsung dan dikelola oleh mahasiswa.&nbsp; Studio televisi ini memiliki siaran tiga kamera tingkat profesional dengan Adobe lab. Selain studio televisi, mahasiswa juga menjalankan surat kabar harian bernama Daily Trojan dan publikasi berita online bernama Neon Timmy.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>1. <strong>University of Amsterdam</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>University of Amsterdam adalah universitas publik yang terletak di kota Amsterdam, Belanda. UvA adalah salah satu dari dua universitas terbesar di Amsterdam. University of Amsterdam memiliki lebih dari 41.000 mahasiswa, 6.000 staff, 3.000 peneliti PhD dan anggaran tahunan sebesar €850 juta, menjadikan universitas ini salah satu universitas riset terbesar di Eropa.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Menurut Qs World Ranking, universitas ini menempati peringkat pertama selama 4 tahun berturut-turut di bidang ilmu komunikasi dan media. Penerimaan di University of Amsterdam adalah salah satu yang paling kompetitif. Tingkat penerimaan masuk ke universitas ini adalah 4,3% untuk pelajar internasional. Namun, untuk mata pelajaran unggulan seperti Sosiologi, Psikologi, Kedokteran, Ilmu Komputer dan Sistem Informasi, tingkat penerimaan yang tercatat adalah 10% dalam 5 tahun terakhir.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Bagus-bagus kan universitas top dunia yang menawarkan fakultas ilmu komunikasi? Seperti yang sudah kamu lihat, tingkat penerimaan masuk ke universitas di atas sangat beragam, ada yang sangat kecil, ada juga yang relatif besar. Maka dari itu, kamu harus mempersiapkan segala persiapanmu untuk masuk ke universitas ini dengan baik.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ingin masuk ke fakultas ilmu hukum terbaik di dunia? Persiapkan semuanya dengan EDUVERSE by ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/id/\">Download Gratis Panduan “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” untuk mencari tahu semua hal yang perlu kamu ketahui sebelum mendaftar beasiswa</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!</p>', 'Downloader.la-62a2efb436aa8.jpg', 'Kampus Fakultas Ilmu Komunikasi Terbaik di Dunia!', 'publish', 'Kampus Fakultas Ilmu Komunikasi Terbaik di Dunia!', 'Fakultas Ilmu Komunikasi', 'Ingin masuk ke fakultas ilmu komunikasi terbaik di dunia? Berikut adalah daftar kampus dengan ilmu komunikasi terbaik menurut QS World Ranking!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-04-06 17:00:00', '2022-06-26 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(11272, 'serba-serbi-jurusan-ilmu-komunikasi', 2, 0, 'Serba-Serbi Jurusan Ilmu Komunikasi', '<p>Ilmu komunikasi merupakan salah satu cabang ilmu yang sedang naik daun. Hal ini karena meningkatnya juga dunia media sosial. Pada era ini, sosial media tidak hanya dijadikan untuk bersosialisasi melainkan juga sebagai sarana pemasaran.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Apa itu Ilmu Komunikasi?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ilmu komunikasi adalah studi tentang bagaimana mengkomunikasikan berbagai jenis informasi secara efektif di berbagai bidang seperti jurnalisme/media, bisnis, politik, dan hukum. Sebagai jurusan komunikasi, kamu akan belajar cara meneliti dan menganalisis informasi dan cara mengomunikasikan topik dengan jelas dan meyakinkan melalui tulisan dan verbal. Kamu akan mempelajari berbagai macam ilmu seperti strategi penelitian, teori, retorika, berbicara di depan umum, menulis, dan jurnalisme/media.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Program sarjana komunikasi dapat akan berpusat ke banyak hal seperti teori dan keterampilan langsung di lapangan. Saat kamu mempelajari teori, kamu akan berurusan dengan berbagai jenis komunikasi, dari secara politik sampai virtual. Di bidang keterampilan langsung, kamu akan mempelajari penerapan dan penguasaan keterampilan utama, termasuk berbicara di depan umum, komunikasi kelompok, dan hubungan masyarakat.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Kampus <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/kampus-fakultas-ilmu-komunikasi-terbaik-di-dunia/\">Fakultas Ilmu Komunikasi</a> Terbaik</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Jika kamu memang tertarik untuk memperdalam atau melanjutkan studi di jurusan ini, berikuta adalah beberapa universitas terbaik di dunia yang menyediakan fakultas ilmu komunikasi terbaik di dunia menurut QS World University Ranking 2022:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>5. The University of Texas at Austin</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>University of Texas di Austin adalah institusi publik yang didirikan pada tahun 1883. Universitas ini memiliki total mahasiswa sebesar 40.048 orang. Universitas ini berlokasi di tengah perkotaan dengan luas sebesar hektar.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>4. Stanford University</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Stanford merupakan salah satu universitas terbaik di dunia. Kualitas pendidikan di universitas ini merupakan salah satu yang terbaik di dunia. Menurut QS World University Ranking, di fakultas ilmu komunikasi, Stanford menduduki urutan keempat terbaik di dunia. Stanford memiliki tingkat penerimaan sebesar 5.2%.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>3. The London School of Economics and Political Science</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>LSE didirikan pada tahun 1895 dan bergabung dengan Universitas London pada tahun 1900. Sekolah secara teratur menarik tokoh masyarakat terkemuka untuk memberikan kuliah, menghadiri seminar dan berkonsultasi dengan staf. Di universitas ini mencakup banyak ilmu sosial dan terkenal untuk mempelajari masalah dunia nyata, mulai dari ekonomi, politik dan hukum hingga sosiologi, antropologi, akuntansi, keuangan, dan ilmu komunikasi.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color has-vivid-cyan-blue-color\"><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/kampus-fakultas-ilmu-komunikasi-terbaik-di-dunia/\">Penasaran dengan universitas mana yang terbaik untuk belajar ilmu komunikasi? Cari tahu di sini!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/prospek-kerja-ilmu-komunikasi-di-masa-depan/\">Prospek Kerja Ilmu Komunikasi</a></strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Setelah kamu menyelesaikan studimu, pastinya kamu akan memulai jenjang karirmu di dunia profesional. Berikut adalah beberapa pilihan karir yang bisa kamu pilih setelah mempelajari ilmu komunikasi:<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Public Relation</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Sebagai lulusan ilmu komunikasi, kamu akan memiliki kemampuan untuk berpikir strategis. Selain itu, kamu juga akan dibekali dengan segala ilmu mengenai proses dan strategi komunikasi yang dapat mewakili sebuah instansi atau perusahaan. PR dan humas memiliki posisi bagaimana mempengaruhi persepsi publik melalui media. Hal ini termasuk memberikan informasi, membuat klarifikasi, atau membuat permintaan maaf kepada audiens.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Event Planner</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Pekerjaan ini akan menuntutmu untuk menjadi lebih kreatif dengan cara mempromosikan dan membuat tema menarik. Tujuannya adalah untuk membuat suatu acara sukses dan menarik untuk didatangi oleh banyak orang. Jurusan ini bisa memberikan kontribusi dalam kelompok untuk mengemas sebuah acara menjadi lebih menarik. Selain itu, lulusan ini memiliki keterampilan untuk memproses dan mengemas sebuah acara agar bisa menjadi sukses. Kemampuan yang dibutuhkan oleh profesi ini adalah keterampilan menulis, menyusun siaran pers dan membuat konten menarik.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Media Planner</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Pekerjaan ini dibutuhkan di televisi/radio, web, social media dan artikel majalah dan surat kabar. Media planner bertugas untuk memahami dan menganalisa kecenderungan orang-orang entah saat mereka mengklik, melihat, ataupun membaca. Selain itu pekerjaan ini bisa memilih campuran media terbaik untuk kampanye iklan. Perencana media membutuhkan keterampilan presentasi dan menulis untuk disampaikan kepada rekan dan eksekutif periklanan.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color has-vivid-cyan-blue-color\"><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/prospek-kerja-ilmu-komunikasi-di-masa-depan/\">Ingin tahu karir lainnya yang bisa kamu pilih dalam bidang ilmu komunikasi? Baca di sini!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Cukup banyak kan hal yang perlu kamu tahu sebelum kamu menjatuhkan pilihan studimu di jurusan ini? Untuk bisa menggapai potensi terbaikmu, kamu perlu untuk menimba ilmu di tempat yang terbaik pula. Dengan begitu, kamu bisa mencapai karir terbaikmu di masa depan.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tertarik untuk masuk ilmu komunikasi di universitas top dunia? EDUVERSE by ALL-in akan membantu semua persiapanmu!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color has-vivid-cyan-blue-color\"><a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/id/\">Download Gratis Panduan “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” untuk mencari tahu semua hal yang perlu kamu ketahui sebelum mendaftar beasiswa</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!</p>', 'Downloader.la-62a2f1215f1bc.jpg', 'Serba-Serbi Jurusan Ilmu Komunikasi', 'publish', '', 'Ilmu Komunikasi', 'Ilmu komunikasi adalah salah satu jurusan yang sedang hangat dieperbutkan oleh pelajar di seluruh dunia. Kamu tertarik? Temukan info lengkapnya di sini!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-04-05 17:00:00', '2022-06-10 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(11306, 'corporate-lawyer-facts-you-need-to-know', 7, 0, 'Corporate Lawyer: Facts You Need to Know', '<p>There has always been a general misunderstanding about what corporate lawyers actually do, with many people mistakenly thinking that the job entails having an overload of responsibility. It\'s common to hear that these lawyers typically work for corporations or big businesses. Some even think that they only handle issues regarding securities law but this is simply not true. But if you\'re looking to become a corporate lawyer, here are the things you should know.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>What is a corporate lawyer?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A corporate lawyer\'s job is to advise clients on their legal rights, responsibilities, and obligations.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>When a corporation hires a corporate <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/get-to-know-all-kinds-of-lawyer/\">lawyer</a>, the lawyer represents the corporation itself rather than its shareholders or employees. This may be a difficult notion to grasp until you realize that a business is treated similarly to a person in the eyes of the law.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A corporation is a legal body formed under state law with the primary aim of conducting business. A company is treated as a separate legal entity or \"person\" from its owners or shareholders.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Because businesses are subject to complicated state and federal regulations, corporate law encompasses all of the legal concerns that surround them. In the USA, most states require businesses to hold regular meetings, such as annual shareholder meetings. These meetings usually run with the presence of a corporate lawyer.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>What do you need to do to become a corporate lawyer?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The approach of becoming a corporate lawyer is similar to that of becoming a lawyer in another field. To practice law as a corporate lawyer, one must first complete law school and acquire a juris doctor (J.D.) degree. Furthermore, because these skills are largely depended upon in day-to-day business law practice, corporate lawyers should have exceptional writing, communication, and negotiation skills.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Because corporate law is such a broad practice area that deals with a wide range of transnational, regulatory, and business-related issues. It\'s critical for a corporate lawyer to want to learn about a wide range of legal topics, unless they want to specialize in a niche area like securities law.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Furthermore, many corporate lawyers represent several clients in various industries, which necessitates a willingness to study the ins and outs of different industries. Finally, when they encounter a specialized area with which they are unfamiliar, such as tax, ERISA, employment, or real estate, corporate lawyers must have the self-awareness and resources to seek assistance from other lawyers.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Job outlook in the future</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The good news is that the demand for corporate lawyers is increasing, albeit slowly. Between 2020 and 2030, the Bureau of Labor Statistics predicts a 3% increase.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Even though lawyers most frequently work for law firms and the government, this is about to change. Many large corporations are attempting to minimize expenses by hiring in-house legal counsel rather than engaging a law firm, according to the BLS.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Other career paths you can pursue which are similar to a corporate lawyer:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Legal aid</li><li>Legal editor</li><li>Policy advisor</li><li>Policy analyst</li><li>Director of ethics</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Being a corporate lawyer is a career that serves as the interface between the business world and the legal system. To be a corporate lawyer, you need advanced education and licensing. Therefore, you need to work very hard to get into the top universities in order to be the best corporate lawyer out there!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Have a dream to study law in top universities and become a corporate lawyer? Together with ALL-in, you can make your dream come true!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top uni preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p> Download FREE Guidebook for You; “A Guide To Polish Your Personal Brand For Top University Applications” and learn how to create a strong personal brand. <a href=\"https://personalbrand-guide.all-inedu.com/\">Download it FREE here</a> </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'Downloader.la-62a808710dedd.jpg', 'Corporate Lawyer: Facts You Need to Know', 'publish', 'Corporate Lawyer: Facts You Need to Know', 'Corporate Lawyer', 'What is a corporate lawyer? and What do you need to do to become a corporate lawyer? Read this article to get complete information', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-04-21 17:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2022-11-03 17:00:00'),
(11311, 'facts-and-outlook-of-criminal-lawyer', 7, 0, 'Facts and Outlook of Criminal Lawyer', '<p>Innocent until proven guilty. Have you ever heard this saying? This is the fundamental legal principle in criminal law. This profession helps a lot of people achieve justice, or at least, prove that they are not guilty. If you are aiming to become one of the best criminal lawyers out there, then this article is perfect for you.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Criminal law establishes the definition of criminal offenses as well as the laws and procedures that apply. Criminal law prohibits all kinds of behavior that endangers the public\'s welfare and property. Therefore, This covers everything from murder, theft, and arson, to motor crime, money laundering, and terrorism.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The criminal justice system serves two purposes. The law is used to regulate citizens\' behavior, but it also assists people in understanding the consequences of their acts. This is because criminal law also deals with the punishment and rehabilitation of people who break the rules.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>What is a Criminal Lawyer?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Due to the broad nature of the profession and the vastness of criminal law, there is no one blueprint detailing the job description for a Criminal <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/get-to-know-all-kinds-of-lawyer/\">Lawyer</a>. In the subject of criminal law, there are various different sorts of attorneys. These are:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Criminal Defense Attorney</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>A Criminal Defense Attorney represents someone who is accused or charged with a crime in court, ensuring that their legal rights are protected and that they receive a fair trial.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Criminal Duty</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>A Criminal Duty Solicitor is another form of Criminal Defense Lawyer. This profession represents those who are suspected or accused of committing crimes but do not have access to a lawyer, whether they are in police custody or not. They provide pro bono (free) services because the Legal Services Commission, the government agency that provides Legal Aid, pays them.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Neither the courts nor the police force hires criminal duty solicitors. Criminal Duty Lawyers work for a group of Solicitors to ensure that they protect the accused\'s legal rights. A Duty Solicitor can help those who have been arrested or held at a police station, as well as accompany them to their initial court appearance. They can\'t aid if the accused already has a lawyer, is in court, or has been charged with a crime that doesn\'t carry a sentence of imprisonment.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Criminal Prosecutor</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The UK has what is called a Crown Prosecutor or Prosecution Lawyer. A profession that is in charge of presenting the case against persons accused of a crime. The Crown Prosecution Service (CPS) is a government department that employs them.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A prosecutor\'s position differs from that of a defense attorney not just in terms of who they represent, but also in terms of whether or not to prosecute the accused and take the matter to court.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>How do you become a Criminal Lawyer?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Criminal lawyers, like all lawyers, must first earn a bachelor\'s degree before pursuing a law degree. The two degrees usually take seven years to accomplish in total. Criminal defense lawyers must pass the bar test in the state where they plan to practice. In the USA, the National Board of Legal Specialty Certification awards board certification to some criminal lawyers.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Criminal Lawyer Job Outlook</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>As there are new criminal laws and more people are charging under state and federal laws, the demand for criminal defense attorneys will increase. According to the Bureau of Labor Statistics, job growth for all attorneys, including criminal attorneys, is growing 8% between 2016 and 2026, higher than other occupations and industries.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Other career paths in criminal law include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Parole/Probation Officer</li><li>Paralegal/Legal Assistant</li><li>Legislator</li><li>Youth Correctional Counselor</li><li>Criminal Profiler</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>A job as a criminal lawyer is very promising. As the profession is broadly needed not only by people who do not understand the law but also by those people who need to clear their names of any criminal accusation. If you have the passion to fight for someone\'s innocence, this is the best career for you.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Are you interested in studying criminal law? Prepare your academic journey to top universities around the globe with ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top uni preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p> Download FREE Guidebook for You; “A Guide To Polish Your Personal Brand For Top University Applications” and learn how to create a strong personal brand. <a href=\"https://personalbrand-guide.all-inedu.com/\">Download it FREE here</a> </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!</p>', 'Downloader.la-62a80b55dc4d5.jpg', 'Facts and Outlook of Criminal Lawyer', 'publish', '', 'Criminal Lawyer', 'Criminal Lawyer may sound familiar in your ear. This profession make sure that the innocent get the justice they deserved. Curious? Find out more!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-04-20 17:00:00', '2022-06-26 17:00:00', '2022-11-03 17:00:00'),
(11316, 'your-complete-guide-on-international-lawyer', 7, 0, 'Your Complete Guide on International Lawyer', '<p>Any student today is interested in becoming an international lawyer. And who wouldn\'t want to be one? These are the people who advise government bodies, corporations, and organizations, where they make and shape laws that affect citizens throughout the world. Therefore, let\'s dive deep into the world of international law!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>What is international law?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>International law, also known as public international law and the law of nations, is a field of law that is concerned with the rules, regulations, principles, and practices that govern the relations between nations, international organizations, and individuals.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The field of international law covers a broad range of topics, including:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Trade and investment law</li><li>International environmental law</li><li>Human rights</li><li>International humanitarian law</li><li>Diplomatic law</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>What is an international lawyer?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>As an international lawyer, you may be working for a law firm, an organization, or a government entity, where you can specialize in one area, such as contract, corporate, customs, immigration, or tax. Moreover, from advising to representing individuals or organizations, you\'ll help resolve legal issues for your clients to bring about the best possible outcome.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>International lawyers may be called upon to represent individuals when they are involved in legal disputes or other matters requiring legal representation. They may also work for large corporations who need assistance in complying with international laws governing their operations in foreign countries or advising them on legal matters concerning mergers, acquisitions, or any multinational business undertakings.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Some international lawyers may also work for non-profits in the private sector, offering legal advice for those who may not be able to afford a lawyer.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>How do you become one?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Before becoming an international lawyer, you will first have to complete an undergraduate degree program. Moreover, this is the requirement for getting into any type of postgraduate or law school program. Also, there is no specific undergraduate field of study required to attend law school. Nonetheless, many law students possess undergraduate degrees in economics, government, or history.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You may benefit from completing a bachelor\'s program in international studies. This is due to these programs offering courses on topics such as politics, economics, and culture. These programs will help you develop a strong knowledge base before starting your law school education. You may also gain a deeper understanding of how different countries interact with one another economically and politically.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>After obtaining an undergraduate degree, you may continue your education in international law by obtaining a Master\'s degree in International Law. Some schools may offer elective courses in international law such as comparative law, international business law, international sales and trade, foreign policy, international legal research, and arbitration of international disputes.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Job Prospect of an International Lawyer</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>According to the US Bureau of Labor Statistics, the job field for all kinds of lawyers in the United States is set to grow by around 9% between 2020 and 2030. Which is average for all jobs in the United States. The BLS also reports that the median annual salary for all kinds of lawyers is about $126,930 in 2020.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are someone who is only interested in pursuing a bachelor\'s degree, there are professions in international law that are available for you. Furthermore, these professions are a mediator, arbitrator, or conciliator. Aside from bringing different parties to an agreement, you would also still have the opportunity to bring closure to legal matters outside of court.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Best universities to study law</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>According to the latest QS World University Rankings for Law & Legal Studies, here are the top 10 universities to study law:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Harvard University&nbsp;</li><li>University of Oxford&nbsp;</li><li>University of Cambridge&nbsp;</li><li>Yale University</li><li>Stanford University</li><li>New York University&nbsp;</li><li>The London School of Economics and Political Science</li><li>Columbia University</li><li>University of California, Berkeley</li><li>University of Chicago&nbsp;</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>If you\'re interested in becoming an international lawyer, try to develop a better understanding of your future career options before moving forward. Remember, all it takes is hard work and dedication to help you succeed in your future endeavors!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dreaming of becoming an international <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/get-to-know-all-kinds-of-lawyer/\">lawyer</a>? Let\'s set you up for success with ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top uni preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p> Download FREE Guidebook for You; “A Guide To Polish Your Personal Brand For Top University Applications” and learn how to create a strong personal brand. <a href=\"https://personalbrand-guide.all-inedu.com/\">Download it FREE here</a> </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!</p>', 'Downloader.la-62a80dafebdbf.jpg', 'Your Complete Guide on International Lawyer', 'publish', '', 'International Lawyer', 'Do you have interest to become the best international lawyer and solve global conflicts for better future? Then, this article is perfect fo you!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-04-19 17:00:00', '2022-06-17 17:00:00', '2022-11-03 17:00:00');
INSERT INTO `tb_blog` (`id`, `slug`, `cat_id`, `mt_id`, `blog_title`, `blog_description`, `blog_thumbnail`, `blog_thumbnail_alt`, `blog_status`, `seo_title`, `seo_keyword`, `seo_desc`, `lang`, `click_count`, `duration_read`, `is_highlight`, `publish_date`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(11320, 'get-to-know-all-kinds-of-lawyer', 7, 0, 'Get to Know All Kinds of Lawyer', '<p>When most people think of a lawyer they think of grilling witnesses in a courtroom, court cases, and a lot of behind-the-scenes drama. This is partially true — lawyers do argue a lot. But there\'s more to being an attorney than just arguing. Here\'s a list of careers that you can pursue after becoming a lawyer. Let\'s start with the basics: what is a lawyer?</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>What is a lawyer?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A lawyer is a person who has gone a lot of training and has a license to prepare, handle, and prosecute or defend a court case on behalf of another person, as well as provide legal advice on situations that do not require judicial action.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Lawyers are professionals who apply the law to specific situations. They gather facts and evidence by speaking with their clients and reviewing documents, then writing and filing pleadings in court. They present evidence, ask witnesses and debate legal and factual issues during the trial. If they don\'t win the case, often they can ask for a fresh trial or redress in an appellate court.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Law is applicable in a lot of ways, which means there are a lot of areas that require the presence of a lawyer. Here are some paths that you can choose as a lawyer:</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/corporate-lawyer-facts-you-need-to-know/\">Corporate Lawyer</a></strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A corporate lawyer\'s job is to advise clients on their legal rights, responsibilities, and obligations.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>When a corporation hires a corporate lawyer, the lawyer represents the corporation itself rather than its shareholders or employees. This may be a difficult notion to grasp until you realize that a business is treated similarly to a person in the eyes of the law.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A corporation is a legal body formed under state law with the primary aim of conducting business. A company is treated as a legal entity or \"person\" separate from its owners or shareholders.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The approach of becoming a corporate lawyer is similar to that of becoming a lawyer in other fields. To practice law as a corporate lawyer, one must first complete law school and acquire a Juris Doctor (J.D.) degree. Furthermore, corporate lawyers should have exceptional writing, communication, and negotiation skills because these talents are largely dependent upon in day-to-day business law practice.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/facts-and-outlook-of-criminal-lawyer/\">Criminal Lawyer</a></strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Due to the broad nature of the profession and the vastness of criminal law, there is no one blueprint detailing the job description for a criminal lawyer. In the subject of criminal law, there are different sorts of attorneys. These are:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Criminal Defense Attorney</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>A Criminal Defense Attorney represents someone who is accused or charged with a crime in court, ensuring that their legal rights are protected and that they receive a fair trial.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Criminal Duty</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>A Criminal Duty Solicitor is another form of Criminal Defense Lawyer. This profession represents those who are suspected or accused of committing crimes but do not have access to a lawyer, whether they are in police custody or not. They provide pro bono (free) services because the Legal Services Commission, the government agency that provides Legal Aid, pays them.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Criminal Prosecutor</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>A Crown Prosecutor or Prosecution Lawyer is in charge of presenting the case against persons accused of a crime. The Crown Prosecution Service (CPS) is a government department that employs them.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Criminal lawyers, like all lawyers, must first earn a bachelor\'s degree before pursuing a law degree. The two degrees usually take seven years to accomplish in total. Criminal defense lawyers must pass the bar test in the state where they plan to practice. In the USA, the National Board of Legal Specialty Certification awards board certification to criminal lawyers.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/your-complete-guide-on-international-lawyer/\">International Lawyer</a></strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>As an international lawyer, you may be working for a law firm, a multinational organization, or a government entity. On the other hand, you can specialize in one area, such as contract, corporate, customs, immigration, or tax. From advising, and counseling, to representing individuals or organizations, you\'ll help resolve legal issues for your clients to bring about the best possible outcome.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Before becoming an international lawyer, you will first have to complete an undergraduate degree program, as this is the requirement of getting into any type of postgraduate or law school program. While there is no specific undergraduate field of study to attend law school, many law students possess undergraduate degrees in economics, government, or history.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You may benefit from completing a bachelor\'s program in international studies as these programs offer courses on topics such as politics, economics, and culture, which help you develop a strong knowledge base before starting your law school education. You may also gain a deeper understanding of how different countries interact with one another economically and politically.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Conclusion</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The amount of career options for lawyers is nearly limitless. A lawyer can be a part of the judicial system, working for courts and judges, and many argue that the best job for a lawyer is working for the government. This would allow you to really reform the system, especially in terms of getting opinions from different areas in the government. It\'s important to know that law school can be extremely difficult and it will take a lot of time and hard work on your end just to get your degree. However, with the right support and enough determination, anything is possible.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Are you interested in becoming a lawyer? Prepare to enter top law universities with ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top uni preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Download FREE Guidebook for You; “A Guide To Polish Your Personal Brand For Top University Applications” and learn how to create a strong personal brand. <a href=\"https://personalbrand-guide.all-inedu.com/\">Download it FREE here</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!</p>', 'Downloader.la-62a80facf26d8.jpg', 'Get to Know All Kinds of Lawyer', 'publish', '', 'Lawyer', 'Have a dream to become the best lawyer in the future? Read this article to find out facts about all kinds of lawyer out there!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-04-18 17:00:00', '2022-06-18 17:00:00', '2022-10-26 17:00:00'),
(11325, 'prospek-kerja-jurusan-akuntansi-di-masa-depan', 8, 0, 'Prospek Kerja Jurusan Akuntansi di Masa Depan', '<p>Jurusan Akuntansi adalah salah satu jurusan yang paling banyak digemari pelajar di Indonesia. Hal ini karena prospek kerja <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/mengenal-lebih-dalam-tentang-jurusan-akuntansi/\">jurusan akuntansi</a> sangatlah luas. Profesi ini xdibutuhkan untuk mengurusi segala macam urusan keuangan yang dimiliki sebuah perusahaan atau instansi. Maka dari itu, jurusan ini akan selalu dicari dan mempunyai prospek kerja di masa depan yang sangat bagus.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Akuntan adalah orang yang menyimpan atau memeriksa catatan keuangan. Profesi ini berisi orang-orang yang unggul dalam organisasi dan pekerjaan yang berorientasi pada detail. Hal ini karena mereka berurusan dengan uang yang terkadang dalam jumlah yang signifikan. Di sisi lain, akuntan juga harus memiliki tingkat integritas yang tinggi.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Pekerjaan akuntan dan auditor diproyeksikan tumbuh 7 persen dari 2020 hingga 2030, sama dengan rata-rata untuk semua pekerjaan. Sekitar 135.000 lowongan untuk akuntan dan auditor diproyeksikan setiap tahun, rata-rata, selama dekade ini.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Berikut adalah beberapa karir yang bisa kamu ambil setelah menyelesaikan jurusan akuntansi:</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Auditor</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Auditor adalah aktivitas konsultasi dan asuransi yang independen dan objektif yang dirancang untuk menambah nilai dan meningkatkan operasi organisasi. Ini membantu organisasi mencapai tujuannya dengan membawa pendekatan yang sistematis dan disiplin untuk mengevaluasi dan meningkatkan efektivitas manajemen risiko, kontrol, dan proses tata kelola.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Pekerjaan ini dijalankan oleh para profesional dengan pemahaman mendalam tentang budaya, sistem, dan proses bisnis, aktivitas audit internal memberikan jaminan bahwa pengendalian internal yang ada cukup untuk mengurangi risiko, proses tata kelola yang efektif dan efisien, dan tujuan serta sasaran organisasi sesuai.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Financial Analyst</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Analis Keuangan bertanggung jawab atas perencanaan dan analisis keuangan perusahaan, memungkinkan organisasi untuk membuat keputusan komersial yang terinformasi dengan baik. Analis Keuangan harus kemampuan untuk menentukan penggunaan terbaik sumber daya untuk mencapai tujuan bisnis. Mereka diharapkan menghasilkan laporan rutin menggunakan data keuangan, dan bekerja sama di seluruh tim keuangan untuk menganalisis kinerja dan strategi bisnis.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Analis keuangan memperkirakan pendapatan dan pengeluaran di masa depan untuk membantu menentukan anggaran untuk proyek yang akan datang. Deskripsi pekerjaan financial analyst berpusat pada penelitian dan pelaporan informasi keuangan, serta memantau pergerakan keuangan di pasar.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Controller</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Prospek kerja jurusan akuntansi yang satu ini mungkin sedikit aneh di telinga. Sebagai pemimpin tim akuntansi, <em>controller</em> bertanggung jawab untuk memantau dengan cermat kesehatan keuangan perusahaan. Mereka biasanya memelihara, mengelola, dan menganalisis laporan keuangan, penggajian, anggaran, masalah kepatuhan pajak, dan banyak lagi.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Pakar keuangan ini bekerja di berbagai industri, baik untuk perusahaan besar maupun kecil. Dalam pengaturan perusahaan yang lebih besar, pengontrol sering mengawasi tim akuntan dan melapor langsung ke chief financial officer (CFO). Di perusahaan yang lebih kecil, pengontrol mungkin satu-satunya akuntan, bekerja dengan tim juru tulis dan melapor langsung ke pemilik atau CEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Chief Financial Officer</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Seorang chief financial officer (CFO) adalah profesional keuangan dengan peringkat tertinggi dalam sebuah organisasi dan bertanggung jawab atas kesehatan fiskal bisnis. Tanggung jawab CFO termasuk, tetapi tidak terbatas pada, membangun tim keuangan dan akuntansi terbaik, memastikan pendapatan dan pengeluaran tetap seimbang, mengawasi fungsi FP&A (perencanaan & analisis keuangan), membuat rekomendasi tentang merger dan akuisisi, memperoleh pendanaan, bekerja dengan kepala departemen untuk menganalisis data keuangan dan menyusun anggaran, membuktikan keakuratan laporan dan berkonsultasi dengan dewan direksi dan CEO tentang strategi.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>CFO juga dapat membantu menetapkan arah teknologi, terutama fintech, dan membuat rekomendasi tentang segala hal mulai dari rantai pasokan hingga pemasaran berdasarkan wawasan fiskal dan pengetahuan industri mereka.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ciri-ciri CFO terbaik adalah visioner. Seorang CFO wajib memiliki pandangan ke masa depan, bekerja sama dengan pimpinan puncak dan tidak malu untuk merekomendasikan langkah strategis.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Cukup beragam kan profesi yang bisa kamu pilih sebagai prospek kerja jurusan akuntansi? Jika kamu mempunyai mimpi untuk menjadi akuntan terbaik hingga bisa menjadi CFO, kamu juga memerlukan kualitas pendidikan terbaik ya.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ingin menggapai karir setinggi mungkin? Ayo masuk ke universitas top dunia besarama Eduverse by ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!</p>\n\n\n\n<p> Download FREE Guidebooks Kami yang akan membantu Kamu untuk mendaftar beasiswa. <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/id/\">Download GRATIS disini</a> </p>', 'Downloader.la-62a811511cc92.jpg', 'Prospek Kerja Jurusan Akuntansi di Masa Depan', 'publish', '', 'Prospek Kerja Jurusan Akuntansi', 'Prospek kerja jurusan akuntansi merupakan salah satu yang paling banyak peluangnya di dunia kerja. Penasaran? Ayo cari tahu lebih lengkapnya di sini!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-04-08 17:00:00', '2022-06-12 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(11331, 'universitas-terbaik-untuk-kuliah-jurusan-akuntansi', 2, 0, 'Universitas Terbaik untuk Kuliah Jurusan Akuntansi', '<p>Apa kamu punya mimpi untuk kuliah <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/mengenal-lebih-dalam-tentang-jurusan-akuntansi/\">jurusan akuntansi</a> di universitas top dunia? Sebagai salah satu profesi yang paling banyak peminatnya di dunia, kamu wajib untuk membangung dirimu dengan kualitas pendidikan terbaik juga. Hal ini agar kamu mampu menjadi yang paling hebat di bidang tersebut.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ada banyak sekali universitas yang menawarkan kuliah jurusan akuntansi untuk pelajar internasionalnya. Tapi, untuk bisa bersaing dengan yang terbaik, kamu perlu masuk ke universitas terbaik di dunia juga.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>5. University of Chicago</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Terakhir, fakultas akuntansi dan keuangan Universitas Chicago berbasis di Booth School of Business, yang menawarkan program PhD dan MBA. Kepentingan penelitian yang relevan termasuk pelaporan keuangan eksternal dan isu-isu pengungkapan, peraturan sekuritas, pelaporan keuangan internasional dan peran akuntansi dalam kontrak.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>4. University of Oxford</strong>, Universitas Kuliah Jurusan Akuntansi</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>University of Oxford terletak di Oxfordshire, Inggris. Sekolah ini didirikan pada abad ke-12 dan meniru Universitas Paris, dengan fakultas awal teologi, hukum, kedokteran, dan seni liberal. Sebagai salah satu universitas tertua di Inggris, Oxford memiliki kualitas pendidikan terbaik di berbagai macam bidang, salah satunya adalah akuntansi.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>University of Oxford tidak memiliki program sarjana khusus di bidang akuntansi dan/atau keuangan, meskipun mata pelajaran ini tersedia dalam gelar ekonomi dan manajemen. Program ini menawarkan beberapa program master yang berbeda di bidang keuangan, baik secara tunggal atau dalam kombinasi dengan mata pelajaran kedua, dan Saïd Business School-nya adalah rumah bagi kelompok penelitian terkenal internasional yang berfokus pada akuntansi dan keuangan.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>3. Massachusetts Institute of Technology (MIT)</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Massachusetts Institute of Technology (MIT), lembaga pendidikan tinggi yang diatur dan dijalankan secara private. Universitas ini memang sangat terkenal dengan pelatihan dan penelitian ilmiah dan teknologinya. Namun, hal ini tidak menutup kemungkinan bahwa MIT juga menjadi yang terdepan di bidang akuntansi dan keuangan.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>MIT, yang saat ini menduduki peringkat satu dalam QS World University Rankings, juga memiliki sekolah bisnisnya sendiri yang terkenal di dunia – MIT Sloan School of Management. Sekali lagi menjadi program akuntansi dan keuangan universitas yang luar biasa bagus dan juga mempunyai&nbsp; kelompok penelitian yang didedikasikan untuk kedua bidang tersebut. Pusat penelitian yang relevan termasuk laboratorium untuk <em>Financial Engineering</em>, <em>Center for Energy and Environmental Policy Research</em>, dan <em>MIT Center for Digital Business</em>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>2. Stanford University</strong>, Universitas Kuliah Jurusan Akuntansi </h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Stanford merupakan salah satu universitas terbaik di dunia. Kualitas pendidikan di universitas ini merupakan salah satu yang terbaik di dunia. Menurut QS World University Ranking, di fakultas ilmu komunikasi, Stanford menduduki urutan keempat terbaik di dunia. Stanford memiliki tingkat penerimaan sebesar 5.2%.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sekolah bisnis Stanford disebut juga Stanford Graduate School of Business. Penelitian akuntansi di sekolah saat ini berfokus pada isu-isu yang berkaitan dengan pelaporan keuangan dan pengendalian manajemen, termasuk strategi penilaian berbasis akuntansi dan desain pengukuran kinerja dan sistem insentif. Sementara topik utama untuk penelitian keuangan di Stanford meliputi penetapan harga aset dan keuangan perusahaan, termasuk analisis keputusan investasi.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>1. Harvard University</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Universitas yang tidak perlu diperkenalkan ini mendapat urutan pertama untuk jurusan akuntansi menurut QS World University Ranking 2022. Harvard merupakan salah satu universitas tertua di Amerika Serikat yang sudah memberikan kualitas pendidikan terbaik sejak sekolah ini pertama berdiri.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Harvard Business School yang bergengsi tidak diragukan lagi merupakan salah satu sekolah universitas yang paling terkenal. Penelitian di bidang akuntansi dan manajemen di sekolah ini tengah berfokus pada penggunaan sistem pengukuran kinerja untuk membantu bisnis berkomunikasi dengan investor eksternal, meningkatkan alokasi dan strategi sumber daya, dan membangun akuntabilitas. Hal ini membuat lulusan Harvard Business School banyak dilirik oleh perusahaan top dunia.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Bagus-bagus kan universitas top dunia untuk kuliah jurusan akuntansi? Seperti yang tertulis di atas, beberapa universitas menawarkan sistem pendidikan yang berbeda. Namun hal ini tidak mengubah fakta kalau kelima universitas di atas merupakan universitas terbaik di dunia untuk kamu kuliah jurusan akuntansi.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Mimpi kuliah jurusan akuntansi di universitas top dunia? Persiapkan semuanya dengan EDUVERSE by ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!</p>\n\n\n\n<p> Download FREE Guidebooks Kami yang akan membantu Kamu untuk mendaftar beasiswa. <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/id/\">Download GRATIS disini</a> </p>', 'Downloader.la-62a812816a472.jpg', 'Universitas Terbaik untuk Kuliah Jurusan Akuntansi', 'publish', '', 'Kuliah Jurusan Akuntansi', 'Apa kamu tertarik untuk melanjutkan kuliah jurusan akuntansi? Berikut adalah daftar universitas terbaik yang bisa kamu pertimbangkan di masa depan!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-04-09 17:00:00', '2022-06-21 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(11338, 'mengenal-lebih-dalam-tentang-jurusan-akuntansi', 2, 0, 'Mengenal Lebih Dalam tentang Jurusan Akuntansi', '<p>Apa sih sebenarnya jurusan akuntansi itu? Kenapa ilmu ini sangat penting? Kamu pasti mulai bertanya-tanya mengenai ilmu ini sejak awal kamu belajar di bangku sekolah. Ternyata, ilmu akuntansi merupakan salah satu ilmu penting yang mempunyai prospek kerja yang bagus lho. Penasaran? Ayo cek di bawah!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Apa itu Jurusan Akuntansi?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Akuntansi adalah ilmu pencatatan dan penyajian data keuangan suatu entitas ekonomi dengan mengamati, mendeteksi, menyelidiki, dan mengidentifikasi peristiwa ekonomi melalui metode pengumpulan, pengujian, analisis dan penyajian yang mapan.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Akuntansi seperti sains mengikuti jalur yang sistematis dan terorganisir untuk memahami status ekonomi entitas. Penerapan ilmu akuntansi berpusat pada pengetahuan tentang pola yang sistematis termasuk pengamatan, studi, praktik, eksperimen, dan penyelidikan di bidang ekonomi. Hal ini termasuk melihat kebiasaan konsumen, arus uang, dll.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/prospek-kerja-jurusan-akuntansi-di-masa-depan/\">Prospek Kerja Jurusan Akuntansi</a></strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Prospek kerja ilmu akuntansi di masa depan salah satu yang terbaik. Hal ini karena kebutuhan untuk profesi di bidang ini selalu meningkat setiap tahunnya. Di sisi lain, semua perusahaan dan instansi wajib memerlukan seseorang yang bisa mengatur dan mengawasi arus uang mereka.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Berikut adalah prospek kerja di bidang akuntansi:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Internal Auditor</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Internal Auditor adalah aktivitas konsultasi dan asuransi yang independen dan objektif yang dirancang untuk menambah nilai dan meningkatkan operasi organisasi. Ini membantu organisasi mencapai tujuannya dengan membawa pendekatan yang sistematis dan disiplin untuk mengevaluasi dan meningkatkan efektivitas manajemen risiko, kontrol, dan proses tata kelola.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Pekerjaan ini dijalankan oleh para profesional dengan pemahaman mendalam tentang budaya, sistem, dan proses bisnis, aktivitas audit internal memberikan jaminan bahwa pengendalian internal yang ada cukup untuk mengurangi risiko, proses tata kelola yang efektif dan efisien, dan tujuan serta sasaran organisasi sesuai.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Chief Financial Officer</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Seorang chief financial officer (CFO) adalah profesional keuangan dengan peringkat tertinggi dalam sebuah organisasi dan bertanggung jawab atas kesehatan fiskal bisnis. Tanggung jawab CFO termasuk, tetapi tidak terbatas pada, membangun tim keuangan dan akuntansi terbaik, memastikan pendapatan dan pengeluaran tetap seimbang, mengawasi fungsi FP&A (perencanaan & analisis keuangan), membuat rekomendasi tentang merger dan akuisisi, memperoleh pendanaan, bekerja dengan kepala departemen untuk menganalisis data keuangan dan menyusun anggaran, membuktikan keakuratan laporan dan berkonsultasi dengan dewan direksi dan CEO tentang strategi.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>CFO juga dapat membantu menetapkan arah teknologi, terutama fintech, dan membuat rekomendasi tentang segala hal mulai dari rantai pasokan hingga pemasaran berdasarkan wawasan fiskal dan pengetahuan industri mereka.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ciri-ciri CFO terbaik adalah visioner. Seorang CFO wajib memiliki pandangan ke masa depan, bekerja sama dengan pimpinan puncak dan tidak malu untuk merekomendasikan langkah strategis.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color has-vivid-cyan-blue-color\"><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/prospek-kerja-jurusan-akuntansi-di-masa-depan/\">Ingin tahu dengan prospek kerja lainnya? Baca di sini!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Universitas Terbaik untuk <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/universitas-terbaik-untuk-kuliah-jurusan-akuntansi/\">Kuliah Jurusan Akuntansi</a></strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Jika kamu ingin menjadi seorang profesional terbaik di bidang akuntansi, kamu tentunya juga perlu untuk masuk ke universitas terbaik di dunia yang menyediakan ilmu ini pula. Hal ini karena perusahaan multinasional akan cenderung melirik ke lulusan top dunia.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Berikut adalah daftar universitasnya:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>5. University of Chicago</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Fakultas akuntansi dan keuangan Universitas Chicago berbasis di Booth School of Business, yang menawarkan program PhD dan MBA. Kepentingan penelitian yang relevan termasuk pelaporan keuangan eksternal dan isu-isu pengungkapan, peraturan sekuritas, pelaporan keuangan internasional dan peran akuntansi dalam kontrak.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>4. University of Oxford</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>University of Oxford tidak memiliki program sarjana khusus di bidang akuntansi dan/atau keuangan, meskipun mata pelajaran ini tersedia dalam gelar ekonomi dan manajemen. Program ini menawarkan beberapa program master yang berbeda di bidang keuangan, baik secara tunggal atau dalam kombinasi dengan mata pelajaran kedua, dan Saïd Business School-nya adalah rumah bagi kelompok penelitian terkenal internasional yang berfokus pada akuntansi dan keuangan.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>3. Massachusetts Institute of Technology (MIT)</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>MIT, yang saat ini menduduki peringkat satu dalam QS World University Rankings, juga memiliki sekolah bisnisnya sendiri yang terkenal di dunia – MIT Sloan School of Management. Sekali lagi menjadi program akuntansi dan keuangan universitas yang luar biasa bagus dan juga mempunyai&nbsp; kelompok penelitian yang didedikasikan untuk kedua bidang tersebut. Pusat penelitian yang relevan termasuk laboratorium untuk <em>Financial Engineering</em>, <em>Center for Energy and Environmental Policy Research</em>, dan <em>MIT Center for Digital Business</em>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color has-vivid-cyan-blue-color\"><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/universitas-terbaik-untuk-kuliah-jurusan-akuntansi/\">Penasaran dengan universitas terbaik lainnya? Cari tahu lebih lengkapnya di sini!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sangat banyak yang perlu kamu tahu tentang ilmu akuntansi sebelum akhirnya kamu memilih untuk melanjutkan studi di jurusan ini. Salah satu yang paling penting adalah mengenai prospek karir di masa depannya. Bagaimanapun juga, selama uang masih menjadi alat transaksi, ilmu ini akan selalu dipakai ke depannya.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Punya mimpi untuk belajar ilmu akuntansi di universitas top dunia? EDUVERSE by ALL-in akan membantu semua persiapanmu.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download FREE Guidebooks Kami yang akan membantu Kamu untuk mendaftar beasiswa. <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/id/\">Download GRATIS disini</a></p>', 'Downloader.la-62a815f891c55.jpg', 'Mengenal Lebih Dalam tentang Jurusan Akuntansi', 'publish', 'Mengenal Lebih Dalam tentang Jurusan Akuntansi', 'Jurusan Akuntansi', 'Jurusan akuntansi merupakan jurusan yang banyak peminatnya di kalangan pelajar. Ingin mengenal lebih jauh tentang jurusan ini? Baca lengkapnya di sini!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-04-10 17:00:00', '2022-06-02 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(11394, 'reasons-why-you-should-study-a-level-math', 3, 0, 'Reasons why you should study A Level Math', '<p>When you are choosing <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/learn-to-choose-a-level-subjects-here/\">A-Level</a> subjects, you need to choose the best for you. Everyone\'s interests are different, and you need to consider your own goals and strengths when choosing your subjects. If you are still confused or considering between subjects, this article is perfect for you! We are going to find out 5 great reasons why you should consider choosing A level Maths.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>When you are studying A-level Maths and Further Maths, the syllabi for each of these subjects vary from school to school and depend on the test board used. There are two groups of topics for A-level Maths by Edexcel: Pure Maths and Applied Maths. Algebra, differentiation, vectors, trigonometry, statistical sampling and testing, mechanics, kinematics, and probability are examples of specific areas of study.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>These might seem like a lot to learn, but learning them is actually very beneficial for you. Don\'t believe us? Take a look at the good reasons why you should choose to take A-level Maths!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>A-Level <strong>Math is the key to the future</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Mathematics plays an increasingly important part in both ordinary and corporate life as technology advances. Every day, scientists found and refind new mathematical ideas, allowing technologies and scientific discoveries to grow. Studying A-level Maths will help you be able to keep up with these new advances.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Applicable Benefits</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Mathematical knowledge offers numerous benefits that extend beyond the subject itself. If you want to pursue courses like Economics, Physics, Computer Science, or Engineering at the university level, having a solid mathematics background will help you do better in these subjects. Some majors will even require you to take A-level Maths!<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Practical Skills</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Math allows you to improve your capacity to tackle mathematical, abstract, and scientific problems. These problem-solving abilities can subsequently be applied to a wide range of situations in your life. You\'ll also learn how to analyze patterns, structures, and problems, which will aid in the development of critical thinking skills. This will be useful in both further education and future employment. Maths at A-Level will provide you with analytical abilities that will enable you to solve issues and analyze theories. Finally, you will hone your logical skills so that you have the tools you need to face a variety of tasks, ranging from financial management to planning projects.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>A-Level Math is <strong>Applicable Over Many Areas</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A-Level Math is a versatile subject that can be combined with a variety of other numerically based subjects. It can be studied in conjunction with disciplines like chemistry or physics, as well as subjects like economics, accounting and finance, and information technology. Maths also pairs with English or History if you want to keep your choices open when it comes to further education and careers.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Entrepreneurial Advantage</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>f you ever decide to start your own business, a thorough understanding of math will assist you in establishing your organization, from calculating costs and profits to managing your money. A-Level Maths will equip you with the abilities you\'ll need to negotiate the business world, whether on your own or as part of a larger organization.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are someone who likes a challenge and enjoys solving problems in a logical way, then this subject could be right for you.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Are you planning to take the A-level program? If so, choosing a handful of subjects isn\'t a decision you should take lightly. The A-levels you pick now can impact what you do later, especially in top university applications.<br><br><a href=\"https://alevel-guide.all-inedu.com/\">Download “The Complete Guide In Choosing A-Level Subjects” Guidebook to help you select your subjects wisely!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Need more help before choosing your A-level subjects? Get your further guidance and consult with the expert on A-Level <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/\">here</a>!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'Downloader.la-62b52c740cb8d.jpg', 'Reasons why you should study A Level Math', 'publish', 'Reasons why you should study A Level Math. Read this article and find out', 'A Level Math', 'Still wondering why you should choose A-Level Math? No more! Read this article and find out all the benefits you can get from A-Level Math', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-04-26 17:00:00', '2022-06-10 17:00:00', '2022-11-04 17:00:00'),
(11400, 'a-level-biology-all-you-need-to-know', 3, 0, 'A-Level Biology: All You Need to Know!', '<p>Is A-level Biology right for you? If so, here\'s everything you need to know about choosing and studying the right course. Whether you\'re applying now or next year (or even further down the line), it\'s always a good idea to look into your options now. Let\'s find out all the good reasons why you should choose Biology as one of your <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/learn-to-choose-a-level-subjects-here/\">A-level</a> subjects.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A-level Biology is an enthralling subject in which you will learn about the biological world and all of the living beings that inhabit it. Getting an A-level certificate in this subject opens up a world of possibilities for university degrees and career opportunities.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Students take Biology for a variety of reasons: it may be a requirement for a degree, or they may have an interest in the human body or the natural world. This subject covers a wide range of topics that appeal to a diverse group of pupils. Many degrees in medical disciplines of study and Biological Sciences require an A-level Biology certification.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Why study A-Level Biology?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>You will first learn about biological molecules, genetic information, and energy transfers in the A-level Biology subject. You\'ll then learn how these aspects affect how organisms adapt to their surroundings, genetic populations, and gene expression control.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This may be the subject for you if you are a gifted biologist who wishes to study the subject at a much higher degree of complexity and pursue the sciences in higher education. It is recommended that you take this course in conjunction with math or another science. The course includes a variety of instructional methods, including lectures, demonstrations, and group and one-on-one tutorial sessions.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can pursue many degrees after studying A-level biology such as audiology, biological sciences, biochemistry, biomedical sciences, and dentistry. Many students go on to pursue careers in medicine, nursing, biomedical science, emergency and uniformed services, healthcare, laboratories, and medical administration.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You will have earned an internationally recognized AQA A-level Biology certificate after passing the test and practical assessments (as conducted by AQA).<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>What will you learn?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This subject will provide you with a thorough comprehension of complicated scientific processes. Also, it consisted filled with the examination of their significance for our global community.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You\'ll learn how to establish hypotheses, use evidence and logic, collaborate, study and scrutinize ideas and discoveries. Furthermore, you will need to be able to present them through well-referenced essays, reports, and examinations.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>What background do I need?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Most A-level Biology courses require grade 4 or higher in Biology (or double science), English, and Mathematics at the GCSE level.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Although there isn\'t much quantitative science work, You need to learn basic understanding of chemical principles. Chemistry A-level is required for many (but not all) biology-related degrees. Biology also necessitates math proficiency. You must be comfortable with data presented in tables and graphs, calculations, and the application of statistical tests.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Biology will help you succeed in other sciences and mathematical areas, as well as courses like geography and psychology – studying it at the A-level alongside a language or an essay subject like English may open up even more job opportunities.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With A-level Biology you can put your life and goals into context, and see exactly how they will benefit your life. It is a great subject to do and a career in the medical field has some of the highest-earning potential. If you want to learn more about this exciting subject, then check out our post below.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Are you planning to take the A-level program? If so, choosing a handful of subjects isn\'t a decision you should take lightly. The A-levels you pick now can impact what you do later, especially in top university applications.<br><br><a href=\"https://alevel-guide.all-inedu.com/\">Download “The Complete Guide In Choosing A-Level Subjects” Guidebook to help you select your subjects wisely!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'Downloader.la-62b572cfbdba6.jpg', 'A-Level Biology: All You Need to Know!', 'publish', 'A-Level Biology: All You Need to Know! Is A-level Biology right for you?', 'A Level Biology', 'A-Level Biology is a very useful and intriguing subject for you to choose. If you are still considering, read here to find out all the benefits you can get!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-04-23 17:00:00', '2022-06-02 17:00:00', '2022-11-03 17:00:00'),
(11406, 'this-is-why-you-should-study-a-level-economics', 3, 0, 'This is Why you should study A-Level Economics', '<p>Are you considering taking economics in your A-Level studies? As you may have already realized, choosing your A-level subjects is crucial for your future. You need to make sure that the subjects you choose are not only beneficial for your university application but also enjoyable for the 2 years you will be studying the <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/learn-to-choose-a-level-subjects-here/\">A-Level</a>. Here, we will tell you why choosing A Level Economics for your further studies is a good choice. Let\'s get to it!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>What is A-Level Economics?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>In A-Level Economics, you will learn about everything related to economics. This includes the market system, market failure, government intervention, the national and international economy, and the economics of work and leisure. You will also learn about the UK economy and economics in a European context to give you knowledge as broad as possible.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Not only that, you will get a lot of skills and insight to handle modern life with a broad knowledge of economics. There are a lot of university majors and career paths where taking A-Level Economics is preferred. In some cases, it is absolutely necessary. Moreover, studying economics will give you the qualification that shows that you have the ability to analyze and understand economic and financial subjects.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Why Study A-Level Economics?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The A-Level curriculum provides you with a solid foundation in topics that you will encounter when you pursue a profession in economics or pursue university studies. It may also be beneficial to students who plan to establish a business after graduation. Many students benefit personally from possessing a basic understanding of economics, regardless of their career goals. It can help you grasp issues like inflation and the economic consequences of unemployment, which will help you navigate the real world after high school.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>An A-Level education teaches pupils how to apply economic theory to a variety of real-world circumstances. Economics is an important subject that can help you gain skills to help you tackle obstacles once you graduate from university, such as determining the worth of commodities and planning for your retirement. It can also help you gain a comprehensive grasp of the impact economic difficulties have had in the past and present, as well as the tools you\'ll need to deal with them.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You\'ll most likely study specific topics and concepts related to economics within these major study umbrellas. Which disciplines are accessible to study depends on your school\'s individual curriculum. Furthermore, these can include the following:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Financial marketplaces</li><li>Production and efficiency in business</li><li>Government policy and intervention</li><li>The difference between economies and diseconomies of scale</li><li>Economics as a social science</li><li>The difference between production and productivity</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Entry Requirements</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Prior economics study or understanding is not required to begin an A-Level economics subject. All you need are the required GCSEs for admission to your chosen college. Which will almost certainly contain English and math. A good mark in both English and math can help you succeed in your studies, with a B or better being desirable. Even though economics isn\'t solely a math course, students with a C or lower in math may find it difficult to keep up. Furthermore, an interest in economics, logical thinking, problem-solving skills, and debate skills are all helpful in this study.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Economics is an important subject for all students. It gives you the tools to think about the world in a structured way. Also, you will be able to understand how to influence it with your choices. In other words, economics teaches you how to be a citizen of the world. The knowledge gained by studying economics at the A-Level will serve you well in your future career, whatever that may be.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Are you planning to take the A-level program? If so, choosing a handful of subjects isn\'t a decision you should take lightly. The A-levels you pick now can impact what you do later, especially in top university applications.<br><br><a href=\"https://alevel-guide.all-inedu.com/\">Download “The Complete Guide In Choosing A-Level Subjects” Guidebook to help you select your subjects wisely!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>What do you think? Need further guidance? Consult with experts on how to choose the most suitable A-Level subject <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/\">here</a>!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'Downloader.la-62b578965bd77.jpg', 'This is Why you should study A-Level Economics', 'publish', 'This is Why you should study A-Level Economics. Let’s get to it!', 'A Level Economics', 'Are you interested in taking A-Level Economics but still have doubt? Find out all you need to know about A-Level Economics in this article!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-04-24 17:00:00', '2022-06-06 17:00:00', '2022-11-03 17:00:00'),
(11411, 'should-you-choose-a-level-accounting', 3, 0, 'Should you choose A Level Accounting?', '<p>The best answer to this question is: it depends. Therefore, your A-Level subject selection has to suit your intended major. One of the subjects you need to consider is A-level accounting. In this article, you will find all the reasons to choose <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/learn-to-choose-a-level-subjects-here/\">A Level</a> Accounting.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>What is A-Level Accounting?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Accounting is recognized as the business language. Therefore, A-Level Accounting it\'s necessary for recording and presenting business activities in the form of business accounts, financial reporting in the form of financial statements, and the provision of pertinent economic data for management decision-making and control. Accounting accomplishes this through discovering, classifying, summarizing, and presenting financial data in order to aid decision-making and legal compliance. Moreover, it examines how companies can increase revenue, save on expenses, and distribute resources more effectively and efficiently.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>After passing the AS-level component, you can proceed on to the A2-level in accounting, the second course of study leading to the full A-level award. You will generally be studying the same topics as in the AS-level, but in greater detail and with greater rigor.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For example, after learning how to construct business accounts, you\'ll learn how to generate final accounts for the end of a tax year and for various business models, as well as learn accounting standards, international accounting issues, budgeting and cost control, and so on.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>What can you do with A-Level Accounting?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This subject will give a student one of the most in-demand talents in any industry. Furthermore, every business must have a thorough understanding of its financial health, and all businesses hire accountants to manage their finances. Also, Accounting expertise can come in handy if you want to be an entrepreneur in the future, work as a successful finance professional, or simply help run your family\'s business.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Students interested in pursuing a degree in accounting or business studies at university should do A-level Accounting. Also, almost all of these degrees will include a number of accounting modules.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Students who take A-Level Accounting have a lot of alternatives at university, and there are a lot of programs with permutations of Business/Management/Administration/Accounting and Finance.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Business graduates usually go into fields like business development, marketing, recruitment, and banking, though there are many other additional opportunities.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>What skills can you get from this subject?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>You\'ll learn how to analyze competitive environments and markets. Also, you are going to know the strategy to evaluate how ethical, environmental, and technological factors influence decision making and evaluate strategic and functional options using a variety of quantitative and non-quantitative data, and comprehend how decisions affect stakeholders and how they will react.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You\'ll improve your critical thinking, decision-making, and problem-solving abilities as well. Moreover, this course will provide you with knowledge and skills that may be used in a wide range of business and management domains, are transferable across many fields of study and professions, and can be utilized to manage your personal decision-making, planning, and budgeting.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Studying A-Level accounting can be very beneficial if you want to pursue a degree and career in banking and finance. Some degrees will even require you to take this subject. Nevertheless, this subject is important not only for your university applications but also to develop your own skills.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Are you planning to take the A-level program? If so, choosing a handful of subjects isn\'t a decision you should take lightly. The A-levels you pick now can impact what you do later, especially in top university applications.<br><br><a href=\"https://alevel-guide.all-inedu.com/\">Download “The Complete Guide In Choosing A-Level Subjects” Guidebook to help you select your subjects wisely!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Need help deciding your A-Level subjects? Get the thorough consultation you need only <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/\">here</a>!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'Downloader.la-62b57eaac13d3.jpg', 'Should you choose A Level Accounting?', 'publish', 'Should you choose A Level Accounting? Read Here for The Facts', 'A Level Accounting', 'Interested to take A-Level Accounting as your subject? Read this article and find out why you should take A-Level Accounting!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-04-25 17:00:00', '2022-06-26 17:00:00', '2022-11-03 17:00:00');
INSERT INTO `tb_blog` (`id`, `slug`, `cat_id`, `mt_id`, `blog_title`, `blog_description`, `blog_thumbnail`, `blog_thumbnail_alt`, `blog_status`, `seo_title`, `seo_keyword`, `seo_desc`, `lang`, `click_count`, `duration_read`, `is_highlight`, `publish_date`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(11417, 'learn-to-choose-a-level-subjects-here', 3, 0, 'Learn to Choose A-Level Subjects Here!', '<p>The most popularly talked about subject by tenth-graders right now across the country is probably which subjects they should and shouldn\'t take at A-level. The process can be really daunting and confusing, so why not get some advice from somebody who knows what they\'re talking about?</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>What are the A-Levels?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A-Levels (Advanced Level Qualifications) are subject-based qualifications available to students in the United Kingdom aged 16 and over. Students usually take them for two years and result in qualifications that are recognized for admission to university or any other higher education institution in the United Kingdom and around the world. Taking a minimum of three subjects is required by most higher education institutions.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Choosing A-Level subjects can be tricky, but that does not mean that you should just randomly choose them. You need to choose subjects that you like, are good at, and can be beneficial for your future. There\'s a delicate balance between these things that you need to maintain when choosing between subjects.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Still need more convincing? Here are a few great reasons why you should choose some of the A-level subjects!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Reasons why you should study A-Level Maths</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>When you are studying <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/reasons-why-you-should-study-a-level-math/\">A-level Maths</a> and Further Maths, the syllabus varies from school to school and depends on the test board used. Topics for A-level Maths are divided into two groups by Edexcel: Pure Maths and Applied Maths. Algebra, differentiation, vectors, trigonometry, statistical sampling and testing, mechanics, kinematics, and probability are examples of specific areas of study.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>They might seem like a lot to learn, but they can be very beneficial for you. Don\'t believe us? Take a look at the good reasons below why you should choose A-level Maths.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Math is the key to the future</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Mathematics plays an increasingly important part in both ordinary and industrial life as technology advances. Every day, new mathematical ideas are found and refined, allowing technologies and scientific discoveries to grow. You will be able to establish a profession at the cutting edge of technological innovation if you study Maths at A-Level.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Applicable Benefits</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Mathematical knowledge offers numerous benefits that extend beyond the subject itself. If you want to pursue courses like Economics, Physics, or Engineering at the university level, having a solid mathematics background will help you enjoy and do better in these subjects.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Practical Skills</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Math allows you to improve your capacity to tackle mathematical, abstract, and scientific problems. These problem-solving abilities can subsequently be applied to a wide range of situations in your life. You\'ll also learn how to analyze patterns, structures, and problems, which will aid in the development of critical thinking skills. This will be useful in both further education and future employment. Math at the A-Level will provide you with the research abilities to help you solve issues and analyze theories. Finally, your logical talents will be honed so that you have the tools you need to face a variety of tasks, ranging from financial management to planning projects.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color has-vivid-cyan-blue-color\"><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/reasons-why-you-should-study-a-level-math/\">Want to find out more about why you should choose A-level Maths? Read all here!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>All about A-Level Biology</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A-Level Biology is a suitable subject for you who want to pursue a degree in medicine and biology. It will help you prepare for the academic challenge in your future studies. Here are some facts that you need to know before choosing biology:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Why study A-Level Biology?</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>You will first learn about biological molecules, genetic information, and energy transfers in the <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/a-level-biology-all-you-need-to-know/\">A-Level Biology</a> subject. You\'ll later learn about how this affects how organisms adapt to their surroundings, as well as genetic populations and gene expression control.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A-level Biology may be the subject for you if you are a gifted biologist who wishes to study the subject at a much higher degree of complexity and wish to pursue the sciences in higher education. It is recommended that you take this course in conjunction with math or another science. The course includes a variety of instructional methods, including lectures, demonstrations, and group and one-on-one tutorial sessions.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>What will you learn?</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>A-level biology will provide you with a thorough comprehension of complicated scientific processes as well as an examination of their significance for our global community.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You\'ll learn how to establish hypotheses, use evidence and logic, collaborate, study and scrutinize ideas and discoveries, and present them through well-referenced essays, reports, and examinations.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color has-vivid-cyan-blue-color\"><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/a-level-biology-all-you-need-to-know/\">Still need more info? Read here!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Should you choose A-Level Accounting?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A-Level Accounting is not any less beneficial for your future! Here are a few facts about <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/should-you-choose-a-level-accounting/\">A Level Accounting</a>:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>What is A-Level Accounting?</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Accounting is recognized as the business language. It\'s necessary for recording and presenting business activities in the form of business accounts, financial reporting in the form of financial statements, and the provision of pertinent economic data for management decision-making and control. Accounting accomplishes this through discovering, classifying, summarizing, and presenting financial data in order to aid decision-making and legal compliance. It examines how companies can increase revenue, save expenses, and distribute resources more effectively and efficiently.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>What can you do with A-Level Accounting?</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Accounting will give a student one of the most in-demand talents in any industry. Moreover, every business must have a thorough understanding of its financial health, and all businesses hire accountants to manage their finances. Accounting expertise can come in handy if you want to be an entrepreneur in the future, work as a successful finance professional, or simply help run your family\'s business.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Students interested in pursuing a degree in accounting or business studies at university should do A-level Accounting. Almost all of these degrees will include a number of accounting modules.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color has-vivid-cyan-blue-color\"><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/should-you-choose-a-level-accounting/\">Need more facts about A Level Accounting? Find out here!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>A-Level Economics</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have any interest in pursuing a career in business or finance, <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/this-is-why-you-should-study-a-level-economics/\">A-Level Economics</a> is something that you have to take. This is because the knowledge that you get in this subject can help prepare you for your future career and intended degree. Take a look at some facts about A-Level Economics:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>What is A-Level Economics?</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>In A-Level Economics, you will learn about all knowledge that is related to economics including the market system, market failure, government intervention, the national and international economy, and economics of work and leisure.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Not only that, you will get a lot of skills and insight to handle modern life with a broad knowledge of economics. There are also a lot of university majors and career paths where you need to take A-Level Economics. In some cases, it is absolutely necessary. Furthermore, studying economics will give you the qualification that shows that you have the ability to analyze and understand economic and financial subjects.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Why Study A-Level Economics?</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The A-Level curriculum provides you with a solid foundation in economic topics that you will encounter when you pursue a profession or degree in economics. It may also be beneficial to students who plan to establish a business after graduation. Many students personally benefit from possessing a basic understanding of economics, regardless of their career goals. It can help you grasp issues like inflation and unemployment\'s economic consequences.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>An A-Level education teaches pupils how to apply economic theory to a variety of real-world circumstances. Economics is an important subject that can help you gain skills that will help you tackle obstacles once you graduate from university, such as determining the worth of commodities and planning for your retirement. It can also offer you a comprehensive grasp of the impact economic difficulties have had in the past and present, as well as the tools you\'ll need to deal with them.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color has-vivid-cyan-blue-color\"><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/this-is-why-you-should-study-a-level-economics/\">Interested to know more about Economics? Find out about everything here!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>There is no right or wrong decision in choosing your A-level subjects. We have all of these options because they are different and offer a variety of different academic opportunities. You just need to figure out what your goals are and which subjects will help you achieve them.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Do you need more guidance in <a href=\"https://alevel-guide.all-inedu.com/\">choosing your A-Level subjects</a>? Get your most needed consultation <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/\">here</a>!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'Downloader.la-62b58d9909f2f.jpg', 'Learn to Choose A-Level Subjects Here!', 'publish', 'Learn to Choose A-Level Subjects Here! Read All Tips Here!', 'A Level', 'Do you want to take A-Level for your further studies? Learn which A-Level subjects that is the most suitable for you in this article!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-04-22 17:00:00', '2022-06-15 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(11427, 'lulusan-jurusan-matematika-kerja-apa-baca-di-sini', 8, 0, 'Lulusan Jurusan Matematika Kerja Apa? Baca di sini!', '<p>Sebagai salah satu jurusan yang paling sedikit peminatnya, tentu saja kamu pasti bertanya-tanya jurusan matematika kerja apa di masa depan nanti. Tapi kamu tidak perlu khawatir! Ternyata, <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/serba-serbi-jurusan-matematika/\">jurusan matematika</a> ini mempunyai banyak aplikasi di dunia profesional dan jenjang karir yang cukup banyak lho. Ayo simak di bawah ini beberapa karir yang bisa kamu ambil setelah kamu lulus dari jurusan matematika.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Data Analyst</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Seorang data analyst mengumpulkan, membersihkan, dan menafsirkan kumpulan data untuk menjawab pertanyaan atau memecahkan masalah. Mereka bekerja di banyak industri, termasuk bisnis, keuangan, peradilan pidana, sains, kedokteran, dan pemerintahan. Di dunia modern ini, posisi data analyst merupakan salah satu posisi penting untuk mengembangkan sebuah bisnis. Entah itu untuk menaikan omset penjualan atau untuk meneliti prilaku pasar saat ingin mengeluarkan sebuah produk baru.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Data Analyst mempunyai tugas yang penting, yaitu adalah mengambil data sebanyak-banyaknya untuk memajukan sebuah perusahaan atau mengembangkan pelayanan publik. Data data tersebut bisa seperti: Pelanggan seperti apa yang harus ditargetkan bisnis dalam kampanye iklan berikutnya? Kelompok usia apa yang paling rentan terhadap penyakit tertentu? Pola perilaku apa yang terkait dengan penipuan keuangan?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dari tahun 2020 hingga 2030, posisi Data Analyst diperkirakan akan tumbuh sebesar 25 persen. Pertembuhan tersebut jauh lebih tinggi dari total tingkat pertumbuhan lapangan kerja sebesar 7,7 persen. Jadi kamu udah nggak perlu bingung lulusan jurusan matematika kerja apa.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Jurusan Matematika Kerja apa? Ya, <strong>Data Scientist</strong> lah!</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Seorang Data Scientist adalah seorang profesional yang bertanggung jawab untuk mengumpulkan, menganalisis, dan menafsirkan data dalam jumlah yang sangat besar. Peran ilmuwan data adalah cabang dari beberapa peran teknis tradisional, termasuk ahli matematika, ilmuwan, ahli statistik, dan profesional komputer. Pekerjaan ini memerlukan penggunaan teknologi analitik canggih, termasuk machine learning dan pemodelan prediktif.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Seorang data scientist membutuhkan sejumlah besar data untuk mengembangkan hipotesis, membuat kesimpulan, dan menganalisis tren pelanggan dan pasar. Tanggung jawab dasar termasuk mengumpulkan dan menganalisis data, menggunakan berbagai jenis alat analisis dan pelaporan untuk mendeteksi pola, tren, dan hubungan dalam kumpulan data.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Pekerjaan data analyst dan data scientist mungkin terlihat sama—keduanya menemukan tren atau pola dalam data untuk mengungkapkan cara baru bagi organisasi untuk membuat keputusan yang lebih baik tentang operasinal mereka. Tetapi data scientist cenderung memiliki tanggung jawab lebih dan umumnya dianggap lebih senior daripada data analyst.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Market Researcher</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Seorang Market Researcher bertanggung jawab untuk mengumpulkan dan menganalisis informasi data untuk membuat keputusan politik, sosial dan ekonomi yang terinformasi. Market Researcher mengkhususkan diri dalam penelitian kuantitatif atau kualitatif. Penelitian kuantitatif melibatkan bekerja dengan statistik dan persentase dan dapat memberikan hasil yang cepat sementara penelitian kualitatif melibatkan menganalisis pendapat. Market Researcher dapat dipekerjakan oleh perusahaan atau klien, di mana mereka mengumpulkan informasi tentang pendapat pelanggan, investasi, dan tren pemasaran. Mayoritas peneliti pasar dipekerjakan oleh agen pemasaran yang ukurannya bervariasi dengan perusahaan dan industri yang berbeda.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Jurusan Matematika Kerja apa? Ya, <strong>Investment Analyst</strong> lah!</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Investment analyst bertanggung jawab untuk mengumpulkan informasi, melakukan penelitian, dan menganalisis aset, seperti saham, obligasi, mata uang, dan komoditas. Analis investasi sering fokus pada ceruk tertentu untuk menjadi ahli di bidang pilihan mereka, seperti industri tertentu, wilayah geografis, atau kelas aset tertentu.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Hasil peneletian ini kemudian dipresentasikan kepada manajer portofolio atau investasi, seringkali sebagai bagian dari tim di mana para ahli di berbagai bidang dapat mempertimbangkan wawasan mereka satu sama lain sebelum rekomendasi akhir dan keputusan investasi dibuat. Kolaborasi adalah bagian penting dari pekerjaan, seperti halnya memberikan presentasi dan berbagi informasi di antara rekan-rekan.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Jadi, kalau kamu memang punya passion untuk melanjutkan studi jurusan matematika, kamu tidak perlu bingung lagi jurusan matematika kerja apa di masa depan. Ilmu yang kamu pelajari akan selalu dipakai ke depannya di berbagai macam bidang terutama bidang pengembangan bisnis dan finansial.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ingin berkarir di posisi seperti di atas? Ayo masuk ke jurusan matematika terbaik di dunia bersama Eduverse by ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tidak pernah ada istilah terlalu dini untuk mencari beasiswa. Beasiswa tidak hanya memberikan manfaat secara materi, tetapi juga dapat membantu prospek masa depanmu bahkan setelah lulus dari universitas.<br><br><a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/id/\">Download Panduan “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” untuk mencari tahu semua hal yang perlu kamu ketahui sebelum mendaftar beasiswa.</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!<br></p>', 'Downloader.la-62b5908e70d0f.jpg', 'Lulusan Jurusan Matematika Kerja Apa? Baca di sini!', 'publish', 'Lulusan Jurusan Matematika Kerja Apa? Baca di sini!', 'jurusan matematika kerja apa', 'Penasaran jurusan matematika kerja apa di masa depan nanti? Simak daftar lengkap karir yang bisa dicapai hanya di artikle ini!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-04-13 17:00:00', '2022-06-21 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(11434, 'kampus-kuliah-jurusan-matematika-terbaik-di-asia', 2, 0, 'Kampus Kuliah Jurusan Matematika Terbaik di Asia ﻿', '<p>Apa kamu salah satu pencinta ilmu matematika dan sedang dengan perhitang dan penyelesaian masalah kompleks? Kalau begitu, jurusan matematika tentu sangat cocok untukmu. Asia sendiri memimiliki beberapa jajaran kampus untuk kuliah jurusan matematika yang mempunyai kualitas luar biasa. Penasaran? Berikut adalah daftar 5 kampus terbaik untuk kuliah <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/serba-serbi-jurusan-matematika/\">jurusan matematika</a> menurut edurank.org:</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>5. Hebrew University of Jerusalem</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Hebrew University of Jerusalem, didirikan pada tahun 1918 dan dibuka secara resmi pada tahun 1925, adalah universitas utama Israel serta lembaga penelitian terkemuka. Universitas Ibrani diperingkatkan secara internasional di antara 100 universitas terkemuka di dunia dan pertama di antara universitas-universitas Israel.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kualitas pendidikan luar biasa yang dimiliki oleh universitas ini menempatkan reputasinya sebagai salah satu universitas terbaik di Asia. Universitas ini juga memiliki keunggulan dan peran utama dalam komunitas ilmiah. Selain itu, universitas ini menawarkan beragam peluang studi di humaniora, ilmu sosial, ilmu eksakta dan kedokteran. Hebrew University of Jerusalem mendorong kegiatan multi-disiplin di Israel dan luar negeri dan berfungsi sebagai jembatan antara penelitian akademis dan aplikasi sosial dan industrinya.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>4. University of Hong Kong</strong>, Kampus Kuliah Jurusan Matematika Terbaik</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Dikenal sebagai sekolah tersier tertua di Hong Kong, University of Hong Kong adalah universitas negeri yang didirikan pada tahun 1911. Universitas secara resmi dibuka pada 11 Maret 1912, menawarkan program studi di bidang kedokteran, seni, dan teknik. Pada tahun 1916, universitas mengadakan pertemuan pertamanya dengan total 23 lulusan, dan mulai menerima siswa perempuan satu dekade setelah pendiriannya.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Di jaman modern ini, UHK menjadi salah satu universitas terbaik di Asia dengan kualitas pendidikan yang tidak ada duanya. Menurut QS World University Ranking, universitas ini menempati urutan ke-22 di daftar universitas terbaik di dunia.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>3. Technion - Israel Institute of Technology</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Beroperasi sejak 1924, Technion adalah universitas tertua di Israel. Sejak didirikan, lembaga ini telah mendidik tiga generasi pelajar yang telah memainkan peran kunci dalam meletakkan infrastruktur negara dan membangun industri pertahanan dan teknologi tinggi yang penting di Asia.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Di jaman modern ini, Tecnion terkenal dengan kualitas pendidikan sains dan teknologinya. Universitas menawarkan gelar dalam sains dan teknik, dan bidang terkait seperti arsitektur, kedokteran, manajemen industri, dan pendidikan dalam lingkungan yang menyegarkan secara intelektual.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>2. Tsinghua University</strong>, Kampus Kuliah Jurusan Matematika Terbaik </h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Universitas Tsinghua, yang terletak di barat laut Beijing, Cina, adalah institusi publik yang berasal dari tahun 1911. Bahasa pengantar utama adalah Bahasa Mandarin, meskipun ada beberapa program gelar sarjana yang ditawarkan dalam bahasa Inggris.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Di sisi lain, universitas ini memiliki program magister yang diajarkan dalam bahasa Inggris seperti kebijakan luar negeri, dan hubungan internasional; teknik Mesin; dan jurnalisme bisnis global. Universitas ini merupakan salah satu universitas terbaik di Asia dan menduduki peringkat 17 dunia menurut QS World University Ranking.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>1. National University of Singapore</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Nation University of Singapore adalah salah satu universitas terbaik di Asia yang menawarkan program sarjana dan master yang berfokus pada bisnis, sains, dan ilmu humaniora. Universitas ini menyajikan kualitas pendidik terbaik yang diberikan dengan perspektif Asia. Untuk kuliah jurusan matematika, tentu saja universitas ini tidak perlu diragukan lagi kualitasnya.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>NUS memiliki 17 fakultas dan sekolah di tiga kampus. Pendidikan transformatifnya mencakup kurikulum berbasis luas yang berpusat pada ilmu-ilmu yang mampu membangun komunitas. Selain itu, universitas ini berada di urutan ke-11 dalam daftar universitas terbaik di dunia menurut QS World University Ranking.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Seperti yang sudah kamu baca, kualitas pendidikan di Asia tentu saja tidak kalah dengan yang ada di Eropa atau AS. Kamu bisa menekuni kuliah jurusan matematikamu dengan kualitas yang pastinya jauh lebih baik daripada di negara kita.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Apa kamu makin tertarik untuk kuliah jurusan matematika di kampus-kampus terbaik di Asia? Ayo persiapkan semuanya dengan Eduverse by ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tidak pernah ada istilah terlalu dini untuk mencari beasiswa. Beasiswa tidak hanya memberikan manfaat secara materi, tetapi juga dapat membantu prospek masa depanmu bahkan setelah lulus dari universitas.<br><br><a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/id/\">Download Panduan “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” untuk mencari tahu semua hal yang perlu kamu ketahui sebelum mendaftar beasiswa.</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!<br></p>', 'Downloader.la-62b5935e28872.jpg', 'Kampus Kuliah Jurusan Matematika Terbaik di Asia ﻿', 'publish', 'Kampus Kuliah Jurusan Matematika Terbaik di Asia', 'Kuliah jurusan matematika', 'Punya mimpi untuk kuliah jurusan matematika di kampus terbaik di Asia? Lihat daftar urutan universitas terbaiknya di artikel ini!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-04-12 17:00:00', '2022-06-25 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(11439, 'serba-serbi-jurusan-matematika', 2, 0, 'Serba-serbi Jurusan Matematika', '<p>Jurusan matematika merupakan salah satu jurusan yang peminatnya tidak begitu banyak. Hal ini mungkin karena tidak begitu banyak orang yang menyukai mata pelajaran ini saat berada di bangku sekolah. Tapi tahukah kamu kalau jurusan yang satu ini mempunyai prospek karir yang menarik? Ayo cari tahu lebih lanjut di bawah ini!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Apa itu Jurusan Matematika?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Matematika adalah ilmu yang mempelajari besaran, struktur, ruang, dan perubahan. Meskipun kelihatannya abstrak, matematika pada intinya adalah pencarian yang absolut, solusi dan jawaban yang pasti.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kita mungkin memikirkan rantai numerik yang panjang, lautan pecahan atau spreadsheet yang ditumpuk dengan angka, tetapi banyak yang tidak menyadari bahwa persamaan matematika yang rumit, pada kenyataannya, adalah jalan menuju kesederhanaan. Akibatnya, orang yang percaya pada solusi yang lebih baik, lebih cepat, dan lebih inovatif sering kali tertarik pada matematika.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sebagian besar gelar sarjana matematika membutuhkan waktu tiga atau empat tahun untuk menyelesaikan studi penuh waktu, dengan China dan Australia menawarkan tahun keempat sebagai tahun \"kehormatan\". Beberapa institusi mengatur tahun penempatan bagi siswa untuk bekerja di industri, memberikan kesempatan untuk menerapkan keterampilan dan pengetahuan matematika dalam pengaplikasian.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Universitas Jurusan Matematika Terbaik di Asia</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Jika kamu punya rencana untuk <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/kampus-kuliah-jurusan-matematika-terbaik-di-asia/\">kuliah jurusan matematika</a> & melanjutkan perjalanan akademismu lebih baik lagi, mungkin Asia merupakan tempat yang cocok untukmu. Pasalnya Asia memimiliki banyak unversitas terbaik untuk kamu belajar ilmu matematika. Berikut adalah daftarnya:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>5. Hebrew University of Jerusalem</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Hebrew University of Jerusalem, didirikan pada tahun 1918 dan dibuka secara resmi pada tahun 1925, adalah universitas utama Israel serta lembaga penelitian terkemuka. Universitas Ibrani diperingkatkan secara internasional di antara 100 universitas terkemuka di dunia dan pertama di antara universitas-universitas Israel.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>4. University of Hong Kong</strong>, Kampus Jurusan Matematika Terbaik</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Dikenal sebagai sekolah tersier tertua di Hong Kong, University of Hong Kong adalah universitas negeri yang didirikan pada tahun 1911. Universitas secara resmi dibuka pada 11 Maret 1912, menawarkan program studi di bidang kedokteran, seni, dan teknik. Pada tahun 1916, universitas mengadakan pertemuan pertamanya dengan total 23 lulusan, dan mulai menerima siswa perempuan satu dekade setelah pendiriannya.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>3. Technion - Israel Institute of Technology</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Beroperasi sejak 1924, Technion adalah universitas tertua di Israel. Sejak didirikan, lembaga ini telah mendidik tiga generasi pelajar yang telah memainkan peran kunci dalam meletakkan infrastruktur negara dan membangun industri pertahanan dan teknologi tinggi yang penting di Asia.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/kampus-kuliah-jurusan-matematika-terbaik-di-asia/\">Ingin tahu universitas untuk jurusan matematika lainnya? Cari tahu di sini!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Prospek Kerja Jurusan Matematika di Masa Depan</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Untuk prospek kerja di masa depannya, <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/lulusan-jurusan-matematika-kerja-apa-baca-di-sini/\">jurusan matematika kerja apa</a>?. Kamu tidak perlu khawatir! Sebagai lulusan jurusan matematika, banyak kesempatan yang menunggumu di luar sana. Seperti:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Data Scientist</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Seorang Data Scientist adalah seorang profesional yang bertanggung jawab untuk mengumpulkan, menganalisis, dan menafsirkan data dalam jumlah yang sangat besar. Peran ilmuwan data adalah cabang dari beberapa peran teknis tradisional, termasuk ahli matematika, ilmuwan, ahli statistik, dan profesional komputer. Pekerjaan ini memerlukan penggunaan teknologi analitik canggih, termasuk machine learning dan pemodelan prediktif.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Market Researcher</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Seorang Market Researcher bertanggung jawab untuk mengumpulkan dan menganalisis informasi data untuk membuat keputusan politik, sosial dan ekonomi yang terinformasi. Market Researcher mengkhususkan diri dalam penelitian kuantitatif atau kualitatif. Penelitian kuantitatif melibatkan bekerja dengan statistik dan persentase dan dapat memberikan hasil yang cepat sementara penelitian kualitatif melibatkan menganalisis pendapat.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/lulusan-jurusan-matematika-kerja-apa-baca-di-sini/\">Penasaran prospek kerja lainnya? Cari tahu lebih lengkapnya di sini!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan matematika bukanlah ilmu yang sepele. Karena ilmu inilah telah lahir banyak inovasi dan pengembangan yang telah memajukan peradaban manusia. Maka dari itu, jika kamu memang tertarik untuk masuk ke jurusan ini, prospe yang bagus akan menunggumu.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tertarik untuk masuk ke jurusan matematika? Ayo persiapkan masuk ke universitas terbaik dengan Eduverse by ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tidak pernah ada istilah terlalu dini untuk mencari beasiswa. Beasiswa tidak hanya memberikan manfaat secara materi, tetapi juga dapat membantu prospek masa depanmu bahkan setelah lulus dari universitas.<br><br><a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/id/\">Download Panduan “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” untuk mencari tahu semua hal yang perlu kamu ketahui sebelum mendaftar beasiswa.</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!</p>', 'Downloader.la-62b59419b1a3e.jpg', 'Serba-serbi Jurusan Matematika', 'publish', 'Serba-serbi Jurusan Matematika & Prospek Karir di Masa Depan', 'Jurusan Matematika', 'Jurusan matematika menyimpan banyak potensi untuk mereka yang tertarik di bidangnya. Penasaran? Ayo baca lebih lengkap di sini!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-04-11 17:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(11458, 'breaking-down-the-complete-ntu-admissions-process', 1, 0, 'Breaking Down the Complete NTU Admissions Process ﻿', '<p>It\'s not a secret that Nanyang Technological University (NTU) is one of the best universities in Asia. With numerous programs offered that rank in the upper tier of university programs worldwide, many have dreamt of studying at NTU. Are you planning to study there? If so, let\'s have a look at the NTU admissions process!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>General Requirements for International Admissions&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Completed at least 12 years of general education&nbsp;</li><li>Satisfy the minimum subject requirements for the applied program (For more detail, check <a href=\"https://indd.adobe.com/view/f2aea706-e3e4-48a9-88b7-180c78445a56\">this </a>out)</li><li>English Language Proficiency test scores&nbsp;</li><li>NTU Entrance Examinations (if applicable)</li><li>Submission of Supporting Documents</li><li>Letters of Recommendation</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>English Language Proficiency&nbsp;</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>As English is the primary language medium in <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/ntu-the-absolutely-complete-facts-you-should-know/\">NTU</a>, you\'ll be required to submit proof of English language proficiency. The following are the minimum test scores required for admissions:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td><strong>Test</strong><strong>	</strong></td><td><strong>Minimum Scores</strong></td></tr><tr><td>IELTS</td><td>Overall - 6 <br>Writing - 6</td></tr><tr><td>TOEFL&nbsp;</td><td>90</td></tr><tr><td>SAT&nbsp;</td><td>1250&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td>ACT&nbsp;</td><td>Writing - 30&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td>Pearson Test of English Academic (PTE Academic)&nbsp;</td><td>55</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Note:&nbsp;</em></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><em>For IELTS, TOEFL, and PTE Academic tests, your scores should be obtained within 2 years of the application deadline.&nbsp;</em></li><li><em>The validity period for SAT and ACT is 5 years.</em></li><li><em>IELTS Indicator and TOEFL iBT® Special Home Edition are acceptable.</em></li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h3>Note for UK A-Level & International A-Level (IAL) holders&nbsp;</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>From the 2022-2023 admission intake onwards, NTU is no longer accepting applications from UK A-Level and IAL holders (CIE/Edexcel/OCR/AQA) whose actual A-level results will be available in August of the application year. This is because the academic term has started and is too late for the school\'s consideration for admissions.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>NTU Admissions Entrance Examination&nbsp;</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If deemed fit by the university, you may be required to sit for an NTU Entrance Examination before a final decision on admission can be made. Furthermore, if you hold the International Baccalaureate / IB Diploma or the A-Level certificates, you are not required to sit for the NTU Entrance Examination.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Step 1: Apply Online</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The application to undergraduate programs at NTU is done online, with no hard-copy application form. Therefore, a confirmation email will be sent along with your application number after you have successfully submitted the application form.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td><strong>Qualifications</strong></td><td><strong>Application Period</strong><strong>	</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Indonesian SMA Ujian Akhir Nasional (UAN)</td><td>15 October -&nbsp; 15 December&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td>International Baccalaureate (IB) Diploma&nbsp;</td><td>15 October - 19 March</td></tr><tr><td>UK A-Level certificates/Cambridge Pre-U&nbsp;</td><td>15 October - 19 March</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Step 2: Pay the Application fee&nbsp;</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>NTU\'s undergraduate application fee is a non-refundable amount of SGD30 (by bank draft), or SGD20 (internet payment such as VISA/MasterCard) for international applicants.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Step 3: Submission of Documents</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The required supporting documents need to be submitted by the deadline above to complete the application. Moreover, all documents submitted during the application process need to be original drafts and in English or translated into English. Furthermore, the documents include:&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Personal Identity - passport (international applicants without a passport may submit a birth certificate or personal identity card)</li><li>High school transcript/certificate/diploma (GCE \'A\' Level Statement of Results & Certificate, Indonesia SMA Rapor Sekolah & SMA UAN, International Baccalaureate Diploma)</li><li>Secondary school result slip or certificate (e.g. IGCSE, GCE \'O\' Level, Grade 10 transcript)</li><li>English Proficiency test results (TOEFL/ TOEFL iBT ® Special Home Edition, SAT, IELTS/ IELTS Indicator, PTE Academic, ACT with Writing)</li><li>International Olympiad Award Certificate (if available)</li><li>Letters of Recommendation&nbsp;</li><li>Additional documents required for Art, Design, and Media Programs (Portfolio, Visual aptitude, Creative project, Personal statement, and writing sample)</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Post-application</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td><strong>Qualifications</strong></td><td><strong>Estimated Application Outcome&nbsp;</strong></td><td><strong>Shortlisting For Entrance Exam</strong><strong>	</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Indonesian SMA Ujian Akhir Nasional (UAN).</td><td>Mid-April - End of June</td><td>Mid-February&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td>International Baccalaureate (IB) Diploma&nbsp;</td><td>End April&nbsp; - End of July</td><td>-</td></tr><tr><td>UK A-Level certificates/Cambridge Pre-U&nbsp;</td><td>May - End of June</td><td>-</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>There you have it, a glimpse into admissions at NTU! Moreover, gaining a spot is no small feat. Therefore, you should remember that you\'re applying for a spot at one of the most competitive and top-ranked universities in the world. While it\'s not impossible to get in, there\'s a lot of work and preparation you need to do to be a strong applicant!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Planning to land a seat at NTU? Let\'s prepare for your NTU admission with our initial consultation <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/\">here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!</p>', 'Downloader.la-62bd17a4139fd.jpg', 'Breaking Down the Complete NTU Admissions Process ﻿', 'publish', 'Breaking Down the Complete NTU Admissions Process', 'NTU Admissions', 'Excited to apply yourself into the NTU? Read this article to find out more about NTU admissions process and kickstart your university application!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-04-29 17:00:00', '2022-06-14 17:00:00', '2022-11-03 17:00:00'),
(11476, 'attractive-ntu-scholarships-you-should-know', 1, 0, 'Attractive NTU Scholarships You Should Know!', '<p>Nanyang Technological University (NTU) is an institution that\'s known for being one of the top universities in Asia as well as one of the top 10 young universities in the world, according to the QS World University Rankings. Apart from offering world-class education, NTU also offers scholarships for prospective undergraduates. Moreover, let\'s dive into the attractive NTU scholarships available for you!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>NTU Scholarship #1: Nanyang Scholarship</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The Nanyang Scholarship is a prestigious award given to outstanding freshmen pursuing undergraduate programs at Nanyang Technological University (<a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/ntu-the-absolutely-complete-facts-you-should-know/\">NTU</a>). This full-tuition scholarship covers the program duration on the condition that the awardee maintains a record of good academic performance and exemplary conduct. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>What does the Nanyang Scholarship cover?&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Full coverage of subsidized tuition fees (after Tuition Grant)</li><li>Living allowance of SGD6,500 per academic year</li><li>Accommodation allowance of up to SGD2,000 per academic year</li><li>Travel grant of up to SGD5,000 for an overseas program&nbsp;</li><li>One-off computer allowance of SGD1,750</li><li>No bond is attached to the Nanyang Scholarship apart from the three-year bond applicable to all Singapore PRs and international students under the MOE Tuition Grant Scheme.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>To be eligible for the Nanyang scholarship, you must meet the following requirements:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Open to all nationalities</li><li>Have received an offer from NTU in one of the undergraduate programs</li><li>Exhibit outstanding performance in previous academic studies such as Singapore-Cambridge GCE \'A\' level, Diploma awarded by a polytechnic in Singapore, NUS High School Diploma, IB Diploma, or any Year 12 equivalent qualifications</li><li>Demonstrate outstanding leadership potential through participation in extracurricular activities</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Note: The Nanyang scholarship covers only the first three years of study at NTU for the Biomedical Sciences & Chinese Medicine Program.&nbsp;</em></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>NTU Scholarship #2: ASEAN Scholarship</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Another NTU scholarship is the ASEAN Undergraduate Scholarship, which is a full-tuition scholarship for citizens or permanent residents from the Association of Southeast Asian Nations (ASEAN), except Singapore. Students from ASEAN countries such as Brunei Darussalam, Cambodia, Indonesia, Laos, Malaysia, Myanmar, Philippines, Singapore, Thailand, and Vietnam can sign up to apply for this scholarship.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What does the ASEAN Scholarship cover?&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Full coverage of subsidized tuition fees (after Tuition Grant)</li><li>Living allowance of SGD5,800 per academic year</li><li>Accommodation allowance of SGD3,000 per academic year</li><li>One-off computer allowance of SGD1,750</li><li>No bond is attached to the ASEAN Undergraduate Scholarship apart from the three-year bond applicable to all Singapore PRs and international students under the MOE Tuition Grant Scheme.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>To be eligible for the ASEAN scholarship, you must meet the following requirements:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Singapore Permanent Residents or Citizens from the ASEAN countries (except Singapore)</li><li>Have received an offer from NTU in one of the undergraduate programs&nbsp;</li><li>Exhibit outstanding performance in previous academic studies such as Singapore-Cambridge GCE \'A\' level, Diploma awarded by a polytechnic in Singapore, NUS High School Diploma, IB Diploma, or any Year 12 equivalent qualifications</li><li>Demonstrate outstanding leadership potential through participation in extracurricular activities</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>NTU Scholarship #3: College Scholarship</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>NTU also offers ​College scholarships. Moreover, it is awarded to outstanding freshmen who are pursuing a full-time undergraduate program at NTU.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What does the College Scholarship cover?&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Full coverage of subsidized tuition fees (after Tuition Grant)​​</li><li>Living allowance of SGD5,000 per academic year</li><li>No bond is attached to the College Scholarship apart from the three-year bond applicable to all Singapore PRs and international students under the MOE Tuition Grant Scheme</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>To be eligible for the College scholarship, you must meet the following requirements:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Open to all nationalities.</li><li>Have received an offer from NTU in one of the undergraduate programs.</li><li>Exhibit outstanding performance in previous academic studies such as Singapore-Cambridge GCE \'A\' level, Diploma awarded by a polytechnic in Singapore, NUS High School Diploma, IB Diploma, or any Year 12 equivalent qualifications.</li><li>Demonstrate outstanding leadership potential through participation in extracurricular activities.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Note: The College scholarship covers only the first three years of study at NTU for the Biomedical Sciences & Chinese Medicine Program.</em></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Applying to the scholarships</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>To apply for the scholarships offered by NTU, you need to submit your application for admission before submitting your application for the scholarship. Therefore, the scholarship application period is the same as the admission application period.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have an IB Diploma, the scholarship application form can be found at the link \'Apply for Scholarship\' at the end of your online application for admission. Furthermore, you need to log in with your assigned application number.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have any other Year 12 qualifications, click <a href=\"https://wis.ntu.edu.sg/pls/webexe/adm_fore_appl.login\">here</a> to apply for the scholarship with your assigned application number before the application closing date for your qualification.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the components of applying for a scholarship is writing a Personal Essay of not more than 300 words. You will see 3 topics for the essay in the scholarship application form. Aside from that, some of the supporting documents that need to be submitted include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>A recent passport-size photo.</li><li>A referee\'s appraisal.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>With all these attractive scholarships offered, have you made up your mind on which NTU scholarship to apply for? Before diving into the application process, don\'t forget to check all the requirements to keep yourself informed and fully prepared. Best of luck!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Aiming to land a scholarship at NTU? Let\'s prepare your NTU scholarships with ALL-in right <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/\">now</a>!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!</p>', 'Downloader.la-62bd1a8d43b83.jpg', 'Attractive NTU Scholarships You Should Know!', 'publish', 'Attractive NTU Scholarships You Should Know About!', 'NTU Scholarships', 'If you have a big ambitious dream to study in NTU, you might find that NTU scholarships will help you a lot. Read this article to find out more!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-04-28 17:00:00', '2022-06-04 17:00:00', '2022-11-04 17:00:00');
