(11820, 'essay-for-study-abroad-everything-you-should-know', 3, 0, 'Essay for Study Abroad: Everything You Should Know!', '<p>You\'ve decided that you want to study abroad, and now it\'s time to get your creativity running wild for your study abroad essay. Writing a <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/study-abroad-your-ultimate-guide-to-be-an-international-students/\">study abroad</a> essay can be really challenging, especially if this is your first time. But fret not, as we\'ll go over some tips on how to craft your study abroad essay!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>What is a study abroad essay?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A study abroad essay is usually part of the application process, where you\'ll talk about your goals, experiences, and reasons for wanting to study abroad. Furthermore, the essay helps university admission officers to gain a more holistic understanding of who the applicants are. From why you have chosen the university, and why the chosen program is the right fit for you.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Tip #1: Brainstorm&nbsp;</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>When applying to study abroad programs, you\'ll need to answer questions like ‘Tell me about yourself,\' or ‘Why do you want to study abroad?\'</p>\n\n\n\n<p>While these questions may sound simple, it can be tricky to narrow down your ideas and summarize them in a way that fits into a 300- to 600-word response.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the ways to tackle these questions is to start by making a list of why you want to study abroad. This helps you get an idea of what your essay will cover. You can think about what you wish to gain from your experience of studying abroad. Not only that, but you can also think about your plans when studying there. If you find yourself confused as to your own motivations to study abroad, then it\'s a good time to start reflecting and thinking about your goals here rather than during the drafting process.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Tip #2: Show Your Personality</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The best way to stand out in your essay is to be yourself. You always want to leave that lasting impression: who are you as a student, a person?&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Knowing that some universities have different essay prompts from others, it\'s best to know where you\'re applying to. Do your research about the different types of essays as well as what each university wants from you. In this way, you can make sure your essay is a good fit for the school you\'re applying to.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To add a personal touch to your essay, try adding a personal story that resonates with your study abroad plan. Remember, your essay should be a reflection of who you are as a person, not as an applicant or a student. Moreover, you want the admission officer to feel like they know who you are as a person. Even if they\'ve never met you before.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Tip #3: Don\'t forget to proofread&nbsp;</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Never hit submit without first proofreading your essay! You might pick up on typos or awkward sentences that need to be fixed at a second glance. During the course of proofreading your essay, you might think of a new idea or way to structure it—it wouldn\'t hurt to try using these new ideas and see if they improve the essay. Also, a little extra time can go a long way toward helping you avoid common issues like spelling errors and sentence structure problems.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>It\'s also always a good idea to have someone else look at your essay, as you might get some feedback on your writing and gain perspective on what worked and what didn\'t.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>There\'s no doubt that applying to study abroad is a long and complicated process. But all the challenges you face right now are nothing compared to the rewards you\'ll receive for tackling them successfully!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>It\'s never too early to begin the search for scholarships. Little did you know, scholarship doesn\'t only give you a cost benefit, but also could help you for your future prospects.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” Guidebook to find out all the things you need to know before applying for scholarships. It\'s FREE, <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/\">download here</a>.\n\n</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Need assistance in crafting your essays to study abroad? Let\'s do it with ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top uni preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>', 'Downloader.la-62cf8f9217471.jpg', 'Essay for Study Abroad: Everything You Should Know!', 'publish', 'Essay for Study Abroad: Everything You Should Know!', 'Essay for Study Abroad', 'Are you looking for the bast way to write essay for study abroad? Read this article and find out the best way to start your essay!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-05-05 17:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(11832, 'scholarship-to-study-abroad-that-you-can-try-applying-to', 1, 0, 'Scholarship to Study Abroad that You Can Try Applying to!', '<p>Studying abroad has become increasingly popular amongst Indonesian high schoolers in the last few years. This means there are more and more students looking for a scholarship to <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/study-abroad-your-ultimate-guide-to-be-an-international-students/\">study abroad</a>. Moreover, according to an article published by ICEF Monitor in 2019, the total amount of Indonesian students studying overseas has increased by 21% over the past six years.  </p>\n\n\n\n<p>You may be wondering, why are all these students moving so far away from their homes just to continue their academic careers? Well, not only does studying abroad offer students a high level of education, but it also teaches them valuable lessons in life.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Moreover, studying abroad puts Indonesian students in completely new surroundings. This allows them to step out of their comfort zone and thrive in places other than home. Furthermore, by studying abroad, Indonesian students can experience and learn new things from new people.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Are you interested to study abroad? Therefore, here are some examples of the best scholarships to study abroad:</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>1. <strong>Provost\'s Scholarship for Excellence (Oregon State University, United States)</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Oregon State University in the United States is one of the best universities to study abroad in. Moreover, it offers the Provost\'s Scholarship for Excellence scholarship for international students who are interested in studying there. Also, this scholarship program allows undergraduate students from all majors to apply.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For up to 4 years, the bursary will provide USD $6,000 per year to aid the study expenses of the students. However, there is a list of requirements that you must be able to fulfill in order to qualify for the scholarship. Moreover, here is the list of requirements:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>You must be a first-year or IYO student with a GPA of 3.5+</li><li>If you are a UTP or Transfer student, then you must have a GPA of 3.25+</li><li>Note: This scholarship is renewable with at least a 3.0 GPA.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>2. Scholarship to Study Abroad: <strong>Principal\'s Scholarship (Queen\'s University, Canada)</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Queen\'s University in Ontario, Canada offers the Principal\'s Scholarship” for international undergraduate students. Also, This scholarship applies to all who wish to start their academic careers there. Undergraduate international students of any major will be able to experience new surroundings while they are learning.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>The amount of financial aid that Queen\'s University is offering with the Principal\'s Scholarship is around CAD $4,000 per year. There is no application needed for this scholarship because students will be automatically selected when they apply to Queen\'s University. Moreover, here is the list of requirements:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Your high school grades must be 95%+</li><li>Your IB Diploma Programme is required to be a 39+ core.</li><li>To renew your scholarship, you must achieve a minimum GPA of 5.5.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>3. <strong>The University of Adelaide Global Citizens Scholarship (The University of Adelaide, Australia)</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The scholarship to study abroad offers both undergraduate and postgraduate students of all majors financial aid for an excellent education.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>All scholars can get 15-30% of their total tuition. Furthermore, they just need to meet the requirements for The University of Adelaide Global Citizens Scholarship. Furthermore, there is no application needed for this program, as all applicants who are eligible will receive this scholarship offer. Moreover, here is the list of requirements:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Grade 12 students must have a minimum Australian Tertiary Admission Rank (ATAR). The score is 80 for a 15% scholarship.</li><li>Grade 12 students must have a minimum Australian Tertiary Admission Rank (ATAR). The score is 80 for a 15% scholarship. </li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>4. Scholarship to Study Abroad: <strong>International Achievement Freshman Scholarship (Oklahoma State University, United States)</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Oklahoma State University\'s International Achievement Freshman Scholarship is four-year partial tuition. Furthermore, this scholarship to study abroad varies depending on applicants\' grades. Also, this scholarship program is for undergraduate international students of all majors as well.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The amount of this scholarship varies from USD $4,000-10,000 depending on the student\'s results. However, you will need to meet the requirements set by Oklahoma State University. Here are the requirements:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><thead><tr><th scope=\"col\">Reward</th><th scope=\"col\">IELTS</th><th scope=\"col\">TOEFL IBT</th><th scope=\"col\">ACT</th><th scope=\"col\">SAT</th><th scope=\"col\">GPA</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"col\">$40,000</th><th scope=\"col\">8.5+</th><th scope=\"col\">115-120</th><th scope=\"col\">30</th><th scope=\"col\">1360</th><th scope=\"col\">3.25</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"col\">$36,000</th><th scope=\"col\">8.0+</th><th scope=\"col\">110-114</th><th scope=\"col\">29</th><th scope=\"col\">1330-1350</th><th scope=\"col\">3.25</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"col\">$32,000</th><th scope=\"col\">7.5+</th><th scope=\"col\">102-109</th><th scope=\"col\">28</th><th scope=\"col\">1300-1320</th><th scope=\"col\">3.25</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>$28,000</td><td>7.0+</td><td>94-101</td><td>27</td><td>1260-1290</td><td>3.25</td></tr><tr><td>$24,000</td><td>6.5+</td><td>79-93</td><td>26</td><td>1230-1250</td><td>3.25</td></tr><tr><td>$16,000</td><td>6.0+</td><td>61-78</td><td>24-25</td><td>1160-1220</td><td>3.25</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Studying abroad will help Indonesian students both learn and have the best possible experience to prepare for their future. Moreover, these scholarships will accommodate your study and help you achieve your dreams.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>It\'s never too early to begin the search for scholarships. Little did you know, scholarship doesn\'t only give you a cost benefit, but also could help you for your future prospects.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” Guidebook to find out all the things you need to know before applying for scholarships. It\'s FREE, <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/\">download here</a>.\n\n</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Are you interested in applying for scholarships to study abroad? Let\'s prepare with ALL-in Eduspace!&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\"><strong>Admission Mentoring</strong></a><strong>.</strong></li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\"><strong>Career Exploration.</strong></a></li><li>Improve grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\"><strong>Academic Tutoring.</strong></a></li><li>Upscale your personal brand in the <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/writing-skills/\"><strong>Writing Skills</strong></a><strong> </strong>improvement program.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!</p>', 'Downloader.la-62cf9bfea14b1.jpg', 'Scholarship to Study Abroad that You Can Try Applying to!', 'publish', 'Scholarship to Study Abroad that You Can Try Applying to!', 'Scholarship to study abroad', 'Are you an international student who is looking for a scholarship to study abroad? Therefore, check out this list of the best scholarships to study abroad!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-05-04 17:00:00', '2022-07-10 17:00:00', '2022-11-03 17:00:00'),
(11850, 'study-abroad-your-ultimate-guide-to-be-an-international-students', 1, 0, 'Study Abroad: Your Ultimate Guide to be an International Students', '<p>Studying abroad may be at the top of your mind, but you\'re not sure where to start. Undoubtedly, the entire process can be a long and pretty tricky one. You may feel overwhelmed trying to figure it out. Lucky for you, we\'ll go over the things you need to know about studying abroad. Also, this includes why you should do it, its benefits, the best countries to study abroad, and even scholarships you can get. Let\'s dive right into your study abroad guide!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Why study abroad?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>First things first, why bother studying abroad? Well, studying abroad is a life-changing experience for a variety of reasons. You may consider these:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Stand out to future employers - While studying abroad, you\'ll gain valuable skills that you may not be aware of, but employers will take note of! For instance, after years of dealing with a range of new situations on your own, you\'ll grow into a stronger and better communicator. Or when you\'re dealing with multiple languages, you\'ll gain the ability to be multilingual, which will put you at an advantage, especially at a multinational company!</li><li>Expand your network - Whether you\'re meeting someone from your country or making friends with a local, it\'s never a bad idea to build your connections. From making lifelong friendships to becoming business partners, the potential of expanding your network is limitless!</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>To learn more about the life-altering reasons why you should study abroad, find out here!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Best countries to study abroad</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Choosing the right destination is crucial to getting the most out of your study abroad. With hundreds of countries, cities, and towns to choose from, you won\'t be short of choices. In fact, you might feel overwhelmed by the large number of destinations to choose from.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To help narrow down your search, try asking yourself some of these questions:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Do I want to study in a country where English isn\'t the first language?</li><li>Do I want to study in a country that\'s close to my home country?</li><li>Which country suits my financial budget best?</li><li>Do I want to live in a quiet town or in a big city?</li><li>Do I want to stay in the country after I graduate?&nbsp;</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Ideal Study Destination</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Aside from asking yourself some of the aforementioned questions, try to pick out two or three ideal study destinations that strike your interest. After that, you can start comparing the pros and cons. Some of the factors you can consider when compiling the pros and cons include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Climate - Which one seems ideal for you? A colder or a warmer climate?</li><li>Student life - Check out the student activities, university societies, and transport systems.</li><li>Culture - Figure out the residents\' attitude towards international students or visitors from other parts of the world.</li><li>Programs offered - See what you\'ll study and how. Some degrees focus more on theory, while others on practice. Take note of the duration of the studies.&nbsp;</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>On top of that, you can also ask friends, families, and others who already study abroad. Moreover, sitting down and chatting with someone about their experiences traveling and studying abroad can help you understand what to expect, the challenges, and even some tips. Chances are, they might give you insightful information you can\'t get anywhere else!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Of course, if you\'re still not sure which countries are the best to study abroad, here are some of the best countries to study abroad:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Singapore - Known for its rapid economic development, Singapore also boasts itself as a highly competitive country in terms of academics. Furthermore, from its stellar reputation in students\' safety to its universities that rub shoulders with the world\'s top universities, Singapore can be on top of your list!</li><li>USA - Home to the well-known Ivy League institutions, the US offers a lot of things, including academic excellence, a diverse environment, and a flexible education system.&nbsp;</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Head over here to explore more about some of the best countries to study abroad!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Benefits of studying abroad</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Many have said it before—studying abroad is not all about academics. Here are some of the benefits you can get while studying abroad:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>A step closer to adult life - Whether you\'re living with some of your closest friends, or living all on your own, studying abroad pushes you to become independent and self-supporting. Also, even in the most stressful moments of maintaining your grades, keeping your room clean, and managing your finances, you\'ll learn to rise and find out what you\'re truly made of.</li><li>Travel, travel, and travel - Whether it\'s a weekend trip to the nearest city or a day trip to the beach, you\'ll expose yourself to new things you wouldn\'t be able to experience at home. In some cases, you may even get the chance to tick off some of your bucket lists!</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Check out even more benefits you can get while you\'re studying abroad here!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Study Abroad with Scholarships</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Tuition fees and living costs can quickly add up to a large budget for your education. Fortunately, scholarships can serve as your financial support! Here are some of the attractive scholarships you can get:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>National University of Singapore - ASEAN Undergraduate Scholarship<ul><li>Award amount: Tuition fees (after MOE Tuition Grant Subsidy), S$5,800 annual living allowance</li></ul></li><li>University of Minnesota - Global Excellence Scholarship<ul><li>Award amount: up to USD 25,000 per year for up to 4 years</li></ul></li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>For further insight into what scholarships are offered, click here!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/how-to-study-abroad-for-free-a-complete-guide/\">How to Study Abroad for Free</a></strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Although studying abroad has its great advantages, it isn\'t exactly affordable. In order to study abroad, you will need to pay for both your tuition fees and other necessary items, such as housing, food, health insurance, etc. The cost of studying abroad drastically adds up when you take all of these things into account. However, there are multiple ways for you to study abroad for free.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Incredibly expensive tuition fees make studying abroad a bit difficult, so here are some of the ways you can study abroad for free:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Seek out financial aid.</strong> Apply to the Indonesia Endowment Funds for Education (LPDP) which is offered to students by the Indonesian Ministry of Finance.</li><li><strong>Check out university scholarships</strong>. Apply by submitting your academic transcript, personal statement, and letters of recommendation.&nbsp;</li><li><strong>Earn while you learn</strong>. Learn for cheaper by working a part-time job along with your studies to take off some of the financial burdens of studying abroad.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>However, not everyone can receive funds or apply for university scholarships. In order to receive the rewards from either the Indonesia Endowment Funds for Education (LPDP) or from university scholarships, you need to meet their standards. Whether it be scoring a certain number on a test, or maintaining a minimum GPA, not everyone can get access to the rewards from these benefactors.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With that being said, these are some of the best methods that you can try in order to study abroad for free. Seeking out funds from the Indonesia Endowment Funds for Education (LPDP), applying for university scholarships, and the “earn while you learn” method are all ways that can help you combat the expensive tuition given by universities abroad.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color has-vivid-cyan-blue-color\"><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/how-to-study-abroad-for-free-a-complete-guide/\">Want to know more about how you can study abroad for free? Read the full article here!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Writing a Study Abroad Essay</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>You might be thinking, what on earth is a study abroad essay? In summary, a study abroad essay is a part of the application process where you share your goals, experiences, and reasons for studying abroad with the college admissions board. This essay will help university admission officers have a better understanding of who you are, what you want, and why their program is the right fit for you.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Writing a study abroad essay can be quite challenging, so here are some tips and tricks to help you write a study abroad essay:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li><strong>Brainstorm</strong>. Make a list of the reasons why you want to study abroad. This will help you get an idea of what to write about.</li><li><strong>Show your personality</strong>. Be yourself when you write and try adding a personal story that relates to why you want to study abroad. But this depends on where you are applying to.</li><li><strong>Don\'t forget to proofread</strong>! Don\'t submit your essay right when you finish so that you can fix typos or awkward sentences.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Writing a study abroad essay is by no means an easy task. It\'s going to be frustrating, and you\'re probably going to come across many problems as you write your essay. However, you must persevere because the essay is a vital part of the application process, and getting accepted to your dream university will outweigh the frustrations of writing the essay.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With that being said, these tips will help you write your <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/essay-for-study-abroad-everything-you-should-know/\">essay for study abroad</a>. Brainstorming, showing your personality, and proofreading are all ways that you can effectively write a good study abroad essay. Show the university admission officers that they should accept you because their university is the right fit for you.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color has-vivid-cyan-blue-color\"><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/essay-for-study-abroad-everything-you-should-know/\">Want to know more about how you can write a study abroad essay? Read the full article here!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Extra <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/scholarship-to-study-abroad-that-you-can-try-applying-to/\">Scholarships to Study Abroad</a></strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Studying abroad can open many doors of opportunity for international students. Not only does it provide a good level of education, but it also teaches students important lessons, such as how to be independent. It is no secret to anyone that studying abroad is very expensive, but this doesn\'t have to stop you. Scholarships are a brilliant way to help pay for your university tuition.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are struggling to find which universities provide scholarship programs, here are some of the best scholarship programs that you can apply to:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Provost\'s Scholarship for Excellence</strong>, a 4-year USD $6,000 scholarship program from Oregon State University, United States.</li><li><strong>Principal\'s Scholarship</strong>, a CAD $4,000 scholarship program from Queen\'s University, Canada.</li><li><strong>The University of Adelaide Global Citizens Scholarship</strong>, a 15-30% discount on the tuition fee from The University of Adelaide, Australia.</li><li><strong>International Achievement Freshman Scholarship</strong>, a USD $16,000-$40,000 scholarship program from Oklahoma State University, United States.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Keep in mind that these university scholarship applications are not for everyone. You will need to meet the standards set by the college admissions board if you want to enroll in the university. Each university has a different requirement, so if you find one that you like, you need to focus on achieving according to the requirements of that university. Moreover, when you get accepted, you will still need to maintain good grades in order to keep your scholarship.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Other than that, studying abroad will teach you important lessons in life, and give you a good education at the same time. Scholarships not only allow you to freely achieve your academic goals while studying abroad but also force you to work hard in order to meet the requirements of the university during the application process.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color has-vivid-cyan-blue-color\"><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/scholarship-to-study-abroad-that-you-can-try-applying-to/\">For more on scholarships to study abroad, read the full article here!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Conclusion</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>And that\'s it! Remember that you should not make any decisions about your study abroad plans instantly. Instead, try to learn as much as you can and take your time to land a well-informed decision so that you can make the most out of your study abroad. Best of luck!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>It\'s never too early to begin the search for scholarships. Little did you know, scholarship doesn\'t only give you a cost benefit, but also could help you for your future prospects.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” Guidebook to find out all the things you need to know before applying for scholarships. It\'s FREE, <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/\">download here</a>.\n\n</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you still feel lost in your study abroad planning, ALL-in will happily assist you!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximise your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\"><strong>Admission Mentoring</strong></a><strong>.</strong></li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\"><strong>Career Exploration.</strong></a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\"><strong>Academic Tutoring.</strong></a></li><li>Highlight your personal brand through the <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/writing-skills/\"><strong>Writing Skills</strong></a><strong> </strong>improvement program.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'Downloader.la-62cfa27db37f9.jpg', 'Study Abroad: Your Ultimate Guide to be an International Students', 'publish', 'Study Abroad: Your Ultimate Guide to be an International Students', 'Study Abroad', 'Have a dream to be an international student and study abroad? Here is the ultimate guide to kickstart your dream of studying abroad!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-05-03 17:00:00', '2022-07-12 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(11859, 'alasan-kamu-wajib-kuliah-jurusan-pertambangan', 2, 0, 'Alasan Kamu Wajib Kuliah Jurusan Pertambangan', '<p>Apa kamu masih menimbang-nimbang untuk kuliah jurusan pertambangan? Eits… tenang aja, di sini kamu akan diyakinkan lagi untuk mengambil jurusan ini. Pamor <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/jurusan-pertambangan-hal-hal-penting-yang-wajib-kamu-tahu/\">jurusan pertambangan</a> yang terus meningkat di kalangan milenial membuatnya menjadi salah satu jurusan yang banyak diminati lho. Penasaran? Ayo simak beberapa alasan kenapa kamu harus kuliah jurusan pertambangan di bawah ini ya!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Kuliah Yang Tidak Membosankan</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Salah satu alasan kenapa kamu harus masuk jurusan pertambangan adalah karena mata kuliah yang tidak membosankan. Di jurusan ini, kamu tidak melulu diajarkan teori tapi juga praktik langsung. Walaupun kamu tetap ada pelajaran menghitung dan di kelas, tapi kamu juga akan tetap mendapatkan porsi pelajaran praktik yang lumayan banyak. Bayangkan jika kamu hanya berada di dalam kelas dan berkutat hanya dengan buku saja, pasti akan sangat cepat jenuh bukan?</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Potensi Penghasilan yang Fantastis</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Jika sudah lulus dan bekerja di perusahaan pertambangan, kamu mungkin bisa mendapatkan penghasilan yang luar biasa lho. Tidak jarang banyak perusahaan tambang menawarkan gaji yang sangat besar, bahkan untuk <em>fresh graduate</em> yang mendaftar di perusahaannya. Maka dari itu, jika kamu masuk ke jurusan ini, kamu tidak perlu khawatir lagi dengan pendapatan di masa depan. Dijamin cuan deh!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Karir yang Luas</strong>, Alasan Kuliah Jurusan Pertambangan</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Prospek karir dari jurusan ini juga sangat bagus lho. Pasalnya, ilmu yang telah kamu pelajari bukan merupakan ilmu umum, melainkan ilmu khusus yang hanya bisa kamu dapatkan di bangku universitas saja. Di Indonesia sendiri, perusahaan tambang sangat banyak. Tidak hanya dari negara kita saja alias BUMN, melainkan banyak perusahaan dari luar negeri yang juga aktif di Indonesia. Kamu juga bisa mempunyai kesempatan untuk bekerja <em>offshore </em>atau di kantor pusat perusahaan-perusahaan internasional. Di sisi lain, kamu bisa dengan mudah mendapatkan portofolio yang bagus ketika sudah bekerja di pertambangan. Hal ini karena variasi perusahaan tambang yang banyak dan sedikit orang yang merupakan lulusan jurusan ini.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Sering Melakukan Kunjungan Lapangan</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Bagi kamu yang tidak mau hanya bekerja di balik meja atau pun di luar ruangan, jurusan ini sangat cocok untukmu. Di masa depan nanti setelah kamu lulus, kamu akan mendapatkan banyak tugas untuk melakukan kunjungan lapangan. Kunjungan lapangan ini tidak hanya di dalam negeri lho, kamu mungkin akan mengunjungi beberapa negara yang ada di seluruh dunia. Alhasil, kamu tidak akan tuh yang namanya terus-menerus berkutat dengan dokumen-dokumen ataupun menatap layar monitor di balik meja kerja. Seru kan?</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Lapangan Kerja yang Selalu Ada</strong>, Alasan Kuliah Jurusan Pertambangan</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Yup, benar! Lapangan kerja yang dimiliki oleh lulusan jurusan pertambangan merupakan salah satu yang akan selalu ada. Industri pertambangan merupakan salah satu industri yang paling penting di dunia. Hal ini karena pertambangan merupakan salah satu industri yang banyak memasok bahan baku untuk bahan bakar. Selain itu, industri ini juga merupakan salah satu tahapan awal dari proses produksi suatu barang. Contohnya batu baterai yang dipakai oleh mobil listrik yang sedang terkenal saat ini. Pembuatan bahan bakarnya memerlukan bahan baku nikel yang hanya bisa diperoleh dari pertambangan nikel.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Terlebih lagi, industri pertambangan merupakan industri vital bagi perekonomian suatu negara. Contoh lah Indonesia yang tengah melakukan ekspor bahan baku besar-besaran keluar negeri. Setelah lulus dari kuliah jurusan pertambangan, kamu akan berperan serta untuk meningkatkan dan menjaga tingkat ekspor pertambangan Indonesia lho.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Cukup banyak kan alasan untuk memilih kuliah jurusan pertambangan? Kuliah jurusan ini memang mempunyai kelebihan yang luar biasa, tapi untuk bisa masuk ke jurusan ini tidak mudah lho, apalagi di universitas top dunia. Maka dari itu, kamu perlu untuk mempersiapkan semuanya dengan baik dan matang ya!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download Panduan “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” untuk mencari tahu semua hal yang perlu kamu ketahui sebelum mendaftar beasiswa. GRATIS! <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/id/\">Download disini</a> </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ingin kuliah jurusan pertambangan di universitas top dunia? Persiapkan semuanya dengan Eduverse by ALL-in sekarang!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!<br></p>', 'Downloader.la-62cfba9e5fe67.jpg', 'Alasan Kamu Wajib Kuliah Jurusan Pertambangan', 'publish', 'Alasan Kamu Wajib Kuliah Jurusan Pertambangan', 'Kuliah Jurusan Pertambangan', 'Apa kamu masih ragu untuk kuliah jurusan pertambangan? Baca artikel ini dan cari tahu beberapa kelebihan yang bisa kamu dapat di jurusan ini!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-04-23 17:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(11874, 'daftar-lengkap-universitas-jurusan-pertambangan-terbaik-di-dunia', 2, 0, 'Daftar Lengkap Universitas Jurusan Pertambangan Terbaik di Dunia', '<p><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/jurusan-pertambangan-hal-hal-penting-yang-wajib-kamu-tahu/\">Jurusan pertambangan</a> merupakan salah satu jurusan yang tengah naik daun di kalangan kaum milenial. Belakangan ini, social media lumayan diramaikan oleh beberapa lulusan pertambangan yang telah bekerja di berbagai perusahaan tambang di Indonesia dan dengan sukses mendapat gaji yang besar. Hal inilah yang memicu beberapa pelajar tertarik untuk mengambil jurusan ini. Berikut adalah beberapa universitas jurusan pertambangan terbaik di dunia yang patut kamu minati!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>5. The University of New South Wales, Australia</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>University of New South Wales (UNSW), juga dikenal sebagai UNSW Sydney, adalah universitas riset publik yang berbasis di Sydney, New South Wales, Australia. Universitas ini merupakan salah satu anggota pendiri Group of Eight, sebuah koalisi universitas penelitian intensif Australia. Didirikan pada tahun 1949, UNSW adalah universitas riset, menempati peringkat ke-44 di dunia dalam QS World University Rankings 2021 dan ke-67 di dunia dalam Times Higher Education World University Rankings 2021. Instansi ini adalah salah satu anggota Universitas 21, jaringan global universitas riset. Universitas ini memiliki jaringan internasional yang kuat dan kemitraan penelitian dengan lebih dari 200 universitas di seluruh dunia.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Menurut QS World University Ranking, universitas ini berada di urutan ke lima untuk jurusan pertambangan. Universitas ini juga merupakan salah satu universitas dengan tingkat penerimaan yang paling rendah yaitu 30%.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>4. McGill University, Kanada</strong>, Universitas Jurusan Pertambangan</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>McGill University (Prancis: Université McGill) adalah universitas riset publik berbahasa Inggris yang berlokasi di Montreal, Quebec, Kanada.&nbsp; Universitas ini didirikan pada tahun 1821 oleh piagam kerajaan yang diberikan oleh Raja George I dan menyandang nama James McGill, seorang pedagang Skotlandia yang warisannya pada tahun 1813 membentuk cikal bakal universitas tersebut. McGill menawarkan gelar dan diploma di lebih dari 300 bidang studi, dengan nilai masuk rata-rata tertinggi dari universitas Kanada mana pun. Sebagian besar mahasiswa terdaftar di lima fakultas terbesar, yaitu Seni, Sains, Kedokteran, Pendidikan, Teknik, dan Manajemen.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Di jurusan pertambangan, universitas ini mempunyai kualitas yang sangat bagus. QS World University Ranking menempatkan universitas ini di urutan keempat untuk jurusan pertambangan dengan tingkat penerimaan sebesar 46.3%.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>3. The University of Queensland, Australia</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>University of Queensland adalah universitas riset publik yang berlokasi di Brisbane, ibu kota negara bagian Queensland, Australia. Didirikan pada tahun 1909 oleh parlemen Queensland, UQ adalah salah satu dari enam universitas <em>sandstone</em>, sebutan informal untuk universitas tertua di setiap negara bagian. Universitas menawarkan gelar associate, sarjana, master, doktoral, dan doktor yang lebih tinggi melalui perguruan tinggi, sekolah pascasarjana, dan enam fakultas. UQ menggabungkan lebih dari seratus lembaga dan pusat penelitian yang menawarkan program penelitian, seperti Institute for Molecular Bioscience, Boeing Research and Technology Australia Center.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>QS World University Ranking menempatkan universitas ini di urutan ketiga untuk jurusan pertambangan dengan tingkat penerimaan sebesar 40%.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>2. Curtin University, Australia</strong>, Universitas Jurusan Pertambangan</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Curtin University juga dikenal sebagai Curtin University of Technology dan Western Australian Institute of Technology (WAIT). Universitas ini merupakan instansi riset publik Australia yang berbasis di Bentley, Perth, Australia Barat. Nama universitas ini diambil dari John Curtin, Perdana Menteri Australia 1941-1945, dan merupakan universitas terbesar di Australia Barat, dengan 59.939 siswa pada tahun 2021.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>QS World University Ranking menempatkan universitas ini di urutan kedua untuk jurusan pertambangan. Universitas ini juga merupakan salah satu universitas dengan tingkat penerimaan yang cukup tinggi yaitu 50%.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>1. Colorado School of Mines, Amerika Serikat</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Colorado School of Mines adalah universitas riset publik di Golden, Colorado, didirikan pada tahun 1874. Sekolah ini menawarkan gelar sarjana dan pascasarjana di bidang teknik, sains, dan matematika, dengan fokus pada energi dan lingkungan. Sementara Mines memang menawarkan gelar minor dalam humaniora, seni, dan ilmu sosial. Universitas ini hanya menawarkan gelar mayor di bidang STEM, dengan pengecualian ekonomi. Pada semester Musim Gugur 2019, sekolah memiliki 6.607 siswa terdaftar, dengan 5.155 di program sarjana dan 1.452 di program pascasarjana.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>QS World University Ranking menempatkan universitas ini sebagai universitas terbaik untuk jurusan pertambangan. Universitas ini juga merupakan salah satu universitas dengan tingkat penerimaan yang cukup tinggi yaitu 55%.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Berikut di atas adalah 5 universitas terbaik di dunia untuk jurusan pertambangan. Beberapa universitas di atas memiliki tingkat penerimaan yang sangat kecil, maka dari itu persiapan kamu juga harus dimaksimalkan lagi jika kamu ingin masuk ke universitas jurusan pertambangan di atas ya!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download Panduan “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” untuk mencari tahu semua hal yang perlu kamu ketahui sebelum mendaftar beasiswa. GRATIS! <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/id/\">Download disini</a> </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Punya mimpi masuk ke universitas jurusan pertambangan seperti di atas? Eduverse by ALL-in akan bantu kamu dari NOL!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!</p>', 'Downloader.la-62cfbe1b3153d.jpg', 'Daftar Lengkap Universitas Jurusan Pertambangan Terbaik di Dunia', 'publish', 'Daftar Lengkap Universitas Jurusan Pertambangan Terbaik di Dunia', 'Universitas Jurusan Pertambangan', 'Sudah yakin ingin melanjutkan belajar di jurusan pertambangan? Simak daftar universitas jurusan pertambangan terbaik di dunia hanya ada di sini!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-04-22 17:00:00', '2022-07-04 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(11890, 'jurusan-pertambangan-hal-hal-penting-yang-wajib-kamu-tahu', 2, 0, 'Jurusan Pertambangan: Hal-Hal Penting yang Wajib Kamu Tahu!', '<p>Kamu mungkin sudah sering mendengar tentang jurusan ini entah di media sosial, teman, atau gurumu di sekolah. Walaupun terlihat sedikit peminatnya, tapi jurusan pertambangan merupakan salah satu jurusan terbaik yang patut kamu perhitungkan lho. Di jurusan ini, kamu akan menemukan banyak sekali potensi, mulai dari peluang karir hingga beberapa kelebihan khusus yang hanya bisa kamu dapat di jurusan ini. Ayo cari tahu lebih lengkapnya di bawah!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Apa itu Jurusan Pertambangan?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan Pertambangan adalah jurusan dimana kamu akan mempelajari berbagai macam hal yang berhubungan dengan proses pertambangan terutama mineral berharga dan batubara. Di dalam proses pertambangan ini, ada tiga tahap yang akan kamu lalui yaitu: eksplorasi, eksploitasi, dan pemrosesan. Eksplorasi adalah proses pencarian mineral berharga. Eksploitasi merupakan proses penambangan mineral tersebut. Sedangkan pemrosesan adalah sebuah kegiatan untuk memisahkan mineral berharga dari partikel-partikel lain yang menyatu dengan mineral tersebut.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Alasan Kamu Wajib Kuliah Jurusan Pertambangan</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Kenapa sih harus masuk ke jurusan ini? Jurusan yang sedikit peminatnya ini sangat patut untuk kamu perhitungkan lho! Kenapa? Berikut adalah alasannya:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Kuliah Yang Tidak Membosankan</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Salah satu alasan kenapa kamu harus <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/alasan-kamu-wajib-kuliah-jurusan-pertambangan/\">kuliah jurusan pertambangan</a> adalah karena mata kuliah yang tidak membosankan. Di jurusan ini, kamu tidak melulu diajarkan teori tapi juga praktik langsung. Walaupun kamu tetap ada pelajaran menghitung dan di kelas, tapi kamu juga akan tetap mendapatkan porsi pelajaran praktik yang lumayan banyak. Bayangkan jika kamu hanya berada di dalam kelas dan berkutat hanya dengan buku saja, pasti akan sangat cepat jenuh bukan?</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Karir yang Luas</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Prospek karir dari jurusan ini juga sangat bagus lho. Pasalnya, ilmu yang telah kamu pelajari bukan merupakan ilmu umum, melainkan ilmu khusus yang hanya bisa kamu dapatkan di bangku universitas saja. Di Indonesia sendiri, perusahaan tambang sangat banyak. Tidak hanya dari negara kita saja alias BUMN, melainkan banyak perusahaan dari luar negeri yang juga aktif di Indonesia. Kamu juga bisa mempunyai kesempatan untuk bekerja <em>offshore </em>atau di kantor pusat perusahaan-perusahaan internasional.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Sering Melakukan Kunjungan Lapangan</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Bagi kamu yang tidak mau hanya bekerja di balik meja atau pun di luar ruangan, jurusan ini sangat cocok untukmu. Di masa depan nanti setelah kamu lulus, kamu akan mendapatkan banyak tugas untuk melakukan kunjungan lapangan. Kunjungan lapangan ini tidak hanya di dalam negeri lho, kamu mungkin akan mengunjungi beberapa negara yang ada di seluruh dunia. Alhasil, kamu tidak akan tuh yang namanya terus-menerus berkutat dengan dokumen-dokumen ataupun menatap layar monitor di balik meja kerja. Seru kan?</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color has-vivid-cyan-blue-color\"><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/alasan-kamu-wajib-kuliah-jurusan-pertambangan/\">Ingin tahu alasan lain kenapa kamu harus kuliah jurusan pertambangan? Baca lebih lengkapnya di sini!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Universitas terbaik di dunia untuk jurusan pertambangan</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Banyak lho universitas di dunia yang menyediakan kualitas pendidikan terbaik untuk jurusan pertambangan. Berikut adalah beberapa <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/daftar-lengkap-universitas-jurusan-pertambangan-terbaik-di-dunia/\">universitas jurusan pertambangan</a> terbaik untuk kamu:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>5. The University of New South Wales</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>University of New South Wales (UNSW), juga dikenal sebagai UNSW Sydney, adalah universitas riset publik yang berbasis di Sydney, New South Wales, Australia. Universitas ini merupakan salah satu anggota pendiri Group of Eight, sebuah koalisi universitas penelitian intensif Australia.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Menurut QS World University Ranking, universitas ini berada di urutan ke lima untuk jurusan pertambangan. Universitas ini juga merupakan salah satu universitas dengan tingkat penerimaan yang paling rendah yaitu 30%.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>4. McGill University</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>McGill University (Prancis: Université McGill) adalah universitas riset publik berbahasa Inggris yang berlokasi di Montreal, Quebec, Kanada.&nbsp; Universitas ini didirikan pada tahun 1821 oleh piagam kerajaan yang diberikan oleh Raja George I dan menyandang nama James McGill, seorang pedagang Skotlandia yang warisannya pada tahun 1813 membentuk cikal bakal universitas tersebut.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Di jurusan pertambangan, universitas ini mempunyai kualitas yang sangat bagus. QS World University Ranking menempatkan universitas ini di urutan keempat untuk jurusan pertambangan dengan tingkat penerimaan sebesar 46.3%.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>3. The University of Queensland</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>University of Queensland adalah universitas riset publik yang berlokasi di Brisbane, ibu kota negara bagian Queensland, Australia. Didirikan pada tahun 1909 oleh parlemen Queensland, UQ adalah salah satu dari enam universitas <em>sandstone</em>, sebutan informal untuk universitas tertua di setiap negara bagian.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>QS World University Ranking menempatkan universitas ini di urutan ketiga untuk jurusan pertambangan dengan tingkat penerimaan sebesar 40%.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color has-vivid-cyan-blue-color\"><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/daftar-lengkap-universitas-jurusan-pertambangan-terbaik-di-dunia/\">Ingin tahu universitas jurusan pertambangan terbaik di dunia yang lainnya? Cari tahu di sini!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Apa kamu sudah semakin mantap untuk masuk ke jurusan pertambangan? Kalau iya, banyak yang harus kamu persiapkan untuk masuk ke jurusan ini. Jika kamu ingin bisa bersaing di tingkat global, kamu juga perlu masuk ke universitas terbaik pula.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tidak pernah ada istilah terlalu dini untuk mencari beasiswa. Beasiswa tidak hanya memberikan manfaat secara materi, tetapi juga dapat membantu prospek masa depanmu bahkan setelah lulus dari universitas.<br><br>Download Panduan “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” untuk mencari tahu semua hal yang perlu kamu ketahui sebelum mendaftar beasiswa. GRATIS! <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/id/\">Download disini</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ayo persiapkan mimpimu kuliah di luar negeri dengan Eduverse by ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!<br></p>', 'Downloader.la-62cfc28d316ea.jpg', 'Jurusan Pertambangan: Hal-Hal Penting yang Wajib Kamu Tahu!', 'publish', 'Jurusan Pertambangan: Hal-Hal Penting yang Wajib Kamu Tahu!', 'Jurusan Pertambangan', 'Jurusan pertambangan adalah salah satu jurusan yang sedang naik daun di kalangan pelajar Indonesia. Apa kamu tertarik? Ayo baca lebih lengkap di sini!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-04-21 17:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00');
