(12062, 'a-glance-at-the-university-of-melbourne-acceptance-rate', 1, 0, 'A Glance at the University of Melbourne Acceptance Rate ﻿', '<p>Planning to study in Australia? The University of Melbourne should definitely be on your list! Aside from the blistering array of cultural activities offered on campus, the University of Melbourne is known for its academic excellence and highly reputable research. Furthermore, if you\'re planning to study there, let\'s take a look at the <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/the-university-of-melbourne-all-you-need-to-know-in-one-swipe/\">University of Melbourne</a> acceptance rate!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>University of Melbourne\'s background&nbsp;</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Since its founding in 1853, the University of Melbourne has grown into a research-intensive university that is consistently ranked among the leading universities in the world.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Encompassing seven campuses in Melbourne, the University of Melbourne is made up of more than 8,000 academic and professional staff, offering more than 300 undergraduate degrees in a wide variety of disciplines. This includes law, medicine, business, engineering, science, humanities and social sciences.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>University of Melbourne Acceptance Rate</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The University of Melbourne acceptance rate may vary based on the competitiveness of each faculty. For example, Commerce and Science programs have a more selective admission process compared to Education and Agricultural Sciences. As a result, the guaranteed entry score in Commerce and Science programs is higher compared to the others.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Additionally, the University of Melbourne has guaranteed entry scores; as long as you meet that score, you are guaranteed to be accepted.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>How to apply to the University of Melbourne</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you\'re planning to apply to the University of Melbourne, your application can be done online via the official <a href=\"https://www.unimelb.edu.au/\">university website</a>. Moreover, the fee is a non-refundable application fee of AUD $100. Furthermore, several supporting documents that are required as part of the application process include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>High school transcript</li><li>Portfolios (for programs in the Arts and Architecture)</li><li>Proof of English language proficiency</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>English Proficiency Test Score Requirement (except for the Bachelor of Oral Health)</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td><strong>Tests</strong></td><td><strong>Minimum Score Required</strong></td></tr><tr><td>IELTS</td><td>Overall 6.5, no bands less than 6.0</td></tr><tr><td>TOEFL	</td><td>Overall 79 (IBT)21 for writing18 for speaking13 for reading13 for listening&nbsp;Overall 577(PBT)</td></tr><tr><td>Cambridge English, Advanced/Certificate in Advanced English (CAE)</td><td>Overall 176, with no skill below 169	</td></tr><tr><td>Pearson Test of English</td><td>Overall 58, no PTE communicative skills below 5</td></tr><tr><td>C2 Proficiency (previously called Cambridge English: Proficiency (CPE) examination</td><td>At least 180, with no skill below 180</td></tr><tr><td>GCE A Levels&nbsp;</td><td>Grade of at least C in:AS or A Level General PaperAS or A Level General StudiesAS or A Level English LanguageAS or A Level English LiteratureAS or A Level English Language and Literature</td></tr><tr><td>International Baccalaureate Diploma&nbsp;</td><td>At least grade 4 in English or English B at SL or HL</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>English Proficiency Test Score Requirement for the Bachelor of Oral Health</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td><strong>Tests</strong></td><td><strong>Minimum Score Required</strong></td></tr><tr><td>IELTS</td><td>Overall 7.0, no bands less than 7.0</td></tr><tr><td>TOEFL	</td><td>Overall 94 (IBT)27 for writing23 for speaking24 for reading24 for listening</td></tr><tr><td>Pearson Test of English</td><td>Overall 65, no PTE communicative skills below 65</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Rankings&nbsp;</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>According to the well-regarded QS World University Rankings 2022, the University of Melbourne is ranked 33rd in the world and 2nd in Australia. Additionally, it is ranked 8th in the QS Graduate Employability Rankings 2022.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are the rankings of several courses that are offered at the University of Melbourne, according to the QS World University Rankings By Subject:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Arts and Humanities - 16th in the world&nbsp;</li><li>Engineering & Technology - 30th in the world&nbsp;</li><li>Life Sciences & Medicine - 17th in the world&nbsp;</li><li>Natural Sciences - 38th in the world&nbsp;</li><li>Social Sciences & Management - 15th in the world </li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Now that you have taken a look at the University of Melbourne acceptance rate, are you planning to apply there? From BA to BSc and everything in between, the University of Melbourne offers a range of undergraduate degrees that is suitable for everyone!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Securing your spot at the University of Melbourne? Let\'s do it with ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top uni preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>', 'Downloader.la-62e25917339ec.jpg', 'A Glance at the University of Melbourne Acceptance Rate ﻿', 'publish', 'A Glance at the University of Melbourne Acceptance Rate ﻿', 'University of Melbourne Acceptance Rate', 'Have a dream to study abroad? Take a look at the University of Melbourne acceptance rate to improve your admission chance on your dream university!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-05-12 17:00:00', '2022-07-08 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(12068, 'the-university-of-melbourne-scholarships-for-international-students', 1, 0, 'The University of Melbourne Scholarships for International Students', '<p>Situated in the city entitled Australia\'s “cultural capital,” the University of Melbourne offers students more than just an elite education. Amongst its 65,000 students, there are around 30,000 international students from 130 different countries around the globe. The University of Melbourne is able to offer students classes with some of the leading academics in the world, which is evident because its 89 different courses mostly rank in the top 100 of their respective majors.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/the-university-of-melbourne-all-you-need-to-know-in-one-swipe/\">University of Melbourne</a> is currently taking place as the best university nationally in the Times Higher Education World University Rankings 2022. Along with its national brilliance, the University of Melbourne is also ranked as the 33rd best university globally in the QS World University Rankings 2023.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Studying abroad at the University of Melbourne is a great choice; however, there is one slight problem. Studying there can get very expensive. The good news is that you can study at the University of Melbourne without spending too much money by applying for scholarships.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are interested in studying at the University of Melbourne, here are some University of Melbourne scholarship opportunities that you can try applying for:</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Melbourne International Undergraduate Scholarship</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The University of Melbourne offers international high schoolers their very own <em>Melbourne International Undergraduate Scholarship</em>. This is one of the best University of Melbourne scholarships because there are approximately 1000 slots per year, and the scholarship is applicable for all majors. In order to receive this award, you must be an international undergraduate high school student in the top 20% of your school. You don\'t need to apply for this award because you will automatically be considered for the award when you apply.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are the benefits of the <a href=\"https://scholarships.unimelb.edu.au/awards/melbourne-international-undergraduate-scholarship#full-benefit-details\"><em>Melbourne International Undergraduate Scholarship</em></a>:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>For the 1st year of your undergraduate degree, you will receive an AUD $10,000 discount on the tuition fee.</li><li>For the next three years of your undergraduate degree, you will either receive a 50% or 100% discount on your tuition fee.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Australia Awards Scholarship</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The next on the list of University of Melbourne scholarships is Australia Awards. The Department of Foreign Affairs and Trade offers the <em>Australia Awards Scholarship</em> to international graduate students who wish to study in Australia. Moreover, the <em>Australia Awards Scholarship</em> can be considered a University of Melbourne scholarship. In order to be eligible for the <em>Australia Awards Scholarship</em>, students must sign a contract with the Commonwealth of Australia to ensure that they will follow the conditions of the scholarship. Students must also leave Australia after completing their scholarship for a minimum of 2 years. Furthermore, this only applies to an applicant who studies a specific subject. With that being said, you have to apply for the <em>Australia Awards Scholarship</em> in order to receive the rewards.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are the benefits of the <a href=\"https://www.dfat.gov.au/people-to-people/australia-awards/australia-awards-scholarships\"><em>Australia Awards Scholarship</em></a>:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Full discount on tuition fees, including travel expenses</li><li>Establishment allowance and living expenses</li><li>Introductory Academic Program (IAP) and Pre-course English (PCE)</li><li>Overseas Student Health Cover (OSHC)</li><li>Academic support and fieldwork</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Indonesia Endowment Funds for Education Scholarship (LPDP) - Master Only</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Indonesia\'s Ministry of Finance offers the <em>Indonesia Endowment Funds for Education Scholarship (LPDP)</em> for students who wish to study abroad, which also includes the University of Melbourne. In order to be eligible for the<em> Indonesia Endowment Funds for Education Scholarship (LPDP)</em>, students must have proof of English proficiency, which you can show by taking either TOEFL iBT, PTE Academic, or IELTS.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are the benefits of the <a href=\"https://lpdp.kemenkeu.go.id/en/investasi/dana-abadi/\"><em>Indonesia Endowment Funds for Education Scholarship</em></a><em>:</em></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Tuition and admission fees</li><li>Travel expenses</li><li>Visa / Residence Permit application&nbsp;</li><li>Health insurance and living costs</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>To wrap things up, the University of Melbourne is a great place to continue your academic career in whatever field you desire. Being a member of the Group of Eight, the University of Melbournes\' prestigious reputation and high rankings both internationally and nationally will make it easier for you to find jobs after your university career.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Are you interested in attending the University of Melbourne? Let\'s prepare with ALL-in Eduspace!&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\"><strong>Admission Mentoring</strong></a><strong>.</strong></li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\"><strong>Career Exploration.</strong></a></li><li>Improve grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\"><strong>Academic Tutoring.</strong></a></li><li>Upscale your personal brand in the <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/writing-skills/\"><strong>Writing Skills</strong></a><strong> </strong>improvement program.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!</p>', 'Downloader.la-62e25c846dec6.jpg', 'The University of Melbourne Scholarships for International Students', 'publish', 'The University of Melbourne Scholarships for International Students', 'University of Melbourne Scholarships', 'Looking for the best and most suitable University of Melbourne scholarships for your further studies? Read the full list in this article now!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-05-11 17:00:00', '2022-07-01 17:00:00', '2022-11-03 17:00:00'),
(12072, 'the-university-of-melbourne-all-you-need-to-know-in-one-swipe', 1, 0, 'The University of Melbourne: All You Need to Know in One Swipe!', '<p>With around 30,000 international students from 130 different countries, the University of Melbourne has been a top choice for many international high schoolers who wish to study abroad. The University of Melbourne\'s 36-hectare campus is home to more than 65,000 students.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Rich with history, the University of Melbourne is in fact the second oldest university in Australia and the oldest school in Victoria. This university is currently ranked as the 33rd best university globally in the QS World University Rankings 2023 and is ranked as the 8th best university in the QS Graduate Employability Rankings 2022.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ranked as the best university nationally by the Times Higher Education World University Rankings 2022, the University of Melbourne not only offers an elite academic program but also offers great experiences outside of academics. This university is situated in the city dubbed Australia\'s “cultural capital,” so if you choose to attend this university, you\'ll have plenty of fun to go with your studies.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s take a look at some of the ways you can prepare yourself for enrolling at the University of Melbourne:</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>A Glance at the University of Melbourne Acceptance Rate</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Although the University of Melbourne sounds like a great place to continue your academic career. But, you still need to get accepted first. It is important to know how selective a university is before you apply so that you aren\'t putting in all your time, effort, and resources into a university that you probably won\'t end up getting accepted to. With that being said, the acceptance rate for the university is around pretty high, making it a lightly selective school.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are wondering how you can apply to the university, here is the list of requirements that you should prepare before you apply:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>High school transcript</li><li>Portfolios (For some majors only)</li><li>Proof of English language proficiency</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Keep in mind that a lot of talented high school students are also considering continuing their studies at this university, so you should try to achieve more than the list of requirements mentioned. Taking up extracurricular activities both outside and inside your field of interest can definitely help you in your application process. Doing extracurricular activities can show the admissions officers that you are both genuinely interested in your desired field. Moreover, this wwill show them that you are a well-rounded person.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color has-vivid-cyan-blue-color\"><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/a-glance-at-the-university-of-melbourne-acceptance-rate/\">Want to know more about the acceptance rate for the University of Melbourne?  Read the full article here!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>University of Melbourne Courses You Should Consider Taking</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Choosing the right major in university is a crucial step for your future. If you choose the wrong major, it will be hard for you to do well in that course because you don\'t genuinely love it. Moreover, when things get challenging, it might be easier to give up since your major isn\'t something you are passionate about.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you want to take both a challenging, but also informative course, here are the top 5 courses you should try taking:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Infectious Diseases </strong>(ranked 9th in the University of Melbourne Subject Rankings from U.S. News)</li><li><strong>Microbiology </strong>(ranked 11th in the University of Melbourne Subject Rankings from U.S. News)</li><li><strong>Immunology </strong>(ranked 11th in the University of Melbourne Subject Rankings from U.S. News)</li><li><strong>Psychiatry/Psychology </strong>(ranked 14th in the University of Melbourne Subject Rankings from U.S. News)</li><li><strong>Public and Environmental Health </strong>(ranked 15th in the University of Melbourne Subject Rankings from U.S. News)</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Want to know more about the <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/top-5-university-of-melbourne-courses-you-should-consider-taking/\">University of Melbourne courses</a>? Read the full article here!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>The University of Melbourne Scholarships for Undergraduate International High Schoolers</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>&nbsp;If you choose to attend the University of Melbourne, you will be a part of one of the best universities both academically and non-academically. Despite all the benefits that the university has to offer, the expenses are quite high. You\'ll need to pay tuition fees, travel expenses, living costs, textbooks, and even health insurance. All these things add up, and it can get very expensive.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are struggling financially to pay the tuition fees for the university, you should check out these scholarship opportunities:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Melbourne International Undergraduate Scholarship</strong></li><li><strong>Australia Awards Scholarship</strong></li><li><strong>Indonesia Endowment Funds for Education Scholarship (LPDP)</strong></li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>These programs, however, have specific, selective requirements if you want to receive their rewards. It might be that you need to achieve a certain score on a standardized test. Or it might be that you need to prove that your English proficiency is good enough for the university. With that being said, there are a limited amount of these scholarships available. So, if you don\'t stand out academically, then you won\'t be selected for the rewards.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/the-university-of-melbourne-scholarships-for-international-students/\">Want to know more about the University of Melbourne scholarships? Read the full article here!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Conclusions</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>To wrap things up, the University of Melbourne is a great place to continue your academic career in whatever field you desire. If you want a place that is not only fun but also great academically, look no further than the University of Melbourne. The courses are challenging, detailed, and informative, so you know you\'re going to learn a lot. Being a member of the Group of Eight, the University of Melbournes\' prestigious reputation and high rankings both internationally and nationally. Therefore, this will make it easier for you to find jobs to work in after your university career. All of these reasons make studying at the University of Melbourne an absolutely fantastic college experience.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” Guidebook to find out all the things you need to know before applying for scholarships. It\'s FREE, <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/\">download here</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Do you have a dream to study at the University of Melbourne? ALL-in will help you secure your spot!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top uni preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!</p>', 'Downloader.la-62e2753d13786.jpg', 'The University of Melbourne: All You Need to Know in One Swipe!', 'publish', 'The University of Melbourne: All You Need to Know in One Swipe!', 'University of Melbourne', 'University of Melbourne is one of the best universities in Australia. Dreaming to go there? Take a look at all insight about the university in this article!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-05-10 17:00:00', '2022-07-24 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(12078, 'kupas-tuntas-jurusan-bisnis-digital-yang-sedang-trendy', 2, 0, 'Kupas Tuntas Jurusan Bisnis Digital yang Sedang Trendy', '<p>Jika kamu adalah seseorang yang suka menangani sebuah usaha atau punya mimpi untuk membuka usaha sendiri, jurusan bisnis digital sangat cocok untukmu. Dengan semakin terkenalnya juga bisnis di bidang digital, jurusan ini juga semakin banyak di cari oleh banyak perusahaan. Ingin tahu informasi lebih dalam mengenai jurusan bisnis digital? Ayo simak lebih lengkap di bawah ini!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kamu inget nggak beberapa lama lalu ada sebuah drama korea yang cukup hits berjudul <em>start up</em>. Sesuai judulnya, drama korea yang satu ini bercerita tentang sekelompok anak muda yang sedang merintis usaha dari nol. Meskipun fiktif, banyak orang yang merasa relate dengan drama yang satu ini. Hal ini karena alur cerita dan tantangan yang dialami para tokoh yang berada di drama ini sangat sama seperti yang ada di dunia nyata. Tidak hanya itu, dari sini kita belajar bahwa dengan berkembangnya teknologi, ada banyak juga perubahan yang terjadi di berbagai bidang, salah satunya adalah bisnis.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Apa itu Jurusan Bisnis Digital?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Bisnis Digital merupakan salah satu jurusan yang masuk ke rumpun ilmu terapan. Pada implementasinya, jurusan ini akan mempelajari tentang cara merancang dan menjalankan bisnis modern maupun tradisional yang berbasis digital. Ilmu yang akan akan kamu dapatkan pada umumnya adalah perpaduan dari&nbsp; beberapa ilmu yang meliputi manajemen, bisnis, teknik informatika, dan juga sistem informasi. Umumnya, Jurusan Bisnis Digital tersedia pada program D4 atau S1.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan ini didirikan untuk mengatasi berbagai macam tantangan bisnis yang mungkin timbul di masa depan. Kemajuan bisnis di masa mendatang akan didominasi oleh sistem informasi dan digital sehingga memerlukan kajian khusus yang terstruktur, mendalam, dan berkelanjutan untuk dapat menyusun dan menjalankan strategi bisnis yang tepat. Bahkan lebih dari itu, ketika kamu sudah berhasil lulus dari jurusan ini, kamu diharapkan untuk memiliki berbagai macam keterampilan mumpuni untuk menjadi seorang ahli di bidang digital business. Kamu juga harus mampu memberikan beberapa solusi dan rekomendasi dalam berbagai permasalahan bisnis digital. Jadi, jurusan ini akan sangat cocok untuk kamu yang memiliki minat bisnis yang kuat.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Prospek Kerja</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan ini mempunyai beberapa prospek baik di masa depan. Sebagai salah satu bidang yang sedang berkembang, bisni digital memberikan opsi yang sangat luas bagi siapapun yang berminat di bidang tersebut. Berikut adalah beberapa prospek karir di masa mendatang yang bisa kamu ambil.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Digital Marketing Manager</strong>. Di posisi ini, kamu bertugas untuk memasarkan produk dan jasa. Selain itu kamu juga mempunyai kewajiban untuk menarik pengguna dan mengkonversi data atau masyarakat umum menjadi pelanggan melalui berbagai macam media dan kanal digital misalnya web, mobile, video dan media sosial. Kamu juga akan menggunakan berbagai macam teknik-teknik pemasaran digital seperti: Search Engine Optimization (SEO), Search Engine Marketing (SEM).</li><li><strong>Business Consultant</strong>. Seperti namanya, kamu akan menyediakan jasa konsultasi kepada suatu organisasi/lembaga/perusahaan. Kamu bertanggung jawab untuk memberikan opsi yang bisa membuat organisasi/lembaga/perusahaan semakin berkembang dan lebih efisien. Konsultan bisnis bertugas mengidentifikasi masalah dan memberikan solusi. Kamu akan membuat beberapa perencanaan bisnis ke depan agar dapat memenuhi target yang diinginkan perusahaan.</li><li><strong>Business Management Analyst</strong>. Di sini, kamu akan bertugas untuk menganalisa suatu perusahaan/organisasi dalam segi prosedur dan desain, sistem operasional, serta sistem lainnya. Profesi ini biasanya mempunyai tanggung jawab secara spesifik kepada bagian/divisi/program tertentu. Tanggung jawab kamu sebagai Business Management Analyst adalah mengidentifikasi sebuah permasalahan bisnis dan menemukan solusi agar manajemen dapat melanjutkan operasi harian dengan lebih efisien dan efektif, serta dapat mengembangkan bisnisnya.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Universitas Top di Australia untuk Jurusan Bisnis Digital</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Jika kamu ingin kuliah di luar negeri, Australia mungkin bisa menjadi salah satu tujuan yang bisa kamu pertimbangkan. Hal ini karena kualitas pendidikannya yang sangat baik dan juga terkenal.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Berikut adalah beberapa universitas yang bisa kamu jadikan pilihan untuk melanjutkan masa studimu di sana:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>University of Sydney.</li><li>University of New South Wales.</li><li>Monash University. </li><li>University of Melbourne.</li><li>University of Queensland Australia.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Kalau kamu adalah seseorang yang mempunyai minat tinggi di bidang bisnis dan aktif dalam dunia sosial di berbagai macam platform di internet, jurusan ini sangat cocok untukmu. Ingat ya, untuk bisa bersaing di industri bisnis digital global, kamu juga perlu untuk mencari ilmu ke universitas top yang mempunyai kualitas pendidikan yang luar biasa.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ingin masuk ke <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/serba-serbi-jurusan-bisnis-yang-sedang-naik-daun/\">jurusan bisnis</a> digital terbaik di dunia? Ayo gabung ke EDU VERSE by ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download Panduan “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” untuk mencari tahu semua hal yang perlu kamu ketahui sebelum mendaftar beasiswa. GRATIS! <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/id/\">Download disini</a> </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!</p>', 'Downloader.la-62e2778daab97.jpg', 'Kupas Tuntas Jurusan Bisnis Digital yang Sedang Trendy', 'publish', 'Kupas Tuntas Jurusan Bisnis Digital yang Sedang Trendy', 'Jurusan Bisnis Digital', 'Apa kamu ingin melanjutkan studi di jurusan bisnis digital? Simak beberapa hal di artikel ini yang sangat penting untuk kamu perhitungkan!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-04-29 17:00:00', '2022-07-24 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(12084, 'hal-yang-wajib-kamu-tahu-tentang-jurusan-bisnis-internasional', 2, 0, 'Hal yang Wajib Kamu Tahu Tentang Jurusan Bisnis Internasional', '<p>Apa kamu tertarik dengan perkembangan ekonomi secara global? Kalau iya, maka jurusan yang satu ini akan sangat cocok untukmu. Jurusan Bisnis Internasional mengkaji tentang perkembangan ekonomi dalam skala internasional. Ingin tahu lebih banyak lagi? Ayo simak di bawah ini!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Apa itu Jurusan Bisnis Internasional?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Program studi Bisnis Internasional adalah sebuah program studi yang berpusat pada pembelajaran mengenai berbagai macam tantangan-tantangan yang telah dan akan dihadapi oleh dunia bisnis internasional. Di jurusan ini kamu akan belajar etika dan macam-macam hukum bisnis di dunia internasional. Semua yang kamu pelajari pastinya berbeda dengan macam-macam etika dan hukum bisnis dalam negeri. Selain itu, kamu juga akan dilatih untuk berpikir secara global dalam menciptakan berbagai macam ide dan solusi dalam permasalahan ekonomi dan bisnis di lingkup internasional.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Biasanya prodi ini akan dilakukan menggunakan bahasa Inggris sebagai bahasa pengantar dalam kegiatan perkuliahan sehari-hari. Tapi bukan berarti kamu harus fasih berbahasa Inggris dulu untuk masuk prodi ini. Disini kamu akan dilatih untuk mahir melakukan komunikasi bisnis dengan bahasa Inggris. Prodi Bisnis Internasional umumnya juga memiliki partner dari perusahaan-perusahaan multinasional yang menyediakan program magang untuk mahasiswa, sehingga kamu akan memeroleh pengalaman kerja dan berpotensi untuk direkrut oleh perusahaan yang bersangkutan.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Prospek Kerja</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Seorang sarjana prodi Bisnis Internasional memiliki prospek karir yang sangat beragam dan cemerlang untuk bergabung di berbagai macam perusahaan multinasional, organisasi nasional dan internasional, perusahaan ekspor-impor, dan perusahaan investasi. Dengan adanya partisipasi Indonesia dalam Masyarakat Ekonomi Asia (MEA), kompetisi perdagangan antar-negara pun tak bisa dihindari lagi. Karena itu, dibutuhkan banyak ahli bisnis yang memiliki pengetahuan tidak hanya mengenai bisnis itu sendiri, tetapi juga mengenai isu-isu internasional yang mempengaruhi proses berjalannya sebuah bisnis. Berikut adalah beberapa prospek karir yang bisa kamu pilih setelah selesai berkuliah di jurusan ini:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Market Research Analyst</strong>. Di posisi ini, kamu akan banyak bertanggung jawab di seputar meneliti dan menganalisa kondisi pasar lokal, regional, maupun nasional. Kamu juga mempunyai tugas untuk mengumpulkan informasi yang nantinya akan dipakai untuk menentukan potensi penjualan dari berbagai macam produk/layanan, atau bahkan membuat sebuah kampanye pemasaran. Market Research Analyst juga bertanggung jawab untuk mengumpulkan banyak informasi mengenai pesaing, harga penjualan, dan metode pemasaran dan distribusi.</li><li><strong>Purchasing Manager</strong>. Sebagai purchasing manager, kamu akan bertugas untuk mengarahkan, merencanakan, atau mengkoordinasi berbagai macam aspek seperti pembelian, petugas pembelian, dan pegawai terkait yang ikut serta dalam kegiatan pembelian bahan, produk, atau jasa.</li><li><strong>Logistic Analyst</strong>. Jika kamu memilih karisi ini, kamu akan menganalisis proses pengiriman produk dan rantai pasokan yang berguna untuk mengidentifikasi atau dan mengimplementasikan solusi. Kamu dituntut untuk dapat mengelola aktivitas rute. Tidak hanya itu, kamu juga akan mengurus faktur, tagihan elektronik, dan pengiriman pelacakan.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Universitas Top di Asia untuk Jurusan Bisnis Internasional</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Jika kamu ingin kuliah di luar negeri, Asia mungkin bisa menjadi salah satu tujuan yang bisa kamu pertimbangkan. Selain karna masih bisa dibilang cukup dekat dengan negara kita, kualitas pendidikannya yang sangat baik dan juga terkenal.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Berikut adalah beberapa universitas yang bisa kamu jadikan pilihan untuk melanjutkan masa studimu di sana:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>INSEAD, Singapura.</li><li>CEIBS (China Europe International Business School), China.</li><li>National University of Singapore Business School, Singapura.</li><li>HKUST Business School, Hong Kong.</li><li>Indian School of Business, India.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Bagaiamana? Apa kamu semakin tertarik untuk masuk ke jurusan program studi bisnis internasional. Jurusan yang satu ini juga mempunyai banyak pilihan karir yang bisa kamu pilih. Tapi jika kamu ingin bersaing dengan banyak profesional di tingkat internasional, kamu juga harus membekali dirimu dengan kualitas pendidikan yang mumpuni juga. Maka, dari itu pastikan kamu mendapatkan pendidikan terbaik di universitas top dunia.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tertarik untuk menuntut ilmu di <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/serba-serbi-jurusan-bisnis-yang-sedang-naik-daun/\">jurusan bisnis</a> internasional terbaik di dunia? Eduverse by ALL-in akan membantu semua persiapanmu!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download Panduan “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” untuk mencari tahu semua hal yang perlu kamu ketahui sebelum mendaftar beasiswa. GRATIS! <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/id/\">Download disini</a> </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!<br></p>', 'Downloader.la-62e27967a5d5c.jpg', 'Hal yang Wajib Kamu Tahu Tentang Jurusan Bisnis Internasional', 'publish', 'Hal yang Wajib Kamu Tahu Tentang Jurusan Bisnis Internasional', 'Jurusan Bisnis Internasional', 'Jurusan bisnis internasional adalah jurusan yang sedang naik daun karena adanya situasi ekonomi dunia yang bergejolak. Penasaran? Ayo simak di sini!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-04-28 17:00:00', '2022-07-22 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(12088, 'serba-serbi-jurusan-bisnis-yang-sedang-naik-daun', 2, 0, 'Serba-Serbi Jurusan Bisnis yang Sedang Naik Daun', '<p>Jurusan bisnis merupakan salah satu jurusan yang mempunyai banyak peminat di luar sana. Entah itu pelajar dari Indonesia ataupun dari luar negeri, semuanya tampak tertarik dengan prospek yang bisa didapat setelah lulus dari jurusan ini. Ingin tahu lebih banyak soal jurusan bisnis dan macam-macamnya? Baca lebih lanjut di bawah ini!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Apa itu Jurusan Bisnis?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Selama beberapa tahun ini, jurusan Bisnis telah menjadi salah satu jurusan yang paling diminati di berbagai universitas di seluruh dunia. Jurusan ini sangat cocok untuk kamu yang memiliki visi menjadi seorang pengusaha muda. Bisnis merupakan bidang ilmu yang mempelajari bagaimana melakukan pemasaran produk, pembukuan dan pengelolaan keuangan serta hal-hal terkait keberlanjutan dari suatu usaha. Bidang ini membantu memahami kebutuhan pelanggan dan mengkomersialisasikannya. Jadi, bisa dibilang bidang ini merupakan kombinasi dari Manajemen dan Akuntansi.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan ini sendiri mempunyai pendalaman yang berbeda. Berikut adalah beberapa penjurusan yang ada di jurusan bisnis:</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Bisnis Internasional</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Program studi Bisnis Internasional adalah sebuah program studi yang berpusat pada pembelajaran mengenai berbagai macam tantangan-tantangan yang telah dan akan dihadapi oleh dunia bisnis internasional. Di jurusan ini kamu akan belajar etika dan macam-macam hukum bisnis di dunia internasional. Semua yang kamu pelajari pastinya berbeda dengan macam-macam etika dan hukum bisnis dalam negeri. Selain itu, kamu juga akan dilatih untuk berpikir secara global dalam menciptakan berbagai macam ide dan solusi dalam permasalahan ekonomi dan bisnis di lingkup internasional.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Biasanya <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/hal-yang-wajib-kamu-tahu-tentang-jurusan-bisnis-internasional/\">jurusan bisnis internasional</a> akan dilakukan menggunakan bahasa Inggris sebagai bahasa pengantar dalam kegiatan perkuliahan sehari-hari. Tapi bukan berarti kamu harus fasih berbahasa Inggris dulu untuk masuk prodi ini. Disini kamu akan dilatih untuk mahir melakukan komunikasi bisnis dengan bahasa Inggris. Prodi Bisnis Internasional umumnya juga memiliki partner dari perusahaan-perusahaan multinasional yang menyediakan program magang untuk mahasiswa, sehingga kamu akan memeroleh pengalaman kerja dan berpotensi untuk direkrut oleh perusahaan yang bersangkutan.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Universitas Top di A</strong>sia<strong> untuk Jurusan </strong>Ini</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Jika kamu ingin kuliah di luar negeri, Asia mungkin bisa menjadi salah satu tujuan yang bisa kamu pertimbangkan. Selain karna masih bisa dibilang cukup dekat dengan negara kita, kualitas pendidikannya yang sangat baik dan juga terkenal.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Berikut adalah beberapa universitas yang bisa kamu jadikan pilihan untuk melanjutkan masa studimu di sana:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>INSEAD, Singapura.</li><li>CEIBS (China Europe International Business School), China.</li><li>National University of Singapore Business School, Singapura.</li><li>HKUST Business School, Hong Kong.</li><li>Indian School of Business, India.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color has-vivid-cyan-blue-color\"><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/hal-yang-wajib-kamu-tahu-tentang-jurusan-bisnis-internasional/\">Ingin tahu lebih banyak mengenai jurusan ini? Simak di sini!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Jurusan Bisnis Digital</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Bisnis digital merupakan salah satu jurusan yang masuk ke rumpun ilmu terapan. Pada implementasinya, jurusan ini akan mempelajari tentang cara merancang dan menjalankan bisnis modern maupun tradisional yang berbasis digital. Ilmu yang akan akan kamu dapatkan pada umumnya adalah perpaduan dari&nbsp; beberapa ilmu yang meliputi manajemen, bisnis, teknik informatika, dan juga sistem informasi. Umumnya, Jurusan Bisnis Digital tersedia pada program D4 atau S1.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/kupas-tuntas-jurusan-bisnis-digital-yang-sedang-trendy/\">Jurusan bisnis digital</a> didirikan untuk mengatasi berbagai macam tantangan bisnis yang mungkin timbul di masa depan. Kemajuan bisnis di masa mendatang akan didominasi oleh sistem informasi dan digital sehingga memerlukan kajian khusus yang terstruktur, mendalam, dan berkelanjutan untuk dapat menyusun dan menjalankan strategi bisnis yang tepat. Bahkan lebih dari itu, ketika kamu sudah berhasil lulus dari jurusan ini, kamu diharapkan untuk memiliki berbagai macam keterampilan mumpuni untuk menjadi seorang ahli di bidang digital business. Kamu juga harus mampu memberikan beberapa solusi dan rekomendasi dalam berbagai permasalahan bisnis digital. Jadi, jurusan ini akan sangat cocok untuk kamu yang memiliki minat bisnis yang kuat.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Universitas Top di Australia untuk Jurusan Bisnis Digital</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Jika kamu ingin kuliah di luar negeri, Australia mungkin bisa menjadi salah satu tujuan yang bisa kamu pertimbangkan. Hal ini karena kualitas pendidikannya yang sangat baik dan juga terkenal.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Berikut adalah beberapa universitas yang bisa kamu jadikan pilihan untuk melanjutkan masa studimu di sana:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li><span style=\"background-color: rgb(225, 190, 231);\">University of Sydney.</span></li><li>University of New South Wales.</li><li>Monash University.</li><li>University of Melbourne.</li><li>University of Queensland Australia.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color has-vivid-cyan-blue-color\"><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/kupas-tuntas-jurusan-bisnis-digital-yang-sedang-trendy/\">Tertarik untuk masuk ke jurusan ini? Baca lebih lengkapnya di sini!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kedua jurusan ini memang sangat menarik untuk para pelajar dari berbagai penjuru dunia. Kamu tertarik untuk masuk ke salah satu penjurusan yang ada di atas? Pastikan kamu masuk ke universitas top dunia agar kamu bisa bersaing di dunia karir global!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Punya mimpi untuk masuk ke jurusan bisnis terbaik di dunia? Ayo persiapkan semuanya bersama EDUVERSE!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download Panduan “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” untuk mencari tahu semua hal yang perlu kamu ketahui sebelum mendaftar beasiswa. GRATIS! <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/id/\">Download disini</a> </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!<br></p>', 'Downloader.la-62e27a5b71b98.jpg', 'Serba-Serbi Jurusan Bisnis yang Sedang Naik Daun', 'publish', 'Serba-Serbi Jurusan Bisnis yang Sedang Naik Daun', 'Jurusan Bisnis', 'Apa kamu tertarik untuk melanjutkan studi di jurusan bisnis? Berikut adalah pilihan jurusan yang bisa kamu perhitungkan dan beberapa info spesial lainnya!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-04-27 17:00:00', '2022-07-10 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(12149, 'looking-for-mentoring-programs-for-youth-here-it-is', 1, 0, 'Looking for Mentoring Programs for Youth? Here it is!', '<p>What is a mentor and why do you need one? If you\'re still not sure about what mentors and mentoring are all about, don\'t worry! In this article, we\'ll learn more about mentoring programs for youth, particularly those between 13 and 18 years old, their purposes, and what you\'ll gain from them. Let\'s dive into it!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>What is a mentoring program?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/mentoring-programs-these-are-all-reasons-why-you-need-it/\">Mentoring programs</a> for youth connect adults with expertise in a certain area to youths who are interested in that area and need guidance to pursue their interests</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As someone who has “been there, done that”, a mentor can share practical and helpful advice, offer guidance, and act as a sounding board for your thoughts. In a way, mentoring programs for youth help break down any barriers you have, such as not knowing what to pursue after high school or how to pursue it, to create opportunities for success.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>The Role of the Mentor</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Mentoring programs for youth connect teenagers to adults with expertise in a certain area who are able to provide guidance and encouragement throughout the mentee\'s years in school. Moreover, these programs can range from limited guidance for school and academics only, to help with interest exploration and future career goals, to things like navigating friendships.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Instead of going through blind trial and error in your learning process, a mentor is someone who can help direct your learning to make it more effective.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A mentor\'s role is multifaceted, it depends on what kind of mentor you are seeking. A mentor can be:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>a role model</li><li>a supporter&nbsp;</li><li>a coach&nbsp;</li><li>an advisor</li><li>a friend</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Types of Mentoring&nbsp;</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Mentoring programs can help you in several areas. Here are some examples:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Education</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Maybe you find it hard to grasp some concepts at school. With mentor, you can gain a better understanding of real-world applications from someone who is an expert in their field. Furthermore, this would complement your learning in school, helping grow your understanding and possibly even your interest in studying that area.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Future Career Goals</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>With numerous options out there, it may be hard to pick which field is best suited for you. Through a mentoring program, you are encouraged to explore your interests beyond just the school environment. In this way, you\'ll get to understand yourself more and make better-informed decisions for your future.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Benefits of joining a mentoring program for youth&nbsp;</h2>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Receive guidance&nbsp;</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Mentors give their mentees advice on how to approach certain situations or point out things that they may not have considered before. As mentors are people who are successful in their field, they can provide valuable insight into what it takes to succeed.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Networking opportunities</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Through a mentoring program, a mentor can introduce their mentee to industry contacts that they might not have been able to connect with otherwise. Through this, mentees could land an internship or a part-time position to enhance their skills in their desired area.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Increased confidence</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Mentorship programs allow mentees to take ownership of their personal, academic, and professional development. Instead of feeling stagnant, having a mentor can accelerate a mentee\'s growth by having a trustworthy figure to consult for advice.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In short, the mentoring relationship is a relationship between two people who share a common interest and is mutually beneficial. The mentor is someone who has been down the path you\'re on. They can offer their perspective on what it takes to get there. They are there to help you develop your skills and knowledge, as well as provide you with encouragement and guidance through the ever-confusing world.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” Guidebook to find out all the things you need to know before applying for scholarships. It\'s FREE, <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/\">download here</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>So, have you thought about joining mentoring programs for youth? Get the initial consultation with our mentors <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/\">here</a>!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\"><strong>Admission Mentoring</strong></a><strong>.</strong></li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\"><strong>Career Exploration.</strong></a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\"><strong>Academic Tutoring.</strong></a></li><li>Highlight your personal brand through the <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/writing-skills/\"><strong>Writing Skills</strong></a><strong> </strong>improvement program.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'Downloader.la-62ec8bec885fd.jpg', 'Looking for Mentoring Programs for Youth? Here it is!', 'publish', 'Looking for Mentoring Programs for Youth? Here it is!', 'Mentoring Programs for Youth', 'Are you still wondering whether you should look for mentoring programs for youth? Wonder no more! Get the full scoop in this article now!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-05-16 17:00:00', '2022-08-12 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00');
INSERT INTO `tb_blog` (`id`, `slug`, `cat_id`, `mt_id`, `blog_title`, `blog_description`, `blog_thumbnail`, `blog_thumbnail_alt`, `blog_status`, `seo_title`, `seo_keyword`, `seo_desc`, `lang`, `click_count`, `duration_read`, `is_highlight`, `publish_date`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(12153, 'full-scoop-and-facts-on-mentoring-programs-for-students', 1, 0, 'Full Scoop and Facts on Mentoring Programs for Students', '<p>Have you heard the word ‘mentoring\' before? Maybe you have, but you\'re still not sure what it\'s all about. In this article, we\'ll learn more about <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/mentoring-programs-these-are-all-reasons-why-you-need-it/\">mentoring programs</a> for students. Read on to find out what you can gain from joining a mentoring program and why it might be right for you!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>What is a mentor?&nbsp;</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A mentor is someone who possesses expertise in the skills that the mentee would like to develop. They can help guide you in your progression as a student. Aside from providing direct feedback, mentors can also serve as a sounding board for your ideas and problems.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Mentor-mentee relationships can take a variety of forms, depending on the mentor\'s availability and mentee\'s needs. The relationship could be short-term or continue indefinitely, with regular meetings or casual check-ins.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In short, mentors provide guidance on how to achieve your goals, and they also help you identify your strengths and weaknesses.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Different forms of mentoring programs&nbsp;</h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Traditional mentoring</strong> is when a mentor and a mentee are matched one-on-one, either through a program or on their own.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Group mentoring </strong>involves a mentor working with small groups of mentees.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Team mentoring</strong> involves several mentors working together with a small group of mentees.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>E-mentoring </strong>is a form of one-on-one mentoring that happens virtually through the Internet, email, social media, or other forms of internet communication.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Why you should join mentoring programs for students</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Learning all the different concepts and theories in school is fascinating. But of course, it also comes with its challenges. Sometimes there are things that you find hard to understand, or maybe you have an idea for a project and want to discuss it with someone who would know how to help you with it.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Knowing that mentors have gone through the same experience as you, means they know what it takes to succeed in school. By working with a mentor, you\'ll be guided to understand the concepts that you learned in school with real-world expectations and applications, which can be applied throughout your personal and professional lives.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In short, a mentor can be your rock while you face the ups and downs of school.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Difference between mentors and tutors</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A mentor is someone who can act as a role model, navigate your path, and help you with personal development. A tutor, on the other hand, has a more specific role in helping you learn the skills and knowledge needed to succeed in school.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The key difference between a mentor and a tutor is that mentors offer more than just knowledge or technical assistance; they help their mentees develop skills that will help them succeed in their academic and life goals. Mentors also have more time to devote to their mentees than tutors do—tutors have a role solely in academic needs. They provide guidance and instruction to students when it comes down to studying for exams or completing assignments.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Guidance and skills. With that in mind, they can share industry knowledge you would not have access to otherwise. From the things they wish they had known to technical advice on any potential projects, mentors are there to help you reach your goals and succeed in the long run.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>See a different perspective</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Sometimes, it can be hard to know what\'s best for you. When you\'re faced with a decision, it can be tough to know whether or not you\'re making the right choice. What if you could ask someone else\'s opinion?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>That\'s where mentors come in. A mentor is someone who can offer advice from a different perspective with an understanding of your goals and current situation. Through several discussions with your mentor, you\'ll be guided to see things from the bigger picture.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Now you know the importance of joining mentoring programs for students. The benefits that a mentor-mentee relationship can provide for your academic, personal, and professional lives are ones you won\'t want to pass up.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” Guidebook to find out all the things you need to know before applying for scholarships. It\'s FREE, <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/\">download here</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>So, what are you waiting for? Get the initial consultation with our mentors <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/\">here!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\"><strong>Admission Mentoring</strong></a><strong>.</strong></li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\"><strong>Career Exploration.</strong></a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\"><strong>Academic Tutoring.</strong></a></li><li>Highlight your personal brand through the <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/writing-skills/\"><strong>Writing Skills</strong></a><strong> </strong>improvement program.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!</p>', 'Downloader.la-62ec933fe2369.jpg', 'Full Scoop and Facts on Mentoring Programs for Students', 'publish', 'Full Scoop and Facts on Mentoring Programs for Students', 'Mentoring Programs for Students', 'If you are looking for a way to maximise your preparation to top universities abroad, then mentoring programs for students is what you seek. Check all here!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-05-15 17:00:00', '2022-08-25 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(12157, 'mentoring-programs-these-are-all-reasons-why-you-need-it', 1, 0, 'Mentoring Programs: These are All Reasons Why You Need it!', '<p>When you first encounter the word “mentoring programs”, you might think that it is not important at all. However, you should know that many students actually need to have a great mentor to build a great foundation for their future. In this article, you will find all the facts you can get about mentoring programs and why you need one.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Mentoring Programs for Youth</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>What\'s the first thing that pops into your mind when you hear the word ‘mentoring\'? If you\'re still not sure about what mentors and mentoring are all about, don\'t worry! In this article, we\'ll learn more specifically about <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/looking-for-mentoring-programs-for-youth-here-it-is/\">mentoring programs for youth</a>, their purposes, and what you\'ll gain from them. Let\'s dive into it!</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>What is a mentoring program?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Mentoring programs for youth connect adults with expertise in a certain area to youths who are interested in that area and need guidance to pursue their interests</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As someone who has “been there, done that”, a mentor can share practical and helpful advice, offer guidance, and act as a sounding board for your thoughts. In a way, mentoring programs for youth help break down any barriers you have, such as not knowing what to pursue after high school or how to pursue it, to create opportunities for success.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Roles of Mentors</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Mentoring programs for youth connect teenagers to adults with expertise in a certain area who are able to provide guidance and encouragement throughout the mentee\'s years in school. These programs can range from limited guidance for school and academics only, to help with interest exploration and future career goals, to things like navigating friendships.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Instead of going through blind trial and error in your learning process, a mentor is someone who can help direct your learning to make it more effective. A mentor can be:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>a role model</li><li>a supporter&nbsp;</li><li>a coach&nbsp;</li><li>an advisor</li><li>a friend</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Take a look at more info about mentoring programs for youth in this article!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Mentoring Programs for Students&nbsp;</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Maybe you may have heard the word ‘mentoring\' before. Or perhaps you\'re still not sure what that is all about. In this article, we\'ll learn more about <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/full-scoop-and-facts-on-mentoring-programs-for-students/\">mentoring programs for students</a>. Read on to find out what you can gain from joining a mentoring program and why it might be right for you!</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>What is a mentor?&nbsp;</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>A mentor is someone who possesses the expertise in the skills that the mentee would like to develop. They can help guide you in your progression as a student. Aside from providing direct feedback, mentors can also serve as a sounding board for your ideas and problems.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Mentor-mentee relationships can take a variety of forms, depending on the mentor and mentee\'s needs. The relationship could be short-term or continue indefinitely, with regular meetings or casual check-ins.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In short, mentors provide guidance on how to achieve your goal, and they also help you identify your strengths and weaknesses.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Different forms of mentoring programs&nbsp;</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are looking for the most suitable mentoring programs for you, you can choose from all types of mentoring programs below. The 4 types of mentoring programs are:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Traditional mentoring</strong> involves when a mentor and a mentee are matched, either through a program or on their own.&nbsp;</li><li><strong>Group mentoring </strong>involves a mentor working with small groups of mentees.&nbsp;</li><li><strong>Team mentoring</strong> involves several mentors working together with a small group of mentees.&nbsp;</li><li><strong>E-mentoring </strong>is a form of one-on-one mentoring that happens virtually through the Internet, email, social media, or other forms of internet communication.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>If you really want to kickstart your future, you could get the guidance you need from a mentor near you.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Read here for more info about mentoring programs for students!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Mentoring from a University Application Consultant</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Everyone deserves guidance in their university application process. Numerous practical and emotional variables can influence whether a family decides to hire a college admissions adviser. Below you will find a lot of benefits that you can get from getting mentored by a university application consultant.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Relieve the College Application Stress</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>No rational parent wants to hover over their stressed-out children for months on end, nagging them about their essays and exam results. On the other hand, the idea of handling every aspect of the challenging application process alone makes the majority of high school students shudder. School counseling centers meant to assist students are frequently overworked and underfunded, which adds fuel to the flame.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With a university application consultant, you can expect streamlined, facilitated, and effective communication. The very best college admissions counselors start by carefully studying both the student and the family. They are quite explicit about how often and in what format they will communicate with each party. They have reliable mechanisms in place to make sure that any hiccups in the process are discovered quickly and dealt with cooperatively.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Develop an Admissions Strategy</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Have you heard that the acceptance rates to MIT and Harvard have gone up for the class of 2024? No high school student has the time to become an expert in admissions, but there are many stories and legends. You\'ve surely heard of the high school alumna who graduated sixth in her class but was accepted to MIT and Yale, or the youngster who attended Brown despite failing chemistry.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>University Admission Consultants can help you strategize your university shortlisting by choosing a balanced selection of schools. You might have heard of “safety”, “reach”, and “target” schools. But how many do you choose, and how do you choose ones that will fit you best, no matter the category? Along with thoroughly reviewing your application, an admissions consultant will start a dialogue with you about your true educational goals.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Crafting the Right Story in Each Application</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Creating a cohesive personal narrative has become more important as more universities abandon the standardized test and elite colleges lengthen and add additional essays. In many respects, knowing where you\'ve been and where you\'re going go hand in hand with creating a strategy.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With a university application consultant, you will have the opportunity to discuss and reflect on your profile and experiences and how best to represent them in an application. In order to show maturity and progress in the application, a college admissions consultant will guide you in finding out your motivations and goals. Your story should naturally crystallize over time by speaking openly about both the humorous and the serious topics. Whatever is on your mind, no matter how vague or embarrassing, you should feel free to discuss it with the university consultant. The better they know you, the better they\'re able to advise you.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Mentoring programs and university consultants have their own role in helping you with your education and university applications. In order to achieve your dream, you must not do it alone. There are many people that can help you get to pursue your future educational and professional goals. You just need to look and ask.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” Guidebook to find out all the things you need to know before applying for scholarships. It\'s FREE, <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/\">download here</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Interested to join mentoring programs? Click <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/\">here</a> to have your first consultation with the experts!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top uni preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'Downloader.la-62ec966eb84de.jpg', 'Mentoring Programs: These are All Reasons Why You Need it!', 'publish', 'Mentoring Programs: These are All Reasons Why You Need it!', 'Mentoring Programs', 'Have been deciding whether to join mentoring programs? In this article, you will learn all facts about it that can help you admitted in top universities!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-05-14 17:00:00', '2022-08-15 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(12161, 'ingin-tahu-jurusan-multimedia-kerja-apa-baca-di-sini', 2, 0, 'Ingin Tahu Jurusan Multimedia Kerja Apa? Baca di Sini!', '<p>Kamu tertarik untuk masuk ke <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/ingin-tahu-fakta-menarik-seputar-jurusan-multimedia-baca-di-sini/\">jurusan multimedia</a>, tapi bingung lulusan jurusan multimedia bisa kerja apa? Jangan khawatir! Kita bahas semuanya di sini. Jurusan Multimedia adalah salah satu jurusan yang sedang terkenal di kalangan anak muda saat ini. Hal ini juga dipengaruhi dengan berkembangnya dunia digital yang semakin hari semakin menjadi ketergantungan bagi setiap lini bisnis. Ayo simak di bawah ini beberapa career yang bisa kamu pilih sebagai lulusan jurusan multimedia!<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Web Designer</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Web Designer membuat dan membangun situs web dan halaman web dengan menggabungkan sejumlah elemen desain visual termasuk teks, foto, grafik, animasi, dan video. Seorang Web Designer dapat membuat situs web baru atau sekadar memperbarui desain dan tata letak halaman yang ada.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Web Designer tidak bertanggung jawab terutama untuk mengetahui cara kerja kode yang menopang desain mereka — tetapi alih-alih fokus mereka adalah menciptakan tampilan yang estetis dan pengguna memiliki pengalaman pengguna yang positif saat mereka mengunjungi situs web. Web Designer mungkin menggunakan bahasa pemrograman seperti HTML, CSS, dan JavaScript, akan menggunakan perangkat lunak desain grafis — termasuk produk seperti Adobe Photoshop, Illustrator, dan GIMP — untuk membantu menciptakan desain yang menarik, dan mereka akan menguji desain mereka melalui pembuatan prototipe dan gambar rangka.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Jurusan Multimedia Kerja Apa? <strong>Animator</strong>!</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Seorang animator menghasilkan beberapa gambar yang disebut <em>frame</em>, yang bila diurutkan dapat menciptakan ilusi gerakan, yang biasa juga dikenal sebagai animasi. Gambar dapat berupa gambar digital atau gambar tangan, model atau boneka.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Animator cenderung bekerja dalam 2D, pembuatan model 3D, stop-frame atau animasi yang dihasilkan komputer. Animasi yang dihasilkan komputer memiliki fitur yang kuat dalam film (untuk membuat efek khusus atau film animasi dengan sendirinya), serta dalam aspek televisi, internet, dan industri permainan komputer.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Keterampilan dasar animasi masih sangat bergantung pada kemampuan artistik, tetapi ada kebutuhan yang meningkat bagi animator untuk terbiasa dengan paket komputer teknis.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Jurusan Multimedia Kerja Apa?<strong>Illustrator</strong>!</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ilustrator adalah seorang seniman yang menciptakan gambar dua dimensi untuk berbagai perusahaan dan industri, seperti desain fashion, buku anak-anak, majalah, manual medis, situs web, desain teknis, dan periklanan.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ilustrasi dapat menyampaikan perasaan, makna, atau esensi terkadang lebih efektif daripada yang dapat dilakukan oleh dinding teks. Ilustrasi dapat menyederhanakan ide yang rumit, melengkapi kata atau pesan yang disampaikan kepada pengguna, dan terkadang berdiri sendiri tanpa penjelasan yang diperlukan.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Penting bagi ilustrator untuk mendengarkan dan memahami kebutuhan klien, dan dapat bertukar ide dan mengerjakan ulang berbagai konsep hingga kedua belah pihak mencapai interpretasi dan ilustrasi akhir. Bakat alami, pendidikan, dan latihan terus menerus diperlukan untuk menjadi sukses sebagai ilustrator.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ilustrasi telah menjadi karir yang sangat kompetitif. Hal ini berarti bahwa sebagian besar ilustrator mengembangkan estetika desain yang sangat berbeda sehingga karya mereka menonjol. Meskipun karya seorang ilustrator sangat kreatif, terkadang itu berarti bahwa mereka harus terus bekerja keras. Bahkan ketika mereka tidak merasa terinspirasi secara khusus.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Interactive Media Designer</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Media interaktif adalah setiap elektronik yang merespon perintah manusia dengan cara yang spesifik dan jelas. Media interaktif tidak hanya mencakup video game, tetapi juga merupakan prinsip yang mendasari aplikasi pada ponsel pintar karena mereka bereaksi terhadap sentuhan.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Periklanan modern telah mengimplementasikan<em> interactive media</em>. Kamu dapat mengunjungi berbagai situs web dan mengunggah fotomu sendiri untuk melihat seperti apa penampilan kamu dengan warna atau gaya rambut yang berbeda. Kamu juga akan menemukan situs web dengan media interaktif yang hebat. Media tersebut dirancang hanya untuk hiburan pribadi, seperti melihat penampilan kamu jika diubah menjadi <em>zombie</em>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ada banyak sekali pilihan karir yang bisa kamu pilih setelah kamu lulus dari jurusan multimedia. Jadi, kamu sudah tidak perlu ragu lagi untuk memilih jurusan ini sebagai jurusan pilihan kamu ya! Jika kamu punya mimpi untuk berkarir tinggi, kamu harus berusaha untuk masuk ke universitas top dunia!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download Panduan “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” untuk mencari tahu semua hal yang perlu kamu ketahui sebelum mendaftar beasiswa. GRATIS! <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/id/\">Download disini</a> </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ingin masuk ke jurusan multimedia terbaik di dunia? EDUVERSE by ALL-in akan memandu langkahmu masuk ke universitas impian!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!<br></p>', 'Downloader.la-62ec9edc58850.jpg', 'Ingin Tahu Jurusan Multimedia Kerja Apa? Baca di Sini!', 'publish', 'Ingin Tahu Jurusan Multimedia Kerja Apa? Baca di Sini!', 'Jurusan Multimedia Kerja Apa', 'Jurusan multimedia merupakan jurusan yang sedang ramai digemari pelajar di Indonesia. Ingin tahu jurusan multimedia kerja apa di masa depan? Baca di sini!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-05-02 17:00:00', '2022-08-12 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(12166, 'daftar-lengkap-universitas-jurusan-multimedia-terbaik-di-asia', 2, 0, 'Daftar Lengkap Universitas Jurusan Multimedia Terbaik di Asia', '<p><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/ingin-tahu-fakta-menarik-seputar-jurusan-multimedia-baca-di-sini/\">Jurusan multimedia</a> memang menarik bagi banyak orang terutama bagi milenial. Hal ini karena pengaplikasian ilmu yang didapat dari jurusan ini sangat banyak. Untuk mendapat ilmu yang terbaik, kamu perlu juga untuk menuntut ilmu di universitas terbaik. Berikut adalah beberapa universitas jurusan multimedia terbaik di Asia.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>National Central University (China)</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>NCU didirikan pada tahun 1915 di Nanking dan menduduki peringkat di antara universitas terbaik di Cina, seperti universitas Beijing dan universitas Chinghua, NCU didirikan kembali di Chungli, Taiwan pada tahun 1962. Sejak itu telah berkembang dari lembaga pascasarjana Geofisika ke status universitas penuh dengan 6 perguruan tinggi dan lebih dari tiga puluh departemen dan program pascasarjana.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Universitas Jurusan Multimedia; <strong>Tsinghua University (China)</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Tsinghua University adalah universitas terkenal di Beijing, China. Kampus ini didirikan pada tahun 1911 dan merupakan salah satu universitas tertua yang ada di China. Universitas memiliki 19 fakultas dan saat ini mempunyai 33,000 mahasiswa, dengan 2,600 diantaranya merupakan mahasiswa internasional. Tsinghua University merupakan bagian dari Liga C9, sebuah aliansi sembilan universitas hebat di China yang dibentuk oleh pemerintah. Jurusan Arsitektur di universitas ini berada di peringkat ke-10 di dunia.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>University of Tokyo (Jepang)</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Universitas Tokyo, juga dikenal sebagai UTokyo atau Todai, adalah universitas nasional Jepang yang didirikan pada tahun 1877. Kampus ini memiliki tiga kampus utama – kampus Hongo, Komaba dan Kashiwa – dan fasilitas tambahan yang terletak di bagian lain Jepang. Universitas ini punya beberapa mata akademik utama yaitu agrikultur, seni, ekonomi, pendidikan, teknik, hukum, sastra, kesehatan, dan farmasi. University of Tokyo memiliki tingkat penerimaan yang cukup tinggi yaitu sebesar 34%. Jurusan arsitekturnya berhasil menempati posisi ke-19 di dunia lho.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Universitas Jurusan Multimedia; <strong>Nanyang Technological University (Singapura</strong>)</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Sebagai salah satu universitas tertua di Singapura, Nanyang Technological University merupakan salah satu universitas terbaik di Asia yang unggul dalam berbagai bidang akademik. Bidang-bidang ini meliputi sains, teknik, humaniora, dan bisnis. Ini adalah salah satu universitas yang paling disukai siswa Indonesia. Dengan tingkat penerimaan hanya 26%, Universitas Teknologi Nanyang menerima lebih dari 33.000 mahasiswa sarjana dan pascasarjana. Meskipun menerima siswa dari seluruh dunia, badan siswa sebagian besar terdiri dari siswa dari Asia.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>National University of Singapore (Singapura</strong>)</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>NUS, universitas unggulan Singapura, memberikan siswa pendidikan yang ketat dari profesor terbaik di bidangnya, kesempatan untuk belajar di luar negeri di 300 universitas besar di 50 negara, dan pengalaman kerja hingga satu tahun dengan startup dan bisnis terbaik yang menarik. Universitas ini menawarkan magang di Singapura dan luar negeri. Selain itu, universitas ini juga dikenal di seluruh dunia karena mempelopori model pendidikan baru di NUS seperti NUS Overseas College, University Town, University Scholars Program, dan berhasil membangun lulusan Yong Siew Toh Conservatory Duke NUS melalui kemitraan strategis. Untuk peringkat di urutan dunia, jurusan arsitektur di NUS berada di posisi 8.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Memang ada banyak universitas yang menyediakan jurusan multimedia, tapi kamu kamu tentunya harus memilih yang terbaik bukan? Dari beberapa universitas di atas, apa ada yang membuatmu tertarik untuk bergabung dan menuntut ilmu di sana?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download Panduan “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” untuk mencari tahu semua hal yang perlu kamu ketahui sebelum mendaftar beasiswa. GRATIS! <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/id/\">Download disini</a> </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ayo persiapkan dirimu masuk ke universitas terbaik bersama Eduverse by ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!<br></p>', 'Downloader.la-62eca5bbd82f9.jpg', 'Daftar Lengkap Universitas Jurusan Multimedia Terbaik di Asia', 'publish', 'Daftar Lengkap Universitas Jurusan Multimedia Terbaik di Asia', 'Universitas Jurusan Multimedia', 'Apa kamu ingin masuk ke universitas jurusan multimedia terbaik di Asia? Ayo lihat semua daftar lengkapnya di artikel ini ya!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-05-01 17:00:00', '2022-08-02 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(12170, 'ingin-tahu-fakta-menarik-seputar-jurusan-multimedia-baca-di-sini', 2, 0, 'Ingin Tahu Fakta Menarik seputar Jurusan Multimedia? Baca di Sini!', '<p>Jurusan multimedia sudah menjadi primadona untuk banyak pelajar di Indonesia. Hal ini ada karena semakin berkembangnya media digital di Indonesia yang terus menginspirasi banyak anak muda di luar sana. Ingin tahu lebih dalam mengenai jurusan ini? Simak di bawah ya!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Apa itu Jurusan Multimedia?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan Multimedia adalah ilmu komprehensif yang mencakup kursus dalam studi film, studi televisi, jurnalisme, produksi video, animasi komputer, dan studi dan praktik di multimedia, media interaktif, dan teknologi baru. Di sini, kamu akan terlibat dengan menganalisis kekuatan dan tanggung jawab media yang ada dan yang muncul dari perspektif formal, historis, ekonomi, dan ideologis.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kursus studi menekankan tidak hanya makna teks media tetapi juga proses di mana makna ini dibangun dan disebarluaskan. Tujuannya adalah untuk membantu sarjana memahami studi dan penciptaan media visual, cetak dan baru dalam konteks yang lebih besar dari ekspresi visual dan verbal manusia, dan untuk membentuk siswa menjadi pembaca yang canggih dan produsen budaya visual.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Universitas Jurusan Multimedia Terbaik di Asia</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Kalau kamu sudah menetapkan hatimu di jurusan multimedia, kamu perlu masuk ke salah satu <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/daftar-lengkap-universitas-jurusan-multimedia-terbaik-di-asia/\">universitas jurusan multimedia</a> terbaik di dunia. Berikut adalah daftar yang terbaik di Asia:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>National Central University</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>NCU didirikan pada tahun 1915 di Nanking dan menduduki peringkat di antara universitas terbaik di Cina, seperti universitas Beijing dan universitas Chinghua, NCU didirikan kembali di Chungli, Taiwan pada tahun 1962. Sejak itu telah berkembang dari lembaga pascasarjana Geofisika ke status universitas penuh dengan enam perguruan tinggi dan lebih dari tiga puluh departemen dan program pascasarjana.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Tsinghua University</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Tsinghua University adalah universitas terkenal di Beijing, China. Kampus ini didirikan pada tahun 1911 dan merupakan salah satu universitas tertua yang ada di China. Universitas memiliki 19 fakultas dan saat ini mempunyai 33,000 mahasiswa, dengan 2,600 diantaranya merupakan mahasiswa internasional. Tsinghua University merupakan bagian dari Liga C9, sebuah aliansi sembilan universitas hebat di China yang dibentuk oleh pemerintah. Jurusan Arsitektur di universitas ini berada di peringkat ke-10 di dunia.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>University of Tokyo</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Universitas Tokyo, juga dikenal sebagai UTokyo atau Todai, adalah universitas nasional Jepang yang didirikan pada tahun 1877. Kampus ini memiliki tiga kampus utama – kampus Hongo, Komaba dan Kashiwa – dan fasilitas tambahan yang terletak di bagian lain Jepang. Universitas ini punya beberapa mata akademik utama yaitu agrikultur, seni, ekonomi, pendidikan, teknik, hukum, sastra, kesehatan, dan farmasi. University of Tokyo memiliki tingkat penerimaan yang cukup tinggi yaitu sebesar 34%. Jurusan arsitekturnya berhasil menempati posisi ke-19 di dunia lho.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Jurusan Multimedia Bisa Kerja Apa?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Kamu tertarik untuk masuk ke jurusan multimedia, tapi bingung lulusan <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/ingin-tahu-jurusan-multimedia-kerja-apa-baca-di-sini/\">jurusan multimedia bisa kerja apa</a>? Ayo simak di bawah ini beberapa karir yang bisa kamu pilih sebagai lulusan jurusan multimedia!</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Web Designer</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Web Designer membuat dan membangun situs web dan halaman web dengan menggabungkan sejumlah elemen desain visual termasuk teks, foto, grafik, animasi, dan video. Seorang Web Designer dapat membuat situs web baru atau sekadar memperbarui desain dan tata letak halaman yang ada.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Web Designer tidak bertanggung jawab terutama untuk mengetahui cara kerja kode yang menopang desain mereka — tetapi alih-alih fokus mereka adalah menciptakan tampilan yang estetis dan pengguna memiliki pengalaman pengguna yang positif saat mereka mengunjungi situs web. Web Designer mungkin menggunakan bahasa pemrograman seperti HTML, CSS, dan JavaScript, akan menggunakan perangkat lunak desain grafis — termasuk produk seperti Adobe Photoshop, Illustrator, dan GIMP — untuk membantu menciptakan desain yang menarik, dan mereka akan menguji desain mereka melalui pembuatan prototipe dan gambar rangka.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Animator</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Seorang animator menghasilkan beberapa gambar yang disebut <em>frame</em>, yang bila diurutkan dapat menciptakan ilusi gerakan, yang biasa juga dikenal sebagai animasi. Gambar dapat berupa gambar digital atau gambar tangan, model atau boneka.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Animator cenderung bekerja dalam 2D, pembuatan model 3D,<em> stop-frame </em>atau animasi yang dihasilkan komputer. Animasi yang dihasilkan komputer memiliki fitur yang kuat dalam film (untuk membuat efek khusus atau film animasi dengan sendirinya), serta dalam aspek televisi, internet, dan industri permainan komputer. Keterampilan dasar animasi masih sangat bergantung pada kemampuan artistik, tetapi ada kebutuhan yang meningkat bagi animator untuk terbiasa dengan paket komputer teknis.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Berikut di atas adalah beberapa hal yang perlu kamu tahu mengenai jurusan multimedia. Jika kamu memang tertarik ingin masuk ke jurusan ini, tentunya kamu memerlukan banyak persiapan yang menyeluruh. Apalagi jika kamu memang mengincar ke salah satu universitas terbaik di dunia.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download Panduan “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” untuk mencari tahu semua hal yang perlu kamu ketahui sebelum mendaftar beasiswa. GRATIS!&nbsp;<a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/id/\">Download disini</a> </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!<br></p>', 'Downloader.la-62ecb888a0768.jpg', 'Ingin Tahu Fakta Menarik seputar Jurusan Multimedia? Baca di Sini!', 'publish', 'Ingin Tahu Fakta Menarik seputar Jurusan Multimedia? Baca di Sini!', 'Jurusan Multimedia', 'Apa kamu seseorang yang sangat tertarik untuk menyelam di jurusan multimedia? Simak informasi lengkap seputar jurusannya di sini!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-04-30 17:00:00', '2022-08-15 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(12233, 'edinburgh-university-acceptance-rate-heres-what-you-should-know', 1, 0, 'Edinburgh University Acceptance Rate: Here’s What You Should Know', '<p>Is studying in the UK one of your dreams? That means the University of Edinburgh needs to be at the top of your list! Having been consistently ranked as one of the world\'s top universities, how hard is it to get into the university? Let\'s check out the <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/edinburgh-university-all-you-need-to-know-before-applying/\">Edinburgh University</a> acceptance rate!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>A glance at Edinburgh University</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Established in 1582, the University of Edinburgh has grown into the eighth-largest university in the UK by enrollment, with more than 36,000 students.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The University of Edinburgh\'s campus is located in Scotland\'s capital city, which offers students a vibrant and diverse community with plenty to do outside of class. Moreover, the University of Edinburgh is made up of three colleges that comprise 21 schools and departments.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Rankings of Edinburgh University</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td>QS World University Rankings</td><td>15th&nbsp;<br><br></td></tr><tr><td>Times Higher Education World University Rankings&nbsp;</td><td>30th&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td>US News&nbsp;</td><td>32nd in Best Global Universities<br>6th in Best Universities in Europe&nbsp;<br>5th in Best Universities in the United Kingdom&nbsp;</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Edinburgh University Acceptance Rate</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The Edinburgh University acceptance rate is thought to be between 40 and 50 percent, making it a moderately selective university.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here\'s a glance of the undergraduate admission statistics of the University of Edinburgh from 2017 to 2021:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td>Cycle</td><td>Applications&nbsp;</td><td>Offers</td><td>Offer rate	</td></tr><tr><td>2017</td><td>59,876</td><td>25,041</td><td>42%	</td></tr><tr><td>2018</td><td>58,411</td><td>25,532</td><td>44%	</td></tr><tr><td>2019</td><td>60,983</td><td>27,878</td><td>46%	</td></tr><tr><td>2020</td><td>62,220</td><td>31,510</td><td>51%	</td></tr><tr><td>2021&nbsp;</td><td>68,954</td><td>32,432</td><td>47%	</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>However, you should be aware that the Edinburgh university acceptance rate may vary based on how competitive the admissions cycle is. Here are a few highly competitive programs at the University of Edinburgh:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td>BA Film and Television</td><td>7.7%</td></tr><tr><td>BA Graphic Design</td><td>10%</td></tr><tr><td>BSc Oral Health Sciences</td><td>12%</td></tr><tr><td>BA Animation</td><td>12%</td></tr><tr><td>BA Interior Design</td><td>14%</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Minimum English Score Required to Get into Edinburgh University</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>At the University of Edinburgh, the English language requirements vary between degrees. You need to have a passing grade in your English Proficiency test at the following levels or higher unless a higher level is mentioned in the stated entry requirements:<br></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td><strong>Tests</strong></td><td><strong>Minimum Score Required</strong></td></tr><tr><td>International Baccalaureate Diploma</td><td>Grade 5 in IB Standard Level&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td>GCSE / IGCSE</td><td>Grade C or 4&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td>IELTS</td><td>The minimum score required for IELTS varies between degrees. Here\'s an example:<br>BSc Biomedical Sciences - overall 6.5, no bands less than 6.0<br>BSc Computer Science - overall 6.5, no bands less than 5.5<br><br><br></td></tr><tr><td>TOEFL&nbsp;</td><td>The minimum score required for TOEFL varies between degrees. Here\'s an example:<br>BSc Applied Mathematics - overall 92 with at least 20 in each component<br>MBChB Medicine - overall 110 with at least 25 in each component</td></tr><tr><td>Pearson Test of English (PTE)&nbsp;</td><td>The minimum score required for PTE varies between degrees. Here\'s an example:<br>BSc Biological Sciences - overall 62 with at least 54 in each component<br>MBChB Medicine - overall 76 with at least 76 in each component</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Conclusion</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>With an average of 47 percent acceptance rate, Edinburgh University is one of the most selective universities in the UK. But that doesn\'t mean you should shy away. Just make sure you get yourself geared up for the application process by visiting their website for a full guide on how to get in. So go ahead—make your dream come true!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To have a better overview of the University of Edinburgh\'s admissions, check out <a href=\"https://www.ed.ac.uk/studying/admissions\">here</a>!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Planning to study at the University of Edinburgh? Let\'s gear yourself up with ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” Guidebook to find out all the things you need to know before applying for scholarships. It\'s FREE, <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/\">download here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top uni preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'Downloader.la-62f499801a873.jpg', 'Edinburgh University Acceptance Rate: Here’s What You Should Know', 'publish', 'Edinburgh University Acceptance Rate: Here’s What You Should Know', 'Edinburgh University Acceptance Rate', 'One thing that makes college admissions difficult is that it poses a challenge to people. Read all facts behind Edinburgh University acceptance rate now!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-05-19 17:00:00', '2022-08-01 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(12237, 'edinburgh-university-scholarships-find-out-here', 1, 0, 'Edinburgh University Scholarships: Find Out Here!', '<p>The University of Edinburgh is a public research university in Edinburgh, Scotland. Furthermore, this university has a history stretching over 400 years, making the University of Edinburgh has grown into one of the most reputable universities in the world. Also, a member of several associations of research-intensive universities, including the League of European Research Universities, Russell Group, and Universitas 21. Are you interested to find out about <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/edinburgh-university-all-you-need-to-know-before-applying/\">Edinburgh University</a> scholarships for your study? Read all below!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Edinburgh University Scholarship:&nbsp;Edinburgh Global Undergraduate Mathematics Scholarships</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The first Edinburgh University scholarship we\'ll talk about is the Edinburgh Global Undergraduate Mathematics Scholarship, which is a competitive scholarship for outstanding Mathematics students. Moreover, this merit-based scholarship, which is offered by the School of Mathematics at the University of Edinburgh, can be applied for through the University and Colleges Admissions Service (UCAS) portal.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To be eligible for the Edinburgh Global Undergraduate Mathematics Scholarships, you must meet the following requirements:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Be a citizen of a country outside of the UK and Ireland&nbsp;</li><li>Possess an offer for full-time admission to an undergraduate degree program offered by the School of Mathematics at the University of Edinburgh</li><li>Not available to students that are already in the program</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>What the Edinburgh Global Undergraduate Mathematics Scholarships cover:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>£5,000 per year (renewable for the duration of the study if satisfactory academic performance is met)</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Robertson International Scholarships</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Another Edinburgh University scholarship is the Robertson International Scholarships, a merit-based scholarship offered by the School of History, Classics, and Archaeology at the University of Edinburgh. This scholarship, which is for up to 5 students who plan to enroll in an undergraduate program within the School of History, Classics, and Archaeology, can also be applied for through the University and Colleges Admission Service (UCAS) portal.&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>To be eligible for the Robertson International Scholarships, you must meet the following requirements:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Be a national of a country outside the UK&nbsp;</li><li>Liable for the international tuition rate</li><li>Not available to students that are already in the program</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>What the Robertson International Scholarships cover:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>£1,000 (tenable for one year)</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Edinburgh University scholarship:&nbsp;Chevening Scholarships</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>You can also study at the University of Edinburgh through the Chevening scholarship. Moreover, it is a full master\'s degree scholarship by the British Foreign and Commonwealth Office and partner organizations. Furthermore, this scholarship is famous as the UK government\'s international scholarship program, which is a grant for scholars who exhibit leadership skills.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To be eligible for the Chevening Scholarships, you must meet the following requirements:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Citizen of a Chevening-eligible country or territory</li><li>Return to your country of origin for at least two years after receiving the award</li><li>Completion of your undergraduate program to apply for the postgraduate program in the UK university</li><li>Two years or more of work experience</li><li>Application to three different eligible UK university courses, with one of your selections having unconditionally accepted your application</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>What the Chevening Scholarships cover:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Tuition fees</li><li>A monthly stipend</li><li>Costs of travel to and from the UK</li><li>An arrival allowance</li><li>A homeward departure allowance</li><li>Visa application&nbsp;</li><li>A travel grant to attend Chevening events in the UK</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Scholarships for international students can be a great way to cut the cost of your education. Some scholarships are only for students who receive an offer to study at the University, while others are open to students in undergraduate or graduate programs. However, there are a lot of scholarships available in general, and it can be tough trying to find the right one for you.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” Guidebook to find out all the things you need to know before applying for scholarships. It\'s FREE, <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/\">download here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Aiming to land one of the scholarships offered by the University of Edinburgh? Prepare yourself with ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top uni preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!</p>', 'Downloader.la-62f4aa87daac4.jpg', 'Edinburgh University Scholarships: Find Out Here!', 'publish', 'Edinburgh University Scholarships: Find Out Here!', 'Edinburgh University Scholarships', 'Are you looking for Edinburgh University scholarships to support your study there? Read this article to find out the full list!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-05-18 17:00:00', '2022-08-03 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00');
