(12243, 'edinburgh-university-all-you-need-to-know-before-applying', 1, 0, 'Edinburgh University: All You Need to Know Before Applying!', '<p>Studying at Edinburgh University is such a feat and achievement for many international students. Therefore, if you are aspiring to be one of its future students, you must research and prepare everything before you apply. Take a look at the complete facts and info about Edinburgh University.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Edinburgh University</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The University of Edinburgh is a public research university in Edinburgh, Scotland. Moreover, it is one of Scotland\'s four oldest universities and the sixth-oldest university in continuous operation in the English-speaking world. In addition, King James VI granted it a royal charter in 1582 and it was formally opened in 1583. The institution significantly influenced Edinburgh\'s development as a leading intellectual hub during the Scottish Enlightenment, helping to earn the city the moniker \"Athens of the North.\"</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Coimbra Group, League of European Research Universities, Russell Group, Una Europa, and Universitas 21 are just a few organizations that Edinburgh is a part of. Furthermore, it has the third-largest endowment in the UK, behind Cambridge and Oxford, with a total income of £1,175.6 million for the fiscal year that ended on July 31, 2021, of which £324.0 million came from research grants and contracts. Also, Edinburgh is home to the university\'s five main campuses, several of which feature important historical and architectural structures like those in the Old Town.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Edinburgh University Insider Insight</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If studying in the UK is one of your dreams, then this campus is one of the best decisions for your target university. Not only with high-quality education, but this university is famous globally as one of the top universities in Europe.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Rankings of Edinburgh University</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td>QS World University Rankings</td><td>15th</td></tr><tr><td>Times Higher Education World University Rankings&nbsp;</td><td>30th</td></tr><tr><td>US News&nbsp;</td><td>32nd in Best Global Universities6th in Best Universities in Europe&nbsp;5th in Best Universities in the United Kingdom&nbsp;</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>Edinburgh University Acceptance Rate</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The acceptance rate is thought to be between 40 and 50 percent, making it a moderately selective university.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here\'s a glance at the undergraduate admission statistics of the University of Edinburgh from 2017 to 2021:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td>Cycle</td><td>Applications&nbsp;</td><td>Offers</td><td>Offer rate	</td></tr><tr><td>2017</td><td>59,876</td><td>25,041</td><td>42%	</td></tr><tr><td>2018</td><td>58,411</td><td>25,532</td><td>44%	</td></tr><tr><td>2019</td><td>60,983</td><td>27,878</td><td>46%	</td></tr><tr><td>2020</td><td>62,220</td><td>31,510</td><td>51%	</td></tr><tr><td>2021&nbsp;</td><td>68,954</td><td>32,432</td><td>47%	</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>However, you should be aware that the <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/edinburgh-university-acceptance-rate-heres-what-you-should-know/\">Edinburgh university acceptance rate</a> may vary based on how competitive the admissions cycle is. Here are a few highly competitive programs at the University of Edinburgh:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td>BA Film and Television</td><td>7.7%</td></tr><tr><td>BA Graphic Design</td><td>10%</td></tr><tr><td>BSc Oral Health Sciences</td><td>12%</td></tr><tr><td>BA Animation</td><td>12%</td></tr><tr><td>BA Interior Design</td><td>14%</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Want more info about the acceptance rate? Read all here!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/edinburgh-university-scholarships-find-out-here/\">Edinburgh University Scholarships</a></strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The University of Edinburgh is a public research university in Edinburgh, Scotland. Furthermore, with a history stretching over 400 years, the University of Edinburgh has grown into one of the most reputable universities in the world. In addition, a member of several associations of research-intensive universities, including the League of European Research Universities, Russell Group, and Universitas 21, the University of Edinburgh offers undergraduate and postgraduate courses across multiple disciplines that attract over 45,000 students annually.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Edinburgh Global Undergraduate Mathematics Scholarships</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The first scholarship we\'ll talk about is the Edinburgh Global Undergraduate Mathematics Scholarship, which is a competitive scholarship for outstanding Mathematics students. Moreover, this merit-based scholarship, which is offered by the School of Mathematics at the University, can be applied through the University and Colleges Admissions Service (UCAS).&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To be eligible for the Edinburgh Global Undergraduate Mathematics Scholarships, you must meet the following requirements:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Possess an International/EU fee status with an offer for full-time admission to an undergraduate degree program offered by the School of Mathematics at the University.</li><li>Not available to students that are already in the program.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>What the Edinburgh Global Undergraduate Mathematics Scholarships cover:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>£5,000 per year (renewable for the duration of the study if satisfactory academic performance is met)</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h3>Robertson International Scholarships</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Another scholarship is the Robertson International Scholarships, a merit-based scholarship offered by the School of History, Classics, and Archaeology at the University of Edinburgh. This scholarship, which is offered to up to 5 students who plan to enroll in an undergraduate program within the School of History, Classics, and Archaeology, can also be applied through the University and Colleges Admission Service (UCAS).&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>To be eligible for the Robertson International Scholarships, you must meet the following requirements:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Be a national of a country outside the UK&nbsp;</li><li>Liable for the international tuition rate</li><li>Not available to students that are already in the program</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>What the Robertson International Scholarships cover:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>£1,000 (tenable for one year)</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color has-vivid-cyan-blue-color\"><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/edinburgh-university-scholarships-find-out-here/\">Curious about other scholarships? Get the complete list here!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>What do you think? Here is all the information you need to know before applying to Edinburgh University. But to have a good chance of getting into a top university like Edinburgh, you need a lot more information on what and how to prepare for your applications. Therefore, having someone to mentor you throughout the process will increase your admission chances to top universities, including this one.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” Guidebook to find out all the things you need to know before applying for scholarships. It\'s FREE, <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/\">download here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>ALL-in can help you to prepare your applications to top universities around the globe!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top uni preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'Downloader.la-62f4ad6f357c5.jpg', 'Edinburgh University: All You Need to Know Before Applying!', 'publish', 'Edinburgh University: All You Need to Know Before Applying!', 'Edinburgh University', 'Want to put Edinburgh University as your target university for future academic journey? Find the complete info and facts in this article.', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-05-17 17:00:00', '2022-08-18 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(12248, 'mengenal-luar-dalam-mengenai-jurusan-ekonomi-pembangunan', 2, 0, 'Mengenal Luar Dalam Mengenai Jurusan Ekonomi Pembangunan', '<p>Akhir-akhir ini, <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/jurusan-ekonomi-macam-macam-penjurusan-ini-yang-perlu-kamu-tahu/\">jurusan ekonomi</a> pembangunan menjadi sangat diminati oleh banyak pelajar di seluruh Indonesia. Hal ini karena status Indonesia sebagai negara berkembang yang menyediakan banyak prospek untuk jurusan yang satu ini. Ayo baca di bawah ini untuk mengetahui beberapa informasi dan fakta menarik seputar jurusan ekonomi pembangunan!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Apa itu Jurusan Ekonomi Pembangunan?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan Ekonomi Pembangunan adalah salah satu cabang ilmu Ekonomi yang secara khusus mengkaji dan mempelajari berbagai macam persoalan-persoalan seputar pembangunan baik itu ada di sektor bisnis, keuangan, ataupun perbankan. Jika kamu berminat untuk berkuliah di jurusan ini, kamu akan banyak mempelajari berbagai teori dan menganalisa berbagai macam isu perekonomian yang ada untuk mencari dan menemukan solusi yang dibutuhkan dari berbagai persoalan ekonomi dengan kritis, kreatif, dan inovatif.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Selain ilmu ekonomi, menjadi mahasiswa jurusan ekonomi pembangunan dapat memberikan berbagai macam soft skill yang akan kamu butuhkan di dunia kerja nantinya. Soft skill tersebut adalah Kemampuan analisis, komunikasi, logika dan matematika dasar, deskripsi, berpikir logis dan terstruktur.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Kenapa Memilih Jurusan Ini?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ekonomi Pembangunan bisa jadi salah satu program studi yang paling tepat untuk kamu. Terutama jika kamu punya ketertarikan untuk mempelajari berbagai macam ilmu ekonomi. Dengan memilih jurusan ini, kamu akan punya peluang untuk berperan serta dalam mewujudkan segala macam pembangunan negara di masa depan. Terlebih lagi, jika kamu merupakan tipe pelajar yang menyukai pelajaran berhitung, kamu akan sangat cocok di prodi ini. Hal ini karena di prodi ini, kamu akan menemukan banyak pelajaran berhitung, dan menganalisa angka-angka dan menerjemahkannya dalam kurva dan data statistik lainnya.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dengan belajar di jurusan ini, kamu akan mendapatkan banyak modal keahlian yang dimiliki lulusan ekonomi pembangunan. Salah satunya adalah adalah menjalankan tugas pada pengkajian strategis di suatu perusahaan. Di sisi lain, kamu juga akan mampu menganalisa berbagai isu ekonomi yang akan dipakai untuk mencari dan menemukan segala jenis solusi dari berbagai persoalan ekonomi. Selain itu, lulusan ekonomi pembangunan juga dapat bekerja di berbagai sektor dari institusi pemerintahan sampai institusi swasta.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Universitas terbaik untuk Jurusan Ekonomi Pembangunan</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ada ratusan sekolah di dunia ini yang menyediakan program ekonomi pembangunan. Tempat kamu belajar dan menimba ilmu itu sangat berpengaruh untuk masa depan karirmu lho. Hal ini karena kamu akan menginvestasikan waktu dan uangmu untuk belajar dan mendalami ilmu ini. Jika kamu memulai karir di perusahaan multinasional, kamu harus masuk ke universitas terbaik di dunia. Beberapa perusahaan multinasional hanya mengincar lulusan terbaik dari universitas terbaik lho. Berikut adalah daftar universitas terbaik di Australia untuk kuliah ilmu ekonomi pembangunan menurut USNews.com :</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>University of Sydney</li><li>University of New South Wales</li><li>Monash University </li><li>University of Melbourne</li><li>University of Queensland Australia</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Prospek Kerja Jurusan Ekonomi Pembangunan</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ketika ingin memulai karir dalam dunia ekonomi pembangunan, gelar sarjana biasanya diperlukan. Beberapa perguruan tinggi menawarkan gelar di jurusan ini. Ketika lulus, kamu bisa dengan mudah bergabung dengan perusahaan atau institusi di bidang keuangan. Tentunya kamu akan memulai karirnya dari bawah. Tingkat paling bawah yang bisa kamu mulai masuk adalah menjadi seorang analis atau aktuaris.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sesuai namanya, fokus manajemen ini terletak pada seputar keuangan. Berikut adalah daftar beberapa karir yang bisa kamu pilih jika kamu memutuskan mendalami ilmu ini.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Staf Pengembangan dan Penelitian</li><li>Business Analyst</li><li>Credit Analyst</li><li>Aktuaris</li><li>Pegawai Instansi Pemerintahan</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Bagaimana? Apa kamu makin tertarik untuk mendaftarkan diri sebagai mahasiswa jurusan ekonomi pembangunan? Dengan ilmu yang sangat relevan ini, kamu bisa memulai karir di berbagai macam sektor atau perusahaan yang ada di dunia ini. Jika kamu punya cita-cita ingin bersaing di tingkat global, kamu juga perlu mendapatkan kualitas pendidikan terbaik dari universitas terbaik.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download Panduan “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” untuk mencari tahu semua hal yang perlu kamu ketahui sebelum mendaftar beasiswa. GRATIS! <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/id/\">Download disini</a> </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ingin masuk ke jurusan ekonomi pembangunan terbaik di dunia? EDUVERSE by ALL-in akan membimbingmu masuk ke universitas terbaik di dunia!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!<br></p>', 'Downloader.la-62f4af9437dfa.jpg', 'Mengenal Luar Dalam Mengenai Jurusan Ekonomi Pembangunan', 'publish', 'Mengenal Luar Dalam Mengenai Jurusan Ekonomi Pembangunan', 'Jurusan Ekonomi Pembangunan', 'Apa kamu punya ketertarikan untuk melanjutkan studi di jurusan ekonomi pembangunan? Cari tahu seluk-beluk mengenai jurusannya di artikel ini!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-05-05 17:00:00', '2022-08-23 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(12255, 'tertarik-masuk-jurusan-ekonomi-bisnis-baca-artikel-ini', 2, 0, 'Tertarik Masuk Jurusan Ekonomi Bisnis? Baca Artikel Ini!', '<p><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/jurusan-ekonomi-macam-macam-penjurusan-ini-yang-perlu-kamu-tahu/\">Jurusan ekonomi</a> bisnis merupakan salah satu jurusan yang selalu banyak peminatnya. Hal ini karena bidang keuangan dan entrepreneurship banyak pengaplikasiannya di dunia nyata. Selain itu, ada banyak kemampuan yang bisa kamu dapatkan selain ilmu-ilmu dan teori-teori bisnis. Penasaran dengan jurusan ini? Ayo baca lebih lengkapnya di bawah ini!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Apa itu Ekonomi Bisnis?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Pada jurusan Ekonomi Bisnis kamu akan mempelajari berbagai macam cara merancang strategi bisnis dan cara mengambil keputusan bisnis yang ideal. Di sini kamu juga akan mempelajari banyak sekali ilmu dan teori-teori ekonomi yang nantinya akan kamu terapkan dalam berbagai macam praktik bisnis. Ilmu yang ada di jurusan ini cukup berbeda dengan jurusan Ekonomi Pembangunan dan Manajemen Bisnis yang memang mempelajari teori dan ilmu ekonomi untuk kebutuhan pembangunan, kebijakan publik, dan pengelolaan serta perencanaan bisnis.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan Ekonomi Bisnis menggabungkan banyak teori ekonomi dan pendekatan kuantitatif untuk menganalisa dan mengeksekusi proses pengambilan keputusan bisnis yang strategis. Jurusan ini menggunakan Bahasa Inggris sebagai bahasa pengajar. Hal ini bertujuan agar kamu nantinya mempunyai skill komunikasi dan presentasi yang baik yang bisa kamu gunakan untuk berkecimpung di lingkup bisnis global. Belajar Ekonomi Bisnis pastinya merupakan sesuatu yang sangat seru karena sebagai mahasiswa kamu akan berperan aktif dalam&nbsp; pembelajaran studi kasus dari organisasi, perusahaan, struktur keuangan, simulasi bisnis, serta kunjungan perusahaan.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Kenapa Memilih Jurusan Ini?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ekonomi Bisnis bisa jadi salah satu program studi yang paling tepat untuk kamu. Terutama jika kamu punya ketertarikan untuk membuka dan menjalankan bisnismu sendiri. Dengan memilih jurusan ini, kamu akan punya peluang untuk memulai bisnis atau bergabung dengan tim business development di sebuah organisasi atau instansi. Terlebih lagi, jika kamu merupakan tipe pelajar yang menyukai pelajaran berhitung, kamu akan sangat cocok di prodi ini. Hal ini karena di prodi ini, kamu akan menemukan banyak pelajaran berhitung, dan menganalisa angka-angka dan menerjemahkannya dalam kurva dan data statistik lainnya.Berbagai macam pengetahuan pengetahuan yang kamu peroleh dari jurusan ini akan sangat menguntungkan karena secara langsung dapat diaplikasikan dalam proses pengambilan keputusan bisnis.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Universitas terbaik untuk Jurusan Ekonomi Bisnis</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ada ratusan sekolah di dunia ini yang menyediakan program jurusan ekonomi bisnis.&nbsp; Universitas penyedia program yang kamu pilih sangat berpengaruh. Hal ini karena kamu akan menginvestasikan waktu dan uangmu untuk belajar dan mendalami ilmu ini. Jika kamu ingin memulai karir di pasar internasional, kamu harus masuk ke universitas terbaik di dunia dan juga mendapatkan pendidikan dengan kualitas terbaik. Berikut adalah daftar universitas terbaik di Asia untuk kuliah ilmu ekonomi bisnis menurut Financial Times:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>INSEAD</li><li>CEIBS (China Europe International Business School)</li><li>National University of Singapore Business School</li><li>HKUST Business School</li><li>Indian School of Business</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Prospek Kerja Jurusan Ekonomi Bisnis</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ketika ingin memulai karir dalam dunia ekonomi bisnis, gelar sarjana biasanya diperlukan. Beberapa perguruan tinggi menawarkan gelar di jurusan ekonomi Bisnis. Ketika lulus, kamu bisa dengan mudah bergabung dengan perusahaan atau institusi di bidang keuangan. Tentunya kamu akan memulai karirnya dari bawah. Tingkat paling bawah yang bisa kamu mulai masuk adalah menjadi seorang analis atau aktuaris.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sesuai namanya, fokus manajemen ini terletak pada seputar keuangan. Berikut adalah daftar beberapa karir yang bisa kamu pilih jika kamu memutuskan mendalami ilmu ini.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Business Management Analyst</li><li>Business Consultant</li><li>Financial Analyst </li><li>Business Development Staff</li><li>Business Owner</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Banyak sekali bukan informasi yang wajib kamu tahu sebelum masuk ke jurusan ekonomi bisnis? Selain memilih universitas yang bagus kamu juga perlu memperhitungkan karir apa yang kamu mau di masa depan nanti. Untuk bisa bersaing dengan global, kemampuan bahasa inggris saja tidak cukup, kamu juga harus mendapatkan pendidikan berkualitas terbaik dari universitas terbaik.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download Panduan “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” untuk mencari tahu semua hal yang perlu kamu ketahui sebelum mendaftar beasiswa. GRATIS! <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/id/\">Download disini</a> </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Punya mimpi melanjutkan studi di jurusan ekonomi bisnis terbaik di dunia? EDUVERSE by ALL-in akan membimbing semua persiapanmu!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!</p>', 'Downloader.la-62f4b0e4c83e0.jpg', 'Tertarik Masuk Jurusan Ekonomi Bisnis? Baca Artikel Ini!', 'publish', 'Tertarik Masuk Jurusan Ekonomi Bisnis? Baca Artikel Ini!', 'Jurusan ekonomi Bisnis', 'Jurusan ekonomi bisnis tengah masuk sebagai salah satu jurusan terpopuler untuk para pelajar di Indonesia. Apa kamu tertarik? Simak info lengkapnya di sin!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-05-04 17:00:00', '2022-08-08 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(12265, 'jurusan-ekonomi-macam-macam-penjurusan-ini-yang-perlu-kamu-tahu', 2, 0, 'Jurusan Ekonomi: Macam-Macam Penjurusan Ini Yang Perlu Kamu Tahu!', '<p>Jurusan ekonomi mempunyai beberapa fokus pembelajaran lho. Jadi, kamu tidak hanya berkutat di ilmu ekonomi secara keseluruhan tetapi juga mendalami salah satu yang menarik perhatianmu. Penasaran apa aja penjurusan yang bisa kamu pilih di ilmu ekonomi? Ayo baca di bawah ini!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Apa Itu Ilmu Ekonomi?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ekonomi adalah studi yang berkutat dan meneliti penggunaan sumber daya, produksi barang dan jasa, pertumbuhan produksi dan kesejahteraan dari waktu ke waktu. Tidak hanya itu, ilmu ini juga membahas berbagai macam masalah kompleks lainnya yang menjadi perhatian vital masyarakat.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Business Economics Major</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Business economics major atau jurusan ekonomi bisnis, mempelajari berbagai macam cara merancang strategi bisnis dan cara mengambil keputusan bisnis yang ideal. Di sini kamu juga akan mempelajari banyak sekali ilmu dan teori-teori ekonomi yang nantinya akan kamu terapkan dalam berbagai macam praktik bisnis. Ilmu di jurusan ini cukup berbeda dengan jurusan Ekonomi Pembangunan dan Manajemen Bisnis yang memang mempelajari teori dan ilmu ekonomi untuk kebutuhan pembangunan, kebijakan publik, dan pengelolaan serta perencanaan bisnis.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan Ekonomi Bisnis menggabungkan banyak teori ekonomi dan pendekatan kuantitatif untuk menganalisa dan mengeksekusi proses pengambilan keputusan bisnis yang strategis. Jurusan ini menggunakan Bahasa Inggris sebagai bahasa pengajar. Hal ini bertujuan agar kamu nantinya mempunyai skill komunikasi dan presentasi yang baik yang bisa kamu gunakan untuk berkecimpung di lingkup bisnis global. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Universitas terbaik untuk Jurusan Ekonomi Bisnis</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Ada ratusan sekolah di dunia ini yang menyediakan program <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/tertarik-masuk-jurusan-ekonomi-bisnis-baca-artikel-ini/\">jurusan ekonomi bisnis</a>.  Universitas penyedia program yang kamu pilih sangat berpengaruh. Hal ini karena kamu akan menginvestasikan waktu dan uangmu untuk belajar dan mendalami ilmu ini. Jika kamu ingin bersaing dengan pasar internasional, kamu harus masuk ke universitas terbaik di dunia. Berikut adalah daftar universitas terbaik di Asia untuk kuliah di jurusan ini menurut Financial Times:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>INSEAD</li><li>CEIBS (China Europe International Business School)</li><li>National University of Singapore Business School</li><li>HKUST Business School</li><li>Indian School of Business</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Development Economics Major</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Development economics major adalah salah satu cabang ilmu Ekonomi yang secara khusus mengkaji dan mempelajari berbagai macam persoalan-persoalan seputar pembangunan baik itu ada di sektor bisnis, keuangan, ataupun perbankan. Jika kamu berminat untuk berkuliah di jurusan ekonomi pembangunan, kamu akan banyak mempelajari berbagai teori dan menganalisa berbagai macam isu perekonomian yang ada untuk mencari dan menemukan solusi yang dibutuhkan dari berbagai persoalan ekonomi dengan kritis, kreatif, dan inovatif.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Selain ilmu ekonomi, menjadi mahasiswa jurusan ekonomi pembangunan dapat memberikan berbagai macam soft skill yang akan kamu butuhkan di dunia kerja nantinya. Soft skill tersebut adalah Kemampuan analisis, komunikasi, logika dan matematika dasar, deskripsi, berpikir logis dan terstruktur.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Universitas terbaik untuk Jurusan Ekonomi Pembangunan</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Ada ratusan sekolah di dunia ini yang menyediakan program <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/mengenal-luar-dalam-mengenai-jurusan-ekonomi-pembangunan/\">jurusan ekonomi pembangunan</a>.  Universitas penyedia program yang kamu pilih sangat berpengaruh. Hal ini karena kamu akan menginvestasikan waktu dan uangmu untuk belajar dan mendalami ilmu ini. Jika kamu ingin bersaing dengan pasar internasional, kamu harus masuk ke universitas terbaik di dunia. Berikut adalah daftar universitas terbaik di Australia untuk kuliah ilmu manajemen pemasaran menurut USNews.com :</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>University of Sydney</li><li>University of New South Wales</li><li>Monash University </li><li>University of Melbourne</li><li>University of Queensland Australia</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan ekonomi sangat menarik bukan? Jurusan ini tidak hanya diminati banyak orang lho, tapi juga menyediakan banyak kesempatan untuk dunia karirmu di masa depan nanti. Kalau kamu ingin masuk ke universitas terbaik untuk mempelajari ilmu ekonomi, kamu wajib untuk mempersiapkan semuanya.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download Panduan “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” untuk mencari tahu semua hal yang perlu kamu ketahui sebelum mendaftar beasiswa. GRATIS! <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/id/\">Download disini</a> </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ayo bersama-sama mempersiapkan dirimu untuk masuk ke universitas top dunia bersama Eduverse by ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!<br></p>', 'Downloader.la-62f4b4b851330.jpg', 'Jurusan Ekonomi: Macam-Macam Penjurusan Ini Yang Perlu Kamu Tahu!', 'publish', 'Jurusan Ekonomi: Macam-Macam Penjurusan Ini Yang Perlu Kamu Tahu!', 'Jurusan Ekonomi', 'Kamu pasti sudah tidak asing dengan jurusan ekonomi, tapi apa kamu tahu ada macam-macam cabang di jurusan tersebut? Ayo cari tahu di artikel ini!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-05-03 17:00:00', '2022-08-18 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(12332, 'ucla-a-dive-into-californias-academic-powerhouse', 1, 0, 'UCLA: A Dive Into California\'s Academic Powerhouse', '<p>If you\'re planning to turn the California dream into a reality, studying at UCLA shouldn\'t be overlooked. Moreover, with its history and reputation, it is one of the most prestigious universities in the world. Also, having a diverse student body, top-notch faculty, and prime campus location in Los Angeles, it\'s no wonder that UCLA is one of the most highly sought-after schools in the country. Let\'s learn more about UCLA here!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>A Glance into UCLA</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The University of California, Los Angeles (UCLA) is a public research university in Los Angeles, California. Moreover, founded in 1919 as the second-oldest of the University of California system, UCLA initially served the purpose of training teachers through a two-year undergraduate program.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>UCLA is made up of 10 campuses that spread across Los Angeles. It is home to a highly-reputable faculty teaching more than 230 undergraduate and graduate majors offered. Until now, the university has been affiliated with 27 Nobel laureates, five Turing Award winners, and 3 Pulitzer Prizes.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>UCLA in Numbers</h2>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>QS World University Rankings 2022</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>According to the latest QS World University Rankings, the university is ranked 5th nationally and 40th in the world.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>UCLA also ranks among the top 20 universities in the world for:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Arts and Humanities</li><li>Biology and Biochemistry</li><li>Cell Biology</li><li>Clinical Medicine</li><li>Geosciences&nbsp;</li><li>Surgery</li><li>Social Sciences and Public Health&nbsp;</li><li>Psychiatry or Psychology&nbsp;</li><li>Optics</li><li>Oncology&nbsp;</li><li>Neuroscience and Behaviour</li><li>Nanoscience and Nanotechnology&nbsp;</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Facts</strong> about the University</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>UCLA\'s Student-Faculty Ratio - 18:1</li><li>Undergraduate fields offered - 125&nbsp;</li><li>Number of undergraduate students - 31,600</li><li>Percentage of international undergraduate students - 10%</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Admissions into UCLA</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>UCLA has an acceptance rate of around 12%, making it a highly selective university. However, you should know that acceptance rates depend on several factors, including the number of applicants, their qualifications, the competitiveness of the field, and the amount of space available.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In the latest admissions cycle, 139,488 students applied for a chance on this university. Moreover, of those students, roughly 31,000 students got accepted. Also, this brings the university acceptance rate for the 2021/2022 admission cycle down to only 11 percent.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To apply to this university, <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/dreaming-to-go-to-uc-universities-lets-get-to-know-some-of-them/\">UC</a> schools have their own application system. That means you cannot use the Common or Coalition Applications to apply to UCLA. The UC application opens on August 1st, with the application filing period running from October 1 until November 30. Furthermore, each UC campus that you apply to has an application fee of $80.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Popular majors at UCLA&nbsp;</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are 5 popular undergraduate majors that you can choose:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Sociology</strong> - In this university, you can study Sociology of Criminal Justice, Gender studies, Industrial sociology, and Race and ethnicity studies.&nbsp;</li><li><strong>Political Science and Government</strong> - In this field, you\'ll study American politics, international relations, political theory, and public policy.&nbsp;</li><li><strong>Psychology </strong>- Some of the fields you can study at UCLA include clinical psychology, cognitive psychology, developmental psychology, and personality psychology.&nbsp;</li><li><strong>Econometrics and Quantitative Economics</strong> - In this field, you\'ll study econometrics, finance, international economics, and economic theory.&nbsp;</li><li><strong>Business Administration and Management</strong> - Some of the courses you\'ll take at UCLA include accounting, marketing, business mathematics, and management.&nbsp;</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>UCLA is one of the most prestigious universities in the world. It has a lot of potentials to elevate your future career in the world. Not only that, studying at a top university will bring you a whole new opportunity.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Saving your seat at UCLA? Boost your chances through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/\">initial consultation</a> with ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top uni preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p> Download “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” Guidebook to find out all the things you need to know before applying for scholarships. It\'s FREE, <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/\">download here</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'dl.beatsnoop.com-166141308711JH.jpg', 'UCLA: A Dive Into California\'s Academic Powerhouse', 'publish', 'UCLA: A Dive Into California\'s Academic Powerhouse', 'UCLA', 'UCLA is one of the greatest school out there. Are you interested in getting into the university? Let\'s find out all the facts about UCLA in here!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-05-24 17:00:00', '2022-08-03 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(12344, 'uc-berkeley-californias-prime-top-university-profile', 1, 0, 'UC Berkeley: California\'s Prime Top University Profile', '<p>If you\'re looking for a university in California that has it all, look no further than <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/dreaming-to-go-to-uc-universities-lets-get-to-know-some-of-them/\">UC</a> Berkeley. Moreover, the school\'s reputation is well-known across the world: it\'s considered one of the best in the world and is consistently ranked at the top of many lists. Therefore, if you\'re planning to study there, let\'s get to know the university!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>A Glance into the University</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The University of California, Berkeley (also known as UC Berkeley) is a public land-grant research university that was established in 1868 as the University of California. Moreover, famous for the first campus of the University of California system, the university consists of more than 130 academic departments and over 100 interdisciplinary research units.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>UC Berkeley\'s campus sits on approximately 1,232 acres in the city of Berkeley, California. Also, its faculty includes 114 Nobel laureates, 108 MacArthur Fellows, 30 Pulitzer Prize recipients, and 19 Academy Award winners.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>UC Berkeley Application&nbsp;</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Your UC Berkeley application starts by filling out the UC application, a centralized online system for applying to UC schools. Moreover, you can apply to as many of the ten University of California campuses as you like. For every application you submit, you will need to pay a non-refundable application fee of $80.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The application timeline for University of California applicants is as follows:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td><strong>Date&nbsp;</strong></td><td><strong>Application Status</strong></td></tr><tr><td>August 1	</td><td>UC application opens</td></tr><tr><td>October 1 - November 30 	</td><td>Application filling period&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td>Late March</td><td>Notification of admission decisions&nbsp;</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Test Scores</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Recently, standardized test scores such as the SAT and ACT were not considered for scholarship and admission decisions. Of course, you can still submit your test scores if you want to–, as the scores can be used for course placement or subject credit purposes once you are enrolled at UC Berkeley.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As an international student, you must also submit English proficiency tests such as TOEFL or IELTS. You can also state whether you intend to take these tests in the future if you have not taken them yet.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Learn more about the UC Berkeley application <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/uc-berkeley-application-turn-your-uc-dream-into-a-reality/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"here! (opens in a new tab)\">here!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>UC Berkeley Acceptance Rate</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The acceptance rate at UC Berkeley varies from year to year and depends on the number of applicants and the number of spots available in the incoming class. Furthermore, in recent years, the acceptance rate at UC Berkeley has been around 14.4%. Also, this means that about 14.4% of applicants to UC Berkeley were offered admission. Moreover, it\'s worth noting that the acceptance rate at UC Berkeley is highly competitive and has been trending downward in recent years.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>How hard is it to get into the university?</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>This university is a highly competitive school, and getting admitted can be difficult. The admissions process at UC Berkeley is holistic, meaning that the admissions committee considers a variety of factors in addition to grades and test scores when making its decisions. These factors can include things like your personal statement, letters of recommendation, and extracurricular activities.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The admissions committee is looking for students who are well-rounded and have a strong record of academic and personal achievement. The admissions rate at UC Berkeley varies from year to year, but it is typically quite low, with only about 14.4% of applicants being admitted in recent years. Moreover, to increase your chances of getting into UC Berkeley, it is important to have a strong academic record, participate in extracurricular activities, and write a compelling personal statement.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Learn more about the UC Berkeley acceptance rate <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/get-the-full-info-on-the-uc-berkeley-acceptance-rate-only-in-this-article/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"here! (opens in a new tab)\">here!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>UC Berkeley Ranking</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>UC Berkeley has secured its position among the top twenty universities in the world according to the QS, US News & World Report, and Times Higher Education rankings. Furthermore, here\'s a glance at UC Berkeley\'s ranking for the past five years:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td><strong>Year&nbsp;</strong></td><td><strong>QS World University Rankings&nbsp;</strong></td><td><strong>US News & World Report Global Universities Rankings</strong></td><td><strong>Times Higher Education World University Rankings</strong></td></tr><tr><td>2023</td><td>27</td><td>4</td><td>8</td></tr><tr><td>2022</td><td>32</td><td>4</td><td>8</td></tr><tr><td>2021</td><td>30</td><td>4</td><td>7</td></tr><tr><td>2020</td><td>28</td><td>4</td><td>13</td></tr><tr><td>2019</td><td>27</td><td>4</td><td>15</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>UC Berkeley\'s world-class faculty is reflected in its high standing in subject rankings. Moreover, here are a few of the majors that, according to several university rankings by subject, are among the top 20 worldwide:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td><strong>QS World University Rankings&nbsp;</strong></td><td><strong>US News & World Report</strong></td><td><strong>Times Higher Education World University Rankings</strong></td></tr><tr><td>#3 in Electrical and Electronic Engineering&nbsp;<br>#4 in Arts and Humanities<br>#5 in Chemistry<br>#6 in Mechanical Engineering&nbsp;</td><td>#4 in&nbsp;PhysicsEconomics and Business&nbsp;Biology and Biochemistry&nbsp;Chemistry&nbsp;<br>#5 in&nbsp;Computer SciencePlant and Animal Science&nbsp;<br>#6 in&nbsp;Mathematics&nbsp;Environment/Ecology&nbsp;<br>#11 in Engineering&nbsp;<br>#12 in Materials Science&nbsp;<br></td><td>#2 in Physical Sciences<br>#3 in Engineering&nbsp;<br>#5 in Psychology&nbsp;<br>#6 in Social Sciences&nbsp;<br>#7 in Economics and Business&nbsp;<br>#8 in Arts and Humanities&nbsp;#9 in Life Sciences&nbsp;<br>#13 in Law<br>#19 in Clinical and Health<br><br></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Want to know more about UC Berkeley\'s rankings? Find it <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/uc-berkeley-ranking-learn-more-about-californias-top-university/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"here! (opens in a new tab)\">here!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Conclusion</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Getting into a top university such as UC Berkeley is as hard as it gets. Therefore, you need to make sure to put some time and effort into your preparation so that you will have a higher chance of getting into the university.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Planning to study at UC Berkeley? Pave your way into Cal with ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top uni preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p> Download “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” Guidebook to find out all the things you need to know before applying for scholarships. It\'s FREE,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/\">download here</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'dl.beatsnoop.com-1661415726TF6I.jpg', 'UC Berkeley: California\'s Prime Top University Profile', 'publish', 'UC Berkeley: California\'s Prime Top University Profile', 'UC Berkeley', 'Do you have a dream to study at UC Berkeley? Read this article to find out the complete information to improve your application chance!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-05-23 17:00:00', '2022-07-31 17:00:00', '2023-01-18 17:00:00'),
(12359, 'uc-irvine-here-is-everything-you-need-to-know-about-uc-irvine', 1, 0, 'UC Irvine: Here is Everything You Need to Know about UC Irvine', '<p>In the middle of the 20th century, there was a significant increase in the number of babies born due to the end of World War II. Since this would\'ve resulted in more students hoping to enroll in schools, the University of California decided to build three more schools; <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/dreaming-to-go-to-uc-universities-lets-get-to-know-some-of-them/\">UC</a> San Diego, UC Santa Cruz, and UC Irvine. UC Irvine is located in the city of Irvine, Orange County, California, and is also considered a Public Ivy.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>History of UC Irvine</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>UC Irvine was one of the many University of California campuses that does not draw the name for the city in which it was located. UC Irvine\'s name takes after the Irvine family, who founded the Irvine Company. The land that the Irvine Company owned was sold to the University of California, and the city of Irvine was then established in 1975.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The first schools built at UC Irvine include a College of Arts, Letters, and Science, a School of Engineering, and a Graduate School of Administration. In 1967, the California College of Medicine, which was originally a school dedicated to studying osteopathic medicine, became a part of UC Irvine. 9 years later UC Irvine purchased the Orange County Medical Center, now named the UC Irvine Medical Center, which became a large teaching hospital in Orange County.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Academics and Colleges</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>UC Irvine offers almost 200 undergraduate, graduate, and professional degrees, and it is classified as a research university in the Carnegie Classification of Institutions of Higher Education. The university was also ranked 4th in the world and 1st in the US for 2012 among universities that have been around for less than 50 years.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>UC Irvine is the third most selective University of California School and has a 26% acceptance rate as of the fall of 2019. Also, the average scores of freshmen who enrolled were around 600-720 for reading and writing and 650-790 for math. Meanwhile, the average score on the ACT was around 26. Most of the first-year students who enrolled in 2018 were mainly from California Counties such as Los Angeles County, Orange County, San Diego County, and the Bay Area Counties.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The university has about fourteen academic units, also known as Schools, which include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Claire Trevor School of the Arts</li><li>School of Biological Sciences</li><li>Paul Merage School of Business</li><li>Henry Samueli School of Engineering</li><li>School of Law</li><li>Interdisciplinary Studies</li><li>School of Physical Sciences</li><li>School of Medicine</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Faculty and Research</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>UC Irvine is also famous for its health care. The UC Irvine Medical Center is popular as one of the top 50 hospitals in the United States. UC Irvine\'s School of Medicine has around 25 clinical and basic science departments with almost 2,000 full-time and volunteer faculty members involved in research, patient care, and teaching.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>UC Irvine also has numerous other research organizations, which include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Center for Global Peace and Conflict Studies</li><li>Institute of Transportation Studies</li><li>National Fuel Cell Research Center</li><li>Center for Health Policy Research</li><li>W. M. Keck Center for Accelerator Mass Spectrometry</li><li>Sue and Bill Gross Stem Cell Research Center</li><li>Institute for Genomics and Bioinformatics (IGB)</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Notable Alumni</h2>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Michael Chabon</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Michael Chabon is a short story writer, novelist, and screenwriter born in Washington, DC. Moreover, he was a student at Carnegie Mellon University and the University of Pittsburgh. Later, he attained an MFA (Master of Fine Arts) from UC Irvine. His first novel, <em>The Mysteries of Pittsburgh</em>, was published in 1988. In 2001, he earned a Pulitzer Prize for his book <em>The Amazing Adventures of Kavalier & Clay</em>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Thùy Trang</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Thùy Trang was a Vietnamese actress who first study in civil engineering before she decides to study acting instead. She was famous for her role as Trini Kwan, who was the Yellow Power Ranger in the <em>Mighty Morphin Power Rangers</em> TV show. Trang also played roles in movies such as <em>Spy Hard</em> and <em>The Crow: City of Angels</em>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>There is a lot of information that you should know about UC Irvine before you apply to the university. Even though it is quite hard to get into the university, it is not impossible! You need to make sure you have thorough preparation long before the application deadline.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dreaming of getting into UC Davis? Get yourself prepared with ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top uni preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p> Download “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” Guidebook to find out all the things you need to know before applying for scholarships. It\'s FREE, <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/\">download here</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!</p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>', 'UCI-SIGNAGE-1600x960-1-1600x960.jpg', 'UC Irvine: Here is Everything You Need to Know about UC Irvine', 'publish', 'UC Irvine: Here is Everything You Need to Know about UC Irvine', 'UC Irvine', 'UC Irvine is one of the most famous UC school out there. Are you interested to be part of the university? Read the full scoop in this article!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-05-22 17:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00');
