(12509, 'benefits-of-a-university-admissions-consultant-for-aspiring-students', 1, 0, 'Benefits of a University Admissions Consultant for Aspiring Students', '<p>University admissions consultants have so many benefits for any aspiring student who wants to study abroad. They not only act as your mentor but also as your friend and brainstorming buddy. Let\'s find out more below!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>What is a university admissions consultant?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/university-admissions-consultant-reliable-partner-for-your-application/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">university admissions consultant</a> is a consultant who works with a student to help them with their application to get into a college or university. The goal of a university admissions consultant is on getting the student into a school or program by guiding the student toward the right schools, programs, and careers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” Guidebook to find out all the things you need to know before applying for scholarships. It\'s FREE, <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/\">download here</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>3 Benefits of a University Admissions Consultant</h2>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Relieve the College Application Stress</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>To most high school students, the prospect of creating a college application and applying to schools is daunting. It can be difficult to organize and research all the information needed to apply to schools, and that is exactly what a university admissions consultant is for.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>University admissions consultants help you make a clear timeline to organize your activities. When is the right time to start an extracurricular, or to study for a standardized test? Some of these things are subject to change, and a university admissions consultant is up to date when it comes to these changes. They are responsible for mapping out each step in the process, though the student must also keep up and remain consistent with the plan for it to be efficient.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Develop a Strategy for Tackling the Undergraduate Admissions Process</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ever wondered how difficult it is to get into a certain school, or wondered what tips and tricks can help you land into them? University admissions consultants are there to answer your questions on these topics. Ask important and detailed questions early and pay careful attention to these replies.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>University admissions consultants also help you set up a balanced school list. Your school list shouldn\'t only be a list of the top universities; instead, there are three categories of schools students normally put on their school lists.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Reach schools: Also known as top or dream schools. These are schools that are difficult to get into, with acceptance rates of under 30 or 20 percent.</li><li>Target schools: Schools that you may have a shot at. If you have good test scores or grades, there is a chance you may be able to get into these schools.</li><li>Safety schools: These are schools where you have over an 80% chance of acceptance. You can be certain that you\'ll be accepted to these schools.&nbsp;</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>University admissions consultants carefully assess your applications to see if they can give you a good chance to get into a certain school. However, you must also remember that nothing in life is guaranteed. There is a chance that you can\'t get into your dream school. Additionally, there is also a chance you can get rejected by a safety school while getting accepted to a target or reach school. Sometimes, getting into a college requires luck. University admissions consultants are there to help you organize your activities and scores to give you the best chance of getting into the school you want. Your success and happiness are your consultant\'s priorities.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Tell the Right Story in Each Application</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>More top schools and universities tend to go test-optional, choosing to emphasize the importance of supplemental essays instead. As a result, crafting a personal narrative has become an increasingly essential skill for college applications. To create an interesting and intriguing portrait of a student, university admissions consultants must help students discover experiences and values that matter most to them, and communicate these with clarity.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A university admissions consultant must guide their student to reflect and brainstorm with a couple of new, challenging questions. These questions help a student give voice to certain topics and reveal maturity and growth, as well as help a student find out what they want from life. University admissions consultants must also aid their students with verbalizing and putting into writing episodes of their life that have made them who they are now.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Conclusion</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A university admissions consultant is there to help you get into a good school. However, they don\'t only do this by prompting you to constantly study or keep up with your activities. They are also there when you need a shoulder to cry on when things get hard. Not only that but when you need to rant to someone about the difficulty of college applications. Their core responsibility is not just to help you with university prep. But they also to aid you in finding out what makes you happy.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Prepare yourself for top university with ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top uni preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p> Click <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/\">here</a> to get the initial consultation for your dream university! </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!</p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>', 'Downloader.la-6319780fbb7e4.jpg', 'Benefits of a University Admissions Consultant for Aspiring Students', 'publish', '', 'University Admissions Consultant', 'University admissions consultant has so many benefits for those of you who wants to apply to top unviersity. Read the full benefits here!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-05-31 17:00:00', '2022-09-17 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(12515, 'here-is-how-university-application-consultant-helps-students', 1, 0, 'Here is How University Application Consultant Helps Students', '<p>Getting into your dream university isn\'t as simple as ABC. There are so many factors that go into building your application—your professional experiences, academic transcripts, extracurricular activities, essays, letters of recommendation—and making sure they\'re all at the best level possible. Moreover, this is where a university application consultant comes in. Also, they help maximize your chances of getting into your dream school. But, how? Let\'s find out here!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>What is a university application consultant?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A<a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/university-admissions-consultant-reliable-partner-for-your-application/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\"> university application consultant</a> works with a student throughout every step of the university application process. Some of their roles may include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Creating a personalized plan for applying to and selecting the right school</li><li>Planning students\' high school curriculum&nbsp;</li><li>Maximizing students\' academic records, including high school transcripts, standardized tests, and English proficiency tests&nbsp;</li><li>Utilizing students\' networks to help land internships&nbsp;</li><li>Developing personal goals and action plans for success in high school and university&nbsp;</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>A university application consultant is an invaluable resource for high school students as they navigate the often-confusing world of applying to university. In contrast with the educational agents that connect students with universities, a university application consultant has a role in guiding and helping students to write their personal statements, choose the right university, and navigate the admissions process. They can advise students on what they need in order to get into their dream school and what other factors are important when applying.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” Guidebook to find out all the things you need to know before applying for scholarships. It\'s FREE, <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/\">download here</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Should I hire a university application consultant?</h2>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Increasingly competitive university admissions&nbsp;</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>In recent years, admission rates at highly competitive universities have dropped to single digits. This is due to the ease of submitting multiple applications through online application portals like the University of California application system and the Common Application.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here\'s an overview of the acceptance rates of top universities in the United States in the latest admissions cycle:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Harvard University: 4.59%</li><li>Stanford University: 4.3%</li><li>Massachusetts Institute of Technology (MIT): 6.7%</li><li>UC Berkeley: 11-14%</li><li>UCLA: 12%</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>With a bigger application pool, it\'s harder than ever for applicants to stand out. A university application consultant helps you understand what schools want by providing insight into the admissions process, how they evaluate applications, and how to tailor your application accordingly.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Detailed application process</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Getting into your dream university requires thoughtful planning from years ahead.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For instance, how did you spend your time in high school? Are you involved in volunteering activities, or do you have any internship experiences? What have you accomplished that sets yourself apart from others?&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A university application consultant helps you build your stories throughout high school so your applications are well put when it\'s time to apply. Not only do they help you craft a unique story that highlights your strengths and interests, but they\'ll also make sure that all of your essays are cohesive and compelling.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Offering a neutral perspective</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Sometimes, families can be emotionally involved in deciding where a student should attend university (e.g. close to home, siblings\' or parents\' alma mater).&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With so many factors at play, it is harder for students to make their own decisions about the university that is right for them. A university application consultant can be involved in offering a different perspective while also helping students to land the best outcome. After all, they want the student to attend a school that best fits them socially, academically, and financially.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Need a university application consultant to season your application? ALL-in is here for you!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top university preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p> Click <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/\">here</a> to get the initial consultation for your dream university! </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'Downloader.la-63198f60001bc.jpg', 'Here is How University Application Consultant Helps Students', 'publish', '', 'University Application Consultant', 'Are you a student who is applying for top university? Have you considered having a university application consultant? Know the benefits here!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-05-30 17:00:00', '2022-09-15 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(12521, 'get-to-know-all-about-university-education-consultant', 1, 0, 'Get to Know All About University Education Consultant', '<p>Have you ever thought about how to get into a good school, but you don\'t really know where to start? Moreover, that\'s what university education consultants are for: to help students to get into their dream universities with a handful of tips and tricks!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>What is a university education consultant?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/university-admissions-consultant-reliable-partner-for-your-application/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">university education consultant</a> is a consultant who guides a student or parent with educational planning, specifically a plan to get the student into university. Though similar to school counselors, education consultants are normally self-employed or employed by consulting firms instead of schools.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>What do they do?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>University education consultants focus on training and advising students to prepare them for university. Moreover, they advise students on what classes, lessons, extracurriculars, or other activities they should take that can help them get to their dream universities or pursue their dream majors.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Some of their duties include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Supervising online education</li><li>Report on the effectiveness of current academic systems</li><li>Advise academic intervention program</li><li>Match students to appropriate learning environments, such as special education programs</li><li>Guide college selection and application</li><li>Implement and guide usage of new technologies</li><li>Devise strategies to improve educational quality&nbsp;</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>University education consultants have a responsibility to understand the student\'s special strengths and needs and to include the students\' family members in the planning process.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” Guidebook to find out all the things you need to know before applying for scholarships. It\'s FREE, <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/\">download here</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>What makes a good university education consultant?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Good university education consultants are good at planning and organizing, oriented towards service, analytical and adept at decision-making. Also, they possess good writing and oral communication skills. They should be able to work independently and collaboratively, as well as meet aggressive deadlines. They are also usually qualified with a degree in curriculum and instruction or education leadership.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Some education consultants are also specialized in other specific areas, such as:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Essay Writing&nbsp;</li><li>Career Exploration</li><li>Academic Tutoring (STEM/English Education)</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>A University education consultant is one of the best solutions for students who are struggling with their preparation for top university applications. When you are trying to get into your dream university, it is not an easy task to do. Therefore, you need a great university education consultant to help you succeed in your dream.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Need a university education consultant? Get yourself prepared with ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top uni preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p> Click <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/\">here</a> to get the initial consultation for your dream university! </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'Downloader.la-6319938ec1cbb.jpg', 'Get to Know All About University Education Consultant', 'publish', '', 'University Education Consultant', 'Are you thinking on having a university education consultant? Learn all you need to know about it and the benefits in this article!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-05-29 17:00:00', '2022-09-03 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(12524, 'university-admissions-consultant-reliable-partner-for-your-application', 1, 0, 'University Consultant: Reliable Partner for Your Application', '<p>Universities, at their core, want to admit students who will succeed. Admission rates are higher than ever. However, students are not always prepared for the academic and social expectations of the university. Even for those that are, it is a unique process to apply and gain admission prior to college. It is important that you get all the help you need as soon as possible before it is too late. Here is where the <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/benefits-of-a-university-admissions-consultant-for-aspiring-students/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"University Admission Consultant (opens in a new tab)\">University Admission Consultant</a> (UAC) can help you. Still in doubt whether you need a UAC? Take a look below to have more insight about it!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>What is a </strong>University Admissions Consultant<strong>?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>An admissions consultant assists an individual student with their application for admission to a particular institution or university\'s program. A UAC uses the student\'s <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/get-to-know-all-about-university-education-consultant/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">educational</a> interests and career ambitions to help direct the student toward the right university, the right programs, and the right career. They will offer advice on when to apply, how to word specific sections of an application, and what can make a student stand out from the competition. Through one-on-one preparation with the student, their tasks and responsibilities in this position are centered on helping the student get into the most suitable school or program for the student.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” Guidebook to find out all the things you need to know before applying for scholarships. It\'s FREE, <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/\">download here</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>What Benefits Can You Get From a UAC?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>In essence, college admissions consulting helps you choose the schools that are the best fit for you while also providing you with strategic assistance and appropriate direction throughout the application and essay-writing procedures. <strong>Mentors</strong> or UACsmay also give you assistance with choosing courses, financial aid, career counseling, test preparation, and more. But it does not stop there. There are a lot of benefits you can get from having a mentor or a UAC. These benefits are:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>1. Personalized Support</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Although guidance counselors from school are an enormous help, many of them are just overburdened. They have a lot of students to assist, therefore it is impossible to provide each one of the students with individualized input. Instead, having a mentor will provide you with the personalized support you need to successfully navigate the college admissions process.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>2. Higher Chance of Acceptance</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>A mentor cannot individually ensure acceptance, but they can raise the likelihood by directing you to a university that is better suited to your requirements. This assists in eliminating pointless applications to institutions that might be unable to provide the student with what they are seeking.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>3. Get Rid of Unnecessary Stress</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Eliminating unneeded stress for students and parents is one of the many amazing benefits that you can get from having a mentor or university admissions consultant. You will get insider assistance so that you won\'t have to worry about deadlines, or what might or might not impress the university.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>4. Assistance in Identifying an Area of Focus</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>A confused student will have complete assistance from mentors in choosing a specialty area or major because they have comprehensive knowledge of many different universities, majors, and other topics. In turn, you will have a clear path toward the best-suited top university and program where you have the best chance of succeeding and flourishing.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>5. The Best Investment for Future</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Hiring a consultant or counselor with experience in college admissions is a wise financial decision. For instance, it can assist you in creating a specific college career plan and help them graduate on time. Therefore, you will have a personal supporting unit to make sure you do everything on time with your planned goals.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>How Does a University Admission Consultant Help Students?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Mentors or UACs will help you with everything you need regarding your university preparation. Not only that, but you will also get academic support in regards to how to maintain your grades, what kind of grades you will need for a specific major and many other things. Here is the complete list of what a UAC can help you with:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Essay Writing Strategy</li><li>Improved Standardized Test Score</li><li>Building Personal Brand</li><li>Identifying the Right Extracurricular Activities</li><li>Career Exploration</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Mentor\'s Big Role in the Admission Process</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Even when they meet all the major requirements, students frequently fail to enroll in the university they want to attend. Ignorance of several crucial events, like on-the-spot admissions, admissions at the last minute, and admissions for specific seats, is one of the issues.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The expert admission advisors can assist you in making the most of them because they are familiar with these and many other varieties of admittance scenarios. They have accumulated a wealth of knowledge and experience over the years and are aware of when to apply. Therefore, even when all hope seems lost, a skilled mentor or a university admissions consultant can still make things happen for you.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>How to Find the Right </strong>University Admissions Consultant<strong>?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This is the big question, isn\'t it? First, you know that you need a university admissions consultant to maximize your chance to get into your dream university. But, how do you find one? Finding the best mentor for your future <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/here-is-how-university-application-consultant-helps-students/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">university application</a> is a crucial decision in your early years. There are a lot of ways to find out which UAC is the best. But here are things that you should look for in a mentor or a UAC:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li><strong>Results</strong>. The most important thing is the result. Find out the success rate of the mentors from a certain organization or institution. After all, you want the best help that can get you into your dream university.</li><li><strong>Service</strong>. Find out whether they provide hands-on guidance or intensive personalized support. You need to make sure that you can get a one-on-one session with the mentors and not just chat via text message.</li><li><strong>Admitted Mentees</strong>. The best mentors can help utilize anyone\'s potential to get into their dream university and possibly their dream job. Make sure that the consultant does not require you to take an admissions test or choose their mentees. Everyone might have different potential, but they all deserve the best.</li><li><strong>Identify their process</strong>. You need to know what kind of plan they have prepared for you. This will help you decide whether the mentors have the right help for you.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Mentors or UACs play a very big part in your top university application. Whether you need more help preparing for administration, academic preparation, or your personal brand, the mentors will be there to provide you with the right guidance.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Want the best UAC? With ALL-in, you will have a 100% chance of getting into top universities!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Click <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/\">here</a> to get the initial consultation for your dream university!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What ALL-in can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top university preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Preparation Class</a>.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!</p>', 'Downloader.la-6319971ec5ba2.jpg', 'University Consultant: Reliable Partner for Your Application', 'publish', '', 'University Consultant', 'University admissions consultant is the best partner for you who have a dream of studying abroad at top university. Learn all insight about UAC now!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-05-28 17:00:00', '2022-09-05 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(12528, 'universitas-jurusan-animasi-ini-daftar-5-terbaik-di-asia', 2, 0, 'Universitas Jurusan Animasi: Ini Daftar 5 Terbaik di Asia', '<p>Apa kamu suka menggambar dan punya <em>passion </em>di bidang animasi? Kalau iya, kamu mungkin sedang mencari universitas jurusan animasi terbaik untuk melanjutkan perjalanan akademikmu ke depannya. Walaupun Indonesia mempunyai banyak universitas bagus, tentunya kamu harus punya mimpi untuk masuk ke universitas terbaik di dunia. Berikut adalah daftar beberapa universitas jurusan animasi terbaik di Asia. Ayo kita simak bareng-bareng!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Hongik University, Korea Selatan</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Universitas <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/mau-masuk-jurusan-animasi-baca-dulu-faktanya/\">jurusan animasi</a> yang satu ini memberikan banyak ilmu dan keterampilan dalam aspek desain film dan media digital. Mahasiswa dapat mempelajari teknik terbaru dari film dan media digital serta estetika, teori, dan simulasi. Program pascasarjana menawarkan jurusan Desain Film, Desain Interaksi, Desain Produksi, Animasi Digital, dan Konten Game. Universitas ini pun menyediakan peralatan pengeditan resolusi HD, SD atau campuran seperti program untuk editing yaitu Quantel eQ, Avid, Final Cut Pro, dan Premiere. Sekolah Pascasarjana film dan Media Digital juga menyediakan studio rekaman suara yang lengkap dan kamera serta peralatan HD yang canggih.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Tokyo Animation College, Jepang</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Tokyo Animation College adalah salah satu sekolah animasi paling populer di Jepang. Terletak di jantung kota Tokyo, sekolah kejuruan memiliki dua departemen populer - Animasi dan Komik. Kualitas animator jepang sudah tidak perlu diragukan lagi. Kamu pasti sudah mengenal banyak sekali karya-karya animasi jepang yang sudah mendunia seperti Naruto, One Piece, Sailor Moon, dan masih banyak lagi. Universitas ini juga memberikan paparan industri dan bantuan untuk pengembangan karirmu di masa depan nanti.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Nanyang Technological University, Singapura</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Sebagai salah satu universitas tertua di Singapura, Nanyang Technological University merupakan salah satu universitas terbaik di Asia yang unggul dalam berbagai bidang akademik. Bidang-bidang ini meliputi sains, teknik, humaniora, dan bisnis. Ini adalah salah satu universitas yang paling disukai siswa Indonesia. Dengan tingkat penerimaan hanya 26%, Universitas Teknologi Nanyang menerima lebih dari 33.000 mahasiswa sarjana dan pascasarjana. Meskipun menerima siswa dari seluruh dunia, badan siswa sebagian besar terdiri dari siswa dari Asia.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Beijing Film Academy, Tiongkok</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>BFA (Beijing Film Academy) adalah satu-satunya akademi film di China dan akademi film terbesar di Asia. Melalui pengembangan selama 65 tahun, universitas ini telah membangun sistem budidaya multidisiplin dan multi level yang mencakup seluruh spektrum pembuatan film, termasuk produksi, pengajaran, penciptaan dan penelitian untuk melatih bakat film tingkat lanjut. Sutradara terkenal Tiongkok seperti Zhang Yimou, Chen Kaige, Tian Zhuangzhuang, Jia Zhangke dan Gu Changwei semuanya merupakan alumni dari Beijing Film Academy.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Chung Kang College of Cultural Industries, Korea Selatan</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Universitas jurusan animasi yang satu ini tidak hanya yang terbaik di Korea Selatan saja, melainkan di seluruh Asia. Chungkang terdiri dari tujuh sekolah khusus - Animasi, Manhwa (komik & kartun), Desain Game, Makanan, Mode, Musikal, dan TI Seluler - dan satu departemen - Pendidikan Anak Usia Dini, dan menyampaikan program unik Chungkang untuk mengembangkan bakat luar biasa untuk memimpin industri budaya.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Chungkang menyediakan infrastruktur pendidikan yang unik, menggabungkan kurikulum praktis, produksi kreatif berbasis studio, kursus proyek praktis, program magang di luar negeri, dan pendidikan berbasis konvergensi interdisipliner.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Setelah melihat seluruh daftar ini, apa kamu sudah bisa menetapkan tujuan studimu berikutnya? Ingat ya, ada banyak hal yang perlu kamu persiapkan jika kamu memang mengincar universitas terbaik!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ayo persiapkan dirimu masuk ke universitas terbaik bersama Eduverse by ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download Panduan “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” untuk mencari tahu semua hal yang perlu kamu ketahui sebelum mendaftar beasiswa. GRATIS! <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/id/\">Download disini</a> <br></p>', 'Downloader.la-631998db1c8bd.jpg', 'Universitas Jurusan Animasi: Ini Daftar 5 Terbaik di Asia', 'publish', '', 'Universitas Jurusan Animasi', 'Apa kamu punya keinginan untuk masuk ke universitas jurusan animasi terbaik di Asia? Ayo lihat daftar lengkapnya di dalam artikel ini!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-05-15 17:00:00', '2022-09-17 17:00:00', '2022-11-04 17:00:00'),
(12533, 'nggak-usah-bingung-jurusan-animasi-kerja-apa-ini-daftar-lengkapnya', 2, 0, 'Nggak Usah Bingung Jurusan Animasi Kerja Apa, Ini Daftar Lengkapnya!', '<p>Dengan berkembangnya industri film dan game di luar sana, prospek kerja <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/mau-masuk-jurusan-animasi-baca-dulu-faktanya/\">jurusan animasi</a> juga semakin bertambah luas. Mungkin kamu pernah menonton film seperti Avengers, Interstellar, atau Avatar. Film itu menerapkan visual efek yang merupakan karya dari beberapa seniman dan animator hebat yang bekerja di Hollywood. Masih penasaran jurusan animasi kerja apa? Ayo simak di sini!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Video Game Designer</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Seorang desainer video game membayangkan hampir semua hal tentang sebuah game, termasuk plot, karakter, desain visual, dan tata letaknya. Desainer bertemu dengan tim yang berbeda dan menciptakan visi yang kohesif. Mereka juga bekerja sama dengan programmer dan seniman untuk memastikan desain diikuti, menguji berbagai konsep, dan mengidentifikasi dan memperbaiki kesalahan atau masalah lain yang muncul.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Bandingkan tugas ini dengan tugas pengembang video game, yang memprogram pengkodean game dan memastikan bahwa semua aspek teknis diterapkan dengan benar. Pengembang juga meminta bantuan beberapa kelompok lain untuk mengatasi bug dan memastikan game berjalan semulus mungkin sebelum membuatnya menjadi milik gamer.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Animator</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Seorang animator menciptakan serangkaian gambar yang luas yang membentuk animasi yang terlihat di film, iklan, program televisi, dan video game. Mereka biasanya mempunyai spesialisasi dalam salah satu media ini dan selanjutnya dapat berkonsentrasi pada area tertentu, seperti karakter, latar belakang, atau desain latar belakang. Animator biasanya menggunakan perangkat lunak komputer untuk melakukan pekerjaan mereka. Mereka adalah anggota tim yang terdiri dari animator dan seniman lain yang berkolaborasi dalam proyek.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Jurusan Animasi Kerja Apa? <strong>TV/Film Producer</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Produser televisi mengkoordinasikan dan mengawasi semua aspek produksi, mulai dari kreatif hingga administrasi. Walaupun tidak berkaitan langsung, tapi seorang produser akan selalu terlibat dalam setiap tahap pembuatan sebuah acara. Produser TV juga membuat keputusan keuangan dan menangani kontrak, perjanjian bakat dan tawar-menawar, dan detail administratif lainnya. Sementara produsen bisa bersenang-senang merencanakan dan melaksanakan produksi, mereka juga menangani masalah selama produksi dan menjaga semuanya sesuai anggaran.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>TV/Film Editor</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Sebagai editor film/video, kamu akan mengelola materi seperti rekaman kamera, dialog, efek suara, grafik, dan efek khusus untuk menghasilkan produk film atau video final. Ini adalah peran kunci dalam proses pasca produksi dan keterampilan kamu dapat menentukan kualitas dan pengiriman hasil akhir. Kamu biasanya akan bekerja sama dengan sutradara untuk mencapai hasil akhir yang diinginkan.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Pekerjaan cenderung bersifat lepas, dan kemungkinan besar kamu akan bekerja dengan kontrak jangka pendek untuk studio pascaproduksi, perusahaan televisi, dan perusahaan perusahaan.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Teknologi digital, perangkat lunak komputer khusus, dan digitalisasi suara dan gambar berkualitas tinggi telah secara efektif menggantikan metode pemotongan film manual tradisional. Dalam beberapa kasus, kamu mungkin diberi kebebasan berkreasi, sementara di kasus lain kamu hanya diminta untuk mengoperasikan mesin yang diperlukan.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Jurusan Animasi Kerja Apa? <strong>Visual Effect Designer</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Seniman VFX membuat fotoreal atau sebuah gambaran nyata yang dihasilkan secara digital. Untuk menciptakan fotoreal tersebut membutuhkan integrasi yang mulus dari efek-efek ini ke dalam aksi langsung dalam film layar lebar, televisi, game online dan konsol.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Seniman VFX menggunakan teknologi terbaru untuk menghasilkan beberapa objek seperti monster, aktor, kerumunan, pemandangan, dan pemeran pengganti. Ada juga area efek partikel digital yang berkembang, yang mencakup cairan dan api, serta manipulasi objek dan pencahayaan.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kamu perlu membuat para penonton percaya bahwa apa yang mereka lihat adalah nyata. Ini bisa berupa naga, kastil megah, badai hujan, gelombang besar, pesawat ruang angkasa, pahlawan super, kota asing, atau bahkan sebuah planet.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ada banyak sekali karir yang bisa kamu kejar sebagai lulusan dari jurusan animasi, jadi kamu tidak perlu bingung jurusan animasi kerja apa. Tapi untuk bisa mengejarnya, dibutuhkan ilmu dan keterampilan khusus yang hanya bisa kamu dapatkan dari universitas jurusan animasi terbaik. Maka dari itu, kamu harus mempersiapkan dirimu untuk masuk ke universitas jurusan animasi terbaik sebelum akhirnya mengejar karir di atas ya!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tertarik untuk mempunyai masa depan di bidang animasi? Eduverse by ALL-in akan membantu seluruh persiapanmu!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download Panduan “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” untuk mencari tahu semua hal yang perlu kamu ketahui sebelum mendaftar beasiswa. GRATIS! <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/id/\">Download disini</a> </p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>', 'Downloader.la-63199bd72ea8f.jpg', 'Nggak Usah Bingung Jurusan Animasi Kerja Apa, Ini Daftar Lengkapnya!', 'publish', '', 'Jurusan Animasi Kerja Apa', 'Tertarik tapi bingung jurusan animasi kerja apa? Kamu udah nggak perlu bingung lagi. Ayo simak daftar lengkapnya ada di sini!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-05-16 17:00:00', '2022-09-07 17:00:00', '2022-11-04 17:00:00'),
(12539, 'mau-masuk-jurusan-animasi-baca-dulu-faktanya', 2, 0, 'Mau Masuk Jurusan Animasi? Baca Dulu Faktanya!', '<p>Apa kamu tertarik untuk masuk jurusan animasi? Sudah tau fakta dan prospek kerjanya belum? Jurusan yang sedang naik daun ini menyimpan segudang potensi yang bisa kamu gali lho. Apalagi dengan sedang meningkatnya industri perfilman dan animasi di dunia. Ayo simak lebih lanjut di bawah ini!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Apa itu Jurusan Animasi?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Program gelar animasi atau animasi komputer memberimu kesempatan untuk mengembangkan dan mengasah keterampilan kreatifmu. Kamu juga akan belajar dari para profesional industri dan mempelajari berbagai topik, termasuk prinsip animasi dasar, jalur produksi, desain karakter dan latar belakang, storyboard, dan pemodelan.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Di jurusan animasi ini pula, kamu akan mengembangkan kemampuan artistik dengan bekerja dengan grafik gerak, efek visual 2D dan 3D, dan pengeditan video. Kamu juga akan mengembangkan keterampilan seperti tipografi, penulisan skenario, arah kamera, perencanaan pra dan pasca produksi, manajemen waktu, dan literasi komputer.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Universitas Jurusan Animasi</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ada banyak sekali <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/universitas-jurusan-animasi-ini-daftar-5-terbaik-di-asia/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"universitas jurusan animasi (opens in a new tab)\">universitas jurusan animasi</a> yang ada di Asia. Beberapa deretan universitas tersebut pun telah menghasilkan beberapa orang luar biasa yang sangat berperan dibalik karya-karya terkenal di dunia. Ayo simak daftarnya di bawah ini!</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>5. Hongik University, Korea Selatan</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Universitas jurusan animasi yang satu ini memberikan banyak ilmu dan keterampilan dalam aspek desain film dan media digital. Mahasiswa dapat mempelajari teknik terbaru dari film dan media digital serta estetika, teori, dan simulasi. Program pascasarjana menawarkan jurusan Desain Film, Desain Interaksi, Desain Produksi, Animasi Digital, dan Konten Game. Universitas ini pun menyediakan peralatan pengeditan resolusi HD, SD atau campuran seperti program untuk editing yaitu Quantel eQ, Avid, Final Cut Pro, dan Premiere. Sekolah Pascasarjana film dan Media Digital juga menyediakan studio rekaman suara yang lengkap dan kamera serta peralatan HD yang canggih.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>4. Tokyo Animation College, Jepang</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Tokyo Animation College adalah salah satu sekolah animasi paling populer di Jepang. Terletak di jantung kota Tokyo, sekolah kejuruan memiliki dua departemen populer - Animasi dan Komik. Kualitas animator jepang sudah tidak perlu diragukan lagi. Kamu pasti sudah mengenal banyak sekali karya-karya animasi jepang yang sudah mendunia seperti Naruto, One Piece, Sailor Moon, dan masih banyak lagi. Universitas ini juga memberikan paparan industri dan bantuan untuk pengembangan karirmu di masa depan nanti.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>3. Nanyang Technological University, Singapura</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Sebagai salah satu universitas tertua di Singapura, Nanyang Technological University merupakan salah satu universitas terbaik di Asia yang unggul dalam berbagai bidang akademik. Bidang-bidang ini meliputi sains, teknik, humaniora, dan bisnis. Ini adalah salah satu universitas yang paling disukai siswa Indonesia. Dengan tingkat penerimaan hanya 26%, Universitas Teknologi Nanyang menerima lebih dari 33.000 mahasiswa sarjana dan pascasarjana. Meskipun menerima siswa dari seluruh dunia, badan siswa sebagian besar terdiri dari siswa dari Asia.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Baca artikel ini untuk mengetahui daftar lengkapnya!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Prospek Kerja Jurusan Animasi</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Setelah mengetahui beberapa daftar universitas terbaik yang bisa kamu pertimbangkan, sudah saatnya kamu mengetahui beberapa deretan <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/nggak-usah-bingung-jurusan-animasi-kerja-apa-ini-daftar-lengkapnya/\">prospek kerja</a> yang bisa kamu pilih di masa depan nanti. Berikut adalah daftarnya!</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Video Game Designer</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Seorang desainer video game membayangkan hampir semua hal tentang sebuah game, termasuk plot, karakter, desain visual, dan tata letaknya. Desainer bertemu dengan tim yang berbeda dan menciptakan visi yang kohesif. Mereka juga bekerja sama dengan programmer dan seniman untuk memastikan desain diikuti, menguji berbagai konsep, dan mengidentifikasi dan memperbaiki kesalahan atau masalah lain yang muncul.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Bandingkan tugas ini dengan tugas pengembang video game, yang memprogram pengkodean game dan memastikan bahwa semua aspek teknis diterapkan dengan benar. Pengembang juga meminta bantuan beberapa kelompok lain untuk mengatasi bug dan memastikan game berjalan semulus mungkin sebelum membuatnya menjadi milik gamer.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Animator</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Seorang animator menciptakan serangkaian gambar yang luas yang membentuk animasi yang terlihat di film, iklan, program televisi, dan video game. Mereka biasanya mempunyai spesialisasi dalam salah satu media ini dan selanjutnya dapat berkonsentrasi pada area tertentu, seperti karakter, latar belakang, atau desain latar belakang. Animator biasanya menggunakan perangkat lunak komputer untuk melakukan pekerjaan mereka. Mereka adalah anggota tim yang terdiri dari animator dan seniman lain yang berkolaborasi dalam proyek.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>TV/Film Producer</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Produser televisi mengkoordinasikan dan mengawasi semua aspek produksi, mulai dari kreatif hingga administrasi. Walaupun tidak berkaitan langsung, tapi seorang produser akan selalu terlibat dalam setiap tahap pembuatan sebuah acara. Produser TV juga membuat keputusan keuangan dan menangani kontrak, perjanjian bakat dan tawar-menawar, dan detail administratif lainnya. Sementara produsen bisa bersenang-senang merencanakan dan melaksanakan produksi, mereka juga menangani masalah selama produksi dan menjaga semuanya sesuai anggaran.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ingin tahu prospek kerja lainnya? Baca di sini ya!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Hal-hal yang bisa kamu dapat dari jurusan ini sangat banyak lho. Sebelum kamu memutuskan untuk kuliah dimana, banyak lho yang perlu kamu perhitungkan. Seperti biaya, beasiswa, minat, dan semua persiapanmu lainnya. Jadi, kamu harus sudah siap semuanya jadi jauh-jauh hari ya!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Perlu panduan lebih lanjut untuk menggapai mimpi di jurusan animasi? Ayo gabung ke Eduverse by ALL-in sekarang!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download Panduan “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” untuk mencari tahu semua hal yang perlu kamu ketahui sebelum mendaftar beasiswa. GRATIS! <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/id/\">Download disini</a> <br></p>', 'Downloader.la-63199e17151b3.jpg', 'Mau Masuk Jurusan Animasi? Baca Dulu Faktanya!', 'publish', '', 'Jurusan Animasi', 'Apa kamu seorang pelajar yang sedang memperhitungkan ingin masuk jurusan animasi? Ayo baca semua info lengkapnya di dalam artikel ini!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-05-14 17:00:00', '2022-09-05 17:00:00', '2022-11-04 17:00:00');
