(12591, 'a-full-scoop-of-university-of-cambridge-acceptance-rate', 1, 0, 'A Full Scoop of University of Cambridge Acceptance Rate', '<p>Are you on the search for the best universities in the United Kingdom? Surely the University of Cambridge would be on your list. This esteemed university, which has been consistently ranked as one of the top universities in the world, has been the dream university of many students. In this article, we\'ll learn more about the <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/all-in-one-information-about-the-university-of-cambridge/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"University of Cambridge (opens in a new tab)\">University of Cambridge </a>acceptance rate and application process!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>A glance at the University of Cambridge&nbsp;</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The University of Cambridge is a collegiate research university in Cambridge, England. Founded in 1209 and granted a royal charter by King Henry III in 1231, it is the second-oldest university in the English-speaking world and the world\'s second-oldest surviving university.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The university is made up of 31 constituent colleges and over 100 academic departments divided into six schools. Currently, it is home to over 21,000 students, with 10,500 members of staff. Cambridge has an expansive alumni network, which consists of more than 120 Nobel laureates, 7 Fields Medalists, and 6 Turing Award winners among others.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>University of Cambridge Acceptance Rate</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The University of Cambridge acceptance rate is estimated to be between 15 and 25 percent, making it a highly selective school.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The University of Cambridge\'s undergraduate admissions statistics are shown below:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td>Cycle</td><td>Acceptance rate	</td></tr><tr><td>2018</td><td>24.8%	</td></tr><tr><td>2019</td><td>24.2%	</td></tr><tr><td>2020</td><td>23.1%	</td></tr><tr><td>2021&nbsp;</td><td>18.7%	</td></tr><tr><td>2022</td><td>20.8%</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Below are the acceptance rates of the colleges at the University of Cambridge over a three-year period (2019-2021):</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td>College</td><td>Acceptance Rate&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td>Christ\'s&nbsp;</td><td>12.0%</td></tr><tr><td>Churchill&nbsp;</td><td>13.49%</td></tr><tr><td>Clare&nbsp;</td><td>10.8%</td></tr><tr><td>Corpus Christi</td><td>18.6%</td></tr><tr><td>Downing</td><td>12.8%</td></tr><tr><td>Emmanuel</td><td>12.1 %</td></tr><tr><td>Fitzwilliam</td><td>13.9%</td></tr><tr><td>Girton</td><td>14.6%</td></tr><tr><td>Gonville and Caius&nbsp;</td><td>14.6%</td></tr><tr><td>Homerton</td><td>10.0%</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>University of Cambridge Acceptance Rate: How to Apply&nbsp;</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>You will need to apply through the UCAS website for the Cambridge application process. The Universities and Colleges Admissions Service (UCAS) is a centralized organization that operates the application processes for universities in the United Kingdom.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>After the submission of your documents, you can track your application through the Applicant Portal.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Key dates and deadlines</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td>Early September&nbsp;</td><td>UCAS Apply opens&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td>15 September&nbsp;</td><td>LNAT registration deadline for Law applicants</td></tr><tr><td>30 September&nbsp;</td><td>BMAT registration deadline for Medicine applicants.TMUA registration deadline for Computer Science and Economics applicants.ENGAA registration deadline for Engineering applicants.NSAA registration deadline for Chemical Engineering and Biotechnology, Natural Sciences, and Veterinary Medicine applicants.</td></tr><tr><td>15 October&nbsp;</td><td>UCAS application deadline</td></tr><tr><td>22 October</td><td>Transcript deadline for applicants&nbsp;&nbsp;Deadline for the submission of additional application form</td></tr><tr><td>December&nbsp;</td><td>Interviews&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td>January&nbsp;</td><td>Decisions were sent out. A further interview for some applicants</td></tr><tr><td>August&nbsp;</td><td>Examination results published and confirmation of conditional offers&nbsp;</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>English Proficiency Test Score Requirement</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are several English proficiency tests that are accepted by the University of Cambridge:&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td><strong>Tests</strong></td><td><strong>Minimum Score Required</strong></td></tr><tr><td>IELTS</td><td>7.5 and above</td></tr><tr><td>TOEFL	 iBT</td><td>110 and above</td></tr><tr><td>Cambridge English: C1 Advanced</td><td>193 and above&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td>Cambridge English: C2 Proficiency</td><td>200 and above&nbsp;</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>There is a lot more information you need before you decide whether you want to study at the University of Cambridge. But, the acceptance rate is one of the most important elements for you to know before applying there. The acceptance rate may be low but with the right guidance, you can get into any top university around the world.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Planning to study at the University of Cambridge? Gear yourself up with ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top uni preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'Downloader.la-6322cd94de31b.jpg', 'A Full Scoop of University of Cambridge Acceptance Rate', 'publish', '', 'University of Cambridge Acceptance Rate', 'Are you still deciding your target university? Take a look at the University of Cambridge Acceptance Rate to know your chance on getting into it!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-06-04 17:00:00', '2022-09-09 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(12599, 'university-of-cambridge-ranking-all-world-class-subject', 1, 0, 'University of Cambridge Ranking: All World-Class Subject', '<p>The University of Cambridge is a research university in Cambridge, the United Kingdom, that was founded in the early 1200s and is the third-oldest surviving university in the world. There are six notable schools at the <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/all-in-one-information-about-the-university-of-cambridge/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"University of Cambridge (opens in a new tab)\">University of Cambridge</a>: arts and humanities; biological sciences; clinical medicine; humanities and social sciences; physical sciences; and technology. It also contains around 31 residential colleges, 3 of which are women-only.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>University of Cambridge Ranking</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Colleges and universities are ranked according to their performance across a number of factors and indicators of excellence.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>University of Cambridge Rankings</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>#8 in Best Global Universities</li><li>#2 in Best Global Universities in Europe</li><li>#2 in Best Global Universities in the United Kingdom</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>The Best Subjects in the University of Cambridge Ranking</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<h3>1. Arts and Humanities (#3 in the World)</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Arts and humanities are normally a single academic discipline. Moreover, this is a major that specializes in the areas of human culture, context, and achievements. Furthermore, they mainly examine the many ways humans understood and expressed themselves throughout different subject areas and broad timeframes in history.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The University of Cambridge has a diverse community of instructors that teaches most of the subjects listed under this umbrella. Moreover, this subject includes architecture and history of art, Asian and Middle Eastern studies, classics, divinity, English, modern and medieval languages, music, and philosophy.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>2. Biology and Biochemistry (#5 In the world)</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Biology is the study of living organisms and their anatomy and physiology, while biochemistry is the study of the chemistry of these organisms. Biochemistry is also considered an area of biology, and research in both areas helps to discover how living organisms function in the real world.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The University of Cambridge\'s Department of Biochemistry is located in the center of Cambridge, across from the Hopkins and Sanger buildings. Moreover, it holds numerous notable undergraduate and postgraduate education programs, with over 40 research groups led by investigators. Also, they study many aspects of biology, including Chemical Biology & Drug Design, Disease Biology, Molecular Microbiology, Stem Cell Biology, and Systems Biology. Furthermore, the University has state-of-the-art facilities and equipment, which include protein chemistry, metabolomics, crystallography, cryo-electron microscopy, and mass spectrometry.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>3. Cell Biology (#4 in the world)</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The study of cell structure and function is the definition of cell biology. Also, it is based on the idea that a cell is the basic building block of all life. Moreover, a thorough grasp of the tissues and organisms that cells make up is made possible by concentrating on the cell. While some creatures just contain one cell, others consist of massive cooperative groupings with many cells. Furthermore, cell biology as a whole concentrates on the structure and function of a cell, from the most universal characteristics shared by all cells to the distinctive, extremely complex functions exclusive to specialized cells.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The University of Cambridge has a lot of facilities. Moreover, all of them have a great quality of education to ensure that the students will get the best experience here. Also, it provides students with late research and opportunities to bring real change into the world through cell biology.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Conclusion</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The University of Cambridge is one of the most famous and highest-ranking universities in the world with exceptional classes and programs, which is why many students set their sights on this glorious school. However, rankings don\'t define everything; there are other factors that can make your experience with a school better or worse, so remember to do thorough research!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Planning to be a student of the University of Cambridge? Come get yourself prepared with ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top uni preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!</p>', 'Downloader.la-6322d1781eb0f.jpg', 'University of Cambridge Ranking: All World-Class Subject', 'publish', '', 'University of Cambridge Ranking', 'Interested to find out the University of Cambridge Ranking and their subject? Find the complete list and explanation inside this article!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-06-03 17:00:00', '2022-09-02 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(12607, 'university-of-cambridge-master-program-for-your-amazing-study-journey', 1, 0, 'University of Cambridge Master Program for Your Amazing Study Journey', '<p>Consistently ranked among the top 5 universities worldwide, the University of Cambridge has been the dream of many. After all, it has an alumni network that has left a lasting mark on history in all fields including politics, economics, and science. Moreover, with an exceptional reputation for offering world-class education and research facilities, it\'s no surprise this school is extremely competitive. In this article, let\'s find out about the <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/all-in-one-information-about-the-university-of-cambridge/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"University of Cambridge (opens in a new tab)\">University of Cambridge</a> Master Program!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>University of Cambridge\'s Background&nbsp;</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The University of Cambridge has been offering a world-leading education since its founding year in 1209. Since then, thousands of bright minds have come through Cambridge and gone on to be world leaders in their fields.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sitting across 710 acres of land, the University of Cambridge is made up of 31 colleges, each with its own unique history, traditions, and architecture. The university also has more than 100 libraries with collections totaling more than 15 million books and manuscripts.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>University of Cambridge Master Program</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>There are around 330 postgraduate programs available to study at Cambridge. Moreover, you can choose from taught or research-based master\'s degrees, with subjects ranging from sciences and engineering to humanities and social sciences. There are also many programs that offer a combination of these disciplines.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Some of the most popular master\'s programs at the University of Cambridge include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>The Cambridge MBA</li><li><span style=\"background-color: rgb(225, 190, 231);\">Mphil Public Health</span></li><li>Master of Finance (MFin)</li><li>MPhil in Economics</li><li>MPhil in Management&nbsp;</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Discover all the master\'s programs offered at the University of Cambridge <a href=\"https://www.postgraduate.study.cam.ac.uk/courses\">here</a>!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As a Cambridge postgraduate student, you will receive a world-class education that will aim to help you develop the skills you need to succeed in today\'s rapidly changing workplace. Furthermore, your time at Cambridge will prepare you to think critically and creatively, understand complex problems, solve problems analytically, and communicate effectively.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In each of the three 8-week terms, you\'ll gain knowledge from lectures, seminars, labs (if applicable), and supervisions. Later, a personal supervisor will be assigned to you with the purpose of guiding your study program or research plan.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>How to apply to University of Cambridge Master Program </h2>\n\n\n\n<p>To apply for the University of Cambridge Master Program, there are several admissions requirements that must be fulfilled. This includes:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Possess a minimum of a good upper second class honors degree from a UK university or an equivalent standard from an overseas university and completion of, or release from, any current training or education course</li><li>Has a minimum of three years\' work experience after graduation</li><li>Demonstrable enthusiasm and/or aptitude for sustainability leadership</li><li>Good ability in written and spoken English language</li><li>Endorsement from an employer or from an organization that will be the focus of your work on the program</li><li>Access to appropriate computer technology and internet software</li><li>Ability to pay the course fees or to identify a sponsoring institution</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Your Cambridge application will be completed when:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>You have submitted your application and supporting documents via the Applicant Portal</li><li>You have paid the £75 application fee</li><li>Your referees have submitted their reference</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>For more information about the University of Cambridge Master Program, click <a href=\"https://www.postgraduate.study.cam.ac.uk/\">here</a>!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Conclusion</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>There are a lot of things that you need to prepare if you want to get into the University of Cambridge Master Program. Moreover, just like the bachelor\'s degree, you need to take this seriously and make sure you fill all the requirements that you need to apply there.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Planning to be a student of the University of Cambridge master program? Come get yourself prepared with ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top uni preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'Downloader.la-6322d2ffc81ce.jpg', 'University of Cambridge Master Program for Your Amazing Study Journey', 'publish', '', 'University of Cambridge Master Program', 'it’s no surprise this school is extremely competitive. In this article, let’s find out about the University of Cambridge Master Program!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-06-02 17:00:00', '2022-09-27 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(12628, 'all-in-one-information-about-the-university-of-cambridge', 1, 0, 'All-in-One Information about The University of Cambridge', '<p>The University of Cambridge is one of the oldest and most well-known universities in the United Kingdom. Numerous students from all over the globe had set their sights on this glorious school. Are you one of them? Here are a few tips and tricks on how to get in!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Introduction</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The University of Cambridge is a collegiate research university in Cambridge, England. Moreover, founded in 1209 and granted a royal charter by King Henry III in 1231, it is the second-oldest university in the English-speaking world and the world\'s second-oldest surviving university.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The university comprises 31 constituent colleges and over 100 academic departments organized into six schools. Currently, it is attended by over 21,000 students, with 10,500 members of staff. Cambridge has an impressive alumni network, which consists of more than 120 Nobel laureates, 7 Fields Medalists, and 6 Turing Award winners among many others.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>University of Cambridge Rankings</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The University of Cambridge is a research university in Cambridge, the United Kingdom that was founded in the early 1200s and is the third-oldest surviving university in the world. Moreover, there are six notable schools at the University of Cambridge: arts and humanities, biological sciences, clinical medicine, humanities, and social sciences, physical sciences, and technology. It also contains around 31 residential colleges, 3 of which are women-only.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Ranks</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Colleges and universities are ranked according to their performance across a number of factors and indicators of excellence.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/university-of-cambridge-ranking-all-world-class-subject/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"University of Cambridge Rankings (opens in a new tab)\">University of Cambridge Rankings</a></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>#8 in Best Global Universities</li><li>#2 in Best Global Universities in Europe</li><li>#2 in Best Global Universities in the United Kingdom</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>University of Cambridge Master Program</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>There are around 330 postgraduate programs available to study at Cambridge. You can choose from taught or research-based masters\' degrees, with the subjects ranging from sciences and engineering to the humanities and social sciences. Many programs offer a combination of these disciplines.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Some of the most popular master\'s programs at the University of Cambridge include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>The Cambridge MBA</li><li>Mphil Public Health</li><li>Master of Finance (MFin) </li><li>MPhil in Economics</li><li>MPhil in Management&nbsp;</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Discover all the master\'s programs offered at the University of Cambridge <a href=\"https://www.postgraduate.study.cam.ac.uk/courses\">here</a>!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As a Cambridge postgraduate student, you will receive a world-class education that is designed to help you develop the skills you need to succeed in today\'s rapidly changing workplace. Your time at Cambridge will prepare you to think critically and creatively, understand complex problems, solve problems analytically, and communicate effectively.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In each of the three 8-week terms, you\'ll gain knowledge from lectures, seminars, labs (if applicable), and supervisions. Later, a personal supervisor will be assigned to you with the responsibility of guiding your study program or research plan.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>How to Apply to Master Program</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>To apply for the <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/university-of-cambridge-master-program-for-your-amazing-study-journey/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"University of Cambridge Master Program (opens in a new tab)\">University of Cambridge Master Program</a>, several admissions requirements must be fulfilled. This includes:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Possess a minimum of a good upper second class honors degree from a UK university or an equivalent standard from an overseas university and completion of, or release from, any current training or education course</li><li>Has a minimum of three years\' work experience after graduation</li><li>Demonstrable enthusiasm and/or aptitude for sustainability leadership</li><li>Good ability in written and spoken English language</li><li>Endorsement from the employer or from an organization that will be the focus of your work on the program</li><li>Access to appropriate computer technology and internet software</li><li>Ability to pay the course fees or to identify a sponsoring institution</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Your Cambridge application will be completed when:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>You have submitted your application and supporting documents via the Applicant Portal</li><li>You have paid the £75 application fee</li><li>Your referees have submitted their reference</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>University of Cambridge Acceptance Rate</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/a-full-scoop-of-university-of-cambridge-acceptance-rate/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"acceptance rate (opens in a new tab)\">acceptance rate</a> at the University of Cambridge is estimated to be between 15 and 25 percent, making it a highly selective school.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The University of Cambridge\'s undergraduate admissions statistics are shown below:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td>Cycle</td><td>Acceptance rate	</td></tr><tr><td>2018</td><td>24.8%	</td></tr><tr><td>2019</td><td>24.2%	</td></tr><tr><td>2020</td><td>23.1%	</td></tr><tr><td>2021&nbsp;</td><td>18.7%	</td></tr><tr><td>2022</td><td>20.8%</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Below are the acceptance rates of the colleges at the University of Cambridge over three years (2019-2021):</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td>College</td><td>Acceptance Rate&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td>Christ\'s&nbsp;</td><td>12.0%</td></tr><tr><td>Churchill&nbsp;</td><td>13.49%</td></tr><tr><td>Clare&nbsp;</td><td>10.8%</td></tr><tr><td>Corpus Christi</td><td>18.6%</td></tr><tr><td>Downing</td><td>12.8%</td></tr><tr><td>Emmanuel</td><td>12.1 %</td></tr><tr><td>Fitzwilliam</td><td>13.9%</td></tr><tr><td>Girton</td><td>14.6%</td></tr><tr><td>Gonville and Caius&nbsp;</td><td>14.6%</td></tr><tr><td>Homerton</td><td>10.0%</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>How to apply to the University of Cambridge&nbsp;</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>You will need to apply through the UCAS website for the Cambridge application process. The Universities and Colleges Admissions Service (UCAS) is a centralized organization that operates the application processes for universities in the United Kingdom.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>After the submission of your documents, you can track your application through the Applicant Portal.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Key dates and deadlines</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td>Early September&nbsp;</td><td>UCAS Apply opens&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td>15 September&nbsp;</td><td>LNAT registration deadline for Law applicants</td></tr><tr><td>30 September&nbsp;</td><td>BMAT registration deadline for Medicine applicants.TMUA registration deadline for Computer Science and Economics applicants.ENGAA registration deadline for Engineering applicants.NSAA registration deadline for Chemical Engineering and Biotechnology, Natural Sciences, and Veterinary Medicine applicants.</td></tr><tr><td>15 October&nbsp;</td><td>UCAS application deadline</td></tr><tr><td>22 October</td><td>Transcript deadline for applicants&nbsp;&nbsp;Deadline for the submission of additional application form</td></tr><tr><td>December&nbsp;</td><td>Interviews&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td>January&nbsp;</td><td>Decisions sent outA further interview for some applicants</td></tr><tr><td>August&nbsp;</td><td>Examination results published and confirmation of conditional offers&nbsp;</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>English Proficiency Test Score Requirement</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are several English proficiency tests that are accepted by the University of Cambridge:&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td><strong>Tests</strong></td><td><strong>Minimum Score Required</strong></td></tr><tr><td>IELTS</td><td>7.5 and above</td></tr><tr><td>TOEFL	 iBT</td><td>110 and above</td></tr><tr><td>Cambridge English: C1 Advanced</td><td>193 and above&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td>Cambridge English: C2 Proficiency</td><td>200 and above&nbsp;</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>For those of you who want to get into the Univesity of Cambridge, these insights are one of the most essential for your preparation. Make sure you get all the complete insight to make sure that you tackle every single requirement.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Planning to be a student of the University of Cambridge? Come get yourself prepared with ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top uni preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'Downloader.la-6322deef5372e.jpg', 'All-in-One Information about The University of Cambridge', 'publish', '', 'The University of Cambridge', 'Do you have a dream to get into the University of Cambridge? Get the best insigth to complete your preparation for top university in here!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-06-01 17:00:00', '2022-09-03 17:00:00', '2023-01-04 17:00:00'),
(12653, 'bukan-cuman-tentang-hotel-ayo-cari-tahu-jurusan-perhotelan-kerja-apa', 2, 0, 'Bukan Cuman Tentang Hotel! Ayo Cari Tahu Jurusan Perhotelan Kerja Apa!', '<p>Walaupun jurusan yang satu ini merupakan salah satu jurusan yang banyak peminatnya, tetapi masih banyak pelajar yang belum tahu jurusan perhotelan kerja apa di masa depan nanti. Kamu tidak perlu ragu mengenai karirmu di jurusan ini lho. Ayo simak daftar lengkap prospek karir <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/ayo-cari-tahu-seluk-beluk-jurusan-perhotelan-di-artikel-ini/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"jurusan perhotelan (opens in a new tab)\">jurusan perhotelan</a> yang gak itu-itu aja!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Wedding Organizer/Wedding Planner</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Wedding Planner</em> adalah seseorang yang akan mengurus segalanya mengenai logistik pernikahan. Hal ini mulai dari referensi vendor dan negosiasi kontrak hingga hari pelaksanaan pernikahan sang klien. Seorang perencana bertugas untuk melacak anggaran dan menangani logistik. Ini adalah keterampilan yang dapat dipelajari banyak orang, tetapi hanya perencana terbaik yang memiliki pengalaman bertahun-tahun dan kredensial yang menempatkan mereka di atas yang lainnya.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Beberapa perencana juga menyediakan layanan desain atau gaya, membantu spesifik kreatif hari pernikahan klien, sementara ada juga yang lain memilih untuk menyerahkan detail tersebut kepada desainer pernikahan. Kunci dari pekerjaan ini adalah komunikasi yang baik antara kamu dengan klien. Karena kamu akan berkolaborasi dengan klien untuk mewujudkan pernikahan impian mereka.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Jurusan Perhotelan Kerja Apa? <strong>Staf Darat <em>(Ground Crew) </em>Maskapai Penerbangan</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Tidak ada bandara atau maskapai penerbangan yang dapat beroperasi secara berkelanjutan tanpa staf darat. Mereka adalah roda penggerak vital dalam roda industri penerbangan, dan mereka tidak dapat digantikan oleh komputer atau mesin. Ini berarti pekerjaan staf darat akan tetap ada di masa depan.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ada banyak tugas dan tanggung jawab yang harus dilakukan dengan pekerjaan staf darat, tetapi yang utama adalah memastikan keselamatan dan kenyamanan semua penumpang yang melakukan perjalanan melalui bandara. Bandara dan maskapai penerbangan yang berbeda memiliki deskripsi pekerjaan yang berbeda untuk staf darat mereka, tetapi dalam banyak kasus, staf darat dibebankan dengan tugas-tugas yang mengutamakan kenyamanan para penumpang.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Concierge Hotel</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Concierge atau Pramutamu bertindak sebagai penjaga utama, baik itu hotel butik kecil atau gedung tinggi yang besar. Pramutamu yang baik menggambarkan dirinya sebagai panutan untuk keunggulan layanan. Mereka dipercaya dengan bentuk akuntabilitas yang tinggi karena mereka bertanggung jawab atas interaksi orang-ke-orang sehari-hari. Mereka memanggil taksi, membuat reservasi, membantu dengan tas, menyarankan acara dan atraksi, dan banyak lagi. Ketika kamu mengunjungi kota baru dan menginap di hotel, tidak ada perasaan yang lebih baik daripada disambut dan diperhatikan.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Meskipun seorang pramutamu mungkin memiliki pengetahuan tentang kota mereka, mereka sering bekerja dalam ambiguitas setiap hari. Mereka memang memiliki tugas yang biasanya tetap sama, tetapi pasti ada sesuatu yang baru yang menghampiri mereka setiap harinya. Apa yang membuat pramutamu hebat adalah kemampuan mereka untuk tidak terpengaruh oleh \"sesuatu yang baru\" yang mungkin diberikan tamu kepada mereka. Pramutamu yang hebat melakukan ini dengan bersikap ramah tetapi tidak mengambil sesuatu terlalu pribadi.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Jurusan Perhotelan Kerja Apa? <strong>Sales Hotel Manager</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Sebagai Sales Hotel Manager, kamu akan bertanggung jawab untuk mengembangkan dan membina bisnis melalui penjualan langsung, pemasaran, pemasaran jarak jauh, surat langsung, panggilan janji temu, dan tur hotel yang proaktif. Juga mengembangkan rencana aksi strategis bagi hotel untuk mendorong pendapatan penjualan tambahan yang terukur.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Selain itu, kamu juga akan mengidentifikasi berbagai macam kebutuhan yang bisa digunakan untuk meningkatkan penjualan dan sewa di hotel tempat kamu bekerja.. Kamu juga akan dengan tim hotel individu untuk mengidentifikasi area pengembangan keterampilan dan menerapkan sumber daya penjualan dan pemasaran dengan benar.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Event Planner/Event Organizer</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Event Planner bertanggung jawab untuk mengatur acara perusahaan atau pribadi untuk perusahaan atau individu. Tugas mereka termasuk bertemu dengan klien untuk mendiskusikan kebutuhan mereka, memelihara kemitraan dengan vendor dan katering dan mengawasi pengaturan, pelaksanaan, dan pembersihan acara. Tugas dan tanggung jawab seorang Event Planner membutuhkan kemampuan untuk berkomunikasi dengan baik dengan pelanggan dan tempat. Perencana acara harus memperhatikan detail dengan menggunakan informasi dari beberapa sumber untuk merencanakan acara yang sukses.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Wah… banyak ya prospek karir jurusan perhotelan di masa depan. Maka dari itu, kamu tidak perlu bertanya-tanya lagi jurusan perhotelan kerja apa. Untuk bisa menjadi yang terhebat di karirmu, kamu juga butuh bekal ilmu terbaik. Maka dari itu, kamu harus mulai melengkapi segala persiapan agar sukses berkarir di bidang <em>hospitality</em>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ayo lengkapi persiapanmu menimba ilmu di jurusan perhotelan terbaik dengan Eduverse by ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download Panduan “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” untuk mencari tahu semua hal yang perlu kamu ketahui sebelum mendaftar beasiswa. GRATIS! <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/id/\">Download disini</a> </p>', 'Downloader.la-6322e906e0ad1.jpg', 'Bukan Cuman Tentang Hotel! Ayo Cari Tahu Jurusan Perhotelan Kerja Apa!', 'publish', '', 'Jurusan Perhotelan Kerja Apa', 'Apa kamu tertarik untuk berkarir di bidang yang sedang naik daun, kamu tidak perlu khawatir jurusan perhotelan kerja apa. Simak lengkapnya di sini!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-05-18 17:00:00', '2022-09-01 17:00:00', '2022-11-04 17:00:00'),
(12658, 'ayo-simak-rentetan-universitas-jurusan-perhotelan-terbaik-di-dunia', 2, 0, 'Ayo Simak Rentetan Universitas Jurusan Perhotelan Terbaik di Dunia!', '<p>Dengan semakin berkembangnya industri <em>hospitality</em>, hal ini membuat semakin banyak pelajar yang tertarik untuk menimba ilmu di bidang manajemen perhotelan. Jika kamu memang mempunyai ambisi untuk berkarir di jurusan perhotelan, kamu harus mendapatkannya dari tempat yang terbaik untuk bisa bersaing di kanca internasional. Ayo simak daftar universitas <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/ayo-cari-tahu-seluk-beluk-jurusan-perhotelan-di-artikel-ini/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"jurusan perhotelan (opens in a new tab)\">jurusan perhotelan</a> terbaik di dunia ini ya!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>EHL - Ecole hôtelière de Lausanne, Swiss</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>EHL adalah universitas jurusan perhotelan pertama di dunia. Kampus ini didirikan pada tahun 1893 dan dinamakan Ecole hôtelière de Lausanne. Pada tahun 2022, untuk keempat kalinya berturut-turut, EHL menduduki peringkat sekolah manajemen hotel terbaik dunia oleh QS World University Rankings for Hospitality and Leisure Management.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>EHL juga telah menerima penghargaan untuk “inovasi terbaik dalam pendidikan” di Worldwide Hospitality Awards 2019 untuk program Sarjana Manajemen Perhotelan Internasional. Kampus ini memberikan fasilitas dan kualitas pendidikan terbaik yang akan membekali para siswanya untuk bekerja di hotel terbaik di dunia.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>University of Nevada, Las Vegas</strong>; Universitas Jurusan Perhotelan</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>University of Nevada juga menyediakan jurusan perhotelan kepada para calon mahasiswanya. Kampus yang menyediakan jurusan tersebut bernama William F. Harrah College of Hospitality. Kampus ini merupakan institusi terbaik di bidang ini di Amerika Serikat. Universitas ini menggabungkan pendidikan kelas dunia dengan pengalaman dunia nyata. Siswa lulusan kampus ini dapat berhasil karena mereka telah menyelam dalam lingkungan belajar holistik yang secara unik mempersiapkan mereka untuk karir seumur hidup di bidang perhotelan dan pariwisata.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Mahasiswa UNLV Hospitality belajar dari beberapa pakar perhotelan paling terkenal di negara ini. Selain itu kampus ini terletak sangat dekat dengan pusat perhotelan dan dunia hiburan terbesar di Amerika Serikat, yaitu Las Vegas. Dengan tempat yang sangat dekat dengan jantung industri perhotelan ini, siswa mendapatkan akses langsung&nbsp; ke peluang magang dan bimbingan yang tidak tersedia di program lain. Di sisi lain, hubungan kuat perguruan tinggi dengan industri perhotelan berarti siswa lebih siap dan terhubung lebih baik untuk memulai karir mereka setelah lulus.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Les Roches Global Hospitality Education, Swiss</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Didirikan di Swiss pada tahun 1954, Les Roches merupakan salah satu universitas jurusan perhotelan terbaik yang menyediakan gelar sarjana dan pascasarjana di bidang perhotelan dan pariwisata. Universitas ini berada di peringkat 3 terbaik dari daftar universita jurusan perhotelan terbaik di dunia. Dengan masuk ke universitas ini, kamu akan mempunyai peluang karir yang gemilang nantinya. Hal ini dibuktikan dengan data yang mengatakan bahwa 94% lulusan dari universitas ini diterima di hotel-hotel terbaik di dunia.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Les Roches memiliki kampus di beberapa negara. Salah satunya ada di Crans-Montana (Swiss), Marbella (Spanyol), dan Shanghai (Cina). Sebagai tambahan, kampus ini menyediakan lingkungan belajar yang unik untuk badan mahasiswa yang beragam budaya, di mana lebih dari 100 kebangsaan yang berbeda diwakili.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Glion Institute of Higher Education, Swiss</strong>; Universitas Jurusan Perhotelan</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Sejak tahun 1962, Institut Pendidikan Tinggi Glion telah menetapkan standar tertinggi untuk kualitas akademik dan keunggulan di jurusan perhotelan. Saat ini, kampus ini dicap sebagai salah satu kampus terbaik di jurusan perhotelan.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dengan kampus-kampus di Swiss dan London, Glion memberikan pendidikan premium yang dipersonalisasi dengan menggabungkan keterampilan praktis dengan ketelitian akademis. Fakultas yang bisa kamu pilih telah memenangkan penghargaan bergengsi, mengajar di berbagai institusi dan bekerja di industri global. Badan mahasiswa di universitas ini juga sangat beragam, dengan banyak sekali pelajar internasional yang bergabung, kampus ini menjadi lingkungan yang sempurna untuk mengembangkan kefasihan antar budaya yang sangat dihargai dalam industri perhotelan.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>The Hong Kong Polytechnic University</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Jika kamu memang ingin mendalami ilmu di industri pariwisata dan perhotelan, Kamu harus berada di tempat yang tepat. Asia lah tempatnya. Benua ini merupakan kawasan pariwisata dengan pertumbuhan tercepat di dunia. Dengan peran kuncinya sebagai hub maskapai regional dan pintu gerbang ke Daratan China, perpaduan budaya Timur dan kecanggihan Barat yang semarak, tidak ada tempat yang lebih baik selain Hong Kong.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Selama lebih dari 40 tahun, universitas jurusan perhotelan ini telah menyempurnakan visi khas pendidikan perhotelan dan pariwisata dan menjadi simbol keunggulan di bidangnya. Universitas ini menjunjung tinggi kemajuan pengajaran, pembelajaran dan penelitian yang dapat menginspirasi generasi baru profesional mengambil posisi sebagai pemimpin dalam industri perhotelan dan pariwisata.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Cukup beragam bukan universitas jurusan perhotelan terbaik di dunia. Universitas ini tersebar di berbagai benua, mulai dari Asia, Eropa, dan Amerika. Dengan belajar di tempat ini, kamu akan mendapatkan kualitas pendidikan terbaik dengan peluang berkarir yang sangat tinggi lho. Jadi, kamu harus mempersiapkan semuanya untuk masuk ke salah satu universitas di atas ya!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tertarik untuk masuk ke universitas jurusan perhotelan terbaik di dunia? Eduverse by ALL-in akan siap untuk membantu persiapan akademikmu!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download Panduan “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” untuk mencari tahu semua hal yang perlu kamu ketahui sebelum mendaftar beasiswa. GRATIS! <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/id/\">Download disini</a> <br></p>', 'Downloader.la-6322eac4cead3.jpg', 'Ayo Simak Rentetan Universitas Jurusan Perhotelan Terbaik di Dunia!', 'publish', '', 'Universitas Jurusan Perhotelan', 'Apa kamu sudah tahu deretan universitas jurusan perhotelan terbaik di dunia? Ayo simak semua daftarnya di dalam artikel ini!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-05-19 17:00:00', '2022-09-21 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(12664, 'ayo-cari-tahu-seluk-beluk-jurusan-perhotelan-di-artikel-ini', 2, 0, 'Ayo Cari Tahu Seluk-Beluk Jurusan Perhotelan di Artikel ini!', '<p>Kamu mungkin sudah sering banyak dengar teman-temanmu tertarik untuk masuk jurusan perhotelan. Tapi kamu sudah tahu belum jurusan perhotelan itu apa dan bagaimana proyeksi ke depannya? Kalau belum, kamu datang ke tempat yang tepat! Ayo simak lebih dalam mengenai jurusan perhotelan di bawah ini!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Apa itu Jurusan Perhotelan?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan perhotelan adalah bidang luas yang melibatkan pengawasan kegiatan administrasi, operasional, dan komersial sehari-hari dari bisnis di industri perhotelan. Berbeda dengan “manajemen hotel” yang terfokus secara lebih sempit, jurusan perhotelan adalah istilah umum yang mencakup berbagai industri seperti makanan dan minuman, perjalanan dan akomodasi, serta manajemen acara. Bidang yang berada di dalam jurusan perhotelan dapat berkisar dari pemeliharaan dan tata graha hingga layanan spa, pramutamu, resepsi, dan banyak lagi.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Universitas Jurusan Perhotelan Terbaik</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Banyak sekali lho sekolah yang menyediakan jurusan ini yang bisa kamu pilih. Beberapa <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/ayo-simak-rentetan-universitas-jurusan-perhotelan-terbaik-di-dunia/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"universitas (opens in a new tab)\">universitas</a> bahkan ada yang menjanjikan karirmu di masa depan setelah lulus nanti. Ayo simak di bawah!</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>EHL - Ecole hôtelière de Lausanne, Swiss</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>EHL adalah universitas jurusan perhotelan pertama di dunia. Kampus ini didirikan pada tahun 1893 dan dinamakan Ecole hôtelière de Lausanne. Pada tahun 2022, untuk keempat kalinya berturut-turut, EHL menduduki peringkat sekolah manajemen hotel terbaik dunia oleh QS World University Rankings for Hospitality and Leisure Management.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>University of Nevada, Las Vegas</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>University of Nevada juga menyediakan jurusan perhotelan kepada para calon mahasiswanya. Kampus yang menyediakan jurusan tersebut bernama William F. Harrah College of Hospitality. Kampus ini merupakan institusi terbaik di bidang ini di Amerika Serikat. Universitas ini menggabungkan pendidikan kelas dunia dengan pengalaman dunia nyata. Siswa lulusan kampus ini dapat berhasil karena mereka telah menyelam dalam lingkungan belajar holistik yang secara unik mempersiapkan mereka untuk karir seumur hidup di bidang perhotelan dan pariwisata.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Les Roches Global Hospitality Education, Swiss</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Didirikan di Swiss pada tahun 1954, Les Roches merupakan salah satu universitas terbaik yang menyediakan gelar sarjana dan pascasarjana di bidang perhotelan dan pariwisata. Universitas ini berada di peringkat 3 terbaik dari daftar universitas terbaik di dunia. Dengan masuk ke universitas ini, kamu akan mempunyai peluang karir yang gemilang nantinya. Hal ini dibuktikan dengan data yang mengatakan bahwa 94% lulusan dari universitas ini diterima di hotel-hotel terbaik di dunia.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Penasaran dengan universitas lainnya? Semuanya ada di sini!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Prospek Karir Jurusan Perhotelan</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan perhotelan merupakan salah satu jurusan yang menjanjikan dalam segi karir. Ingin tahu apa saja <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/bukan-cuman-tentang-hotel-ayo-cari-tahu-jurusan-perhotelan-kerja-apa/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"karir (opens in a new tab)\">karir</a> yang bisa kamu capai di jurusan ini? Ayo simak di bawah ini!</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Wedding Organizer/Wedding Planner</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Wedding Planner</em> adalah seseorang yang akan mengurus segalanya mengenai logistik pernikahan. Hal ini mulai dari referensi vendor dan negosiasi kontrak hingga hari pelaksanaan pernikahan sang klien. Seorang perencana bertugas untuk melacak anggaran dan menangani logistik. Ini adalah keterampilan yang dapat dipelajari banyak orang, tetapi hanya perencana terbaik yang memiliki pengalaman bertahun-tahun dan kredensial yang menempatkan mereka di atas yang lainnya.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Staf Darat Maskapai Penerbangan</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Tidak ada bandara atau maskapai penerbangan yang dapat beroperasi secara berkelanjutan tanpa staf darat. Mereka adalah roda penggerak vital dalam roda industri penerbangan, dan mereka tidak dapat digantikan oleh komputer atau mesin. Ini berarti pekerjaan staf darat akan tetap ada di masa depan.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Concierge Hotel</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Concierge atau Pramutamu bertindak sebagai penjaga utama, baik itu hotel butik kecil atau gedung tinggi yang besar. Pramutamu yang baik menggambarkan dirinya sebagai panutan untuk keunggulan layanan. Mereka dipercaya dengan bentuk akuntabilitas yang tinggi karena mereka bertanggung jawab atas interaksi orang-ke-orang sehari-hari. Mereka memanggil taksi, membuat reservasi, membantu dengan tas, menyarankan acara dan atraksi, dan banyak lagi. Ketika kamu mengunjungi kota baru dan menginap di hotel, tidak ada perasaan yang lebih baik daripada disambut dan diperhatikan.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ingin tahu lebih banyak? Baca di sini ya!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan perhotelan memang merupakan salah satu jurusan paling menjanjikan di dunia. Kamu bisa mendapatkan banyak keterampilan dan juga karir yang gemilang di masa depan nanti. Yang perlu kamu persiapkan adalah untuk masuk ke universitas terbaik di dunia untuk bisa bersaing di kanca internasional.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Gapai mimpimu di jurusan perhotelan dengan Eduverse by ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download Panduan “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” untuk mencari tahu semua hal yang perlu kamu ketahui sebelum mendaftar beasiswa. GRATIS! <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/id/\">Download disini</a> <br></p>', 'Downloader.la-6322ecd508b5e.jpg', 'Ayo Cari Tahu Seluk-Beluk Jurusan Perhotelan di Artikel ini!', 'publish', '', 'Jurusan Perhotelan', 'Jurusan perhotelan merupakan salah satu jurusan yang paling diminati oleh hampir semua murid di seluruh dunia. Penasaran? Simak infonya di sini!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-05-17 17:00:00', '2022-09-22 17:00:00', '2022-11-04 17:00:00');
