(12685, 'cornell-university-acceptance-rate-the-complete-information', 1, 0, 'Cornell University Acceptance Rate: The Complete Information', '<p>Cornell University is a private Ivy League university, located in Ithaca, New York. Moreover, it was founded in 1865 by Andrew Dickson White and Ezra Cornell, the latter of whom the university&nbsp; was named after. Furthermore, the university is organized into seven undergraduate colleges and seven graduate divisions. Each&nbsp; college and division has&nbsp; its own admission standards and academic programs.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The school was built upon the intention to teach and contribute to all fields and aspects of knowledge. Also, it ranges from the math and sciences, the theoretical and&nbsp; applied, to&nbsp;the arts and classics.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Cornell University Acceptance Rate</h2>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/full-scoop-on-cornell-university-profile-just-for-you!/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Cornell University (opens in a new tab)\">Cornell University</a> is one of the most selective schools in the U.S., with an acceptance rate of 10.7%. The school\'s acceptance rate has fluctuated over the past few years, ranging from around 8 to 14%.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td><strong>Year</strong></td><td><strong>Acceptance Rate</strong></td></tr><tr><td>2017</td><td>13.47%</td></tr><tr><td>2018</td><td>10.9%</td></tr><tr><td>2019</td><td>14.9%</td></tr><tr><td>2020</td><td>14%</td></tr><tr><td>2021</td><td>8.7%</td></tr><tr><td>2022</td><td>20.8%</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Cornell University Applications and Admission Requirements</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Like most universities, Cornell University highlights the importance of education. Cornell&nbsp; University is one of the leading universities&nbsp; in terms of its academic quality. If you are considering&nbsp; applying to Cornell University, there are some dates and information you must note before applying. Moreover, you may add this date to your schedule to&nbsp; make sure that you prepare everything for the application. Furthermore, This is important to keep&nbsp; track of&nbsp; your progress and all the preparation.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Notable Dates</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td><strong>Important Dates</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Regular Decision</td><td>January 2</td></tr><tr><td>Early Decision Deadline</td><td>November 1</td></tr><tr><td>SAT/ACT Scores Must be Received by</td><td>January 2</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Application Fee</strong>: $80</li><li><strong>Common Application Accepted</strong>: Yes</li><li><strong>Deadline for Housing Deposit</strong>: N/A</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Admission Interview</strong>: Neither required nor recommended</li><li><strong>Required Standardized Tests</strong>: SAT/ACT not required</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h3>International Students</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are an international student, there are other&nbsp; things you must remember before applying to Cornell University, such as notable deadlines and required additional tests.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Application Deadline</strong>: Fall Intake, January 2</li><li><strong>Separate Application Form Required</strong>: No</li><li><strong>Conditional Admission Offered</strong>: No</li><li><strong>Advance Deposit Required</strong>: No</li><li><strong>TOEFL Accepted Instead of SAT or ACT</strong>: No</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h3>Required Tests</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>To&nbsp; apply to Cornell University, you may need to take required testsNo matter which test it is, you need to take it&nbsp; as seriously as possible. Below are&nbsp; some required tests that you may need to take:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td>Test</td><td>Requirements</td></tr><tr><td>TOEFL (paper)</td><td>Required</td></tr><tr><td>TOEFL (internet-based)</td><td>Required</td></tr><tr><td>Michigan Test</td><td>N/A</td></tr><tr><td>IELTS</td><td>Required</td></tr><tr><td>SAT</td><td>Considered</td></tr><tr><td>ACT</td><td>Considered</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>Conclusion</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Cornell University is a prestigious school that will surely boost your profile into your next career, but not many people can get in . Only those who are bright in academics and extracurriculars can get into the&nbsp; university. Therefore, you need to make sure that you have thoroughly prepare before applying to Cornell University.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Planning to study at Cornell University? Gear yourself up with ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” Guidebook to find out all the things you need to know before applying for scholarships. It\'s FREE, <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/\">download here</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top university preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!</p>', '7xm.xyz549524.jpg', 'Cornell University Acceptance Rate: The Complete Information', 'publish', '', 'Cornell University Acceptance Rate', 'Are you looking for Cornell University Acceptance Rate? Get the full insight in this article to kickstart your top university application!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-06-07 17:00:00', '2022-09-08 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(12689, 'cornell-university-ranking-your-guide-to-this-ivy-league-institution', 1, 0, 'Cornell University Ranking: Your Guide to This Ivy League Institution', '<p>Is Cornell University your dream study destination? Look no further! Situated in the hills of Ithaca, <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/full-scoop-on-cornell-university-profile-just-for-you!/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Cornell University\'s (opens in a new tab)\">Cornell University\'s</a> campus is a hotbed for innovation and collaboration. Moreover, with its classic brick buildings and stately grounds, it\'s no surprise that this Ivy League school has been named one of the most beautiful college campuses in America. In this article, we\'ll dive deep into the Cornell University ranking!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Cornell University, at a Glance&nbsp;</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>In 1865, Cornell University was founded by Ezra Cornell and Andrew Dickson White as a land-grant university. The university has since grown from its humble beginnings as a small college to what it is today: a large research institution with schools across Ithaca, New York, and Qatar.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As of September 2021, Cornell has been affiliated with 61 Nobel laureates, four Turing Award winners, and 63 Olympic Medalists. Since its founding, Cornell has been a co-educational school with no racial or religious requirements for admission. Also, Cornell boasts a diverse student body of nearly 26,000 students, with about 24% coming from abroad.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Cornell University Ranking</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>When it comes to its ranking, Cornell University stands 12th domestically and 20th globally according to the latest QS World University Rankings.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Applying to Cornell University</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Cornell has nine academic colleges, each with its academic requirements, admissions, and specialties. Before applying, you should pick a college that you would like to attend. Here are the nine Cornell undergraduate schools:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>College of Human Ecology</li><li>School of Industrial and Labor Relations (ILR)</li><li>College of Art, Architecture, and Planning</li><li>College of Arts and Sciences</li><li>Cornell Ann S. Bowers College of Computing and Information Science</li><li>College of Engineering</li><li>College of Agriculture and Life Sciences</li><li>Cornell SC Johnson College of Business: the Peter and Stephanie Nolan School of Hotel Administration (offers undergraduate, graduate, and professional degree programs), the Charles H. Dyson School of Applied Economics and Management (offers undergraduate, graduate, and professional degree programs), and the Samuel Curtis Johnson Graduate School of Management (offers only graduate and professional degree programs</li><li>Cornell Jeb E. Brooks School of Public Policy</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>While each Cornell college has its own majors and specific graduation requirements, some majors cross over multiple colleges. For example, the major of Biological Sciences is available in both the College of Arts and Sciences and the College of Agriculture and Life Sciences. Since the courses, specializations, and requirements for the major are similar across both colleges, it is advised to make your decision according to your secondary interests.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Common App</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>When applying to Cornell, you will use the Common Application (also known as the Common App), a centralized online portal for undergraduate applications. In addition to the Common App essays, you will also need to write two supplemental essays. Therefore each applicant can differentiate themselves and demonstrate their interest in attending Cornell.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are some prompts for Cornell\'s supplemental essays:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>College of Architecture, Art, and Planning:</strong> What is your \"thing\"? What energizes you or engages you so deeply that you lose track of time? Everyone has different passions, obsessions, quirks, and inspirations. What are yours?</li><li><strong>Cornell SC Johnson College of Business: </strong>What kind of a business student are you? Using your personal, academic, or volunteer/work experiences, describe the topics or issues that you care about and why they are important to you.&nbsp;</li><li><strong>College of Engineering:</strong> How do your interests directly connect with Cornell Engineering? If you have an intended major, what draws you to that department at Cornell Engineering? If you are unsure what specific engineering field to study, you should describe how your general interest in engineering directly connects with Cornell Engineering. It may be helpful to concentrate on one or two things that you are most excited about.</li><li><strong>School of Industrial and Labor Relations</strong>: Using your personal, academic, or volunteer/work experiences, describe the topics or issues that you care about and why they are important to you. Furthermore, your response should show us that your interests align with the ILR School.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are the undergraduate admissions deadline for Cornell\'s admissions:&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Early Decision: November 1</li><li>Financial Aid: November 1</li><li>Regular Decision: January 2</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Conclusion</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>While Cornell is among one of the most competitive schools in the world, it is possible to gain admission if you go the extra mile. After all, a Cornell student is not born overnight. In the end, it comes down to all the work you\'ve done throughout your four years of high school.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Planning to get into Cornell University? Get yourself prepared by having an <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/\">initial consultation</a> with ALL-in mentors now!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” Guidebook to find out all the things you need to know before applying for scholarships. It\'s FREE, <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/\">download here</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\"><strong>Admission Mentoring</strong></a><strong>.</strong></li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\"><strong>Career Exploration.</strong></a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\"><strong>Academic Tutoring.</strong></a></li><li>Highlight your personal brand through the <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/writing-skills/\"><strong>Writing Skills</strong></a><strong> </strong>improvement program.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', '7xm.xyz383092.jpg', 'Cornell University Ranking: Your Guide to This Ivy League Institution', 'publish', '', 'Cornell University Ranking', 'When you are talking about Cornell University Ranking, there are a lot of factors that you need to know. Learn the full info here!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-06-06 17:00:00', '2022-09-17 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(12692, 'cornell-university-master-program-heres-your-guide', 1, 0, 'Cornell University Master Program: Here’s Your Guide!', '<p>Cornell University has long been known as one of the most reputable universities in the world. According to the latest QS World University Rankings, Cornell ranked 20th best university in the world, making it an attractive option for those seeking to enter graduate programs. In this article, we will learn about the highly-coveted <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/full-scoop-on-cornell-university-profile-just-for-you!/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Cornell University (opens in a new tab)\">Cornell University</a> master\'s program!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Cornell University\'s Background</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Cornell University has its roots dating back to 1865 when Ezra Cornell and Andrew Dickson White founded it. Its main campus stretches across 2,300 acres of land in Ithaca, upstate New York. Cornell University is home to seven undergraduate colleges and seven graduate divisions. Each college and division has its own set of admissions standards and curriculum.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In addition to its picturesque Ivy League campus in Ithaca, New York, Cornell University has two satellite campuses. One is located in New York City, and the other is in Qatar\'s Education City.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Cornell\'s student body is made up of more than 23,000 students. Among those students, there are approximately 14,700 undergraduates and 6,200 graduates.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Cornell University Master\'s Program</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Nearly 100 areas of study are covered by the research and professional degrees offered by Cornell\'s Graduate School. Here are some of the popular graduate courses offered at Cornell:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>MBA at SC Johnson College of Business</li><li>M. Eng. Electrical and Computer Engineering at Cornell Tech</li><li>M.S. in Computer Science at Cornell Tech</li><li>M.S in Biomedical Engineering at Cornell Tech</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Learn more about the programs offered at Cornell <a href=\"https://www.cornell.edu/\">here</a>!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Admissions to Cornell</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Before landing in the Cornell University master program, you will need to submit an online application form. In your application, there are several things you must submit, including:&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Standardized test scores (Graduate Record Examination (GRE) and/or Graduate Management Admission Test (GMAT))</li><li>Letters of recommendation&nbsp;</li><li>Personal statement or statement of purpose</li><li>Transcripts&nbsp;</li><li>Resume or CV</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>To meet the language requirements, you must submit proof of your English language proficiency test scores (if you are an international student):</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td><strong>Accepted English Proficiency Tests&nbsp;</strong></td><td><strong>Minimum Scores Required&nbsp;</strong></td></tr><tr><td>IELTS (International English Language Testing System) Academic</td><td>Overall band score of&nbsp; 7.0 or higher<br><em>The IELTS score is valid within two years of your program\'s application deadline.</em></td></tr><tr><td>TOEFL (Test of English as a Foreign Language)</td><td>Speaking: 22<br>Reading: 20<br>Listening: 15<br>Writing: 20<br><em>The TOEFL score is valid within two years of your program\'s application deadline</em></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>These are the general English language test requirements for most Cornell programs.&nbsp; However, some courses may have higher requirements.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Tuition Fees</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are the latest tuition fees for the Cornell University master program:&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td><strong>Degree Type and Area</strong><strong>	</strong></td><td><strong>Tuition (per academic year)</strong></td></tr><tr><td>M.P.S. (Applied Statistics, AEM, Information Sciences, Real Estate)M.S. (Information Systems, AAD)</td><td>$62,456<br></td></tr><tr><td>M.H.A.&nbsp;M.I.L.R.M.L.A.M.P.A.M.P.H.M.R.P.M.S. (Nutrition, Atmospheric Science)</td><td>$40,888<br><br></td></tr><tr><td>Endowed Research Master\'s IthacaM.A.M.F.A.M.S.</td><td>$29,500<br><br></td></tr><tr><td>New York CityM.P.S.</td><td>$31,226</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>To sum up, if you present a strong applicant profile to the table, there is no harm in filling out a Cornell application. After all, the experiences and opportunities you will gain at Cornell will be unforgettable!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Considering applying to Cornell University\'s master\'s program? Come and get an <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/\">initial consultation</a> with ALL-in mentors now!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” Guidebook to find out all the things you need to know before applying for scholarships. It\'s FREE,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/\">download here</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\"><strong>Admission Mentoring</strong></a><strong>.</strong></li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\"><strong>Career Exploration.</strong></a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\"><strong>Academic Tutoring.</strong></a></li><li>Highlight your personal brand through the <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/writing-skills/\"><strong>Writing Skills</strong></a><strong> </strong>improvement program.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', '7xm.xyz337976.jpg', 'Cornell University Master Program: Here’s Your Guide!', 'publish', '', 'Cornell University Master Program', 'Cornell university master program is one of the most hot topic if you want to research of your further education. Learn the full insight here!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-06-08 17:00:00', '2022-09-02 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(12697, 'full-scoop-on-cornell-university-profile-just-for-you', 1, 0, 'Full Scoop on Cornell University Profile Just For You!', '<p>Cornell University is one of the best universities out there. Being accepted into this university is a big achievement for many students around the world. However, to be accepted by the university requires a lot of time and preparation. Take a look at the full information about Cornell University down below!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Cornell University</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Cornell University has its roots dating back to 1865 when it was founded by Ezra Cornell and Andrew Dickson White. Moreover, its main campus stretches across 2,300 acres of land in Ithaca, upstate New York. Furthermore, the university is home to seven undergraduate colleges and seven graduate divisions. Also, each college and division has its own set of admissions standards and curriculum.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In addition to its picturesque Ivy League campus in Ithaca, New York, Cornell University has two satellite campuses. Also, one is located in New York City, and the other is in Qatar\'s Education City.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Cornell\'s student body is made up of more than 23,000 students. Among those students, there are approximately 14,700 undergraduates and 6,200 graduates.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Cornell University Acceptance Rate</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Cornell University is one of the most selective schools in the U.S., with an <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/cornell-university-acceptance-rate:-the-complete-information/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"acceptance rate (opens in a new tab)\">acceptance rate</a> of 10.7%. The school\'s acceptance rate has fluctuated over the past few years, ranging from around 8 to 14%.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td><strong>Year</strong></td><td><strong>Acceptance Rate</strong></td></tr><tr><td>2017</td><td>13.47%</td></tr><tr><td>2018</td><td>10.9%</td></tr><tr><td>2019</td><td>14.9%</td></tr><tr><td>2020</td><td>14%</td></tr><tr><td>2021</td><td>8.7%</td></tr><tr><td>2022</td><td>20.8%</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Cornell University Applications and Admission Requirements</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Like most universities, this university highlights the importance of education. Furthermore, Cornell is one of the leading universities in terms of its quality. If you are thinking about applying to Cornell University, there are some dates and information you must note before applying. Furthermore, you may add this date to your schedule to make sure that you prepare everything for the application. Moreover, this is important to stay on track with your progress and all the preparation.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Notable Dates</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td><strong>Important Dates</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Application Deadline</td><td>January 2</td></tr><tr><td>Early Decision Deadline</td><td>November 1</td></tr><tr><td>SAT/ACT Scores Must Be Received By</td><td>January 2</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Application Fee</strong>: $80</li><li><strong>Common Application Accepted</strong>: Yes</li><li><strong>Deadline for Housing Deposit</strong>: N/A</li><li><strong>Admission Interview</strong>: Neither required/recommended</li><li><strong>Required Standardized Tests</strong>: Neither SAT nor ACT</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Read here for further information about the acceptance rate!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Cornell University Master\'s Program&nbsp;</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Nearly 100 areas of study are covered by the research and professional degrees offered by Cornell\'s Graduate School. Moreover, here are some of the popular graduate courses offered at Cornell:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>MBA at SC Johnson College of Business</li><li>M. Eng. Electrical and Computer Engineering at Cornell Tech</li><li>M.S. in Computer Science at Cornell Tech</li><li>M.S in Biomedical Engineering at Cornell Tech</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Admissions Into Cornell Master\'s Program</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Before landing in the <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/cornell-university-master-program:-here\'s-your-guide!/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Cornell University master program (opens in a new tab)\">Cornell University master program</a>, you will need to submit an online application form. In your application, there are several things you must submit, including: </p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Standardized test scores (Graduate Record Examination (GRE) and/or Graduate Management Admission Test (GMAT))</li><li>Letters of recommendation&nbsp;</li><li>Personal statement or statement of purpose</li><li>Transcripts&nbsp;</li><li>Resume or CV</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Interested in going into the master program at Cornell? Read here!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Cornell University Ranking</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>When it comes to the <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/cornell-university-ranking:-your-guide-to-this-ivy-league-institution/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Cornell University ranking (opens in a new tab)\">Cornell University ranking</a>, it stands 12th domestically and 20th globally according to the latest QS World University Rankings. With a top ranking comes an equally high standard. Furthermore, Cornell University has successfully provided students with a great quality of education. Also, there are a lot of outstanding undergraduate colleges that you can choose from.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Cornell University College</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Cornell has nine academic colleges, each with its own academic requirements, admissions, and specialties. Before applying, you should pick the one you would like to attend. Here are the nine Cornell undergraduate colleges:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>College of Human Ecology</li><li>School of Industrial and Labor Relations (ILR)</li><li>College of Art, Architecture, and Planning</li><li><span style=\"background-color: rgb(225, 190, 231);\">College of Arts and Sciences</span></li><li>Cornell Ann S. Bowers College of Computing and Information Science</li><li>College of Engineering</li><li>College of Agriculture and Life Sciences</li><li>Cornell SC Johnson College of Business: the Peter and Stephanie Nolan School of Hotel Administration, the Charles H. Dyson School of Applied Economics and Management, and the Samuel Curtis Johnson Graduate School of Management</li><li>Cornell Jeb E. Brooks School of Public Policy</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>While each Cornell college has its own majors and specific graduation requirements, there are some majors that cross over multiple colleges. Moreover, for example, the major of Biological Sciences is available in both the College of Arts and Sciences and the College of Agriculture and Life Sciences. Since the courses, specializations, and requirements for the major are similar across both colleges, it is advised to make your decision according to your secondary interests.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Want to learn more about Cornell University Ranking? Find out here!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Conclusion</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>As part of the Ivy League, Cornell is as hard as it gets when we are talking about the application. You need to prepare everything and make sure that you get the admission officer\'s attention. Even though the challenge is great, the benefits from the university are greater. By attending a top university such as Cornell, you will find better careers and opportunities..</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Have a plan to apply to Cornell University? Prepare yourself with an <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/\">initial consultation</a> with ALL-in mentors now!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” Guidebook to find out all the things you need to know before applying for scholarships. It\'s FREE, <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/\">download here</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\"><strong>Admission Mentoring</strong></a><strong>.</strong></li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\"><strong>Career Exploration.</strong></a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\"><strong>Academic Tutoring.</strong></a></li><li>Highlight your personal brand through the <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/writing-skills/\"><strong>Writing Skills</strong></a><strong> </strong>improvement program.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!</p>', '7xm.xyz410745.jpg', 'Full Scoop on Cornell University Profile Just For You!', 'publish', '', 'Cornell University', 'Cornell University is one of the most prestigious university out there. If you are aiming to be the university, this is the insight for you!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-06-05 17:00:00', '2022-09-09 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(12707, 'ayo-simak-4-alasan-kamu-wajib-kuliah-jurusan-gizi', 2, 0, 'Ayo Simak 4 Alasan Kamu Wajib Kuliah Jurusan Gizi', '<p>Jurusan gizi merupakan salah satu jurusan yang mempunyai banyak kontribusi di bidang kesehatan. Untuk kamu yang belum tahu, di luar sana ada banyak sekali orang dengan kondisi khusus yang harus memperhatikan asupan makanan mereka dengan cermat agar mereka bisa kembali sehat. Dengan begitu, ahli gizi berperan untuk membantu mereka kembali sehat lewat asupan makanan yang sudah disesuaikan. Masih belum yakin ingin kuliah<a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/fakta-lengkap-seputar-jurusan-gizi-yang-wajib-kamu-tahu/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" jurusan gizi (opens in a new tab)\"> jurusan gizi</a>? Ayo simak beberapa alasan keren lainnya di bawah ini!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Industri yang Sedang Booming</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Di jaman ini, orang-orang sudah mulai paham mengenai pentingnya kesehatan. Hal ini lah yang membuat industri ini semakin booming dari hari ke hari. Pada tahun 2001, ahli ekonomi Paul Zane Pilzer meramalkan industri kesehatan akan menjadi industri triliunan dolar berikutnya. Dan dia benar!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Menurut Australian Financial Review, industri kesehatan global diperkirakan mencapai US$4,5 triliun. Diet yang sempurna telah menjadi standar hidup kesehatan banyak orang di luar sana. Selain itu juga, banyak orang yang sudah paham akan pentingnya makan bersih, jus, <em>superfood</em>, mylks, suplemen, rutinitas perawatan kulit dan perawatan diri, berolahraga di gym, butik, yoga, dan meditasi. Selain nilai moneter, industri ini berkembang pesat karena merupakan sebuah dorongan yang positif dan didukung oleh banyak orang di luar sana.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Alasan Kuliah Jurusan Gizi; <strong>Aplikasi di Kehidupan Nyata</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Kamu akan memiliki kekuatan untuk mempengaruhi masa depan makanan dan kesehatan. Seperti yang kita ketahui, makanan bergizi sangat diminati lebih dari sebelumnya. Orang-orang di seluruh dunia menampilkan pola nutrisi favorit mereka di media sosial.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ketika orang menjadi lebih sadar akan kesehatan, mempelajari nutrisi dapat membantu kamu memahami pola-pola kesehatan dan membedakan mana kandungan yang baik dari yang buruk. Gelar yang kamu dapat akan memungkinkan kamu untuk mendidik orang dan menginspirasi cara berpikir baru, serta memicu perdebatan kritis dan membantu masyarakat menjadi lebih sehat.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Pemahaman Mendalam Mengenai Nutrisi</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Asam amino, lipid, mikronutrien, larut, tidak larut. Apakah kamu pernah membaca atau mendengar istilah industri dan kompleksitas nutrisi? Kenapa tidak ada yang pernah membuatnya mudah bagi kita untuk mengerti? Dengan kuliah di jurusan gizi, kamu akan mendapatkan banyak informasi dan pengetahuan mendalam tentang berbagai kompleksitas nutrisi.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Nutrisi bertanggung jawab untuk hampir semua hal di dalam tubuh manusia. Maka dari itu dengan kamu mendalami pengetahuan mengenai nutrisi, hal ini akan memungkinkan kamu untuk terjun langsung di dunia kesehatan. Lihatlah contohnya di rumah sakit. Ketika kamu sedang rawat inap, apa kamu pernah bingung kenapa makanan yang diberikan porsinya khusus dan berbagai macam? Hal ini karena makanan itu sudah dirancang oleh ahli gizi untuk memenuhi semua nutrisi yang kamu butuhkan.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Alasan Kuliah Jurusan Gizi; <strong>Kualitas Hidup yang Lebih Baik</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Pertimbangkan berapa banyak uang yang kamu habiskan setiap tahun untuk janji temu dengan dokter, spesialis, atau bahkan praktisi holistik. Bagaimana jika ada cara yang lebih sederhana untuk meningkatkan kualitas hidupmu sendiri? Dengan kuliah di jurusan gizi, pengetahuan dan pendidikan kamu dapatkan akan mampu kamu gunakan untuk dapat mengatasi masalah kesehatan apa pun pada sumbernya dan mulai menjalani kehidupan yang lebih sehat. Di sisi lain, kamu juga mempengaruhi orang-orang di sekitar kamu untuk menyusun pola hidup sehat dimulai dari makanan yang akan dimakan. Bagaimanapun juga, mencegah lebih baik daripada mengobati, bukan?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Keren-keren kan manfaat yang bisa kamu dapatkan dari kuliah jurusan gizi? Semua ini dapat membantumu menopang hidupmu sendiri untuk kualitas yang lebih baik atau bahkan berkarir di bidang kesehatan, seperti menjadi ahli gizi. Tapi, jangan lupa! Kamu harus berani bermimpi untuk kuliah di jurusan gizi agar kamu mendapatkan ilmu yang terbaik juga.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ayo kuliah di jurusan gizi terbaik di dunia! Persiapkan semuanya bersama Eduverse by ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!</p>\n\n\n\n<p> Download Panduan “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” untuk mencari tahu semua hal yang perlu kamu ketahui sebelum mendaftar beasiswa. GRATIS! <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/id/\">Download disini</a> </p>', '7xm.xyz667591.jpg', 'Ayo Simak 4 Alasan Kamu Wajib Kuliah Jurusan Gizi', 'publish', '', 'Kuliah Jurusan Gizi', 'Penasaran apa saja yang bisa kamu dapatkan dari kuliah jurusan gizi? Ayo baca semua info lengkapnya hanya di artikel ini ya!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-05-22 17:00:00', '2022-09-09 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(12713, 'berikut-adalah-5-universitas-jurusan-gizi-terbaik-di-asia', 2, 0, 'Berikut adalah 5 Universitas Jurusan Gizi Terbaik di Asia', '<p>Dengan beragamnya makanan sehat yang ada di Asia, sudah tidak diragukan lagi bahwa Asia merupakan salah satu tempat terbaik untuk kamu kuliah di jurusan ini. Dengan belajar <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/fakta-lengkap-seputar-jurusan-gizi-yang-wajib-kamu-tahu/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"jurusan gizi (opens in a new tab)\">jurusan gizi</a>, kamu akan mendapatkan banyak manfaat yang luar biasa untuk dirimu sendiri dan orang lain. Tapi, kamu sangat perlu untuk mendapatkan ilmu terbaik dari tempat yang terbaik. Ayo simak daftar universitas jurusan gizi terbaik di Asia berikut ini!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Nanjing Agricultural University</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Nanjing Agricultural University (NAU) adalah salah satu universitas ilmu pertanian tertua dan paling bergengsi di Tiongkok di bawah administrasi Kementerian Pendidikan. Akar paling awal dari universitas dapat ditelusuri kembali ke 1902 ke Department of Agriculture of Sanjiang Normal School. Sekolah ini menjadi pelopor pendidikan pertanian modern, penelitian dan penyuluhan dan pelopor program sarjana empat tahun dalam pendidikan pertanian tinggi di Cina. Dengan pengalaman mempelajari dan meneliti semua aspek yang berhubungan dari bahan pokok, universitas ini menjadi salah satu tempat terbaik untuk belajar semua hal mengenai gizi.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Universitas Jurusan Gizi Terbaik; <strong>China Agricultural University</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Bertempat di Beijing, China Agricultural University adalah universitas pertanian tertua di negara Tiongkok. Didirikan sebagai Sekolah Tinggi Pertanian pada tahun 1905, menjadi China Agricultural University setelah penggabungan Republik Rakyat Tiongkok dibentuk pada tahun 1949. Kemudian bergabung dengan Beijing Agricultural Engineering University pada tahun 1995, menjadi China Agricultural University, seperti yang dikenal sekarang. Universitas ini menempati urutan keempat di daftar universitas jurusan gizi terbaik di Asia.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Putra Malaysia University</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Universiti Putra Malaysia (UPM) sebelumnya bernama Universiti Pertanian Malaysia didirikan pada tahun 1971 melalui penggabungan Fakultas Pertanian, Universitas Malaya dan Sekolah Tinggi Pertanian di Serdang. Tiga fakultas pendiri pertama adalah Fakultas Pertanian, Fakultas Kehutanan dan Fakultas Kedokteran Hewan dan Ilmu Peternakan. UPM mempertahankan peran tradisional pendidikannya dalam memfokuskan penelitian tingkat tersiernya pada pertanian dan bidang-bidang yang relevan. Di awal tahun 80-an, UPM telah memperluas cakupannya dengan memasukkan ilmu pengetahuan dan teknologi ke dalam bidang studinya. Hingga saat ini, kampus ini telah menjadi salah satu universitas terbaik untuk mempelajari bidang gizi dan nutrisi. Universitas ini juga menempati urutan ketiga terbaik di Asia untuk jurusan ini.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Universitas Jurusan Gizi Terbaik; <strong>Zhejiang University</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Zhejiang University berfokus pada studi dan penelitian yang serta inovasi sains dan teknologi. Universitas ini telah meluncurkan sejumlah platform akademik kelas atas internasional dan mengumpulkan master dan tim peneliti tingkat tinggi yang merupakan ahli di bidangnya masing-masing. Dalam beberapa tahun terakhir, Zhejiang University mempertahankan posisi terdepan di Tiongkok dalam indikator keluaran termasuk publikasi, paten, dan lain-lain, dan telah membuat banyak pencapaian penting dalam sains, teknologi, humaniora, dan ilmu sosial. Universitas ini telah menempati urutan kedua dari daftar universitas jurusan gizi terbaik di Asia.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Jiangnan University</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Jiangnan University adalah salah satu universitas negeri terbaik di Wuxi, Cina. Universitas ini terdiri dari 18 sekolah dan 51 program sarjana dengan disiplin ilmu termasuk teknik, sains, sastra, ekonomi, manajemen, hukum, kedokteran, pertanian, seni, dan pendidikan. Dengan sistem pendidikan yang luar biasa, beberapa jurusan yang ada di universitas ini masuk ke 1% yang terbaik di dunia. Beberapa jurusan itu adalah biologi, kimia, dan biokimia. Untuk jurusan pertaniannya, universitas ini masuk ke 0.4% terbaik di dunia. Sudah jelas kan, seberapa hebat dan bagusnya jurusan gizi di universitas ini?<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Bagus-bagus banget ya universitas jurusan gizi terbaik di Asia? Universitas-universitas ini tidak hanya memberikan kualitas pendidikan yang terbaik lho. Semuanya memberikan kualitas pelayanan dan fasilitas terbaik di dunia. Dijamin, setelah lulus dari sini, kamu mampu berlari dengan cemerlang dan bersaing di kancah internasional.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ingin masuk ke salah satu universitas di atas? Ayo gabung Eduverse by ALL-in sekarang!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p> Download Panduan “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” untuk mencari tahu semua hal yang perlu kamu ketahui sebelum mendaftar beasiswa. GRATIS! <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/id/\">Download disini</a> <br></p>', '7xm.xyz624777-1.jpg', 'Berikut adalah 5 Universitas Jurusan Gizi Terbaik di Asia', 'publish', '', 'Universitas Jurusan Gizi', 'Jika kamu ingin melanjutkan kuliah, mungkin daftar universitas jurusan gizi ini perlu untuk kamu lihat. Ayo simak lengkapnya di sini!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-05-21 17:00:00', '2022-09-12 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(12722, 'fakta-lengkap-seputar-jurusan-gizi-yang-wajib-kamu-tahu', 2, 0, 'Fakta Lengkap seputar Jurusan Gizi yang Wajib Kamu Tahu!', '<p>Apa kamu tertarik untuk masuk dan belajar jurusan gizi? Jurusan ini menyimpan banyak sekali manfaat yang bisa kamu dapatkan lho. Tidak hanya dari ilmu yang berkualitas dan bisa dipakai kapanpun, tapi juga dari karir yang cemerlang di masa depan. Ayo cari tahu lebih banyak mengenai jurusan gizi di bawah ini!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Apa Itu Jurusan Gizi?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan gizi mempelajari hubungan antara nutrisi dalam makanan dan kesehatan manusia. Di sini kamu akan mengeksplorasi bagaimana nutrisi dan makanan dari mana mereka berasal membantu tubuh dalam pertumbuhan dan perkembangan dan dalam menjaga kesehatan dan kebugaran. Mahasiswa dengan jurusan ini sering dapat memilih dari beberapa jalur dan konsentrasi - seperti nutrisi umum atau ilmu gizi, kesehatan masyarakat atau nutrisi masyarakat, pra-pengobatan, atau dietetika. Penjurusan yang kamu pilih tentunya bergantung pada tujuan karir yang kamu pilih.Dengan kepedulian nasional dan internasional terhadap dampak makanan dan gizi pada kesehatan dan kesejahteraan serta penyakit, ada banyak peluang karir bagi lulusan program ini. Terlebih lagi, mahasiswa dengan jurusan ini akan dilengkapi dengan ilmu dan keterampilan untuk menjadi ahli diet dan ahli gizi.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Alasan Kamu harus Masuk ke Jurusan Gizi</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Butuh alasan lagi untuk masuk ke jurusan gizi? Ayo simak manfaat yang bisa kamu dapatkan di bawah ini!</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Industri yang Sedang Booming</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Di jaman ini, orang-orang sudah mulai paham mengenai pentingnya kesehatan. Hal ini lah yang membuat industri ini semakin booming dari hari ke hari. Pada tahun 2001, ahli ekonomi Paul Zane Pilzer meramalkan industri kesehatan akan menjadi industri triliunan dolar berikutnya. Dan dia benar!&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Menurut Australian Financial Review, industri kesehatan global diperkirakan mencapai US$4,5 triliun. Diet yang sempurna telah menjadi standar hidup kesehatan banyak orang di luar sana. Selain itu juga, banyak orang yang sudah paham akan pentingnya makan bersih, jus, <em>superfood</em>, mylks, suplemen, rutinitas perawatan kulit dan perawatan diri, berolahraga di gym, butik, yoga, dan meditasi. Selain nilai moneter, industri ini berkembang pesat karena merupakan sebuah dorongan yang positif dan didukung oleh banyak orang di luar sana.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Aplikasi di Kehidupan Nyata</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Kamu akan memiliki kekuatan untuk mempengaruhi masa depan makanan dan kesehatan. Seperti yang kita ketahui, makanan bergizi sangat diminati lebih dari sebelumnya. Orang-orang di seluruh dunia menampilkan pola nutrisi favorit mereka di media sosial.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ketika orang menjadi lebih sadar akan kesehatan, mempelajari nutrisi dapat membantu kamu memahami pola-pola kesehatan dan membedakan mana kandungan yang baik dari yang buruk. Gelar yang kamu dapat akan memungkinkan kamu untuk mendidik orang dan menginspirasi cara berpikir baru, serta memicu perdebatan kritis dan membantu masyarakat menjadi lebih sehat.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ingin tahu manfaat lainnya? Baca di sini!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Universitas Jurusan Gizi Terbaik</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Untuk bisa mendapatkan ilmu yang terbaik, kamu juga harus masuk ke universitas terbaik. Berikut adalah daftar <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/berikut-adalah-5-universitas-jurusan-gizi-terbaik-di-asia/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"universitas terbaik untuk jurusan gizi (opens in a new tab)\">universitas terbaik untuk jurusan gizi</a>:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Nanjing Agricultural University</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Nanjing Agricultural University (NAU) adalah salah satu universitas ilmu pertanian tertua dan paling bergengsi di Tiongkok di bawah administrasi Kementerian Pendidikan. Akar paling awal dari universitas dapat ditelusuri kembali ke 1902 ke Department of Agriculture of Sanjiang Normal School. Sekolah ini menjadi pelopor pendidikan pertanian modern, penelitian dan penyuluhan dan pelopor program sarjana empat tahun dalam pendidikan pertanian tinggi di Cina. Dengan pengalaman mempelajari dan meneliti semua aspek yang berhubungan dari bahan pokok, universitas ini menjadi salah satu tempat terbaik untuk belajar semua hal mengenai gizi.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>China Agricultural University</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Bertempat di Beijing, China Agricultural University adalah universitas pertanian tertua di negara Tiongkok. Didirikan sebagai Sekolah Tinggi Pertanian pada tahun 1905, menjadi China Agricultural University setelah penggabungan Republik Rakyat Tiongkok dibentuk pada tahun 1949. Kemudian bergabung dengan Beijing Agricultural Engineering University pada tahun 1995, menjadi China Agricultural University, seperti yang dikenal sekarang. Universitas ini menempati urutan keempat di daftar universitas jurusan gizi terbaik di Asia.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Putra Malaysia University</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Universiti Putra Malaysia (UPM) sebelumnya bernama Universiti Pertanian Malaysia didirikan pada tahun 1971 melalui penggabungan Fakultas Pertanian, Universitas Malaya dan Sekolah Tinggi Pertanian di Serdang. Tiga fakultas pendiri pertama adalah Fakultas Pertanian, Fakultas Kehutanan dan Fakultas Kedokteran Hewan dan Ilmu Peternakan. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>UPM mempertahankan peran tradisional pendidikannya dalam memfokuskan penelitian tingkat tersiernya pada pertanian dan bidang-bidang yang relevan. Di awal tahun 80-an, UPM telah memperluas cakupannya dengan memasukkan ilmu pengetahuan dan teknologi ke dalam bidang studinya. Hingga saat ini, kampus ini telah menjadi salah satu universitas terbaik untuk mempelajari bidang gizi dan nutrisi. Universitas ini juga menempati urutan ketiga terbaik di Asia untuk jurusan ini.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ingin tahu universitas lainnya? Lihat lebih lengkap di sini!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Conclusions</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Lengkap kan informasi mengenai jurusan gizi? Jika kamu sudah menetapkan hatimu di jurusan ini, kamu juga harus lebih berani untuk mengambil langkah ke depan untuk mempersiapkan masa depanmu. Kamu harus punya ambisi untuk masuk ke jurusan gizi terbaik di dunia!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Butuh bantuan untuk mempersiapkan masa depanmu di jurusan gizi? Eduverse by ALL-in akan membantumu!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download Panduan “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” untuk mencari tahu semua hal yang perlu kamu ketahui sebelum mendaftar beasiswa. GRATIS!&nbsp;<a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/id/\">Download disini</a> <br></p>', '7xm.xyz675124.jpg', 'Fakta Lengkap seputar Jurusan Gizi yang Wajib Kamu Tahu!', 'publish', '', 'Jurusan Gizi', 'Apa kamu tertarik untuk melanjutkan kuliahmu di jurusan gizi. Ayo simak informasi lengkap dan menyeluruh mengenain jurusan gizi di sini!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-05-20 17:00:00', '2022-09-18 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00');
