(12784, 'complete-list-of-famous-columbia-university-graduates', 1, 0, 'Complete List of Famous Columbia University Graduates', '<p>As one of the best universities out there, Columbia University graduates are leaving their mark on the world. They are part of the best and brightest people who achieve something that no one thought was possible. Curious? Let\'s take a look at the list of notable <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/full-overview-on-columbia-university-profile/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Columbia (opens in a new tab)\">Columbia </a>University graduates.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>1. Barack Obama</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>By becoming the country\'s first African American president, Barack Obama made history in the United States of America. Obama worked extremely hard to represent his country with pride, enacting new financial legislation and fostering better connections with other nations. He enacted policies to combat climate change, save the environment, and support female entrepreneurs. Barack Obama is one of Columbia University\'s illustrious alumni. In 1979, he enrolled at Occidental College to begin his study in Political Science. He then went to Columbia University where he majored in Political Science with English Literature and an emphasis in International Relations.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>2. Amelia Earhart</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Millions of women were inspired by Amelia Earhart. Not only was she the first woman aviator to fly across the Atlantic, she was also a writer. Also, the best-selling novel in America was her book, which detailed her aviation experiences. Furthermore, the renowned American aviator was enrolled in Columbia University for medical studies. She also advocated for women to defy restrictive social standards, which encouraged more women to enter the aviation industry. She was a true representation of female empowerment.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>3. Franklin Delano Roosevelt</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>From 1933 until his passing in 1945, Franklin Delano Roosevelt, also known by his initials FDR, was a politician and attorney from the United States. He was the 32nd president of the country. During the beginning of the 20th century, he played a major role in global events as a member of the Democratic Party and won a record number of presidential elections. Moreover, he established the New Deal Coalition, which for the middle third of the 20th century characterized modern liberalism in the United States, as a dominating leader of his party.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>4. Ruth Bader Ginsburg</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>From 1993 until her passing in 2020, Joan Ruth Bader Ginsburg, an American lawyer and judge, was a member of the Supreme Court of the United States as an associate justice. Furthermore, as a moderate consensus builder at the time of her nomination by President Bill Clinton to succeed retiring justice Byron White, she was well-liked. She subsequently joined the Court\'s liberal wing as the Court\'s conservative majority grew over time. After Sandra Day O\'Connor, Ginsburg was the second woman and first Jewish person to serve on the Supreme Court.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>5. Alexander Hamilton</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>American revolutionary, politician, and one of the country\'s founding fathers, Alexander Hamilton is one of the most influential Columbia University graduates. Hamilton was also the founding member of The Federalist Party, the United States Coast Guard, the nation\'s financial system, and the New York Post newspaper. He was also a prominent constitutional translator and advocate. Moreover, Hamilton was a key contributor to the economic policy of President George Washington\'s administration as the first secretary of the treasury.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>There are a lot more Columbia University graduates with amazing feats like the people above. Furthermore, you can be one of the next people on the list, or you can create your own mark on the world. It is all possible due to the great quality of education and various opportunities that you can find in Columbia University.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Excited to get into Columbia University? Take your first <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/\">initial consultation</a> with ALL-in mentors today!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” Guidebook to find out all the things you need to know before applying for scholarships. It\'s FREE, <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/\">download here</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\"><strong>Admission Mentoring</strong></a><strong>.</strong></li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\"><strong>Career Exploration.</strong></a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\"><strong>Academic Tutoring.</strong></a></li><li>Highlight your personal brand through the <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/writing-skills/\"><strong>Writing Skills</strong></a><strong> </strong>improvement program.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'GetPaidStock.com-63368e0a9becb.jpg', 'Complete List of Famous Columbia University Graduates', 'publish', '', 'Columbia University Graduates', 'Columbia University graduates is filled with a lot of names that have a great impact for the world. Read this article to know the famous figures!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-06-12 17:00:00', '2022-09-24 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(12789, 'columbia-university-rankings-the-new-york-based-ivy-league-university', 1, 0, 'Columbia University Rankings: The New-York Based Ivy League University', '<p>What do Barack Obama, Jake Gyllenhaal, and Warren Buffett have in common? They all went to Columbia University! On top of its well regarded education, <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/full-overview-on-columbia-university-profile/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Columbia (opens in a new tab)\">Columbia</a> is known as one of the most selective Ivy League schools. So, are you planning to study there? In this article, we\'ll learn more about the Columbia University rankings!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Columbia University, at a glance&nbsp;</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The founding of King\'s College in 1754 by the royal charter of George II of Great Britain marked the beginning of Columbia. Later, in 1784, it adopted the name Columbia College. Since then, Columbia has grown into a highly prestigious university.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Currently, there are three undergraduate schools in Columbia, which includes The Fu Foundation School of Engineering and Applied Science, Columbia College, and the School of General Studies. Columbia is also made up of several graduate and professional schools, including the highly ranked Business School, Teachers College, and College of Physicians and Surgeons.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Columbia University Rankings</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>When it comes to the Columbia University rankings, it stands 7th in the United States and 22nd globally according to the latest QS World University Rankings.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are a few of the Columbia subjects, according to the QS World University Rankings by subjects, that are among the top 15 worldwide:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Arts and Humanities - 7th&nbsp;</li><li>Law and Legal Studies - 8th&nbsp;</li><li>English Language and Literature - 9th&nbsp;</li><li>Economics and Econometrics - 12th</li><li>Mathematics - 15th&nbsp;</li><li>Psychology - 12th&nbsp;</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Applying to Columbia University</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Being an Ivy League school, Columbia is known for having a low acceptance rate. In the latest undergraduate admissions cycle, the university accepted less than 4% of its applicants! Moreover, below is the table showing Columbia\'s recent undergraduate admissions statistics:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td><strong>Admissions cycle&nbsp;</strong></td><td><strong>Total Applicants</strong><strong>	</strong></td><td><strong>Accepted Students</strong><strong>	</strong></td><td><strong>Acceptance rate&nbsp;</strong></td></tr><tr><td>2021&nbsp;</td><td>63,318</td><td>2,577</td><td>4%</td></tr><tr><td>2020</td><td>40,083</td><td>2,544</td><td>6%</td></tr><tr><td>2019</td><td>42,569</td><td>2,245</td><td>5%</td></tr><tr><td>2018&nbsp;</td><td>40,203</td><td>2,260</td><td>6%</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>If you\'re planning to apply to Columbia, there are three application systems that Columbia accepts:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>The Coalition Application</li><li>The Common Application</li><li>The QuestBridge Application from QuestBridge Finalists</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>You will have to pay a non-refundable $85 fee for your Columbia application. Here are several requirements you need to submit when applying to Columbia University:&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Supplemental essays&nbsp;</li><li>High school transcripts&nbsp;</li><li>Standardized test scores</li><li>Columbia-specific application questions</li><li>English proficiency test scores</li><li>Teacher recommendations</li><li>Supplementary materials (if applicable)</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>The following shows the minimum score required for the English Language Proficiency tests:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td><strong>English Proficiency test</strong></td><td><strong>Minimum score required&nbsp;</strong></td></tr><tr><td>TOEFL (Test of English as a Foreign Language) iBT&nbsp;</td><td>Minimum of 105</td></tr><tr><td>IELTS (International English Language Testing System)</td><td>Minimum of 7.5</td></tr><tr><td>DET (Duolingo English Test)</td><td>Minimum of 125</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>There are two application deadlines for undergraduate admission at Columbia:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td><strong>Decision plan</strong></td><td><strong>Deadline&nbsp;</strong></td><td><strong>Decision notification</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Restrictive Early Action&nbsp;</td><td>1 November</td><td>Mid-December&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td>Regular Decision</td><td>1 January&nbsp;</td><td>Early April</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Admissions essays to get into Columbia</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>To get a more holistic view of applicants, you will also need to respond to Columbia-specific questions. In your essays, you can go into greater detail about your academic and extracurricular interests. As an applicant, you can also express why you are the perfect candidate for Columbia and how you can contribute to the Columbia community.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are some sample prompts of Columbia\'s supplemental essays:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>A hallmark of the Columbia experience is being able to learn and live in a community with a wide range of perspectives. How do you or would you learn from and contribute to diverse, collaborative communities? (200 words or fewer)</li><li>List the titles of the required readings from academic courses that you enjoyed most during secondary/high school. (75 words or fewer)</li><li>Why are you interested in attending Columbia University? We encourage you to consider the aspect(s) that you find unique and compelling about Columbia. (200 words or fewer)</li><li>Please tell us what from your current and past experiences (either academic or personal) attracts you specifically to the areas of study that you noted in the application. (200 words or fewer)</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Being a prestigious school, gaining admission to Columbia may seem out of reach. Despite this, with the right amount of preparation and dedication, you could soon be on your way to be a Columbia student!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Planning to study in Columbia? Get advice on your application by booking an <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/\">initial consultation</a> with ALL-in mentors now!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” Guidebook to find out all the things you need to know before applying for scholarships. It\'s FREE, <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/\">download here</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top uni preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', '7xm.xyz826923.jpg', 'Columbia University Rankings: The New-York Based Ivy League University', 'publish', '', 'Columbia University Rankings', 'Columbia University rankings is one of the best information that you need to maximize your application there. Get the full scoop here!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-06-11 17:00:00', '2022-09-14 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(12792, 'the-ultimate-guide-to-columbia-university-master-programs', 1, 0, 'The Ultimate Guide To Columbia University Master Programs', '<p>If you\'re planning to further your study in the United States, Columbia University should top your list. The school has a reputation for being one of the best universities in the world, with its rankings consistently high on various reputable lists. <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/full-overview-on-columbia-university-profile/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Columbia (opens in a new tab)\">Columbia</a> also boasts its exceptional education across various programs, from business administration to engineering and law. In this article, we\'ll go over the Columbia University Master Programs!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>A glance at Columbia University</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Columbia University in the city of New York, more commonly known as Columbia University, is a private university in the United States. Founded as King\'s College in 1754 and a member of the Ivy League since its inception in 1956, Columbia has grown into twenty schools: four undergraduate schools and sixteen graduate schools.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Situated across 32 acres of land in Morningside Heights, Columbia\'s historic main campus have of 71 buildings. Furthermore, most of Columbia\'s undergraduate and graduate classes are in here.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Columbia is home to a large and diverse student body, with about 6,398 undergraduate students and 24,412 postgraduate students. To this date, the institution has produced four US presidents, 99 Nobel laureates, and 25 Pulitzer Prize recipients.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Columbia University Master Programs</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Every graduate school at Columbia has its own curriculum and set of requirements, but they share a commitment to excellence in education. Of all 16 Columbia\'s graduate schools, 19% are part-time students.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are some of the highly-ranked Columbia University graduate schools:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Columbia Business School</strong>&nbsp;</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>In the US News 2023 Best Business Schools rankings, Columbia Business School is ranked 8th. Moreover, Founded in 1916 as a professional business training institute, Columbia Business School is best known for its MBA programs. Furthermore, the school offers a wide range of concentrations, including accounting, consulting, general management, health care administration, international business, and real estate. Also, Columbia Business School has a highly selective admissions process; of 6,033 applicants, only 948 students got accepted.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Columbia Law School</strong>&nbsp;</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Columbia Law School is in fourth place on the list of the US News Best Law Schools for 2023. The school offers several degree options: Juris Doctor (J.D.), a one-year Master of Laws (LL.M.), and Doctor of the Science of Law (J.S.D.). For students interested in pursuing multidisciplinary studies, the school also offers a wide range of joint or dual degree programs, including the well-known J.D. or M.B.A. programs with Columbia Business School.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Columbia Climate School&nbsp;</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Recently established in 2021, the Climate School is the first new school to be established at the university in 25 years. Moreover, Columbia University\'s school of climate research currently offers eight master programs.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Columbia University School of Nursing</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>On the list of the top nursing schools according to US News for 2023. Columbia University Nursing School is in sixth place. Furthermore, founded in 1892, Columbia University School of Nursing is one as one of the oldest nursing schools in the United States. There are a number of degree programs which are available for the training of Registered Nurses, Nurse Practitioners, Certified Nurse Midwives, Nurse Anaesthetists, Clinical Nurse Leaders, and Nurse-Scientists.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>School of International and Public Affairs</strong>&nbsp;</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The Columbia University Nursing School is the 23rd of the best among the top public affairs schools by US News for 2023. Furthermore, Columbia\'s School of International and Public Affairs offers two master degrees. Moreover, this is including business leaders, journalists, diplomats, and elected representatives.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Now that you are familiar with Columbia University\'s graduate schools, will you consider studying there? Remember that once you earn your Columbia degree, all of your efforts will be worth it!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Have a dream in continuing your study in Columbia? Let\'s prepare yourself with ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” Guidebook to find out all the things you need to know before applying for scholarships. It\'s FREE, <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/\">download here</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top uni preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!</p>', '7xm.xyz664233-1.jpg', 'The Ultimate Guide To Columbia University Master Programs', 'publish', '', 'Columbia University Master Programs', 'Interested to know more about the Columbia University master programs to pursue your further education? Read all in this article!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-06-10 17:00:00', '2022-09-08 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(12796, 'full-overview-on-columbia-university-profile', 1, 0, 'Full Overview on Columbia University Profile!', '<p>Columbia University is one of the most prestigious schools in the USA. There are a lot of students fighting their way into the university with thorough preparation and a lot of internship experience. Are you one of them? If so, check out the full profile about the university below!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Columbia University</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Columbia University in the city of New York, more commonly known as Columbia University, is a private university in the United States. Founded as King\'s College in 1754 and a member of the Ivy League since its inception in 1956, Columbia has grown into twenty schools: four undergraduate schools and sixteen graduate schools.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Situated across 32 acres of land in Morningside Heights, Columbia\'s historic main campus is made up of 71 buildings. Furthermore, most of Columbia\'s undergraduate and graduate classes are conducted here.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Columbia University Rankings</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>When it comes to <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/columbia-university-rankings-the-new-york-based-ivy-league-university/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Columbia University\'s rankings (opens in a new tab)\">Columbia University\'s rankings</a>, it stands 7th domestically and 22th globally according to the latest QS World University Rankings. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are a few of the Columbia subjects that, according to the QS World University Rankings by subjects, are among the top 15 worldwide:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Arts and Humanities - 7th&nbsp;</li><li>Law and Legal Studies - 8th&nbsp;</li><li>English Language and Literature - 9th&nbsp;</li><li>Economics and Econometrics - 12th</li><li>Mathematics - 15th&nbsp;</li><li>Psychology - 12th&nbsp;</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h3>Applying to Columbia University</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Being an Ivy League school, Columbia is known for having a low acceptance rate. In the latest undergraduate admissions cycle, the university accepted less than 4% of applicants! Moreover, below is the table showing Columbia\'s recent undergraduate admissions statistics:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td><strong>Admissions cycle&nbsp;</strong></td><td><strong>Total Applicants</strong><strong>	</strong></td><td><strong>Accepted Students</strong><strong>	</strong></td><td><strong>Acceptance rate&nbsp;</strong></td></tr><tr><td>2021&nbsp;</td><td>63,318</td><td>2,577</td><td>4%</td></tr><tr><td>2020</td><td>40,083</td><td>2,544</td><td>6%</td></tr><tr><td>2019</td><td>42,569</td><td>2,245</td><td>5%</td></tr><tr><td>2018&nbsp;</td><td>40,203</td><td>2,260</td><td>6%</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>If you\'re planning to apply to Columbia, there are three application systems that Columbia accepts:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>The Coalition Application</li><li>The Common Application</li><li>The QuestBridge Application from QuestBridge Finalists</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Need to know more about the subject ranking and the application? Read full here!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Columbia University Master Programs</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Every graduate school at Columbia has its own curriculum and set of requirements, but they share a commitment to excellence in education. Moreover, of all 16 <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/the-ultimate-guide-to-columbia-university-master-programs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Columbia\'s graduate schools (opens in a new tab)\">Columbia\'s graduate schools</a>, 19% are part-time students.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are some of the highly-ranked Columbia University graduate schools:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Columbia Business School</strong>&nbsp;</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>In the US News 2023 Best Business Schools rankings, Columbia Business School is ranked 8th. Moreover, founded in 1916 as a professional business training institute, Columbia Business School is best known for its MBA programs. Furthermore, the school offers a wide range of concentrations, including accounting, consulting, general management, health care administration, international business, and real estate. Columbia Business School has a highly selective admissions process; of 6,033 applicants, only 948 students got accepted.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Columbia Law School</strong>&nbsp;</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Columbia Law School is placed fourth on the list of the US News Best Law Schools for 2023. Furthermore, the school offers several degree options: Juris Doctor (J.D.), a one-year Master of Laws (LL.M.), and Doctor of the Science of Law (J.S.D.). For students interested in pursuing multidisciplinary studies, the school also offers a wide range of joint or dual degree programs, including the well-known J.D. or M.B.A. programs with Columbia Business School.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Columbia Climate School&nbsp;</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Recently established in 2021, the Climate School is the first new school to be established at the university in 25 years. Moreover, Columbia University\'s school of climate research currently offers eight master programs.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Find the complete info about the Master Programs here!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Notable Columbia University Graduates</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>In researching a university thoroughly, you may feel that you need to know about its alumni and your predecessors. Furthermore, Columbia University is home to many talented and bright students with the ability to change the world. Check out the notable alumni for the university:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>1. Barack Obama</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>By becoming the country\'s first African American president, Barack Obama made history in the United States of America. Moreover, Obama worked extremely hard to represent his country with pride around the world, enacting new financial legislation and fostering better connections with other nations. Furthermore, he enacted policies to combat climate change, save the environment, and support female entrepreneurs. Also, Barack Obama is one of the illustrious alumni of Columbia University. In 1979, he enrolled at Occidental College to begin his academic study in Political Science. He then went to Columbia University where he majored in Political Science with English literature and an emphasis in International Relations.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>2. Ameila Earhart</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Millions of women were inspired by Amelia Earhart. Not only was she the first woman aviator to fly across the Atlantic ocean, she was also a writer. Furthermore, the best-selling novel in America was her book, which detailed her aviation experiences. Moreover, The famous American aviator was enrolled in Columbia University for medical studies. She also advocated for women to defy restrictive social standards, which encouraged more women to enter the aviation industry. She was a true representation of female empowerment.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Interested to know more alumni from Columbia University? Read all here!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Now you have a better understanding of the Columbia University profile. As you can see, there are a lot of aspects that you need to learn if you want to pursue a further education there. What is important is that you prepare everything thoroughly before you start applying to Columbia University.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Need help preparing for Columbia University? Let\'s prepare yourself with ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” Guidebook to find out all the things you need to know before applying for scholarships. It\'s FREE, <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/\">download here</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top uni preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!</p>', '7xm.xyz685893.jpg', 'Full Overview on Columbia University Profile!', 'publish', '', 'Columbia University', 'Are looking to find out about the best information regarding Columbia University? Find the complete insight in this article!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-06-09 17:00:00', '2022-09-22 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(12799, 'daftar-universitas-jurusan-teknik-informatika-terbaik-di-australia', 2, 0, 'Daftar Universitas Jurusan Teknik Informatika Terbaik di Australia', '<p>Apa kamu tertarik untuk belajar lebih dalam mengenai komputer dan perangkat lunak? Kalau iya, artinya kamu akan cocok jika belajar di jurusan teknik informatika. Untuk bisa bersaing di dunia profesional dan bisa bekerja di perusahaan teknologi yang terkenal, kamu perlu membekali diri dengan kualitas pendidikan yang cukup baik juga. Maka dari itu, kamu harus masuk ke universitas <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/simak-semua-info-lengkap-tentang-jurusan-teknik-informatika/\">jurusan teknik informatika</a> terbaik pula. Ayo simak daftar lengkapnya di bawah ini!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Universitas Jurusan Teknik Informatika Terbaik; <strong>Australian National University</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Australian National University didirikan pada tahun 1946. Kampus utama yang bernama “Acton” terletak di ibu kota Australia, Canberra. Akomodasi universitas tersedia untuk mahasiswa sarjana dan pascasarjana; dalam satu tahun terakhir, lebih dari 20 persen mahasiswa universitas tinggal di kampus. Mahasiswa sarjana tahun pertama dari luar wilayah Canberra akan mendapatkan fasilitas tempat tinggal gratis selama belajar di universitas ini.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Di ANU School of Computing, para mahasiswa akan belajar dengan komunitas siswa, guru, dan peneliti inovatif. Di sini, para mahasiswa juga akan berada di lingkungan positif yang berkualitas untuk masa depan mereka. ANU berada di peringkat pertama di Australia dan ke-21 di dunia untuk Graduate Employability menurut Global University Employability Ranking 2017. Artinya, lulusan dari universitas ini akan mendapatkan banyak tawaran pekerjaan setelah selesai belajar di universitas ini.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>University of New South Wales</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>UNSW Sydney adalah universitas terkemuka dunia di bidang penelitian, pembelajaran, dan inovasi. Didirikan pada tahun 1949, jumlah mahasiswa di universitas ini sudah bertumbuh hingga 64.000 mahasiswa yang berasal dari 130 negara. Universitas ini juga mempunyai komunitas alumni yang kuat yang berjumlah lebih dari 300.000 orang.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>UNSW berada di peringkat ketiga di Australia untuk Graduate Employability. Jadi, kamu tidak perlu khawatir lagi dengan pencarian pekerjaanmu di masa depan nanti. Selain itu, universitas ini merupakan satu-satunya universitas yang diundang untuk bergabung di Global Alliance of Technological Universities.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Universitas Jurusan Teknik Informatika Terbaik; <strong>University of Sydney</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>University of Sydney didirikan dengan prinsip memberi setiap orang kesempatan untuk mewujudkan potensi mereka melalui pendidikan dan masih memegang keyakinan itu dengan kuat hingga saat ini. Dengan kurikulum sarjana yang dirancang sempurna, fasilitas canggih, pengajaran dan pembelajaran kelas dunia, dan kehidupan kampus yang dinamis, institusi ini sangat cocok untuk mahasiswa yang ingin memperoleh kualifikasi yang diakui dan dihormati secara global.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Universitas menawarkan berbagai disiplin ilmu terluas di Australia dan penelitiannya berfokus pada menemukan solusi untuk tantangan terbesar masyarakat. Dengan lebih dari 400 bidang studi yang dapat dipilih, siswa memiliki fleksibilitas untuk mengikuti minat mereka, memperluas keterampilan mereka, dan mengejar kesempatan magang dan pertukaran global.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>University of Adelaide</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>University of Adelaide adalah lembaga penelitian dan pengajaran kelas dunia yang berpusat pada penemuan pengetahuan baru, mengejar inovasi dan mempersiapkan pemimpin masa depan yang terdidik.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sebagai universitas tertua ketiga di Australia, kampus memiliki reputasi yang mapan untuk keunggulan dan pemikiran progresif. Hal ini berlanjut hingga hari ini, dengan Universitas dengan bangga menempati peringkat satu persen teratas, di antara elit dunia. Secara lokal universitas ini diakui sebagai kontributor penting bagi kesehatan, kekayaan, dan kehidupan budaya di Australia Selatan. Sebagai tambahan, alumni University of Adelaide berisi lebih dari 100 Rhodes Scholars dan 5 Peraih Nobel.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Universitas Jurusan Teknik Informatika Terbaik; <strong>University of Technology Sydney</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>UTS dikenal luas karena pendekatan pembelajaran dan pengajarannya yang inovatif, yang memadukan pengalaman online dan tatap muka terbaik. Siswa mendapat manfaat dari pendidikan yang berfokus pada karir yang mendalam, ditambah dengan hubungan yang kuat dengan industri.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Keren-keren kan universitas jurusan teknik informatika terbaik di Australia? Beberapa kampus di atas bahkan masuk ke daftar terbaik di dunia lho. Tapi, untuk bisa masuk ke universitas di atas, kamu perlu mempersiapkan semuanya sebaik mungkin. Mulai dari nilai akademik hingga beberapa kebutuhan lainnya.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tertarik masuk ke universitas top di atas? Ayo gabung ke Eduverse by ALL-in sekarang!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Download Panduan “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” untuk mencari tahu semua hal yang perlu kamu ketahui sebelum mendaftar beasiswa. GRATIS! <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/id/\">Download disini</a> </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!<br></p>', '7xm.xyz396810.jpg', 'Daftar Universitas Jurusan Teknik Informatika Terbaik di Australia', 'publish', '', 'Universitas Jurusan Teknik Informatika', 'Apa kamu ingin meneruskan kuliah di jurusan teknik informatika? Ayo simak daftar universitas jurusan teknik informatika terbaik di artikel ini!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-05-24 17:00:00', '2022-09-10 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(12806, '5-manfaat-kuliah-jurusan-teknik-informatika-yang-bisa-kamu-dapatkan', 2, 0, '5 Manfaat Kuliah Jurusan Teknik Informatika yang Bisa Kamu Dapatkan', '<p>Masih ragu-ragu untuk kuliah jurusan teknik informatika? Tenang aja, wajar kok untuk memperhitungkan semuanya sebelum menetapkan pilihan di jurusan tersebut. Jurusan ini sebenarnya menyimpan banyak manfaat dan keuntungan yang bisa kamu petik lho. Penasaran? Ayo kita cari tahu lebih mengenai manfaat kuliah <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/simak-semua-info-lengkap-tentang-jurusan-teknik-informatika/\">jurusan teknik informatika</a> di bawah ini!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Semuanya Sudah Menggunakan Komputer</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Tidak ada industri di luar sana yang tidak menggunakan data dan teknologi komputer setiap hari. Semuanya, mulai dari keuangan dan perbankan, aplikasi game dan <em>smartphone</em>, hingga perawatan kesehatan dan keamanan, semuanya memerlukan komputer. Artinya, ilmu yang akan kamu pelajari di jurusan ini akan sangat relevan untuk masa depan nanti.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dengan menuntut ilmu di jurusan ini kamu juga sudah tidak perlu khawatir mengenai peluang kerja di masa depan. Pasalnya, semua kebutuhan untuk menjalankan sebuah perusahaan atau organisasi juga memerlukan ilmu ini untuk setiap harinya.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Kuliah Jurusan Teknik Informatika Memebrikan <strong>Kesempatan Untuk Mengubah Dunia</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Pengetahuan TI yang akan kamu dapatkan di perguruan tinggi akan memungkinkanmu membuat aplikasi dan program yang memiliki peluang untuk mengubah dunia. Aplikasi seperti PayPal atau Uber telah mengubah gaya hidup jutaan orang di seluruh dunia. Kamu juga memiliki kesempatan untuk membuat revolusi atau menjadi salah satu orang yang mengerjakan inovasi yang akan membawa umat manusia ke depan.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Kemungkinan Tinggi Untuk Bekerja Remote atau Jarak Jauh</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Menurut Survei Pengembang Stack Overflow 2019 yang diikuti oleh 70 ribu responden 51,8% programmer bekerja secara <em>remote</em> atau setidaknya beberapa hari setiap bulan. 12% dari semua programmer tersebut bahkan bekerja penuh waktu dari jarak jauh. Ada banyak tawaran pekerjaan jarak jauh untuk lulusan ilmu komputer dan banyak kemungkinan untuk bisnis mandiri dan aktivitas lepas, yang dapat dijalankan oleh orang yang ahli di bidang ilmu komputer.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Kuliah Jurusan Teknik Informatika Memberikan<strong> Keahlian yang Berguna</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Dengan mempelajari ilmu komputer, kamu akan memperoleh keterampilan yang akan memperluas wawasan dan menjadikanmu seorang profesional yang sangat berharga yang akan dipekerjakan oleh banyak perusahaan. Selain itu, kamu akan mendapatkan kesempatan untuk menciptakan hal-hal menakjubkan dari hasil programmu. Kamu akan mendapatkan pengetahuan dan keterampilan yang akan dapat diterapkan di masa depan untuk memfasilitasi dan mempercepat banyak proses.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Mengembangkan Diri Sendiri</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Kamu akan merasakan seberapa menakjubkannya menjadi siswa di jurusan teknik informatika yang berkembang dengan luar biasa. Banyak siswa datang ke tahun pertama studi sebagai anak-anak, masih hidup dengan biaya orang tua mereka, dan setelah 2 tahun mereka menemukan pekerjaan yang baik yang mereka lakukan paruh waktu setelah kelas dan mulai mendapatkan penghasilan sebanyak orang yang bekerja penuh waktu saat masih menjadi siswa.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Selain itu, belajar di jurusan teknik informatika dapat mengembangkan imajinasi dan keterampilan matematika yang ketat dan mengajarkan cara memecahkan masalah sulit secara efisien. Salah satu manfaat terbesar dari dari belajar di jurusan ini adalah pemecahan masalah, yang merupakan keterampilan penting untuk kehidupan. Keterampilan ini berguna di kemudian hari dan memungkinkanmu untuk menyelesaikan masalah dengan pragmatis dan logis.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Pengertian Lebih Mengenai Dunia Digital</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Masing-masing dari kita membawa komputer atau bahkan beberapa komputer setiap hari (<em>smartphone</em>, laptop, jam tangan pintar, dll.) tetapi hampir tidak ada yang tahu apa sebenarnya komputer ini dan seberapa besar dan menakjubkan kemampuannya. Ilmu komputer menjadi semakin penting di setiap bidang kehidupan – mulai dari memanggang roti hingga penelitian ilmiah tingkat lanjut. Dengan kuliah di jurusan teknik informatika, kamu akan semakin sadar tentang segala macam aspek digital dan pentingnya keamanan digital.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Manfaat yang bisa kamu petik dari jurusan informatika ada sangat banyak. Selain itu, kamu juga akan mendapatkan keuntungan di masa depan yang luar biasa seperti lapangan pekerjaan yang sangat luas. Untuk itu, kamu perlu mendapat gelar yang diakui oleh seluruh dunia agar bisa bersaing di dunia professional.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ingin kuliah di jurusan teknik informatika? Eduverse by ALL-in akan membantu seluruh persiapanmu!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Download Panduan “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” untuk mencari tahu semua hal yang perlu kamu ketahui sebelum mendaftar beasiswa. GRATIS! <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/id/\">Download disini</a> </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!</p>', '7xm.xyz141986.jpg', '5 Manfaat Kuliah Jurusan Teknik Informatika yang Bisa Kamu Dapatkan', 'publish', '', 'Kuliah Jurusan Teknik Informatika', 'Apa kamu tertarik untuk melanjutkan kuliah di jurusan teknik informatika? Simak beberapa manfaat kuliah teknik informatika di artikel ini!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-05-23 17:00:00', '2022-09-24 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(12811, 'prospek-kerja-jurusan-teknik-informatika-di-masa-depan', 8, 0, 'Prospek Kerja Jurusan Teknik Informatika di Masa Depan!', '<p>Ilmu yang kamu bisa dapatkan di jurusan teknik informatika sangat dicari oleh banyak perusahaan di luar sana. Selain itu, ada banyak sekali posisi yang bisa kamu pilih untuk memulai karirmu. Ingin tahu lebih lanjut? Ayo simak prospek kerja <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/simak-semua-info-lengkap-tentang-jurusan-teknik-informatika/\">jurusan teknik informatika</a> yang bisa kamu pilih di bawah ini!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Menurut U.S. Bureau of Labor Statistics, lulusan ilmu komputer akan merasakan stabilitas pekerjaan seiring dengan meningkatnya permintaan akan profesional ilmu komputer yang berkualitas. Diperkirakan bahwa pekerjaan terkait komputer dan teknologi informasi akan tumbuh sebesar 11 persen antara 2019 dan 2029, yang secara signifikan lebih tinggi daripada 5 persen dari pekerjaan lain.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Computer and Information Systems Manager</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Individu dalam peran ini merencanakan, mengkoordinasikan, dan mengarahkan kegiatan yang berhubungan dengan komputer dalam suatu organisasi. Mereka membantu menentukan tujuan teknologi informasi untuk organisasi dan bertanggung jawab untuk menerapkan sistem komputer untuk memenuhi tujuan ini. Karir ini membutuhkan pengalaman tambahan di luar gelar sarjana, itulah sebabnya ini merupakan pilihan karir yang populer bagi mereka yang memiliki gelar master dalam ilmu komputer.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Computer and Information Research Scientist</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Salah satu tanggung jawab dari para peneliti di jurusan teknik informatika adalah merancang teknologi baru dan menyelidiki cara agar teknologi yang ada dapat digunakan kembali untuk memecahkan masalah modern atau membuat hidup menjadi lebih mudah. Ilmuwan penelitian komputer dan informasi menerapkan konsep teoritis untuk merancang perangkat lunak dan arsitektur komputer baru, menemukan bahasa pemrograman dan alat baru, dan melakukan eksperimen untuk menguji keefektifan teknologi yang mereka rancang. Jika kamu tertarik untuk menjadi peneliti dan memecahkan masalah, kamu mungkin akan cocok untuk memilih karir ini.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Prospek Kerja Jurusan Teknik Informatika; <strong>Information Security Analyst</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Analis keamanan informasi merencanakan dan melaksanakan langkah-langkah keamanan untuk melindungi jaringan dan sistem komputer organisasi. Peran ini merupakan salah satu yang paling penting terutama pada perusahaan teknologi. Semakin hari, semakin banyak serangan digital yang mengancam informasi penting yang dimiliki perusahaan dan pengguna. Maka dari itu, posisi ini merupakan posisi yang akan selalu dicari banyak perusahaan di luar sana.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Software Development Engineer</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Pekerjaan paling populer yang dilakukan lulusan dari jurusan teknik informatika adalah pengembangan perangkat lunak. Insinyur pengembangan perangkat lunak, juga disebut SDE, membuat kode dan membangun perangkat lunak di berbagai industri, baik secara mandiri di perusahaan start-up atau sebagai bagian dari tim dalam organisasi yang lebih besar, seperti di Google atau Amazon. Peran dari posisi ini sangat penting untuk perkembangan perusahaan teknologi.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Database Administrator</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Database administrator, juga disebut DBA, memastikan bahwa data organisasi disimpan dan diatur dengan benar sehingga aman dan mudah diakses oleh Data Scientist atau Data Analyst. Orang-orang ini mengembangkan <em>database</em> baru dan memelihara <em>database</em> yang ada, membuat perubahan yang diperlukan untuk meningkatkan efisiensi. Database Administrator diharapkan mahir dalam perangkat lunak manajemen <em>database</em> umum dan bahasa <em>database</em> seperti SQL dan perlu memiliki keterampilan analitis dan pemecahan masalah yang kuat.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Prospek Kerja Jurusan Teknik Informatika; <strong>Data Scientist</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ilmuwan data merancang proses pemodelan data untuk membuat algoritma dan model prediktif serta melakukan analisis khusus di berbagai industri. Karena ilmu data adalah bidang yang berkembang pesat, profesional yang terampil langka, organisasi terkemuka mengandalkan profesional dengan gelar yang lebih tinggi. Tanggung jawab di jurusan ini adalah menganalisa data penjual agar mempermudah dan memperlancar strategi marketing yang akan digunakan perusahaan.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Lapangan pekerjaan untuk jurusan teknik informatika memang terbuka dengan luas untukmu. Jika kamu memperdalam ilmu komputer didalam dan diluar kelas, kamu akan menyadari bahwa prospek kerja jurusan teknik informatika ada banyak dan beragam di luar sana. Untuk bisa memulai karir di bidang ini, kamu perlu untuk menimba ilmu di universitas yang terbaik juga.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ayo mulai persiapanmu di universitas terbaik di jurusan ini dengan Eduverse by ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Download Panduan “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” untuk mencari tahu semua hal yang perlu kamu ketahui sebelum mendaftar beasiswa. GRATIS! <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/id/\">Download disini</a> <br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!<br></p>', '7xm.xyz610455-1.jpg', 'Prospek Kerja Jurusan Teknik Informatika di Masa Depan!', 'publish', '', 'Prospek Kerja Jurusan Teknik Informatika', 'Apa kamu ingin tahu apa saja prospek kerja jurusan teknik informatika di masa depan nanti? Simak daftar lengkapnya di artikel ini!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-05-25 17:00:00', '2022-09-19 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00');
