(13205, 'kyoto-university-scholarship-you-need-to-check-on', 1, 0, 'Kyoto University Scholarship You Need to Check On!', '<p>As one of the world\'s most advanced countries, Japan is a popular destination for students who plan to take their studies to the next level. Furthermore, it is home to cutting-edge technology, excellent research, and top-notch universities. Also, even with its high cost of living, studying in Japan shouldn\'t be much of a problem, especially with scholarship schemes available for international students. In this article, we\'ll dive deep into the <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/lets-get-to-know-about-the-full-kyoto-university-info/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Kyoto University (opens in a new tab)\">Kyoto University</a> Scholarship scheme!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Kyoto University, at a Glance&nbsp;</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Kyoto University was established on 18 June 1897 as the second university established in Japan. Moreover, it is located in the historic city of Kyoto, famously known as Japan\'s hub of culture and technology. Furthermore, it was within an era of rapid growth in culture, technology, and industry that Kyoto University was established.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To this day, the university is famous throughout Japan and around the world for its unique culture of academic freedom and for being at the forefront of cutting-edge research. Moreover, Kyoto University is made up of 10 faculties, 18 graduate schools, and 13 research institutions.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kyoto University currently houses 22,600 students, with 9,600 students taking their graduate studies and 13,000 students pursuing their bachelor\'s degrees. When it comes to international students, there are about 2,715 enrolled at&nbsp; Kyoto University.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Kyoto University Scholarship #1: Japanese Government (Monbukagakusho: MEXT) Scholarships</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The first Kyoto University scholarship is the Japanese Government MEXT Scholarship. Furthermore, this scholarship gains its funding from the Japanese Ministry of Education, Culture, Sports, Science, and Technology. This scholarship is available for international students who are:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Pursuing their undergraduate studies&nbsp;</li><li>Research students (graduate-degree students and non-degree students)</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>To be eligible for the Japanese Government (Monbukagakusho: MEXT) Scholarship, you must meet the following requirements:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Undergraduate students</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>At least 17 and under 24 years of age&nbsp;</li><li>Have graduated, or expect to graduate, from a secondary school or equivalent</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Research students</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Under 34 years of age&nbsp;</li><li>Have graduated, or expect to graduate, from an undergraduate or higher degree program</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>What does the Japanese Government (Monbukagakusho: MEXT) Scholarship cover?</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Undergraduate students</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Monthly stipend of 117,000 Yen</li><li>Full coverage of tuition fees (including examination and admission fees)</li><li>One round-trip ticket</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Research students</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Monthly stipend of 143,000 Yen for non-degree students and 144,000 Yen for master\'s and professional degree students</li><li>Full coverage of tuition fees (including examination and admission fees)</li><li>One round-trip ticket</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>The application period for undergraduate students is in April - May, and late December to January for research students.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Kyoto University Scholarship #2: AEON Scholarship</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Another Kyoto University scholarship is the AEON Scholarship, which is an allowance-based scholarship for university students. Also, the scholarship program, which is for students in several Asian nations, was established in 2006 with the hope that awardees would actively contribute to their respective specialist fields in the future.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To be eligible for the AEON Scholarship, you must meet the following requirements:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Be a student from China (including Hong Kong), Malaysia, Thailand, Taiwan, Indonesia, Philippines, Vietnam, Cambodia, Laos, Myanmar, or Bangladesh majoring in any subject other than religion or politics</li><li>Undergraduate students - Under 30 years of age</li><li>Master\'s students - Under 35 years of age&nbsp;</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>What does the AEON Scholarship cover?</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Undergraduate students</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Monthly stipend of 100,000 Yen</li><li>Full coverage of tuition fees with a maximum of 4 years&nbsp;</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Master\'s students</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Monthly stipend of 100,000 Yen</li><li>Full coverage of tuition fees with a maximum of 2 years&nbsp;</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are planning to study in Japan, these scholarships can be a great opportunity for you. Moreover, they may be selective, but as long as you remember to do your research, stay organized, and start preparing early, you\'ll be setting yourself up for success.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” Guidebook to find out all the things you need to know before applying for scholarships. It\'s FREE, <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/\">download here</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Do you want to get your hands on the Kyoto University scholarship? Let\'s prepare everything through initial consultation with ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\"><strong>Admission Mentoring</strong></a><strong>.</strong></li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\"><strong>Career Exploration.</strong></a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\"><strong>Academic Tutoring.</strong></a></li><li>Highlight your personal brand through the <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/writing-skills/\"><strong>Writing Skills</strong></a><strong> </strong>improvement program.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'GetPaidStock.com-6350e848dc943.jpg', 'Kyoto University Scholarship You Need to Check On!', 'publish', '', 'Kyoto University Scholarship', 'Are you looking for a way to get Kyoto University scholarships to help you study there? Let\'s get the full info in this article now!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-06-22 17:00:00', '2022-10-25 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(13209, 'kyoto-university-master-program-a-glimpse-of-japans-university', 1, 0, 'Kyoto University Master Program: A Glimpse of Japan’s University!', '<p>If you\'re looking for a place to study where you may experience both cutting-edge technological developments and rich cultural heritage, Kyoto University offers the best of both worlds. With a student body of 22,600, Kyoto University has produced some of the world\'s finest minds and contributed significantly to research and science. In this article, we\'ll learn more about the <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/lets-get-to-know-about-the-full-kyoto-university-info/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Kyoto University (opens in a new tab)\">Kyoto University</a> master program!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Kyoto University Master Program</h2>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Graduate School of Letters</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Since its founding, the Graduate School of Letters has been a leading academic hub for the arts and humanities. Furthermore, for education and research, the graduate school has collaborated closely with the Faculty of Integrated Human Studies, the Institute for Research in Humanities, and other divisions of the institution.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Graduate School of Law</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The Graduate School of Law has been the center of political science, law education, and research in Japan for more than a century. Currently, the school is made up of 60 professors and 13 associate professors.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Graduate School of Agriculture</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The Graduate School of Agriculture places a strong emphasis on finding solutions to the various problems that humanity faces to promote peaceful coexistence of the global community. Moreover, as master\'s graduates, your options for employment after graduation include the manufacturing industry, government service, academia, and telecommunications.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Graduate School of Pharmaceutical Sciences</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>This graduate school has a learning process that focuses on gaining professional knowledge, technical skills, and problem-solving abilities. Furthermore, this Master\'s Degree program seeks to cultivate the production of original drug discovery research in its students. Also, in terms of research, students can base their work on their specialized areas of study.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Graduate School of Science</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The Graduate School of Science has garnered six Nobel laureates and two Fields Medal winners through all the major discoveries they have made. Moreover, the school is made up of five divisions: Mathematics and Mathematical Sciences, Physics and Astronomy, Earth and Planetary Sciences, Chemistry, and Biological Sciences.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Kyoto University master program starts its academic year in April, with the exception of some schools that accept students in October.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>How to Apply to Kyoto University Master Program</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you graduated from universities outside of Japan, you\'ll need to contact the Admissions Assistance Office (AAO) for a preliminary review. This is right before submitting application documents. The AAO will later notify applicants so that they can proceed with applying to graduate programs in accordance with the results. Moreover, through the AAO process, you could connect with your prospective supervisor.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Please be aware that the AAO application process and the master\'s program application process are two independent processes. Submitting your AAO application does not mean that you have filled in the graduate school application.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are several documents that you will need to submit for the AAO process:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Photo (above shoulders, facing the camera)</li><li>Statement of Purpose</li><li>Graduation Certificate (if you have already graduated)</li><li>Academic Transcript&nbsp;</li><li>Expected Graduate Certificate or Certificate of Enrollment (if you expect to graduate)</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>The Kyoto University master program application process varies for each school in terms of the test schedule and application deadline. In some cases, preliminary screening may be required before submitting the application documents. Also, the screening consists of written and oral examinations to evaluate language proficiency and knowledge of the chosen field.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” Guidebook to find out all the things you need to know before applying for scholarships. It\'s FREE, <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/\">download here</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Planning to further your study at Kyoto University? ALL-in can help you prepare your application with our initial consult!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\"><strong>Admission Mentoring</strong></a><strong>.</strong></li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\"><strong>Career Exploration.</strong></a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\"><strong>Academic Tutoring.</strong></a></li><li>Highlight your personal brand through the <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/writing-skills/\"><strong>Writing Skills</strong></a><strong> </strong>improvement program.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'GetPaidStock.com-6350eee31358b.jpg', 'Kyoto University Master Program: A Glimpse of Japan’s University!', 'publish', '', 'Kyoto university master program', 'Are you looking for the complete info regarding Kyoto University master program? Let\'s dive deep about it in this article now!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-06-21 17:00:00', '2022-10-06 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(13214, 'kyoto-university-ranking-application-complete-facts-and-figures', 1, 0, 'Kyoto University Ranking & Application: Complete Facts and Figures!', '<p>Japan has become one of the best travel destinations for many international students. Many aspects have attracted students, such as the scenery, the education quality, and the new opportunities that you can get. Let\'s check out<a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/lets-get-to-know-about-the-full-kyoto-university-info/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\"> Kyoto University</a>\'s ranking below!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>A Glance at Kyoto University&nbsp;</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Kyoto University originally had the name Kyoto Imperial University. The university was founded on June 18, 1897. This establishment was based on the Emperor\'s rule. Furthermore, Kyoto University is the second university established in Japan. Initials at this university included the College of Science and Engineering, Law, Medicine, and Literature.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The period before and during the world war was a difficult time for the university, but it was able to survive. In March 1947, the law officially opened on this campus and provided a breath of fresh air. Over time, the university added more majors and classes. As of 2017, the campus has 10 buildings, 18 graduate schools, etc.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Kyoto University Ranking</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>As the second university in Japan, the university has gone through a lot in terms of educational development. Furthermore, it placed 36th on QS World University Rankings 2022. Also, the university has consistently placed in the top 50 best universities in the world.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are a few of Kyoto University\'s subjects, according to the QS World University Rankings by subjects, that are among the top 10 worldwide:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Chemistry - 10th</li><li>Modern Languages - 6th&nbsp;</li><li>Engineering (Mechanical) - 8th</li><li>Social Policy & Administration - 9th</li><li>Physics & Astronomy - 9th</li><li>Pharmacy - 9th</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Kyoto University Application</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Although each faculty has unique admission standards, you can see the requirements of all faculties below. Before you submit the application form, in some circumstances, a preliminary selection may occur. For more information, please contact the concerned faculty.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Candidates must have either:&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Completed or anticipate completing 12 years of schooling, or the equivalent, as determined by the Minister of Education, Culture, Sports, Science, and Technology (MEXT),&nbsp;</li><li>By the end of the year before admission, obtained a high school diploma or an International Baccalaureate or other diploma recognized by MEXT.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Selection</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Classes for overseas students other than those in English-Taught Degree Programs are typically taught in Japanese. All applicants for undergraduate, master\'s, or professional degree programs must demonstrate sufficient competency in Japanese before being admitted. There isn\'t a separate faculty at Kyoto University for the study of the Japanese language. You can enroll in a Japanese language program instead to get ready for university admission.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A six-month preparatory course is followed by four years of undergraduate education during the 4.5-year Kyoto iUP program. Since the curriculum offers intensive Japanese language training, prior knowledge of the language is not necessary. In the first two years of Kyoto international undergraduate program, students can take liberal arts classes in either English or Japanese. Moreover, the final two years of the curriculum concentrate on particular courses related to the student\'s chosen majors and are entirely or mostly taught in Japanese. Students receive a bachelor\'s degree in their chosen major upon graduation.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>There is a lot of information about Kyoto University for you to learn. There are still many things to research before you decide to apply to the university. Nevertheless, this university still holds its place as one of the best universities in Asia.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” Guidebook to find out all the things you need to know before applying for scholarships. It\'s FREE, <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/\">download here</a>. <br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dreaming to study at Kyoto University? Get your <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/\">initial consultation</a> with ALL-in mentors now!<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top uni preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'GetPaidStock.com-6350f5614cc1e.jpg', 'Kyoto University Ranking & Application: Complete Facts and Figures!', 'publish', '', 'Kyoto University Ranking', 'Have a dream of getting into Kyoto University Ranking? Get to know the full info about Kyoto University Ranking in this article!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-06-20 17:00:00', '2022-10-23 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(13218, 'lets-get-to-know-about-the-full-kyoto-university-info', 1, 0, 'Let\'s Get to Know about the Full Kyoto University Info', '<p>As the second university founded in Japan, Kyoto University has gone through many educational developments that turned it into one of the best universities in Asia. Also, it offers a lot of opportunities for every international student who studies there. Are you aiming to get into Kyoto University? Let\'s get to know some of the information about the university.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>A Glance at Kyoto University&nbsp;</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Kyoto University originally had the name Kyoto Imperial University. The university was founded on June 18, 1897. This establishment was based on the Emperor\'s rule. Furthermore, Kyoto University is the second university established in Japan. Moreover, initials at this university included the College of Science and Engineering, Law, Medicine, and Literature.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The period before and during the world war was a difficult time for the university, but it was able to survive. Moreover, in March 1947, the law officially opened on this campus and provided a breath of fresh air. Furthermore, over time, the university added more majors and classes. As of 2017, the campus has 10 buildings, 18 graduate schools, etc.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Kyoto University Ranking</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>As the second university in Japan, the university has gone through a lot in terms of educational development. Furthermore, it ranked 36th on the QS World University Rankings 2022. Moreover, the university has consistently placed in the top 50 best universities in the world.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are a few of the Kyoto University subjects, according to the QS World University Rankings by subjects, that are among the top 10 worldwide:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Chemistry - 10th</li><li>Modern Languages - 6th&nbsp;</li><li>Engineering (Mechanical) - 8th</li><li>Social Policy & Administration - 9th</li><li>Physics & Astronomy - 9th</li><li>Pharmacy - 9th</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Want to know more about the ranking and the application? Find it <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/kyoto-university-ranking-application-complete-facts-and-figures/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"here! (opens in a new tab)\">here!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Kyoto University Master Program</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Aside from its extraordinary bachelor\'s program, Kyoto University also has a great graduate school for those of you who want to pursue further education. Here are some of the 14 great graduate schools of Kyoto University:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Graduate School of Letters</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Since its founding, the Graduate School of Letters has been a leading academic hub for the arts and humanities. Furthermore, for education and research, the graduate school has collaborated closely with the Faculty of Integrated Human Studies, the Institute for Research in Humanities, and other divisions of the institution.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Graduate School of Law</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The Graduate School of Law has been at the center of political science, law education, and research in Japan for more than a century. Currently, the school is made up of 60 professors and 13 associate professors.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Graduate School of Agriculture</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The Graduate School of Agriculture places a strong emphasis on finding solutions to the various problems that humanity faces to promote the peaceful coexistence of the global community. Furthermore, as master\'s graduates, your options for employment include the manufacturing industry, government service, academia, and telecommunications.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Get the complete list of graduate schools <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/kyoto-university-master-program-a-glimpse-of-japans-university/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"here! (opens in a new tab)\">here!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Kyoto University Scholarship:</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Though there are a lot of scholarships that you can get as an Indonesian student, the Japanese government also provides international students with some amazing scholarships. One of those scholarships is:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Japanese Government (Monbukagakusho: MEXT) Scholarships</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The first Kyoto University scholarship is the Japanese Government MEXT Scholarship, which is funded by the Japanese Ministry of Education, Culture, Sports, Science, and Technology. This scholarship is available for international students who are:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Pursuing their undergraduate studies&nbsp;</li><li>Research students (graduate-degree students and non-degree students)</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>To be eligible for the Japanese Government (Monbukagakusho: MEXT) Scholarship, you must meet the following requirements:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Undergraduate Students</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>At least 17 and under 24 years of age&nbsp;</li><li>Have graduated, or expect to graduate, from a secondary school or equivalent</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Research Students</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Under 34 years of age&nbsp;</li><li>Have graduated, or expect to graduate, from an undergraduate or higher degree program</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>What does the Japanese Government (Monbukagakusho: MEXT) Scholarship cover?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Undergraduate Students</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Monthly stipend of 117,000 Yen</li><li>Full coverage of tuition fees (including examination and admission fees)</li><li>One round-trip ticket</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Research Students</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Monthly stipend of 143,000 Yen for non-degree students and 144,000 Yen for master\'s and professional degree students</li><li>Full coverage of tuition fees (including examination and admission fees)</li><li>One round-trip ticket</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>The application period for undergraduate students is April to May and late December to January for research students.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Want to know about more scholarships? Read them<a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/kyoto-university-scholarship-you-need-to-check-on/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" here! (opens in a new tab)\"> here!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>There is a lot of other information about Kyoto University that you can learn more about. But for now, this information should be sufficient to kickstart your application to top universities in Asia. All you need to do now is develop yourself and prepare any other requirements that you need to get into your dream university!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” Guidebook to find out all the things you need to know before applying for scholarships. It\'s FREE, <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/\">download here</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Need help preparing your application for Kyoto University? Grab your <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/\">initial consultation</a> with ALL-in today!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top uni preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'GetPaidStock.com-6351029a19e9e.jpg', 'Let\'s Get to Know about the Full Kyoto University Info', 'publish', '', 'Kyoto University', 'Kyoto University is one of the best university in Asia, so getting into it si going to be a huge challange. Get to know about the full facts here!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-06-19 17:00:00', '2022-10-21 17:00:00', '2022-11-02 17:00:00'),
(13231, 'penasaran-lulusan-teknik-industri-kerja-apa-simak-lengkapnya-di-sini', 8, 0, 'Penasaran Lulusan Teknik Industri Kerja Apa? Simak Lengkapnya Di Sini!', '<p>Sebagai salah satu jurusan yang paling diminati oleh banyak siswa di luar sana dan juga dengan bertambahnya peluang kerja, sudah tidak perlu pusing lagi memikirkan lulusan <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/teknik-industri-jurusan-universitas-dan-prospek-kerja-di-masa-depan/\">Teknik Industri</a> kerja apa. Prospek yang bisa kamu dapat dari jurusan yang satu ini sangatlah banyak dan beragam. Ingin tahu apa saja? Simak di bawah ini ya!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Manufacture Technician</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Teknisi manufaktur bertanggung jawab untuk memastikan standar kualitas produksi di pabrik. Mereka menggunakan pengetahuan mereka tentang peralatan dan mesin manufaktur untuk mengkalibrasi dan memanipulasinya secara manual sesuai dengan kebutuhan produksi. Mereka juga menyimpan catatan produksi dan menyelesaikan perawatan dasar peralatan sesuai kebutuhan.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Quality Assurance Inspector</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Quality assurance inspector bekerja di pabrik atau pabrik untuk memeriksa kualitas produk sebelum mereka mengirimkan produk ke gudang atau lokasi ritel. Mereka melakukan ini dengan memantau proses produksi dan memilih produk acak untuk pengujian. Mereka juga memelihara catatan jaminan kualitas untuk menentukan apakah prosedur manufaktur saat ini bekerja dengan benar.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Teknik Industri Kerja Apa? <strong>Industrial Mechanic</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Seorang mekanik industri menggunakan pengetahuan mereka tentang mesin manufaktur dan proses mekanis untuk memecahkan masalah mekanis, mengkalibrasi peralatan, dan mengganti mesin yang ada. Mereka juga menyelesaikan uji coba setelah instalasi atau perbaikan. Di dunia perindustrian, posisi yang satu ini merupakan salah satu yang paling penting untuk keberlangsungan proses produksi.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Industrial Designer</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Seorang desainer industri menciptakan desain produk sebelum tahap manufaktur. Mereka mengembangkan prototipe, menggambar cetak biru, menentukan bahan yang diperlukan dan menghitung biaya produksi relatif. Mereka juga berkoordinasi dengan profesional manufaktur untuk memutuskan waktu produksi rata-rata untuk setiap produk individu untuk memastikan kualitas sambil mempertahankan kebutuhan inventaris.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Supply Chain Analyst</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Supply chain analyst menggunakan laporan dan data pada setiap tahap rantai pasokan, termasuk dari tahap perencanaan hingga pengangkutan barang. Dari data yang mereka analisis, mereka dapat menentukan apakah standar manufaktur dan transportasi saat ini bekerja sama dengan baik. Mereka membawa temuan mereka ke pemimpin rantai pasokan di sebuah perusahaan untuk membantu mereka menentukan cara terbaik untuk memaksimalkan proses rantai pasokan mereka.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Teknik Industri Kerja Apa? <strong>Cost Estimator</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Cost Estimator bertugas berkolaborasi dengan perusahaan, operasi manufaktur dan perusahaan konstruksi untuk biaya yang diperlukan untuk membangun infrastruktur atau memproduksi produk. Mereka melakukan ini dengan berkonsultasi dengan pakar industri dan meninjau biaya relatif untuk melakukan aktivitas di area tertentu. Berdasarkan jumlah waktu, tenaga dan bahan yang dibutuhkan, penaksir biaya menyajikan gambaran realistis tentang apa yang dibutuhkan klien mereka untuk mencapai tujuan bisnis mereka.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Quality Engineer</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Insinyur kualitas bekerja untuk pabrik dan pabrik untuk memastikan kualitas produk. Mereka melakukan ini dengan membantu menetapkan prosedur produksi dan restrukturisasi sistem produksi jika perlu. Mereka mengawasi karyawan selama proses perakitan produk dan menginstruksikan mereka tentang cara menyelesaikan pemeriksaan kualitas.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Energy Efficiency Engineer</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Energy efficiency engineer melakukan audit energi dan membantu klien mereka menyesuaikan diri dengan sistem yang lebih hemat energi. Mereka biasanya berkolaborasi dengan pembangun komersial atau perumahan, pabrik dan lokasi industri untuk membantu mereka mengurangi pemborosan energi mereka. Mereka juga membantu memasang atau meningkatkan sistem energi sesuai dengan anggaran klien.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Teknik Industri Kerja Apa?<strong>Occupational Health and Safety Manager</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Posisi lulusan teknik industri ini akan menjalankan tanggung jawabnya di lokasi konstruksi, pabrik, dan lokasi industri lainnya untuk menetapkan prosedur keselamatan. Mereka menentukan faktor potensial resiko untuk lokasi industri berdasarkan mesin dan proses yang terlibat. Dari sini, mereka mengembangkan rencana untuk meminimalkan risiko kesehatan dan keselamatan. Mereka juga melakukan pelatihan keselamatan karyawan sehingga mereka memahami cara mengoperasikan peralatan dan bereaksi terhadap situasi berbahaya.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Banyak juga kan karir yang bisa kamu ambil sebagai lulusan Teknik Industri? Semua karir ini akan selalu dibutuhkan lho. Jadi, kamu tidak perlu khawatir tentant jurusan teknik industri kerja apa. Dengan semakin banyaknya pabrik manufaktur yang buka, permintaan untuk lulusan Teknik Industri pun semakin meningkat. Jika kamu ingin bersaing dengan yang terbaik, kamu juga perlu untuk lulus dari universitas terbaik di dunia.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ayo persiapkan semuanya untuk masuk ke jurusan teknik industri di universitas terbaik di dunia dengan Eduverse by ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p> <br>Download Panduan “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” untuk mencari tahu semua hal yang perlu kamu ketahui sebelum mendaftar beasiswa. GRATIS!&nbsp;<a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/id/\">Download disini</a> </p>', 'GetPaidStock.com-6351058c9fbe7.jpg', 'Penasaran Lulusan Teknik Industri Kerja Apa? Simak Lengkapnya Di Sini!', 'publish', '', 'Teknik Industri Kerja Apa', 'Apa kamu penasaran lulusan teknik industri kerja apa di masa depan nanti? Ayo simak daftar lengkapnya hanya di dalam artikel ini!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-06-06 17:00:00', '2022-09-30 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(13236, 'universitas-jurusan-teknik-industri-berikut-adalah-5-yang-terbaik-di-asia', 2, 0, 'Universitas Jurusan Teknik Industri: Berikut Adalah 5 Yang Terbaik di Asia!', '<p>Asia merupakan benua terbesar dalam industri manufaktur. Ada banyak sekali pabrik yang dibuka dan terus berkembang, maka tak heran banyak juga universitas <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/teknik-industri-jurusan-universitas-dan-prospek-kerja-di-masa-depan/\">jurusan teknik industri </a>dengan kualitas pendidikan terbaik berada di Asia. Ayo simak daftar lengkapnya di bawah ini!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>5. Huazhong University of Science and Technology, China.</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Huazhong University of Science and Technology (HUST) adalah salah satu universitas kunci milik publik yang berada langsung dibawah administrasi Kementerian Pendidikan China. Kampus ini didirikan pada 26 Mei 2000 sebagai hasil penggabungan dari Huazhong University of Science and Technology, Tongji Medical University dan Wuhan Urban Construction Institute. Walau terbilang masih cukup baru, universitas ini merupakan salah satu yang terbaik untuk menuntut pendidikan di bidang teknologi.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>4. Harbin Institute of Technology, China.</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Harbin Institute of Technology (HRBUST) adalah universitas teknik milik provinsi terbesar di Provinsi Heilongjiang, yang terletak di Kota Es Harbin — kota yang indah di timur laut Cina. Universitas ini didirikan pada awal 1950-an, dan setelah lebih dari setengah abad berkembang, HRBUST telah menjadi universitas sains dan teknik. Universitas yang sudah lama berdiri ini telah melalui berbagai macam penyempurnaan kualitas pendidikan hingga akhirnya menjadi salah satu yang terbaik di Asia.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>3. National University of Singapore, Singapore.</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>NUS, universitas unggulan Singapura, memberikan siswa pendidikan yang ketat dari profesor terbaik di bidangnya, kesempatan untuk belajar di luar negeri di 300 universitas besar di 50 negara, dan pengalaman kerja hingga satu tahun dengan startup dan bisnis terbaik yang menarik. Universitas ini menawarkan magang di Singapura dan luar negeri. Selain itu, universitas ini juga dikenal di seluruh dunia karena mempelopori model pendidikan baru di NUS seperti NUS Overseas College, University Town, University Scholars Program, dan berhasil membangun lulusan Yong Siew Toh Conservatory Duke NUS melalui kemitraan strategis. Universitas terbaik di Singapura ini memang memegang banyak peringkat terbaik di Asia, apalagi di bidang teknologi dan kesehatan.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>2. Nanyang Technological University, Singapore.</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Sebagai salah satu universitas tertua di Singapura, Nanyang Technological University merupakan salah satu universitas terbaik di Asia yang unggul dalam berbagai bidang akademik. Bidang-bidang ini meliputi sains, teknik, humaniora, dan bisnis. Ini adalah salah satu universitas yang paling disukai siswa Indonesia. Dengan tingkat penerimaan hanya 26%, Universitas Teknologi Nanyang menerima lebih dari 33.000 mahasiswa sarjana dan pascasarjana. Meskipun menerima siswa dari seluruh dunia, badan siswa sebagian besar terdiri dari siswa dari Asia.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>1. Tsinghua University, China.</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Tsinghua University adalah universitas terkenal di Beijing, China. Kampus ini didirikan pada tahun 1911 dan merupakan salah satu universitas tertua yang ada di China. Universitas memiliki 19 fakultas dan saat ini mempunyai 33,000 mahasiswa, dengan 2,600 diantaranya merupakan mahasiswa internasional. Tsinghua University merupakan bagian dari Liga C9, sebuah aliansi sembilan universitas hebat di China yang dibentuk oleh pemerintah. Untuk saat ini, universitas ini masih memegang predikat universitas terbaik di Asia.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ada banyak sekali universitas jurusan teknik industri di Asia yang bisa kamu perhitungkan. Dengan masuk ke universitas tersebut, kamu akan mendapatkan banyak sekali kesempatan dan ilmu baru untuk memulai karirmu di kancah internasional. Terlebih lagi, kamu akan sangat mudah diterima di perusahaan-perusahaan besar di seluruh dunia.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tertarik untuk masuk ke jurusan farmasi terbaik di Asia? Eduverse by ALL-in akan siap untuk membantu persiapan akademikmu!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!</p>\n\n\n\n<p><br>Download Panduan “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” untuk mencari tahu semua hal yang perlu kamu ketahui sebelum mendaftar beasiswa. GRATIS!&nbsp;<a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/id/\">Download disini</a> </p>', 'GetPaidStock.com-635108782291a.jpg', 'Universitas Jurusan Teknik Industri: Berikut Adalah 5 Yang Terbaik di Asia!', 'publish', '', 'Universitas Jurusan Teknik Industri', 'Penasaran apa saja universitas jurusan teknik industri terbaik di Asia? Ayo mari kita bersama-sama simak daftar lengkapnya di artikel ini!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-06-05 17:00:00', '2022-10-12 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00'),
(13239, 'teknik-industri-jurusan-universitas-dan-prospek-kerja-di-masa-depan', 2, 0, 'Teknik Industri: Jurusan, Universitas dan Prospek Kerja di Masa Depan', '<p>Dari berbagai macam cabang jurusan teknik, teknik industri mungkin merupakan salah satu yang paling terkenal dan paling banyak peminatnya. Hal ini karena Indonesia merupakan salah satu negara dengan industri manufaktur terbesar di Asia. Apa kamu ingin juga menyelam di jurusan teknik industri? Ayo baca dulu informasi lengkapnya di bawah ini!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Apa Itu Jurusan Teknik Industri?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Teknik industri adalah cabang dari manajemen teknik yang berkaitan dengan bagaimana memproduksi berbagai macam barang dengan cara yang lebih efektif dan efisien. Cabang ilmu yang satu ini melintasi berbagai disiplin ilmu yang terkait dengan manufaktur produk industri atau konsumen. Secara keseluruhan, teknik industri melibatkan peningkatan efisiensi, mengurangi biaya produksi, meningkatkan kontrol kualitas, memastikan kesehatan dan keselamatan karyawan, melindungi lingkungan atau mematuhi peraturan pemerintah.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Insinyur industri bekerja untuk mengurangi pemborosan waktu, uang, bahan, energi, atau komoditas lain dengan menyederhanakan prosedur dan proses. Hal ini dicapai melalui penerapan pengetahuan dan keterampilan khusus untuk menentukan, memprediksi dan mengevaluasi hasil dari proses dan sistem.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Universitas Teknik Industri Terbaik di Asia</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Jika kamu memang benar-benar tertarik untuk mendalami bidang ilmu yang satu ini, kamu harus belajar di tempat terbaik. Dimana lagi tempat yang mempunyai banyak industri manufaktur selain di Asia? Berikut adalah beberapa universitas terbaik di Asia untuk jurusan Teknik Industri:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>5. Huazhong University of Science and Technology, China.</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Huazhong University of Science and Technology (HUST) adalah salah satu universitas kunci milik publik yang berada langsung dibawah administrasi Kementerian Pendidikan China. Kampus ini didirikan pada 26 Mei 2000 sebagai hasil penggabungan dari Huazhong University of Science and Technology, Tongji Medical University dan Wuhan Urban Construction Institute. Walau terbilang masih cukup baru, universitas ini merupakan salah satu yang terbaik untuk menuntut pendidikan di bidang teknologi.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>4. Harbin Institute of Technology, China.</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Harbin Institute of Technology (HRBUST) adalah universitas teknik milik provinsi terbesar di Provinsi Heilongjiang, yang terletak di Kota Es Harbin — kota yang indah di timur laut Cina. Universitas ini didirikan pada awal 1950-an, dan setelah lebih dari setengah abad berkembang, HRBUST telah menjadi universitas sains dan teknik. Universitas yang sudah lama berdiri ini telah melalui berbagai macam penyempurnaan kualitas pendidikan hingga akhirnya menjadi salah satu yang terbaik di Asia.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>3. National University of Singapore, Singapore.</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>NUS, universitas unggulan Singapura, memberikan siswa pendidikan yang ketat dari profesor terbaik di bidangnya, kesempatan untuk belajar di luar negeri di 300 universitas besar di 50 negara, dan pengalaman kerja hingga satu tahun dengan startup dan bisnis terbaik yang menarik. Universitas ini menawarkan magang di Singapura dan luar negeri. Selain itu, universitas ini juga dikenal di seluruh dunia karena mempelopori model pendidikan baru di NUS seperti NUS Overseas College, University Town, University Scholars Program, dan berhasil membangun lulusan Yong Siew Toh Conservatory Duke NUS melalui kemitraan strategis. Universitas terbaik di Singapura ini memang memegang banyak peringkat terbaik di Asia, apalagi di bidang teknologi dan kesehatan.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Penasaran dengan universitas lainnya? Semua ada <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/universitas-jurusan-teknik-industri-berikut-adalah-5-yang-terbaik-di-asia/\">di sini!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Prospek Kerja Jurusan Teknik Industri</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Peluang kerja di masa depan untuk jurusan ini sudah tidak perlu dipertanyakan lagi. Ada banyak sekali posisi atau karir yang bisa kamu raih ketika kamu lulus dari jurusan ini. Berikut adalah beberapa contohnya:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>1. Manufacture Technician</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Teknisi manufaktur bertanggung jawab untuk memastikan standar kualitas produksi di pabrik. Mereka menggunakan pengetahuan mereka tentang peralatan dan mesin manufaktur untuk mengkalibrasi dan memanipulasinya secara manual sesuai dengan kebutuhan produksi. Mereka juga menyimpan catatan produksi dan menyelesaikan perawatan dasar peralatan sesuai kebutuhan.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>2. Quality Assurance Inspector</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Quality assurance inspector bekerja di pabrik atau pabrik untuk memeriksa kualitas produk sebelum mereka mengirimkan produk ke gudang atau lokasi ritel. Mereka melakukan ini dengan memantau proses produksi dan memilih produk acak untuk pengujian. Mereka juga memelihara catatan jaminan kualitas untuk menentukan apakah prosedur manufaktur saat ini bekerja dengan benar.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>3. Industrial Mechanic</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Seorang mekanik industri menggunakan pengetahuan mereka tentang mesin manufaktur dan proses mekanis untuk memecahkan masalah mekanis, mengkalibrasi peralatan, dan mengganti mesin yang ada. Mereka juga menyelesaikan uji coba setelah instalasi atau perbaikan. Di dunia perindustrian, posisi yang satu ini merupakan salah satu yang paling penting untuk keberlangsungan proses produksi.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>4. Industrial Designer</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Seorang desainer industri menciptakan desain produk sebelum tahap manufaktur. Mereka mengembangkan prototipe, menggambar cetak biru, menentukan bahan yang diperlukan dan menghitung biaya produksi relatif. Mereka juga berkoordinasi dengan profesional manufaktur untuk memutuskan waktu produksi rata-rata untuk setiap produk individu untuk memastikan kualitas sambil mempertahankan kebutuhan inventaris.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ingin tahu karir lainnya? Baca lebih lengkap <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/penasaran-lulusan-teknik-industri-kerja-apa-simak-lengkapnya-di-sini/\">di sini!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Teknik industri memang merupakan jurusan yang sudah pasti masa depannya. Pasalnya ada banyak sekali perusahaan besar di luar sana yang menggantungkan proses produksi mereka pada keahlian jurusan ini. Maka dari itu, jika kamu memang tertarik di jurusan ini, kamu wajib masuk ke universitas terbaik!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Punya mimpi masuk jurusan teknik industri terbaik? Ayo persiapkan dengan Eduverse by ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Download Panduan “University Preparation Guidebook: Scholarship Edition” untuk mencari tahu semua hal yang perlu kamu ketahui sebelum mendaftar beasiswa. GRATIS! <a href=\"https://scholarship-guide.all-inedu.com/id/\">Download disini</a> <br></p>', 'GetPaidStock.com-63511507e4478.jpg', 'Teknik Industri: Jurusan, Universitas dan Prospek Kerja di Masa Depan', 'publish', '', 'Teknik Industri', 'Teknik industri merupakan salah satu jurusan teknik yang paling banyak diminati pasa siswa. Ingin tahu lebih banyak? Baca di sini sekarang!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-06-03 17:00:00', '2022-10-13 17:00:00', '2022-11-06 17:00:00');
