(14760, 'top-schools-with-software-engineering-degrees-in-the-world', 7, 0, 'Top Schools with Software Engineering Degrees in the World', '<p>There are a lot of great universities scattered around the globe. However, only a handful of them placed in the top 5 in the world, especially in software engineering degrees. It is essential for students to learn a lot about the university before they apply there. Let\'s take a look at the list of schools with software engineering degrees below!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>5. University of Illinois Urbana-Champaign</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The University of Illinois, which was founded in 1867, is one of the top research universities in the US (research spending was $664 million). Moreover, Illinois has a long history of making ground-breaking discoveries that have changed the world, including the creation of the modern web browser, the discovery of the archaea, the transistor, and cutting-edge breakthroughs in photosynthesis.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Researchers from this university have pioneered agricultural systems that feed the globe, invented technologies that enable contemporary electronic devices, changed government regulations that protect the weak in our society, and made fundamental discoveries that have changed the world.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>4. Carnegie Mellon University</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Carnegie Mellon University (CMU) is a private, global research university that ranks among the world\'s most prestigious educational institutions and charts its own course. Furthermore, you can connect CMU to multiple digital brands and companies out there.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>More than 400 CMU-affiliated firms have raised more than $7 billion in follow-on funding in the last ten years. These figures are notably high due to the sheer scale of Pittsburgh\'s burgeoning autonomous vehicle cluster, which includes Uber, Aurora, and Argo AI, all of which have close ties to CMU.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>3. University of California, Berkeley</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The University of California, Berkeley (also known as UC Berkeley) is a public land-grant research university that was established in 1868 as the University of California. Known as the first campus of the University of California system, UC Berkeley is made up of more than 130 academic departments and over 100 interdisciplinary research units.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>UC Berkeley\'s campus sits on approximately 1,232 acres in the city of Berkeley, California. Its faculty includes 114 Nobel laureates, 108 MacArthur Fellows, 30 Pulitzer Prize recipients, and 19 Academy Award winners. Furthermore, the university has made significant contributions to the world of software engineering, such as with the CPU design of David Patterson.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>2. Stanford University</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>When we are talking about rank, Stanford is one of the best universities in the world, only second to MIT. Moreover, Stanford is a popular destination for international students. The campus is around 8,180 acres, among the largest in the United States, and enrolls over 17,000 students.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>It is even named the “Start-up School” because it seems like everyone there has start-up fever. Entrepreneurship has always been in Stanford\'s crimson blood, going back to the Hewlett Packard (HP Founder) days.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>1. Massachusetts Institute of Technology</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This university does not need any introduction. Everyone must already be aware that this university is the best in the world. MIT has reserved the number one spot in the QS World University Rankings for the last eight years. The software engineering major at MIT also placed first. Furthermore, aside from the great quality of education, the demand for computing-related courses is at an all-time high. At MIT, there has been a remarkable tide of interest in computer science programs, which is one of the many reasons that make this university one of the best in the world.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Software engineering is one of the most targeted degrees by many students around the world. This is due to the development of the technology field and the digital era. All of these schools require thorough preparation and the fulfillment of a list of requirements. Nevertheless, all of your efforts will be worth it because these schools provide good quality education and great opportunities.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Want to get into schools like these? Get the initial consultation with ALL-in today!<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\"><strong>Admission Mentoring</strong></a><strong>.</strong></li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\"><strong>Career Exploration.</strong></a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\"><strong>Academic Tutoring.</strong></a></li><li>Highlight your personal brand through the <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/writing-skills/\"><strong>Writing Skills</strong></a><strong> </strong>improvement program.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!</p>', 'Downloader.la-63bfbdc04c68d.jpg', 'Top Schools with Software Engineering Degrees in the World', 'publish', '', 'Schools with Software Engineering', 'There are a lot of schools with Software Engineering with provides a great quality of education. Interested? Get the full info here!', 'en', 1, '', 'false', '2022-08-01 17:00:00', '2023-01-15 17:00:00', '2023-08-30 06:24:28'),
(14938, 'lets-discover-the-full-breakdown-of-nus-application', 1, 0, 'Let’s Discover The Full Breakdown of NUS Application!', '<p>NUS is a dream university for many people. Furthermore, you will find useful information and tips to help guide you through the application process and increase your chances of getting accepted into one of Singapore\'s top universities. Moreover, we will cover everything from the application requirements and deadlines to the interview process and tips for writing a compelling personal statement. Whether you are a prospective undergraduate or graduate student, this blog is for you. Therefore, let\'s begin your journey on <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/nus-complete-application-and-scholarship-profile/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"NUS (opens in a new tab)\">NUS</a> application!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>NUS <strong>Application</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The NUS application is a special process for aspiring students. This process requires you to put all of your attention and time into it . This is because there are a lot of things that you need to do and every detail needs to be perfect. Not only do you need to make sure that every requirement is fulfilled, but you also need to keep your progress on track with the application deadline.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Below are the application deadlines for NUS application:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"\"><tbody><tr><td><strong>Qualification Type</strong></td><td><strong>AY2023 Application Closing Dates</strong></td><td><strong>Estimated Application Outcome by:</strong></td><td><strong>Appeal Window</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Indonesian Ujian Nasional (UN)<br><br>Vietnam National High School Graduation Examination<br><br>Unified Examination Certificate (UEC)</td><td>31 January 2023, Tuesday</td><td>Mid-May</td><td>May 2022</td></tr><tr><td>All other qualifications</td><td>3 March 2023, Friday</td><td>Mid-May to end July</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>After knowing the application deadline, the next step is to know the application process for international students. Furthermore, the application process is online, which means you can access your application anytime and anywhere. Let\'s take a further look at the NUS application process below:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Step 1: Online application submission</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Visit the application page and apply to the application group.</li><li>Once your application has been received, you will be given an application number and receive an email with the subject line \"Acknowledgement of Application to NUS Undergraduate Courses\", after submitting it online.</li><li>By the application deadline for your qualification, you would still be able to change your contact information, course preferences, accomplishments, and personal statement via the applicant portal.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Step 2: Paying the application fee</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Your application must be accompanied by a $20 non-refundable application fee.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Step 3: Electronic filing of the proof of purchase</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>By the application deadline, you must upload a complete set of supporting documents via the applicant portal.</li><li>Check the document status using the Applicant Portal 3 - 5 working days after electronic submission. Furthermore, if there is no update to your document status, you are required to re-upload your documents again.</li><li>All non-English supporting documents must be submitted with the english translation.</li><li>Do not submit original certificates and documents as they will not be returned.</li><li>Incomplete applications by the deadline may affect the processing of your application or its withdrawal from consideration for admission.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>NUS Application Requirements</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the most important things that you should know about the application is the requirements. An international applicant seeking admission to NUSshould have finished high school or be in the process of finishing it by July of the application year, which equates to at least twelve years of general education. Before submitting an online application, please double-check that you have chosen the appropriate qualification and applicant group type.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Application deadlines are determined by your high school diploma. Unless otherwise stated, your whole application, including all required materials, must be received by the Office of Admissions by the application deadline.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For consideration of undergraduate admission, students—including those enrolled in home studies—may submit the following test results:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>NUS Application Requirements: <strong>ACT with Writing</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>There are five sections on the ACT: the English, Math, Reading, Science, and Writing tests (Optional). The writing portion is essential for applicants who are submitting their ACT application instead of their SAT. Moreover, the minimum acceptable aggregate score for NUS consideration is 29, and the minimum acceptable score for the writing component is 8.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>All ACT components, including the writing section, must be taken in one session. Furthermore, It is not acceptable to combine section scores from various sittings. Also, ACT test results are valid for five years. The admission officers will consider test results from five years prior to the application deadline.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>NUS Application Requirements: <strong>SAT Subjects Test</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Content-based exams make up the SAT Subject Tests. There should be three topic examinations taken. The two additional subjects are up for option, but Level 2 Mathematics is required. Moreover, the three topic tests that applicants must submit are as follows:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Level 2 mathematics (required for all subjects except law);</li><li>An additional topic of your choice (excluding Mathematics Level 1)</li><li>A third subject of your choosing (other than Level 1 Mathematics).&nbsp;</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Candidates for law school admission can take any SAT Subject Test combination.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>NUS accepts the results of three SAT Subject Tests taken in two sittings over a 12-month period. Also, other score combinations or mixing are not allowed.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As you can see, the NUS application is a complicated process with complicated requirements. Moreover, many students have found difficulties in succeeding in the application process. But you do not need to do everything alone. Also, you can find help from friends, family, and mentors that will always be there for you.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Need help with your NUS application? Take your first step with an initial consultation from ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\"><strong>Admission Mentoring</strong></a><strong>.</strong></li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/programs/passion-project-mentoring/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\"><strong>Career Exploration.</strong></a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\"><strong>Academic Tutoring.</strong></a></li><li>Highlight your personal brand through the <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/writing-skills/\"><strong>Writing Skills</strong></a><strong> </strong>improvement program.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'Downloader.la-63c8d982b483c.jpg', 'Let’s Discover The Full Breakdown of NUS Application!', 'publish', '', 'NUS Application', 'Want to have a higher success on your NUS application? Check the full insight on the process exclusively only in this article!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-08-08 17:00:00', '2022-12-31 17:00:00', '2023-01-31 17:00:00'),
(14951, 'discover-the-top-five-list-of-the-best-nus-majors-in-here', 1, 0, 'Discover the Top Five List of the Best NUS Majors in Here!', '<p>If you dream of getting into the <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/nus-complete-application-and-scholarship-profile/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"National University of Singapore (NUS) (opens in a new tab)\">National University of Singapore (NUS)</a>, then information about the major is a very important insight for you. You do not just want to get into the top university, but you also want to get into the best major both in terms of its academic quality and its suitability for you. Curious? Let\'s take a look at the best NUS Majors list below!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Petroleum Engineering (#1 in the world)</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A combination of innovation, exploration, and expansion make up petroleum engineering. Every other major provides the necessary foundational skills for carrying out their work in an efficient manner. Supercomputers in petroleum engineering is not only for reservoir simulation and analysis of exploration data but also for drilling and oilfield production automation.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Petroleum engineers have the option for global assignments because many petroleum corporations have activities across the globe. In these assignments, petroleum engineers must find solutions to a wide range of technological, political, and economic issues. A petroleum engineer can have a career that is extremely fulfilling thanks to these fascinating challenges.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>NUS Majors: <strong>Civil and Structural Engineering (#3 in the world)</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Being in civil engineering immerses you in the modern built environment. Roads, bridges, buildings, airports, sewer systems, and other structures and systems that are known to all of us are designed and built with care and intelligence by civil engineers. Moreover, they are becoming more and more concerned with the how of the world around us, how people live in and use the built environment, and how we might improve it for the benefit of people and the environment.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Chemical Engineering (#3 in the world)</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Chemical engineering is a multidisciplinary field of engineering that combines natural and experimental sciences (like chemistry and physics). Also, you will learn life sciences (like biology, microbiology, and biochemistry), as well as mathematics and economics. Furthermore, chemical engineers design, develop, produce, transform, transport, operate, and manage the industrial processes that turn raw materials into valuable products.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Chemical engineering is a home for chemists who are searching for novel ways to produce goods and researching the mechanisms of chemical reactions because many of the procedures used in the discipline include chemical reactions. The designs created using this chemical information are then created by chemical engineers.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>NUS Majors: <strong>Geography (#5 in the world)</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Students majoring in geography understand how the environment and people interact and influence one another. Physical geography, human geography, as well as geographic representation and analysis are some of the fields that can help students understand this vast subject. There are many crossovers between these topics. The conventional sciences are applicable in physical geography to investigate the linked elements of the environment. Human geography looks at how people interact with the natural world as well as the motivations and strategies behind how people form societies.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Computer Science (#6 in the world)</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A computer science degree is an undergraduate or graduate level degree program that focuses on the study of computers. Moreover, the curriculum typically includes programming, algorithms, data structures, computer systems, computer architecture, software engineering, databases, artificial intelligence, and theoretical computer science. Students in a computer science program will learn how to design, develop, and analyze software and systems. These are applicable in a wide range of industries, including technology, finance, healthcare, and more.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>There are still many NUS majors which are ranked as the best in the world. These are the top 5 that you can use as your reference. From this list, you can assume that NUS is one of the best universities in the world and getting into the university is a great challenge.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Need help securing a place in NUS? Get an initial consultation with ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\"><strong>Admission Mentoring</strong></a><strong>.</strong></li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\"><strong>Career Exploration.</strong></a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\"><strong>Academic Tutoring.</strong></a></li><li>Highlight your personal brand through the <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/writing-skills/\"><strong>Writing Skills</strong></a><strong> </strong>improvement program.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!<br></p>', 'nus-qs-ranking-2023.jpg', 'Discover the Top Five List of the Best NUS Majors in Here!', 'publish', '', 'NUS Majors', 'Are you looking to find the best NUS majors for your application? Then, look no further! In this article, you will find some of the majors for you!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-08-09 17:00:00', '2023-01-08 17:00:00', '2023-01-31 17:00:00'),
(14955, 'nus-master-degree-all-insight-you-need-for-postgraduate-study', 1, 0, 'NUS Master Degree: All Insight You Need for Postgraduate Study', '<p>According to the QS World Ranking 2022, <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/nus-complete-application-and-scholarship-profile/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"NUS (opens in a new tab)\">NUS</a> is the second-best  university in Asia. This university holds a lot of quality opportunities for any international student who chooses to study there. Not only that, but this university also provides great postgraduate studies for international students. Let\'s take a look at some insights about NUS Master Degree below!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>NUS Master Degree</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>NUS Master Degree will provide you with professional and personal progress through a comprehensive and immersive learning environment. The curriculum at NUS also provides you with the information and toolkit to excel in a rapidly changing world by balancing academic rigor with an immersive approach.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You will gain an unmatched breadth and depth of knowledge about business across Asia by fusing Western business concepts with leadership principles from a distinctly Asian perspective. Moreover, through international student exchanges, study abroad programs, case competitions, internships, and other opportunities, you will continue to learn long after the class has ended.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>NUS Master Degree <strong>Requirements</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>To get into the NUS Master Degree, there are some requirements you need to fulfill to be eligible as an applicant. Furthermore, here are some admission requirements for applying to an NUS Master Degree:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Education</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>To be eligible to apply for an NUS Master Degree, you need to at least hold a bachelor\'s degree. This is a MUST.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>GMAT/GRE</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>You need to have a good GMAT/GRE score. No matter your level of job experience, full-time applicants must take the GMAT or GRE. The Executive Assessment (EA) may be taken in lieu of the GMAT or GRE by part-time applicants with at least seven years of work experience. Please be aware that Integrated Reasoning (IR) scores will also be considered if you are submitting your GMAT or EA scores. Score reports must remain valid for at least a month after being submitted.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Work Experience</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>A minimum of two years of full-time working experience–following graduation–is required for all applicants. Non-Singaporeans and Singaporean PR candidates applying for part-time programs must show proof of full-time employment or residency in Singapore that was in effect at the time of application.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>TOEFL/IELTS</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Score reports from the TOEFL or IELTS must be valid for at least a month after submission if English was not the primary language of instruction throughout undergraduate or graduate study.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>TOEFL: Minimum score of 100</li><li>IELTS: Minimum score of 7.0</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>What will you get after finishing your NUS Master Degree?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>60% of the world\'s population resides in Asia, a place that is also home to some of the most dynamic and energetic economies on the planet. Singapore is a hub for international commerce with over 4,000 multinational corporations and a thriving start-up ecosystem.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Numerous career options are available, whether you\'re trying to advance your career in a local or an international firm, a specialty or developing industry, or a start-up. In Singapore and worldwide, graduates with an NUS Master Degree are in high demand across a wide range of businesses.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>NUS Master Degree is a great opportunity for fresh graduates who want to continue their studies. This is also applicable for a professional who wants to boost their career progression. On the other hand, getting into the university can be very challenging and will require most of your time and attention. But, you do not need to do it alone. You can ask for help from your friend, family and mentor to help you get through the admission process.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Looking to secure your spot for&nbsp;a NUS Master Degree? Get an initial consultation with ALL-in now!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance prep with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\"><strong>Admission Mentoring</strong></a><strong>.</strong></li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\"><strong>Career Exploration.</strong></a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\"><strong>Academic Tutoring.</strong></a></li><li>Highlight your personal brand through the <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/writing-skills/\"><strong>Writing Skills</strong></a><strong> </strong>improvement program.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!</p>', 'Downloader.la-63c8ddf56cfa5.jpg', 'NUS Master Degree: All Insight You Need for Postgraduate Study', 'publish', '', 'NUS Master Degree', 'Have a dream to continue your education further at NUS Master Degree? Find out the complete info about the admission only in this article!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-08-07 17:00:00', '2023-01-26 17:00:00', '2023-01-31 17:00:00'),
(14964, 'cari-tahu-manfaat-kuliah-jurusan-marketing-di-sini', 8, 0, 'Cari Tahu Manfaat Kuliah Jurusan Marketing di Sini!', '<p>Kuliah <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/ayo-cari-tahu-info-lengkap-seputar-jurusan-marketing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"jurusan marketing (opens in a new tab)\">jurusan marketing</a> menyimpan banyak sekali potensi yang bisa kamu dapatkan. Jika kamu tertarik masuk ke jurusan ini, akan ada banyak sekali wawasan dan peluang kerja yang akan menunggumu. Di sini, kamu juga akan menemukan seberapa pentingnya peran bidang marketing di jurusan marketing. Ingin tahu manfaat kuliah jurusan marketing? Ayo simak lebih lengkap di bawah ini!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Banyak Perusahaan yang Memerlukan Marketing</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Sebagai perusahaan yang kompetitif, setiap bisnis perlu memasarkan produk dan layanannya secara efektif. Sebagian besar bisnis pada suatu saat membutuhkan bantuan di berbagai bidang seperti pengembangan produk, penjualan, periklanan, atau mengidentifikasi target pasar mereka.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Salah satu manfaat utama mempelajari pemasaran adalah dapat memberi kamu keterampilan berharga yang dapat diterapkan di semua jenis organisasi, termasuk perusahaan komersial, entitas nirlaba, badan amal, dan kelompok minat khusus. Selain itu, kamu juga akan mendapatkan kesempatan untuk berkarir di bidang yang terus berkembang setiap harinya. Munculnya internet sebagai alat pemasaran juga menciptakan media baru yang bisa dipakai untuk melakukan pemasaran di dunia modern.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Manfaat Kuliah Jurusan Marketing: <strong>Membangun Skill Komunikasi yang Baik</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Sebagian besar bidang pemasaran membutuhkan keterampilan komunikasi yang kuat, yang mana studi pemasaran akan membantu kamu untuk mengembangkannya. Mata kuliah penjualan dapat mengajarimu unsur-unsur presentasi persuasif, misalnya, dan mata kuliah periklanan dapat membantu mempelajari cara membuat pesan pemasaran yang efektif yang beresonansi dengan basis pelanggan.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Calon profesional riset pasar akan mempelajari dasar-dasar menyiapkan presentasi tertulis dan lisan dari temuan mereka. Jika kamu memilih untuk tidak mengejar karir di bidang pemasaran setelah menyelesaikan studi, keterampilan komunikasi ini masih dapat membantu dalam profesi lain.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Prospek Karir dan Gaji&nbsp;</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Prospek pekerjaan terlihat menguntungkan untuk posisi terkait pemasaran tertentu pada tahun 2020. Menurut Biro Statistik Tenaga Kerja di Amerika Serikat, jumlah posisi analis riset pasar diperkirakan akan tumbuh sebesar 22 persen dari tahun 2020 hingga 2030, yang jauh lebih cepat daripada rata-rata untuk semua pekerjaan. Mereka yang pindah ke manajemen pemasaran juga dapat mengharapkan penghasilan yang relatif tinggi, karena BLS melaporkan pendapatan tahunan rata-rata $154.470 per Mei 2020.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Manfaat Kuliah Jurusan Marketing: <strong>Menambah Wawasan Bisnis</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Pemasaran lebih dari sekadar produk, layanan, promosi, dan penjualan. Ini adalah area penting untuk bisnis apa pun yang membantunya mencapai tujuannya dan mendorong keuntungan. Mempelajari pemasaran akan membantu memahami mengapa pelanggan berpikir atau berperilaku dengan cara tertentu saat membeli sesuatu. Kamu juga akan memahami kebutuhan mereka, cara membujuk mereka, dan bagaimana tindakan pelanggan dapat menguntungkan bisnis.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Bidang pemasaran akan membiarkanmu dengan berbagai disiplin ilmu. Ini membantu kamu memahami prinsip-prinsip bisnis bersama dengan unsur-unsur psikologi, sosiologi, dan bahkan politik untuk memahami konsumen dengan cara yang lebih baik. Pengetahuan ini membantu para profesional mengembangkan wawasan bisnis yang penting sehingga kamu dapat menyediakan produk dan layanan yang disesuaikan dengan baik yang dapat menguntungkan mereka.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Melatih Berpikir Kritis</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Mempelajari pemasaran memungkinkan kamu untuk menjadi pemikir kritis. Kamu akan mendapatkan banyak keterampilan berkualitas dalam interpretasi data dan pemikiran tingkat tinggi yang membantu kamu mengubah analisis menjadi strategi. Mempelajari pemasaran akan membantu kamu memahami apa yang mendorong bisnis. Kamu akan menjadi pemecah masalah yang strategis dan kreatif.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Banyak sekali manfaat yang bisa kamu dapatkan ketika kamu memutuskan untuk kuliah jurusan marketing. Selain banyaknya prospek kerja yang bisa kamu dapatkan, di sini kamu juga bisa mendapatkan berbagai macam wawasan yang akan berguna untuk mengembangkan karirmu di masa depan.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tertarik kuliah jurusan marketing di luar negeri? Ayo gabung ke Eduverse by ALL-in sekarang!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!<br></p>', 'Downloader.la-63c8f0e0dc37e.jpg', 'Cari Tahu Manfaat Kuliah Jurusan Marketing di Sini!', 'publish', '', 'Kuliah Jurusan Marketing', 'Ingin tahu apa saja manfaat kuliah jurusan marketing yang bisa kamu dapatkan? Ayo simak daftar lengkapnya hanya di artikel ini!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-07-08 17:00:00', '2023-01-16 17:00:00', '2023-01-31 17:00:00'),
(14969, 'berikut-adalah-daftar-teratas-universitas-yang-ada-jurusan-marketing', 8, 0, 'Berikut adalah Daftar Teratas Universitas Yang Ada Jurusan Marketing', '<p><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/ayo-cari-tahu-info-lengkap-seputar-jurusan-marketing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Jurusan marketing (opens in a new tab)\">Jurusan marketing</a> atau pemasaran merupakan salah satu jurusan yang sedang banyak dilirik oleh siswa dari seluruh penjuru dunia. Pasalnya, bidang pemasaran merupakan salah satu aspek yang dibutuhkan oleh banyak perusahaan. Tertarik dengan jurusan ini? Ayo kita simak daftar universitas yang ada jurusan marketing di bawah ini!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>ESCP Europe Business School</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>ESCP Europe Business School didirikan di Paris pada tahun 1819 dan merupakan salah satu sekolah bisnis tertua di dunia. Dari tahun ke tahun, universitas ini secara konsisten menjadi salah satu universitas bisnis terbaik di dunia. Di Prancis, ESCP merupakan salah satu yang paling selektif di Eropa. Universitas ini termasuk dalam <em>grande école</em>, yaitu universitas yang dispesialisasi yang terpisah dari universitas publik, namun tetap paralel dengan bahan utama dari bagan utama dari sistem universitas publik.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Universitas Yang Punya Jurusan Marketing: <strong>ESADE Ramon Llull University</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>ESADE merupakan salah satu institusi internasional dengan lebih dari 50 tahun pengembangan di bidang akademik terutama dalam hal marketing. Universitas ini berisi banyak sekali orang hebat yang memupuk refleksi, dialog, proyek, dan inisiatif untuk memastikan pendidikan yang unggul, penelitian perintis, dan kontribusi berharga untuk debat dan transformasi sosial.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sebagian besar dari +60.000 alumni Esade merupakan orang penting dari lebih dari seratus negara dan memegang jabatan tingkat atas di perusahaan, administrasi publik, dan sektor nirlaba. Universitas ini mempunyai nilai pendidikan yang sangat berkualitas, dengan fokus di skala internasional, dan pendekatan holistiknya terhadap pengembangan keterampilan profesional dan pribadi.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>HEC Paris</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>HEC merupakan salah satu universitas yang menawarkan studi lanjutan S2 di bidang bisnis. Universitas ini didirikan pada tahun 1881 oleh Paris Chamber of Commerce and Industry dan merupakan salah salah satu sekolah bisnis tertua di Eropa. Saat ini, HEC Paris merupakan pemimpin di bidang penelitian dan edukasi di bidang ilmu manajemen dan marketing. Universitas ini menawarkan bisnis program yang unik dan luas untuk banyak sekali profesional yang bertalenta di bidangnya. Setiap tahunnya, ada lebih dari 4,500 siswa yang belajar di universitas ini, dengan 500 siswa di <em>summer school</em>, dan lebih dari 8,000 siswa di program eksekutif.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Di sisi lain, HEC Paris secara konsisten berada di posisi 2 di ranking universitas dengan Magister Management terbaik di dunia menurut Financial Times. Universitas ini juga merupakan universitas pertama di Prancis yang menerima <strong><em>Triple Crown Academic Accreditation</em></strong>: AMBA, EQUIS, AACSB</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Universitas Yang Punya Jurusan Marketing: <strong>Imperial College London</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Berada di peringkat ke-7 di dunia dalam QS World University Rankings® 2022, Imperial College London adalah institusi satu-satunya di Inggris, yang hanya berfokus pada sains, teknik, kedokteran, dan bisnis. Imperial menawarkan pendidikan yang dipimpin oleh penelitian, yang memaparkan para siswanya pada tantangan dunia bisnis internasional.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Salah satu elemen paling khas dari pendidikan Imperial adalah para siswa bergabung dengan komunitas peneliti kelas dunia. Dengan kecanggihan di bidang bisnis dan pengaruh di tingkat global, membuat universitas ini menjadi yang terbaik di dunia. Universitas ini merupakan kolaborasi interdisipliner tingkat tinggi yang membuat penelitian mereka sangat efektif.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Columbia University</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Terletak di lahan seluas 32 hektar di Morningside Heights, kampus utama Columbia yang bersejarah terdiri dari 71 gedung artistik. Sebagian besar kelas sarjana dan pascasarjana Columbia diadakan di sini. Columbia adalah rumah bagi badan mahasiswa yang besar dan beragam, dengan sekitar 6.398 mahasiswa sarjana dan 24.412 mahasiswa pascasarjana. Hingga saat ini, lembaga tersebut telah menghasilkan empat presiden AS, 99 peraih Nobel, dan 25 penerima Hadiah Pulitzer. Jadi, sudah tidak perlu dipertanyakan tentang kualitas pendidikan dan pengaruh yang bisa kamu dapatkan di universitas ini.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Keren-keren kan daftar universitas yang ada jurusan marketing di atas ini? Untuk masuk ke universitas di atas membutuhkan perjuangan yang panjang dan waktu persiapan yang lama. Hal ini karena banyak sekali kebutuhan yang harus kamu penuhi mulai dari dokumen hingga wawancara.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tertarik untuk masuk studi di jurusan marketing? Ayo gabung ke ALL-in sekarang!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>', 'Downloader.la-63c8f38907fa0.jpg', 'Berikut adalah Daftar Teratas Universitas Yang Ada Jurusan Marketing', 'publish', '', 'Universitas Yang Ada Jurusan Marketing', 'Dari sekian universitas di luar sana, ada yang menjadi terbaik di daftar universitas yang punya jurusan marketing. Baca di sini untuk info lebih lanjut!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-07-07 17:00:00', '2023-01-03 17:00:00', '2023-01-31 17:00:00'),
(14974, 'ayo-cari-tahu-info-lengkap-seputar-jurusan-marketing', 8, 0, 'Ayo Cari Tahu Info Lengkap seputar Jurusan Marketing!', '<p>Jurusan marketing merupakan salah satu jurusan dengan peminat yang paling banyak. Dengan selalu bertumbuhnya permintaan untuk bidang pemasaran membuat jurusan ini semakin terkenal. Banyak sekali potensi yang bisa kamu dapatkan jika kamu kuliah di jurusan marketing. Ingin tahu apa saja? Ayo simak di bawah ini!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Jurusan Marketing</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Jurusan marketing mempelajari branding dan promosi produk dan layanan kepada publik, yang ditargetkan melalui demografi tertentu. Pemasaran menyentuh banyak bidang studi, sehingga siswa akan berpengalaman dalam periklanan, komunikasi, perilaku konsumen, hubungan masyarakat, serta strategi dan penelitian pemasaran. Jurusan yang sangat berorientasi dengan karir ini memberikan pendidikan profesional dengan latar belakang yang kuat dalam seni liberal, sebagai Sarjana Seni, atau pendekatan yang lebih teknis, sebagai Sarjana Sains.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Manfaat Kuliah Jurusan Marketing</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ada beragam manfaat kuliah jurusan marketing yang bisa kamu dapatkan. Beberapa bahkan bisa membantu progres karirmu dengan lebih cepat terlepas apapun karir yang kamu pilih. Berikut adalah beberapa contoh manfaat kuliah jurusan marketing yang bisa kamu dapatkan:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Banyak Perusahaan yang Memerlukan Marketing</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Sebagai perusahaan yang kompetitif, setiap bisnis perlu memasarkan produk dan layanannya secara efektif. Sebagian besar bisnis pada suatu saat membutuhkan bantuan di berbagai bidang seperti pengembangan produk, penjualan, periklanan, atau mengidentifikasi target pasar mereka.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Membangun Skill Komunikasi yang Baik</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Sebagian besar bidang pemasaran membutuhkan keterampilan komunikasi yang kuat, yang mana studi pemasaran akan membantu kamu untuk mengembangkannya. Kursus penjualan dapat mengajarimu unsur-unsur presentasi persuasif, misalnya, dan kursus periklanan dapat membantu mempelajari cara membuat pesan pemasaran yang efektif yang beresonansi dengan basis pelanggan.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Prospek Karir dan Gaji&nbsp;</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Prospek pekerjaan terlihat menguntungkan untuk posisi terkait pemasaran tertentu pada tahun 2020. Menurut Biro Statistik Tenaga Kerja di Amerika Serikat, jumlah posisi analis riset pasar diperkirakan akan tumbuh sebesar 22 persen dari tahun 2020 hingga 2030, yang jauh lebih cepat daripada rata-rata untuk semua pekerjaan. Mereka yang pindah ke manajemen pemasaran juga dapat mengharapkan penghasilan yang relatif tinggi, karena Biro Statistik Tenaga Kerja di Amerika Serikat melaporkan pendapatan tahunan rata-rata $154.470 per Mei 2020.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/cari-tahu-manfaat-kuliah-jurusan-marketing-di-sini!/\">Klik di sini</a> untuk mengetahui manfaat kuliah jurusan marketing lainnya!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Universitas Jurusan Marketing Terbaik</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ada banyak sekali universitas yang menyediakan jurusan marketing untuk pelajar internasional. Ingin tahu apa saja? Simak daftarnya di bawah ini!</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>ESCP Europe Business School</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>ESCP Europe Business School didirikan di Paris pada tahun 1819 dan merupakan salah satu sekolah bisnis tertua di dunia. Dari tahun ke tahun, universitas ini secara konsisten menjadi salah satu universitas bisnis terbaik di dunia. Di Prancis, ESCP merupakan salah satu yang paling selektif di Eropa. Universitas ini termasuk dalam <em>grande école</em>, yaitu universitas yang dispesialisasi yang terpisah dari universitas publik, namun tetap paralel dengan bahan utama dari bagan utama dari sistem universitas publik.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>ESADE Ramon Llull University</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>ESADE merupakan salah satu institusi internasional dengan lebih dari 50 tahun pengembangan di bidang akademik terutama dalam hal marketing. Universitas ini berisi banyak sekali orang hebat yang memupuk refleksi, dialog, proyek, dan inisiatif untuk memastikan pendidikan yang unggul, penelitian perintis, dan kontribusi berharga untuk debat dan transformasi sosial.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>HEC Paris</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>HEC merupakan salah satu universitas yang menawarkan studi lanjutan S2 di bidang bisnis. Universitas ini didirikan pada tahun 1881 oleh Paris Chamber of Commerce and Industry dan merupakan salah salah satu sekolah bisnis tertua di Eropa. Saat ini, HEC Paris merupakan pemimpin di bidang penelitian dan edukasi di bidang ilmu manajemen dan marketing. Universitas ini menawarkan bisnis program yang unik dan luas untuk banyak sekali profesional yang bertalenta di bidangnya. Setiap tahunnya, ada lebih dari 4,500 siswa yang belajar di universitas ini, dengan 500 siswa di <em>summer school</em>, dan lebih dari 8,000 siswa di program eksekutif.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Cari tahu universitas yang ada jurusan marketing <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/berikut-adalah-daftar-teratas-universitas-yang-ada-jurusan-marketing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"di sini! (opens in a new tab)\">di sini!</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Banyak juga ya hal yang perlu kamu tahu sebelum mendaftar ke jurusan marketing. Beberapa hal di atas ini penting lho untuk menentukan apakah jurusan ini cocok untukmu. Di sisi lain, kamu juga harus mengetahui manfaat yang bisa kamu dapatkan dari jurusan ini selaras dengan apa yang kamu inginkan.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Punya mimpi masuk jurusan marketing? Eduverse by ALL-in akan membantumu!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dapatkan informasi tambahan tentang:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Study Abroad</li><li>Beasiswa</li><li>Eksplorasi Karir dan Jurusan</li><li>Bedah Universitas</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Yuk follow Instagram kita: @edu.verse_ dan join Telegram: t.me/Allineduverse untuk diskusi sama expert!<br></p>', 'Downloader.la-63c8f55362b48.jpg', 'Ayo Cari Tahu Info Lengkap seputar Jurusan Marketing!', 'publish', '', 'Jurusan Marketing', 'Jurusan marketing adalah salah satu jurusan yang banyak peminatnya. Apa kamu tertarik untuk masuk ke sini? Cari tahu info lebih lanjutnya di sini!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '2022-07-07 17:00:00', '2023-01-18 17:00:00', '2023-01-31 17:00:00'),
(15046, 'entrepreneurial-finance-get-the-full-complete-scoop', 9, 0, 'Entrepreneurial Finance: Get the Full Complete Scoop!', '<p>Technological advances, changing mindsets, and a growing investment landscape made it perfect for entrepreneurial ventures to thrive.&nbsp; Yet, two out of three start-ups never show a positive return. One of the most common reasons for startup failure is the inability to raise new capital. To succeed against the odds, entrepreneurs require an understanding of company ownership, valuation methods, and the different forms of investment methods. This is where entrepreneurial finance comes in.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>What is Entrepreneurial Finance?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>While corporate <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/finance-the-everlasting-field-with-great-potential/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"finance (opens in a new tab)\">finance</a> focuses on already-existing organizations and the challenges they face, entrepreneurial finance is the study of value and resource allocation. It is the process of acquiring capital and making financial decisions for a new venture or startup, and it addresses the owner\'s challenge on several financial components. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>This includes how much money the business should raise, which sources of funding are viable, and how they should arrange funding contracts and exit decisions. By doing so, the business can see whether it can become financially sustainable or not.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>When starting a company, entrepreneurs need to be flexible and fast-moving in order to acquire the finance needed for scaling operations, hiring employees, and turning their vision into a reality. This involves approaching investors and seeking loans. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are several sources of capital financing for firms, each of which uses a different valuation method and investment approach:</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>1. <strong>Venture capital&nbsp;</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Venture capital (VC) is a form of private equity commonly used to fund fast-growing start-ups and small organizations with the intention of selling their shares in the middle stage. They take on high risks and expect high returns when investing. The funds generally come from well-off investors, investment banks, and other forms of financial institutions. Moreover, venture capitalists don\'t always provide investment in the form of financial funding; it can also come in the form of managerial or technological expertise.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>2. <strong>Crowdfunding</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Crowdfunding is the use of small amounts of capital from a large number of individuals to finance a new business venture. Furthermore, it uses social media and crowdfunding websites to connect investors and entrepreneurs. Moreover, there are four main types of crowdfunding: equity crowdfunding, reward-based crowdfunding, donation-based crowdfunding, and debt-securities crowdfunding.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>3. <strong>Financial Bootstrapping</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Bootstrapping is when an entrepreneur starts and builds a company from personal finances or the operating revenues of the new company. In contrast with using venture capital, bootstrapping can be beneficial because the entrepreneur has complete control over all decisions. On the negative side, bootstrapping could expose the business owner to financial risk and might not provide enough funding for the company to grow successfully at a reasonable rate.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What financial skills does an entrepreneur need?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In order to successfully grow a business, entrepreneurs need to possess a strong financial skill set in order to persuade investors to provide funding and turn their vision into a reality. To develop these skills, they can start by taking classes or courses such as:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Financial Literacy</li><li>Financial Modeling</li><li>Sources of Funding</li><li>Company Valuation and Exit Planning</li><li>Negotiation of Terms</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Now that you\'ve gained an insight into entrepreneurial finance, are you interested in gaining an in-depth understanding of it? Knowing that the financial market is extremely fast-paced, it\'s important to continuously develop your skills and financial understanding to keep up with the latest developments.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Planning to learn more about entrepreneurial finance? Let\'s prepare yourself with ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top university preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>', 'Downloader.la-63db324368c41.jpg', 'Entrepreneurial Finance: Get the Full Complete Scoop!', 'publish', '', 'Entrepreneurial Finance', 'Enterpreneurial finance is one of the most essential factor for growing business. If you are interested, take a look at the full scoop in this article!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-08-15 17:00:00', '2023-02-14 17:00:00', '2023-02-09 17:00:00');
