(15117, 'dreaming-of-getting-into-stanford-mba-read-what-it-takes-here', 9, 0, 'Dreaming of Getting Into Stanford MBA? Read What it Takes Here!', '<p>Are you aiming to continue your studies at Stanford MBA? Then there are some things that you should know before you apply. Stanford does not take just anyone into their graduate school, so you need to know the main criteria to optimize your chances of getting an acceptance letter to Stanford MBA.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>What is Stanford MBA?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The Stanford MBA Curriculum is a two-year, full-time general management program that aids in the development of your vision and your ability to carry it out. To get an MBA from Stanford, first, you must apply to the Stanford Graduate School of Business (GSB).&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Stanford GSB is one of the best schools out there if you are aiming to be a master of business. At Stanford GSB, you\'ll be surrounded by intelligent, ambitious individuals from all over the world who want to change it.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Your cohort will challenge you in ways that would never be possible when working alone. Students at Stanford can grow, study and lead alongside one another in an atmosphere that is unmatched by any other.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>What are the Criteria for Stanford MBA?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The Stanford MBA\'s goal is to create moral, perceptive, and creative leaders. Stanford looks for students who will participate in their classes and bring positive influence both on and off campus. The Stanford application asks questions about <strong>how you think</strong>, <strong>how you lead</strong>, and <strong>how you see the world.</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>How You Think</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Your application will not only be evaluated based on your GPA and test results. While Stanford does look at these to determine how prepared you are for the academic program, they go much beyond.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Please consider the times you have taken the initiative to learn new things, to tackle difficult challenges, or to generate new insights as you finish your application. What have you found out? How did you spread your knowledge? Why is it important to you and other people? To better understand how you might contribute to the Stanford learning community both inside and outside of the classroom, they would like to hear about these experiences.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>How You Lead</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The admissions committee wants to know about your past accomplishments, specifically how you improved the organizations and communities in which you have been active in.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>At all levels and in all parts of an organization, leaders help people achieve a common objective. You do not need to occupy a specific function nor reach a certain level or title to display leadership. Stanford is looking for instances in which you have shown initiative, perseverance in the face of difficulties, involvement of others in your endeavors, and support from people around you, whether it was at your university, in a professional capacity, or perhaps during an extracurricular activity.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>How You See the World</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Your goals, identity, and values will influence your journey and broaden your classmates\' viewpoints. In your essays, you will have the chance to talk about the things that are most important to you and your goals. The admissions officers are curious about how your background has influenced both your present career and your future aspirations.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Stanford\'s collaborative teaching process makes use of the diversity of students\' backgrounds to bring a range of ideas and approaches to real-world problems. Due to this, Stanford looks to admit candidates who bring a variety of viewpoints and experiences to the MBA class. You can start to comprehend other people\'s experiences through this diversity, understand in its fullest sense, test your own presumptions, and create new ways of looking at the world.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As you have read, Stanford really aims to build a quality leader to lead the modern global business world. What about you? Can you fulfill the criteria to get into the Stanford MBA? Or do you still think you don\'t know how to ace it?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Need some help to get into Stanford MBA? Get the initial consultation here!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top university preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>', 'Downloader.la-63e4a1d95175e.jpg', 'Dreaming of Getting Into Stanford MBA? Read What it Takes Here!', 'publish', '', 'Stanford MBA', 'Aiming to continue your study at Stanford MBA? Find the best insight and', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-08-12 17:00:00', '2023-02-25 17:00:00', '2023-02-09 17:00:00'),
(15120, 'take-a-look-at-full-breakdown-of-stanford-acceptance-rate', 9, 0, 'Take a Look at Full Breakdown of Stanford Acceptance Rate', '<p>When you are aiming to get into a top university, the acceptance rate is a must-know aspect that you need to research and find out. Furthermore, you also need to make sure that you have the common characteristics of a Stanford University student. Let\'s take a look at the Stanford Acceptance Rate below!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Stanford Acceptance Rate</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>With a 4% acceptance rate, Stanford University admission is among the most selective. An SAT score between 1470 and 1570 or an ACT score between 34 and 35 is essential for admission to Stanford University. This applies for half of the candidates. Nevertheless, 25% of success applicants get scores that were above this range. On the other hand, 25% get scores that were below these levels. The Stanford University admission fee is $90, and the deadline for the application is January 2.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The GPA of a student is a highly significant academic consideration for Stanford University admissions officers. When it is available, a candidate\'s high school class rank is very important to admissions officers at Stanford University, as are letters of recommendation.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For the Class of 2025, the mid-50% SAT range was 1420-1570, while the mid-50% ACT range was 32-35. The math portion of the SAT had an astounding 83% of students scoring above 700, and the reading portion had 77% of students scoring above a 700. The average GPA was 3.96, and 96% of the graduating high school class had achieved a spot in the top 10%. Surprisingly, 96% of freshmen had a cumulative unweighted GPA of 3.75 or higher throughout their high school careers.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>How to be a Good Stanford Applicant</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you want to be a great applicant for Stanford University, there are a lot of things that you should know about the admissions process. You need to learn what elements play important roles in getting people into Stanford University.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The application essay, letters of recommendation, extracurricular activities, level of rigor in secondary school, class rank, GPA, results on standardized tests, talent/ability, and character/personal qualities are among the nine factors that Stanford cites as being \"very important\" to the admissions process. They rank seven other elements as \"considered\". Moreover, this includes: an interview, first-generation status, legacy status, place of residence, race or ethnicity, volunteer work, and previous paid employment.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>When applying to Stanford, it is crucial to have some sort of \"hook\" in your extracurricular activities. For instance, with 36 varsity sports teams, Stanford boasts the best athletic program in the nation. Furthermore, over 350 of the 900 students playing intercollegiate sports have athletic scholarships. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Your chances of being admitted increase dramatically. This applies if you are a top athlete who is being actively sought by a coach at Stanford. Especially if your academic performance is \"in range.\". If you don\'t like sports, you might be a great speaker and a future member of the Stanford Debate Society. On the other hand, you might be a talented ethnographer, dramatist, cellit, poet, scientist, robotics engineer, app designer, or community activist.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Conclusion</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>As you can see, these are some of the essential insights if you want to ace your admissions process. Knowing the Stanford University acceptance rate is important to understand your chances and how much effort and time you need to put in to get that acceptance letter from the university.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Want to get into Stanford University? Get an initial consultation with ALL-in today!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top university preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>', 'Downloader.la-63e4a6fb9d669.jpg', 'Take a Look at Full Breakdown of Stanford Acceptance Rate', 'publish', '', 'Stanford Acceptance Rate', 'Have a dream to get into Ivy League universities? Let\'s learn the Stanford University acceptance rate only in this article now!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-08-11 17:00:00', '2023-02-13 17:00:00', '2023-02-09 17:00:00'),
(15126, 'take-a-look-at-top-stanford-university-majors-here', 9, 0, 'Take a Look at Top Stanford University Majors Here!', '<p>Stanford University majors are varied and cover all of the subjects that you want. Some of these subjects are even ranked as&nbsp; some of the best in the world. Therefore, if you are looking for a great top university to get you&nbsp; into your dream job, Stanford University may be one of the best choices for you. Let\'s take a look at the list of Stanford University Majors here!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Psychology</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A skills-based degree like psychology can help you get ready for graduate programs in psychology, teaching, law, medicine, and business. Moreover, it may be tailored in many different ways and is useful for a variety of occupations. You will gain a fundamental understanding of how to reason, solve problems, and perform psychological research. Studying earlier research to draw lessons from the pioneering achievements in the discipline would help you comprehend the history of psychology.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Stanford University Majors: <strong>Biomedical Sciences</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The biomedical sciences are a group of disciplines that use elements of formal science, natural science, or both. Furthermore, these elements are used to create knowledge, treatments, or other innovations. Also, these factors will be beneficial in healthcare or public health. Medical sciences include fields such as&nbsp; biomedical engineering, clinical virology, clinical epidemiology, and genetic epidemiology. However, pathophysiology can be viewed as a fundamental science when understanding the physiological mechanisms involved in pathological diseases.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Mathematics and Statistics</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The study of quantity, structure, space, and change is known as mathematics. Despite how impersonal it may sound, math really is a search for absolutes and clear-cut solutions.. Many people are unaware that the complicated equations in math are actually pathways to simpler solutions. As a result, math is frequently appealing to those who believe in better, quicker, and more creative solutions.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Stanford University Majors: <strong>Social Sciences</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A liberal arts education, which includes the humanities, social sciences, and natural sciences, frequently involves a social science major. The social sciences are more interested in how systems have been created and how they have operated in the past and present than the natural sciences, which are more concerned with natural systems like biology or chemistry.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Computer and Information Sciences</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Since its establishment in 1965, the Stanford computer science program has maintained a reputation for academic distinction and technological innovation. Moreover, the curriculum focuses on investigating computer science-related topics, including how well you can use the theory, abstraction, design, and implementation methods that define the field to address issues in the field.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Computer science the study of computers and other computational systems. It is a vast area that covers everything from how well programmer produce and construct software to how the algorithms that make software interact with hardware. Furthermore, to investigate computer processes and create new software and systems, computer scientists use a variety of mathematical algorithms, coding techniques, and highly developed programming skills.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Stanford University has really interesting majors for you to choose from. No matter what kind of job you want in the future, this university can offer you a great opportunity to develop yourself. What you need to do is to prepare everything for admission and make sure you get the acceptance letter that you want.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Need help securing your spot at the university? Get your initial consultation with All-in today!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top university preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p></p>', 'Downloader.la-63e4a783405f7.jpg', 'Take a Look at Top Stanford University Majors Here!', 'publish', '', 'Stanford University Majors', 'Are you looking at the best Stanford University majors for you? Take a look at the full list exclusively in this article right now!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '2022-08-10 17:00:00', '2023-02-08 17:00:00', '2023-02-09 17:00:00'),
(15173, 'top-5-computer-science-corporation-for-internship!', 9, 0, 'Top 5 Computer Science Corporation for Internship!', '<p>Are you looking for a good computer science corporation for an internship? Indonesia has a fair few of these. From a start-up to a global company, there are a lot of great opportunities for you to start your internship. Let\'s take a look at the list of great companies to which you can apply for an internship!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Tokopedia</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Tokopedia is an online company that enables business owners in Indonesia to develop and manage their online businesses easily and for free, while also enabling a safer and more convenient online shopping experience. Moreover, it is one of the biggest start-up companies in Indonesia and dominates the Indonesian market. Furthermore, doing an internship in this company will give your CV a great boost that can maximize your chance to get into a top university abroad. Not only that, In 2020, HR Asia awarded Tokopedia with ‘The Best Companies to Work for in Asia 2020\'. With its great reputation both in its business and its employees, this is one of the best computer science corporations for you.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Computer Science Corporation: <strong>Traveloka</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The next top computer science corporation is Traveloka. This is an Indonesian lifestyle superapp that focuses on tickets and travel, operating from Jakarta. In 2022, Traveloka, which operates in six nations, was Southeast Asia\'s top online travel app. It was initially aims to work as a search engine for travel, but it now provides services like tickets for events and attractions, rentals for vehicles, and restaurant discounts. Additionally, it offers financial services, including insurance and credit. It was categorized as a unicorn firm in 2022 and given a US$3 billion valuation.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In 2021, Traveloka made the list of ‘The Best Workplace for Innovators\" which was released on Fast Company. Moreover, if you are a great computer science enthusiast who has a passion for creation and development, this company might be the perfect one for you.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Google Indonesia</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Who doesn\'t know Google? Google is one of the biggest companies with its main business in search engine technology, online advertising, cloud computing, computer software, quantum computing, e-commerce, artificial intelligence, and consumer electronics. Furthermore, this company is your go-to when you are looking for information on the internet. Moreover, with its main field being programming, this may be the best company out there for your internship choice!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Computer Science Corporation: <strong>Gojek</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>An Indonesian on-demand multi-service platform and digital payment firm with headquarters in Jakarta called PT Gojek Indonesia. In 2009, a contact center for connecting customers to courier delivery and two-wheeled ride-hailing services was launched as the first Gojek in Indonesia. GoRide, GoSend, GoShop, and GoFood were the first four services available when Gojek first released its app in 2015. Gojek, now valued at US$10 billion, has developed into a super app that offers more than 20 services.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Telkom Indonesia</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The international Indonesian telecommunications corporation PT Telkom Indonesia (Persero) Tbk, usually referred to as Telkom, was founded in 1997. A secondary listing for Telkom is on the New York Stock Exchange in addition to its listing on the Indonesia Stock Exchange. The Indonesian owns more than half of the outstanding shares of Telkom.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Major business segments by Telkom include fixed-line telephony, the internet, and data communications. Furthermore, the parent company of the Telkom Group engages in a wide range of sectors, including real estate, financial services, multimedia, and telephony. Moreover, telkom is the only company in Indonesia that made the list of World Best Employer by Forbes in 2021.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What do you think about the companies above? Many of them have received awards for the best workplace in which to work. You can imagine the satisfaction that the employees have, both in terms of benefits and satisfaction. Are you interested in doing internships at a computer science corporation?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Explore your passion and internship with ALL-in today!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top university preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\'s #TakeOnYourFuture with ALL-in Eduspace! Remember, #itsALLintheprep!</p>', 'Downloader.la-63ed9bb88c1bb.jpg', 'Top 5 Computer Science Corporation for Internship!', 'draft', '', 'Computer Science Corporation', 'Doing internship in computer science corporation is a good choice to improve your CV. Read here to know the top company you should apply to!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2023-02-11 17:00:00', '2023-02-15 17:00:00'),
(15183, 'computer-science-master’s-program:-launch-your-career-in-it', 9, 0, 'Computer Science Master’s Program: Launch Your Career in IT', '<p>Are you considering advancing your career or upgrading your skills in computer science? Well, pursuing a computer science master degree might be the way to go! Furthermore, according to PayScale, the average annual income for master\'s degree holders in computer science in the US is $101,000. Moreover, the median annual household income in the US is $56,516. Also, to give you better context, let\'s have an overview on what a master\'s degree in computer science is and the job opportunities it offers. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>A Master\'s in Computer Science</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A master\'s degree in computer science usually requires you to complete 30 to 45 credits, with full-time students finishing it in around two years and part-time students often taking three to four years. Furthermore, most programs require core, electives, and project or thesis credits. While pursuing a computer science master\'s degree, you will learn advanced concepts in computer science, including: </p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Computer language theory</li><li>Cloud computing</li><li>Machine learning&nbsp;</li><li>Modeling and simulation</li><li>Advanced algorithms</li><li>Software development and engineering</li><li>Computer architecture</li><li>Operating system principle</li><li>Internet of things (IoT)</li><li>Database management</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>When pursuing a computer science master\'s degree, you will get to specialize in areas such as artificial intelligence, data analytics, ethical hacking, and network protocols. If you want to specialize in a subdiscipline of computer science, you can also earn stand-alone master\'s degrees in subjects like cybersecurity and software engineering. Moreover, by earning a master\'s in a subdiscipline of the field, you will be prepared for more specialized career paths.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Most computer science master\'s programs offer a master of science (MS) in computer science. However, some schools may offer other types of master\'s degrees in this field, such as a master of business administration (MBA) in computer science. Furthermore, MBA in computer science focuses on business skills and theory with a computer science emphasis. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Job Opportunities </h2>\n\n\n\n<p>For computer and information research scientists, the Bureau of Labor Statistics (BLS) predicts a job growth rate of 22% between 2020 and 2030. Moreover, after earning a master\'s in computer science, you can pursue various careers in technology. Some of these job titles include: </p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Information security analyst</li><li>Artificial intelligence specialist</li><li>Computer and information research scientist</li><li>Network and computer systems administrator</li><li>Computer systems analyst</li><li>Cybersecurity manager</li><li>Database administrator</li><li>Software developer</li><li>Network architect</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Requirements for a Computer Science Master\'s degree</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Every master\'s program has unique admission requirements, which differ per university. However, there are a few common requirements for most computer science programs you need to know. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>For one, almost all computer science programs require applicants to have a bachelor\'s degree in computer science or a related field. Moreover, this applies to programs like like mathematics, statistics, programming, or computer engineering. Of course, not having a computer science background does not disqualify you from applying. Furthermore, you may take additional prerequisite courses in computer science to strengthen your application. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>While some programs recommend it, it is not necessarily required to have job experience in the field of computer science. A letter of recommendation may also be required.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you\'re already working in the field of computer science, getting a computer science master\'s degree can help you in furthering your career or setting yourself apart for senior-level positions. If you\'re switching from another field to computer science, this degree will boost your confidence and get your foot in the new industry. Endless opportunities await you!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Planning to pursue a computer science master\'s degree? Prepare yourself through an initial consultation with ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/admissions-mentoring/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top university preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>. </li></ol>', 'Downloader.la-63edb4dd8f133.jpg', 'Computer Science Master’s Program: Launch Your Career in IT', 'draft', '', 'Computer Science Master', 'Computer science master degree can elevate your future career in IT field. Are you interested to apply? Get the complete info onliy in this article!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2023-02-01 17:00:00', '2023-02-15 17:00:00'),
(15190, 'best-universities-for-computer-science:-the-best-list!', 9, 0, 'Best Universities For Computer Science: The Best List!', '<p>According to the US Bureau of Labor Statistics, professionals in the field of computer science earn a median salary of $131,490. On top of that, a 15% growth rate in this field is expected between 2021 and 2031. So, wondering how to get one foot in the door? First let\'s start with knowing the best universities for computer science!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>A degree in computer science</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Computer science is a broad field that encompasses different types of computing systems, networks, and cybersecurity. Furthermore, professionals in computer science often hold positions as web developers, database administrators, software developers, computer systems analysts, network architects, and hardware engineers. Moreover, their day-to-day tasks include seeking solutions to problems, creating improvements to processes, and making forecasts for future developments.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>At the bachelor\'s level, a computer science degree typically takes four years to complete, with most programs requiring you to complete 120 to 128 credits. Moreover, it usually includes core coursework in computer architecture and programming, data science, algorithms, information security, and logic and computation. However, each bachelor\'s program can differ significantly in focus and specializations. Students often get to specialize in areas such as artificial intelligence, data communications, software testing, real-time computing, operating systems, and computer networking.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In general, computer science degree programs emphasize the mathematical and theoretical foundations of computing.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Best universities for computer science</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>According to the 2022 QS World University Rankings by Subject, here are the best universities for computer science:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>1. <strong>Massachusetts Institute of Technology (MIT)</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Established in 1861, Massachusetts Institute of Technology (MIT) is a private research university based in the city of Cambridge, Massachusetts. Furthermore, MIT is made up of five schools: architecture and planning, engineering, humanities, arts and social sciences, management and science. Moreover, MIT\'s Department of Electrical Engineering and Computer Science (EECS) offers several computer science programs that leads to the Bachelor of Science, including:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Minor in Computer Science</li><li>Electrical Science and Engineering&nbsp;</li><li>Electrical Engineering and Computer Science&nbsp;</li><li>Computer Science and Engineering&nbsp;</li><li>Artificial Intelligence and Decision Making&nbsp;</li><li>Computer Science and Molecular Biology&nbsp;</li><li>Computation and Cognition&nbsp;</li><li>Computer Science, Economics, and Data Science&nbsp;</li><li>Urban Science and Planning with Computer Science&nbsp;</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h3>2. <strong>Stanford University</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Since its founding in 1885, Stanford University has gone on to be one of the most prestigious universities in the world. Furthermore, spanning across 8,180 acres of land, there are three academic schools and four professional schools in Stanford. The undergraduate major in Computer Science at Stanford University is offered by the Department of Computer Science, which includes courses such as Mathematical Foundations of Computing, Operating Systems and Systems Programming, and Design and Analysis of Algorithms. Moreover, notable alumni of Stanford\'s Department of Computer Science include Larry Page (co-founder of Google) and Reed Hastings (Netflix founder).&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>3. <strong>Carnegie Mellon University</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Located in Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania, Carnegie Mellon University (CMU) is a private research university established in 1900 by the famous industrialist Andrew Carnegie. Moreover, the Carnegie Mellon School of Computer Science (SCS) offers computer science programs that can mix with courses in the arts, music and technology, computational biology, and artificial intelligence.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In the 2018 admissions cycle, over 8,500 students applied for undergraduate admission to SCS, with only 435 being accepted.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With some of the best universities for computer science listed above, have you decided which one you\'ll apply to? Furthermore, if you\'re looking for a place where you can work on your goals and make them happen, don\'t forget to choose a school that best fits your needs and wants. After all, it\'s only you who can be in charge of your study!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dreaming of getting into the best universities for computer science? Prepare yourself through an initial consultation with ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What we can do for you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maximize your university entrance preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/programs/admissions-mentoring-page/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Explore your interests and dive into different industries through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/passionxplorer/\">Career Exploration.</a></li><li>Improve your grades and knowledge through <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring.</a></li><li>Sharpen your top university preparation with <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/program/academic-test-preparation/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>', 'Downloader.la-63edcad24fb3c.jpg', 'Best Universities For Computer Science: The Best List!', 'draft', '', 'Best Universities For Computer Science', 'Looking for the best universities for computer science? Let\'s take a look at the best list and the full detail only in this article!', 'en', 0, '', 'false', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2023-02-04 17:00:00', '2023-02-15 17:00:00'),
(15197, 'simak-syarat-masuk-jurusan-akuntansi-di-universitas-top-dunia!', 12, 0, 'Simak Syarat Masuk Jurusan Akuntansi di Universitas Top Dunia!', '<p>Kamu mungkin sudah sering mendengar mengenai jurusan akuntansi. Entah itu keluargamu atau temanmu pasti pernah terbesit untuk masuk ke jurusan akuntansi. Jurusan yang satu ini memang banyak sekali peminatnya di seluruh dunia. Bukan karena mata kuliahnya yang menarik, namun juga karena prospek kerja di masa depannya. Tertarik? Simak beberapa syarat masuk jurusan akuntansi di bawah ini!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Mampu Menguasai Penghitungan</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Di jurusan ini kamu sangat akan bergelut dengan yang namanya matematika dan perhitungan. Mungkin kamu akan menemuinya setiap hari selama kamu kuliah. Sudah tidak dipungkiri lagi kalau perhitungan merupakan nyawa dari jurusan akuntansi. Maka dari itu, jika kamu memang benar-benar tertarik untuk masuk ke jurusan ini, kamu wajib menyukai hitung-hitungan dan menguasai matematika.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Terlebih lagi ketika hari kamu berhitung dan bergulat dengan matematika tidak berhenti ketika kamu sudah lulus. Di pekerjaanmu nanti, kamu juga akan mengerjakan perhitungan keuangan perusahaan yang bisa mencapai milyaran lho.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Jujur</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Tidak hanya di jurusan akuntansi, kamu sebagai manusia memang sudah selayaknya memiliki sifat jujur. Terlebih lagi jika kamu mengambil jurusan ini. Disini kamu akan menggeluti di sektor keuangan sebuah perusahaan. Jika kamu sudah bekerja nanti, akan besar kemungkinan kamu untuk bisa melakukan kecurangan terhadap keuangan perusahaan tersebut. Maka dari itu, kejujuran merupakan hal yang penting ketika kamu ingin belajar di jurusan akuntansi.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Punya Sikap Teliti Dan Akurat</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Sikap yang satu ini juga merupakan salah satu yang paling penting untuk masuk ke jurusan akuntansi. Pasalnya, di jurusan ini kamu akan menemukan banyak sekali angka yang mungkin akan membuatmu pusing. Mempunyai sikap teliti dan akurat dan membantumu menjalankan kuliah dengan lebih baik. Hal ini dapat membantumu menghindari kesalahan-kesalahan kecil namun fatal yang mungkin akan kamu temukan di masa kuliahmu atau saat kamu sudah bekerja nanti.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Bisa Berpikir Objektif Dan Logis</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Berpikir objektif merupakan hal yang penting dalam menilai apapun. Sikap seperti sangat penting ketika kamu memutuskan untuk kuliah di jurusan akuntansi bahkan jika kamu meneruskan untuk bekerja sebagai akuntan. Di sini kamu mungkin akan menemukan beberapa angka yang salah perhitungan dan mungkin ada kecurangan saat kamu bekerja nanti. Kamu harus bisa memastikan semua keuangan perusahaan tersebut masuk akal dan selaras dengan data yang kamu punya. Kamu juga harus berani bersikap skeptis pada laporan keuangan yang tidak disajikan dengan benar.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Ulet dan Sabar</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Di jurusan ini, kamu mungkin akan memasukan banyak sekali laporan keuangan satu per satu ke buku besar. Maka dari itu, selain ketelitian dibutuhkan banyak kesabaran untuk mampu kuliah di jurusan akuntansi. Ketika kamu bekerja nanti, kamu mungkin akan mengurus lebih dari satu perusahaan yang membutuhkan laporan keuangan yang detail.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Keterampilan Komputer</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Walaupun pelajaran akuntansi yang kamu pelajari selama masa sekolah dilakukan di atas kertas, namun di masa kuliah, semua perhitungan keuangan akan kamu lakukan dengan komputer. Kamu akan berkutat dengan banyak program komputer, khususnya Microsoft Excel dan Myob Accounting yang menjadi media utama mengerjakan siklus Akuntansi dengan kemajuan teknologi.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Beberapa hal di atas merupakan beberapa sikap dan keterampilan yang menjadi syarat masuk jurusan akuntansi. Jika menurutmu kamu belum memiliki beberapa hal di atas, kamu bisa mulai mengembangkan dirimu sejak di bangku sekolah agar bisa lebih mempersiapkanmu masuk ke jurusan akuntansi di universitas top dunia!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ayo sukseskan masuk ke jurusan akuntansi di universitas top dunia bersama EDUVERSE by ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Berikut bantuan yang kami sediakan:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maksimalkan Persiapan Pendaftaran Universitas dengan <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/programs/admissions-mentoring-page/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Cari Mintamu dan Terjun Langsung ke Industri Tersebut melalui <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/programs/passion-project-mentoring-id/\">Career Exploration</a>.</li><li>Tingkatkan Nilai dan Pengetahuanmu dengan <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/programs/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring</a>.</li><li>Pertajam Persiapan Masuk Universitas melalui <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/programs/academic-test-preparation/sat-program/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>', 'Downloader.la-63edd70898d7f.jpg', 'Simak Syarat Masuk Jurusan Akuntansi di Universitas Top Dunia!', 'draft', '', 'Syarat Masuk Jurusan Akuntansi', 'Ingin tahu info lengkap mengenai syarat masuk jurusan akuntansi? Baca seluruh info lengkapnya untuk persiapa universitasmu hanya di sini!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2023-01-31 17:00:00', '2023-02-15 17:00:00'),
(15202, 'ayo-simak-daftar-mata-kuliah-jurusan-akuntansi-di-sini!', 12, 0, 'Ayo Simak Daftar Mata Kuliah Jurusan Akuntansi di Sini!', '<p>Mata kuliah jurusan akuntansi memang sangat menarik bagi para pelajar yang tertarik dengan bidang ini. Di sisi lain, semua mata kuliah ini sangat penting dan bisa diaplikasikan di karir di masa depan. Apa kamu sudah tahu apa saja mata kuliah yang akan diajarkan nanti? Ayo cari tahu di bawah ini!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>1. Pengantar Akuntansi</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Pengantar Akuntansi merupakan mata kuliah yang memberikan gambaran tentang proses akuntansi atau siklus akuntansi dalam suatu periode akuntansi untuk perusahaan jasa dan niaga. Mata kuliah ini merupakan bahan awal untuk pembelajaran akuntansi. Pembahasan yang disajikan meliputi pengenalan konsep dan persamaan akuntansi dasar, pengenalan sistem akuntansi, analisis dan pencatatan transaksi, serta penyusunan siklus akuntansi.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>2. Akuntansi Sektor Publik</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Kursus akuntan publik mencakup akuntansi, manajemen, audit, perpajakan, ekonomi makro dan ekonomi mikro. Sebagian besar kursus berfokus pada materi yang berkaitan dengan sektor publik. Misalnya, mata kuliah tentang Keuangan Negara dan Daerah, Akuntansi Kota, dan Pajak dan Bea Daerah.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>3. Akuntansi Biaya</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Akuntansi biaya adalah cabang akuntansi atau mata kuliah yang berfokus pada mempelajari cara atau metode pencatatan, pengukuran dan pelaporan informasi biaya yang digunakan selama proses produksi. Di sini kamu akan mempelajari dengan mendalam mengenai aktivitas keuangan sebuah perusahaan saat sedang produksi.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>4. Akuntansi Anggaran</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Akuntansi anggaran adalah bidang akuntansi yang berkaitan dengan perencanaan pengeluaran perusahaan, yang kemudian dibandingkan dengan pengeluaran riil (aktual). Keuntungan dari manajemen adalah kontrol administratif. Dengan akuntansi anggaran, informasi yang diperlukan untuk operasi organisasi dan alokasi sumber daya dapat diperoleh secara akurat, efisien dan ekonomis.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>5. Akuntansi Pemerintah</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Mata kuliah akuntansi pemerintah mempelajari mengenai proses mengidentifikasi, mengukur, mencatat, dan melaporkan peristiwa ekonomi (keuangan) entitas publik, untuk digunakan sebagai informasi ketika membuat keputusan keuangan oleh entitas pemerintah eksternal yang membutuhkannya. Akuntansi pemerintah akan dilakukan untuk mengisi berkas laporan pertanggungjawaban keuangan negara, yang diatur dalam Pasal 23 (5) UUD 1945, dimana negara wajib mengajukan laporan dalam setiap penyelenggaraan keuangan.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>6. Sistem Informasi Akuntansi</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Mata kuliah yang satu ini memperkenalkan dasar-dasar akuntansi dan pemrograman yang dibutuhkan analis sistem untuk merencanakan, mengembangkan, dan menerapkan sistem informasi akuntansi di perusahaan. Sistem informasi akuntansi biasanya terdiri dari enam komponen utama: Orang, prosedur dan kebijakan, informasi, perangkat lunak, infrastruktur TI, dan kontrol internal.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>7. Perpajakan</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Dalam kursus pajak, kamu akan belajar tentang pajak dari perspektif bisnis dan akuntansi, serta dari perspektif hukum. Kamu juga akan mengembangkan keterampilan dalam menyiapkan laporan pajak sesuai dengan aturan dan peraturan perpajakan, mempelajari cara menyelesaikan masalah administrasi perpajakan, dan menyiapkan laporan keuangan sesuai dengan norma hukum yang berlaku. Kursus ini juga membahas undang-undang perpajakan yang mengikat wajib pajak baik individu maupun badan untuk pajak pusat dan daerah. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Selain Pajak penghasilan, ada juga pajak pertambahan nilai, pajak properti, pajak meterai, pajak mobil, pajak akomodasi, pajak restoran, pajak hiburan, dll. Kamu juga akan belajar tentang administrasi pajak, pemantauan dan audit pajak, dan potensi pajak.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>8. Pengauditan</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Kursus ini mencakup instruksi tentang bagaimana melakukan audit / pemeriksaan estimasi laporan keuangan sampai dengan penyusunan laporan audit. Manfaat audit tidak hanya pelaporan keuangan yang lebih akurat, tetapi juga dapat membantu mengungkap kecurangan atau tindakan yang dapat merugikan keuangan perusahaan.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sangat banyak ya mata kuliah jurusan akuntansi yang akan kamu temui. Walaupun kelihatannya sangat rumit, tapi kamu akan mendapatkan cukup waktu untuk mempelajari semuanya. Selain ilmu yang bermanfaat, kamu akan mendapatkan banyak keterampilan yang bisa kamu gunakan untuk memaksimalkan karirmu di masa depan.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ingin masuk ke jurusan akuntansi? Persiapkan semuanya dengan EDUVERSE by ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Berikut bantuan yang kami sediakan:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maksimalkan Persiapan Pendaftaran Universitas dengan <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/programs/admissions-mentoring-page/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Cari Mintamu dan Terjun Langsung ke Industri Tersebut melalui <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/programs/passion-project-mentoring-id/\">Career Exploration</a>.</li><li>Tingkatkan Nilai dan Pengetahuanmu dengan <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/programs/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring</a>.</li><li>Pertajam Persiapan Masuk Universitas melalui <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/programs/academic-test-preparation/sat-program/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>', 'Downloader.la-63edd8202f29f.jpg', 'Ayo Simak Daftar Mata Kuliah Jurusan Akuntansi di Sini!', 'draft', '', 'Mata Kuliah Jurusan Akuntansi', 'Apa kamu ingin tahu apa saja daftar mata kuliah jurusan akuntansi yang akan kamu temui di kuliahmu nanti? Simak lengkapnya di sini!', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2023-02-15 17:00:00', '2023-02-15 17:00:00'),
(15206, 'penasaran-jurusan-akuntansi-belajar-apa?-simak-di-sini!', 12, 0, 'Penasaran Jurusan Akuntansi Belajar Apa? Simak di sini!', '<p>Apa kamu masih ragu untuk melanjutkan kuliah di jurusan akuntansi? Secara garis besar, jurusan akuntansi mempelajari segala hal mengenai keuangan. Entah itu yang dimiliki oleh perusahaan besar maupun UMKM. Tapi, di dalam kuliahnya sendiri jurusan akuntansi mempelajari banyak hal lainnya. Ingin tahu jurusan akuntansi belajar apa saja? Ayo kita cari tahu lebih lanjut!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Jurusan Akuntansi Belajar Apa?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Akuntansi sering dianggap sebagai salah satu jurusan perguruan tinggi paling intens yang pernah ada. Kamu akan diminta untuk mengambil kursus yang sangat ketat di sejumlah mata pelajaran yang berbeda. Selain itu, kursus inti yang diperlukan dalam akuntansi bisa jadi menakutkan dan membutuhkan banyak pembelajaran dan persiapan. Kamu diharuskan mengambil mata kuliah Matematika, Ekonomi, Bisnis, dan tentu saja mata kuliah akuntansi.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Semua mahasiswa akuntansi diharuskan mengambil mata kuliah Aljabar dan Statistik dalam dua tahun pertama studi mereka. Mata kuliah matematika ini biasanya mencakup Aljabar Perguruan Tinggi, Statistik Dasar, dan Statistik Bisnis. Saat kamu sedang mendalami jurusan, kamu akan menemukan banyak kelas matematika baru. Berharap untuk mengambil kursus pengantar Kalkulus di awal studi kamu, serta Kalkulus 1 dan 2 nanti.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Bagaimana Jika Kamu Kuliah di Luar Negeri?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Siswa internasional memiliki kesempatan untuk mengambil beberapa mata kuliah ilmu sosial, tetapi satu-satunya mata kuliah ilmu sosial yang diperlukan adalah Ekonomi I dan Ekonomi 2, yang biasanya diambil secara berurutan. Kursus Ekonomi 1 membahas ekonomi mikro, atau masalah dan teori ekonomi yang lebih kecil, sedangkan Ekonomi 2 berfokus pada ekonomi makro, atau ekonomi dalam skala global atau lebih besar. Jika kamu tertarik dengan mata kuliah ekonomi masa depan atau ilmu sosial yang berbeda, kamu memiliki kesempatan untuk mengambil mata kuliah apapun sebagai mata kuliah pilihan.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kelas bisnis biasanya dimulai dengan kursus akuntansi pengantar seperti akuntansi keuangan dan manajerial. Sebagian besar universitas juga mensyaratkan beberapa mata kuliah hukum bisnis. Apa yang harus kamu harapkan ketika mempelajari akuntansi adalah mengambil kursus pengantar di beberapa disiplin bisnis yang berbeda seperti: administrasi bisnis, keuangan, dan pemasaran. Kelas bisnis lainnya mungkin termasuk kepemimpinan atau kelas perilaku organisasi atau Kebijakan Bisnis.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Yang terpenting dalam kurikulum adalah mata kuliah inti. Kursus inti ini adalah tulang punggung dari program akuntansi dan dimaksudkan untuk membekali kamu dengan keterampilan yang diperlukan untuk mencari pekerjaan setelah lulus. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kamu akan menemui mata kuliah akuntansi dalam akuntansi seperti akuntansi biaya, akuntansi anggaran, perpajakan, hingga pengauditan. Kamu juga dapat memilih antara konsentrasi yang berbeda seperti akuntansi internasional atau sistem bisnis. Beberapa universitas juga menawarkan kursus dalam mata pelajaran tertentu seperti analisis laporan keuangan, akuntansi forensik, dan penelitian akuntansi. kamu akan menemukan kursus ini di beberapa sekolah terbaik di bidang akuntansi.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Kesimpulan</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Sudah cukup jelas kan jurusan akuntansi belajar apa? Di sini kamu akan menemukan banyak ilmu yang lebih mendalam mengenai keuangan. Semua ilmu yang kamu dapatkan bisa kamu aplikasikan dengan baik di pekerjaanmu nantinya entah kamu bekerja sebagai akuntan, konsultan keuangan, ataupun bekerja di sektor publik.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ingin masuk ke jurusan akuntansi? Ayo sukseskan dengan EDUVERSE by ALL-in!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Berikut bantuan yang kami sediakan:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Maksimalkan Persiapan Pendaftaran Universitas dengan <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/programs/admissions-mentoring-page/\">Admission Mentoring</a>.</li><li>Cari Mintamu dan Terjun Langsung ke Industri Tersebut melalui <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/programs/passion-project-mentoring-id/\">Career Exploration</a>.</li><li>Tingkatkan Nilai dan Pengetahuanmu dengan <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/programs/academic-test-preparation/\">Academic Tutoring</a>.</li><li>Pertajam Persiapan Masuk Universitas melalui <a href=\"https://all-inedu.com/id/programs/academic-test-preparation/sat-program/\">SAT/ACT Prep Class</a>.</li></ol>', 'Downloader.la-63edd92f4a791.jpg', 'Penasaran Jurusan Akuntansi Belajar Apa? Simak di sini!', 'draft', '', 'Jurusan Akuntansi Belajar Apa', 'Apa kamu ingin tahu di jurusan akuntansi belajar apa', 'id', 0, '', 'false', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2023-02-06 17:00:00', '2023-02-15 17:00:00'),
